Slowly away, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, no daylight early in straight, cleared 200M, finished off strongly to score.

Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, no clear run early in straight, cleared 125M, hit the front 75M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner late.
Away well, raced prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, kept on well in straight to take a place.
Jumped with them, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 100M, headed 75M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the inside, found rail near 800M, 4 lengths or so back turning in, no clear run early in straight, made minor progress inside final furlong.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced in midfield on the outside, there to turn, made little progress in straight.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover towards rear, very wide into straight, made minor progress in the run home.
Moderately away, positioned 2 wide better than midfield, 3 wide from 500M, made minor progress early in straight, peaked on run 150M, weakened gradually final 50M.
Began only fairly, positioned 2 wide, 4 lengths back, same margin back on turn, no clear running early in straight, bumped 200M, blocked again 150M, one-paced thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths back, similar position on turn, no clear run early in straight, bumped 200M, blocked and snatched up 150M, one-paced thereafter.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced better than midfield on the outside, moved closer after passing 950M, no cover throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened final 250M.
Blundered at the start and became unbalanced, raced in midfield on the inside, 2 wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened and eased final 250M.
Led early from a wide draw, taken 1L back 2-wide before becoming 3rd 1100 metres out, shifted 3-wide entering home straight, hit the front under pressure 200 metres out, just held on.
Ridden forward to midfield on the rail after moderate start, obtained a clear run over 150 metres out, ran on well to just fail to get up on line.
Soon improved to 4th over 2L back on the rail, saved ground turning in but baulked for a run until the 300 metres, finished off the race well though never threatening the winner.
Taken back to last from a wide draw, saved ground rounding home bend, fought on well under pressure despite tight run 150 metres out.

Pressed forward from a wide draw, travelled wide without cover before going forward for 2nd just outside race leader 1000 metres out, held every chance early in straight but unable to sustain effort final 100 metres.
Improved steadily to lead after first 200 metres, led until narrowly headed early in home straight, faded under pressure closing stages.
Well there early settling just over 3L off the pace in 5th, kept on same pace closing stages.
Settled just worse than midfield on the rail, did not find much room early in straight, finished off the race strongly. (Mucus)
Settled just worse than midfield, 3-wide rounding home bend going wider into straight, kept on well.
Settled well behind, shifted to the widest turning for home, kept on steadily down the centre of home straight.
Soon taken back from a wide draw, never seen with a chance.
Taken back to last few from a wide gate racing wide throughout, made no show in straight.
Improving to within 3L of pace early stages before drifting backward 1400 metres out, became midfield coming onto home bend, folded up quickly inside final 200 metres.
Settled wide in midfield after moderate start, went wider entering straight, soon weakened.
Broke well and ridden along to lead, kicked clear at the top of the straight, kept on well and held on.
Had the box-seat run, angled out at 350M, ran on well for 2nd (Lame left front leg)
At the rear 2 wide, stayed on well for 3rd .
Settled last on the rail, closed off okay, just a bit one pace near the line.
Tracked leader, kept on fairly.
Settled behind midfield 2 wide, limited response.
Sat midfield 2 wide, looks a threat in the early part of the straight, but didn't run on, weakened inside 200M. (See Incident Report) (Substantial Mucus in Trachea) (Roarer)
Caught 3 wide no cover throughout, weakened and faded at 500M.

Ridden forward from outside gate & showed good speed to come across to lead. Held 1.5L advantage on straightening, continued to hold similar advantage all the way to the line to win with something in hand.

Raced in midfield along rail early before moving off the rail passing the 900m. Eased wider again on straightening when about 4.5L from the lead before making good headway down the outside to move to second near the 100m.

Raced just worse than midfield along the rail early before improving to midfield around the bend. Entered last section just under 4L from the lead & finished off well all the way to the line to finish third.

Pushed forward before racing second, about a length from the lead for the majority. Was ridden along just before straightening before battling on well all the way to line but being caught for a first three finish in final 75m.

Had a good position in midfield along the rail. Was slightly keen near the 800m when close to heels. Shifted outwards after the 600m, was just under 4L from the lead entering last section & maintained that margin to the line.

Was steadied after the start before shifting across to race just worse than midfield away from the rail. Shifted outwards on straightening when just under 6L behind before making up some late ground when running onto 6th late.

Was slow to begin & then cut across behind runners to race at the tail. Stayed close to the rail on straightening when still last & over 8L from the lead before passing a few tiring rivals late without ever looking a chance
Was slow to begin & raced forth last along the rail. Entered last section 7L from the lead, made up a few lengths but was still beaten just under 5L on line. Never likely.

Began fast & raced third along the rail in early & middles stages. Moved away from the rail passing the 550m, entered last section in third position, only about 2L from the lead before weakening out in last furlong.

Veered outwards sharply on jumping & unbalanced before going forward to race forth away from rail. Raced with head on the side & hung outwards around bend, was still only 1L behind 2nd near 200m but weakened quickly late.

Was badly crowded & bumped heavily at the start & consequently lost ground before racing third last away from the rail. Was just under 7L behind on straightening & made no headway in the dash to the line.
Steadied from wide gate & taken back to race second last away from the rail. Was second last & 8L from the lead on straightening but made no impression & was never likely.
Jumped well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced prominently on the outside, no cover throughout, hit the front 250M, kept on very strongly to the line, won by 6-1/4L.
Began well, sent forward to take the lead, shared the lead with rivals turning in, peaked and headed near 250M, ran on evenly to the line.
Away well, raced 3 wide slightly better than midfield, similar position on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place without threatening.
Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, wider turning in, made some headway in straight.
Average to begin, positioned 3-1/2L behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Began awkwardly and shifted out, raced in midfield on the outside, 2 wide from 500M, 5 lengths back turning in, finished off evenly.
Jumped out awkwardly and shifted out, raced 2 wide towards rear, found rail 700M, 7 lengths back turning in, made no impression in straight.
Moderately away, positioned 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, wider turning in, showed limited response early in straight, weakened inside final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.) (Blood in trachea.)
Jumped well, raced prominently on the outside, took the lead 400M, peaked and headed 250M, weakened inside final furlong.
Jumped awkwardly and crowded, raced at tail, 8 lengths or so back on turn, showed some response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear throughout, never a factor. (See Racing Incidents.) (Bled.)
Slowly away, raced better than midfield on the inside, 2 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final 250M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Broke nicely from the inside barrier and soon assumed the lead on the rail, travelled smoothly throughout, quickened nicely when asked, made all.
Jumped on term and steadied to settle worse than midfield, angled out 400M and responded well, closed off strongly for 2nd.
Settled behind the speed on the rail, kept on okay for 3rd.
Settled midfield on the rail, had trouble obtaining clear running until the 300M, and stayed on well.
Settled 2 wide behind the leaders, showed good dash early in the straight but weakened inside 150M.
Jumped very awkwardly and lost ground, settled near the rear on the rail, made decent headway in the straight. (Barrier Manners unacceptable, must trial)
Broke well but beaten for speed in the early stages, settled midfield 3 wide with cover, and ran on only ordinarily.
Settled near the rear 2 wide, made little progress.
Sat in front of midfield on the rail, raced keenly, found nothing in the straight. (See Incident Report)
Settled at the rear, switched to center track, made some headway early in the straight but then weakened.
Broke smartly and ridden along early to track leader, weakened inside 300M. (See Incident Report)
Travelled 3 wide no cover in front of midfield, weakened and faded in the straight.
At rear and never in contention.
Settled midfield 2 wide between horses, ridden along at 500M but no response, soon faded. (See Incident Report)
Began well from a wide draw, pressed forward to share pace out wide, obtained 2-wide position just outside race leader coming onto home bend, fought on dourly to gain upper hand close to home.
Ridden forward to lead after moderate start, obtained rails run onto home bend, held narrow advantage in straight until collared close to home.
Settled wide in 6th just better than midfield, 3-wide in midfield rounding home bend, fought on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Gradually dropped back to last few despite ridden along, produced strong late impression inside final 250 metres, nearest at finish.
Drifted back gradually from prominent position to rear of midfield in 8th, baulked for a run early in straight until the 200 metres, finished off race strongly.
Settled well back from a wide draw, obtained rails run after first 200 metres, saved ground turning for home, did not find much room in straight until late in closing stages.
Ridden forward to be up with the leaders, gradually settled some 2L back in 5th onto home bend, renewed effort entering straight, kept on same pace under pressure.
Ridden forward to join race leaders, some 1L back when hampered approaching home bend, 3-wide rounding home bend gaining 3rd into straight, unable to sustain effort.
With leaders on the rail, settled one back in 3rd coming onto home bend, gradually weakened under pressure after straightening.
Taken well back from the widest draw, never seen with a chance.
Soon recovered to midfield from moderate start, saved ground turning for home, faded under pressure inside final 200 metres.
From draw 11 given a patient ride, still at last place passing 400M, responded strongly when out into clear 250M, led nearing 50M, won going away.
Settled towards the rear, bustled along 600M, quickened up well on straightening, progressed to reach leaders near 100M but no match for winner final stages.
Held up in mid-division along the inside, ran on well under top weight from 350M, got up for 3rd inside 100M.
Never far off leaders, switched wide 550M, moved up to challenge for the lead mid-straight, kept on final 200M but not pace of first three late stages.
Soon led, joined by rival 1100M vying for lead on inside, couldn't shake off rivals when driven out 350M, caught nearing 100M, no extra late.
Positioned ahead of midfield, driven out 450M, ran on fairly to the line and never found the needed late kick.
Chased leaders along the 3-path, wide no cover from 800M, moved up to join leaders 500M, kept battling early straight, swamped final 100M.
Vied for the lead on outside, fought hard early straight to stay in contention, flattened final 200M.
Slotted into a 2-wide position behind midfield, switched wide 500M, stayed on mildly not reaching leaders.
From draw 1 stalked the leaders along the fence, kept to inside turning into straight, held up behind a weakening rival over final 200M, not tested to the line.
Caught wide early, steadied to a rearward spot, 5Ls to make up 400M but gave limited response on straightening, failed to make an impact
From draw 12 moved up to chase leaders along the 2-path, came up empty passing 300M, weakened.
Settled 2-wide in midfield, wide into straight, outpaced passing 400M, soon out of contention.
Dropped back to race near last, pushed along 600M out but lacked response, soon beaten on straightening.
Away well, raced prominently on the outside, there to turn, hit the front 350M, kept on well to hold off the challengers.
Began well, raced in 3rd, a length or so back, same position on turn, closed off well, just beaten by a narrow margin. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact shortly after start, raced 2 wide in midfield, wider after passing 550M, finished off well to take a place, nearest on line.
Shifted in at start and made contact, raced behind midfield on the inside, 6 lengths or so back, moved closer along the rail on turn, finished off strongly to make frame, nearest on line.
Away with them, raced slightly better than midfield on the inside, saved ground to turn, angled out 450M, unable to obtain clear run until final 100M, finished off well to be nearest on line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide towards rear, found rail near 750M, 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Shifted out at start and made contact, raced 2 wide behind midfield, very wide into straight, finished off well to be nearest on line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear, 9 lengths or so back, commenced move 600M, very wide into straight, closed off well to be nearest on line.
Made contact at start, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, angled out 550M, unable to obtain clear run until final 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Shifted in at start and made contact, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths back, wider from 550M, showed limited response early in straight, no extra and just pushed along final furlong.
Slowly away, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground throughout, made good progress early in straight, no extra final 150M.
Made contact at start, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, 3 wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced towards rear on the outside, 6 lengths back turning in, one-paced in straight.
Made contact at start and unbalanced, sent forward to take the lead, challenged by rival turning in, peaked and headed 350M, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact shortly after start, took the early lead, headed near 950M, a length or so back on turn, retook the lead 250M, kept on very well to the line, easily scored.
Jumped awkwardly, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, a bit closer in the middle stages, 2 wide turning in, closed off well to take 2nd. (A small abrasion to the forehead.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight to take a place without threatening.
Began awkwardly, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made good progress to be nearest on line.

Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide from 800M, carried wider 500M, bumped and unbalanced early in straight, made good progress after passing 300M, peaked 75M, ran on evenly to the line.
Commenced well, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead 950M, led by 1/4L turning in, peaked and headed 300M, weakened gradually final 100M.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, angled out 450M, made some headway in straight.
Jumped with them, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, no clear run near 150M, one-paced thereafter.

Began well from a wide draw, raced prominently on the outside, 2nd on turn, took the lead approaching 300M, peaked and headed 250M, weakened final 150M. (Lost left front plate shortly after start.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Out with rest, raced towards rear on the outside, very wide into straight, passed some tired runners in straight.
Made contact at start, raced better than midfield on the outside, 3 wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Commenced well from a wide draw, raced in midfield on the outside, 4 lengths or so back, no cover for the majority of the race, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Began awkwardly and made contact, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, unable to maintain position on turn, showed limited response early in straight, eased final furlong.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, angled out 550M, bumped 400M, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong.

Began well, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, finished off strongly to score.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length on turn, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner final 50M.
Away well, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, finished off well to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Hampered shortly after start, raced behind midfield on the inside, 4 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, made some headway in straight to make frame without threatening.
Shifted out at start, raced in midfield on rail, saved ground throughout, finished off evenly. (Blood in trachea.)
Began smartly, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Bumped start, raced at tail, 6 lengths back on turn, made some progress early in straight, no extra final 150M.
Slightly slow out, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, very wide turning in, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, raced at rear on the outside, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, no clear run early in straight, ran on evenly thereafter.
Bumped start, raced slightly better than midfield on the outside, no cover throughout, peaked 300M, weakened inside final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Crowded on jumping, unable to slot in, trapper wide behind midfield, peaked on turn, weakened final 200M. (See Racing Incidents.)

Had no early speed & raced a clear last after start. Moved 4 wide & under hard riding when circling the field down back straight, moved to third 500m, continued to finish off one paced to lead at 150m & continue on to win.
Pushed forward to lead. Joined & passed by winner nearing 150m, battle don well to hold second on line.
Raced 1,1 early, then 2,1 from the 1300m. Moved into three wide line with cover near 850m, finished off steadily down the outside to move to third in final 150m.
Steadied & taken back towards the rear throughout. Shifted back inwards after cornering before making late headway nearer the inside to move to forth when passing a few tiring rivals late.
Raced midfield along the rail in early & middle stages. Moved off rail near 700m, was momentarily held up on straightening before finishing off only steadily to be well beaten into midfield.
Had a nice run on the leaders back early before continuing along the rail in midfield down the back straight & around the bend. Was only 2.5L behind at the 400m but weakened out in straight.

Raced three wide without cover early before improving to race outside the leader from passing the winning post first time. Continued second, only about a length behind on straightening but weakened out to be beaten about 6L.

Raced worse than midfield away from the rail early before moving three wide without cover & commencing to improve from the 1100m. Got to third place near 900m, began to struggle near the 450m & gave ground in the straight.

Raced in midfield away from the rail before being relegated to 4th last near the 800m. Was under pressure approaching the 400m mark when about 5L behind before cornering widest but then giving further ground in straight.
Had no early speed but was ridden along & improve to race worse than midfield along the rail, virtually shared last place from 800m, stayed near rail on straightening but did nothing in final 300m.
Raced outside leader early before racing 1,1 from the 1300m. Came under heavy pressure near 400m mark when only 2L from the lead but stopped badly in the straight & weakened to long second last.

Raced towards the rear throughout & virtually shared last place when racing three wide with cover from 800m. Was under hard ridding when last before the 400m mark, swung wide on straightening but weakened badly to long last.
Jumped on terms and ridden along to maintain its position early, settled near the rear, angled out at 300M, closed off strongly, won going away.
Broke nicely and up with the pace, responded well when asked, but just can't hold off the winner.
Broke well and showed very good early speed to lead, kept on okay for 3rd.
Settled midfield 2 wide, ran on okay for 4th.
Sat last 2 wide, angled out initially in the straight but went back towards the inside, stayed on fairly.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, travelled smoothly throughout, but just one pace when asked.
Raced wide throughout and weakened in the straight.
Broke on terms but didn't showed much early speed, settled behind midfield 2 wide, got hampered and taken wider rounding the home turn, made little progress. (See Incident Report)
Steadied towards the rear from a wide barrier, began to improve at 800M but failed to make the turn, found nothing in the straight. (Racing Manners unacceptable, must trial around a bend)
Hard ridden to sit outside the lead, weakened inside 350M.
Settled near the rear, got hampered at 600M rounding the turn, never a threat.
Pushed forward to lead. Kicked strongly on straightening, held comfortable margin over rivals all the way to line & despite racing waywardly under pressure late went on to win by easy 3L.
Raced wide early but improved position to race second, two wide form the 1200m. Couldn't go with the leader/winner who kicked clear in the straight but bud deep to hold well beaten second on line.
Had a nice run on the leaders back for the majority. Couldn't go with the leader who bounded clear in straight, tried hard & held third on line, albeit well behind easy winner.

Slow to begin but made up ground, was checked passing winning post before getting position in midfield off the rail. Eased wider entering last section, finished off ok down the outside, only 0.75L behind second on line.

Pushed forward, shifted inwards near winning post when second before being crossed & racing 1,1 from the 1200m. Was three wide from 600m, battled on ok but was caught for a minor placing late, not beaten far behind 2nd.

Steadied at start & taken back to race second last along rail. Was 6.5L form the lead entering last section, stayed close to the rail on straightening, made some late ground & was only 1L behind second on line.
Raced in midfield along the rail throughout. Battled on only moderately in straight & was only fair.

Taken behind runners after start & raced worse than midfield along the rail. Was 5L from the lead entering last section, shifted away from rail on straightening, was held approaching 50m when finishing off fairly late.
Raced in midfield away from the rail throughout. Entered last section just under 5L from the lead but made no headway in the straight & was beaten the same margin when finishing 9th.

Steadied from outside gate & taken back to race at the tail. Continued a clear last down back straight, shifted three wide passing 450m, shifted to be the widest on straightening, only past a couple of tiring ones late.

Steadied on jumping & raced just worse than midfield away from the rail. Moved into three wide line near the 900m & was wide thereafter. Entered last section 5.5L from lead but weakened out further & likely struggled at trip.

Settled in the second last pair in early stages when racing away from the rail. Came under pressure entering the last section when 6.5L from the lead but was eased out of the race in the straight (bled).
Bumped shortly after start, positioned 2 wide, 2-1/2L back, same position on turn, showed very good response in straight, hit the front 100M, kept on well to hold off the challenger late.
Jumped well, raced 3 wide with cover, 3-1/2L back, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to take 2nd, just beaten by a narrow margin.
Taken back from gate 8, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off well to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Bumped shortly after start, taken back to race at tail, 6 lengths or so back, angled out after passing 500M, very wide turning in, made good progress in straight to make frame.

Began smartly from gate 1, raced prominently on the inside, allowed rival to cross 500M, sat right behind the leader on turn, made good progress early in straight, hit the front 150M, peaked and headed 100M, weakened gradually close home.

Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, made contact and unbalanced near 650M, 4 lengths back turning in, unable to obtain clear run early in straight, made some progress thereafter.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, there to turn, made some progress early in straight, no extra final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped on jumping, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Out with rest, raced better than midfield on the outside, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Began fairly, raced behind midfield on outer, very wide turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length on turn, peaked early in straight, headed 200M, weakened thereafter.
Slowly away, raced towards rear on the inside, made contact near 650M, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Broke on terms and steadied to obtain a position worse than midfield 2 wide, switched to 3 wide to improve at 600M, taken wider rounding the Home Turn, closed off strongly to score.
Settled behind the speed on the rail, switched towards the inside for the run, ran on and kept on well, just got beaten on the line.
Steadied after the start from a wide barrier, sat near the rear 2 wide, stayed on well to grab 3rd.
Broke well and raced in a prominent position 2 wide, moved to 3 wide approaching 700M, did not quickened well enough. (See Incident Report)
Settled near the rear on the rail, made good progress along the rail, stayed on okay.
Sat last, angled out to center track in the straight, and took some time to response, made some progress, best stride late. (See Incident Report)
Caught wide rounding the first turn, then improved to sit outside the lead, under pressured at 500M, limited response.
Broke well and showed good early speed to lead, weakened inside 200M.
Settled midfield on the rail, made no impression
Raced behind midfield on the rail, made no ground in the straight.
Settled midfield 2 wide between horses, never a threat.
Sat in front of midfield 2 wide, hard ridden at 450M and gave ground.
Shared early pace 2-wide, taken over 1L back to 4th turning into straight and becoming 5th 750 metres out, renewed effort entering home straight, quickened to lead 150 metres out and ridden clear.
Began well from a wide draw and pressed forward to join the leader, travelled 2-wide in 2nd before gaining narrow advantage briefly turning into straight, fought on gamely for 2nd.

Broke well from the one draw before taken one back to 3rd, travelled keenly in the slow tempo in back straight, held some chance early in straight before outsprinted by winner inside final 100 metres.

Midfield when hampered and lost ground turning into back straight, pulled forward in slow tempo back to wide in midfield about 700 metres out, hung in and difficult to ride early in straight, fought on quite well under pressure.
Settled in midfield, travelled keenly in slow tempo at about 800 metres, came under pressure to challenge entering home straight and shifted in inside 250 metres, fought on quite well under pressure.
Jumped in midfield settling in last few, travelled keenly in slow tempo in back straight, finished off the race well inside final 200 metres.
Soon taken back to last from the widest draw, trailed the field to straight, produced good late impression under pressure in straight.
Broke quickly to take up running and rails run shortly after setting a slow tempo to 400 metres, weakened under pressure inside final 200 metres.
Travelled strongly wide in last few in the slow tempo, hung out widest into home straight, kept on steadily without quickening.

Travelled wide without cover and keenly just better than midfield, pulled forward in the slow tempo to 4th 750 metres out and 3rd 3-wide around home bend, ever wider turning for home and soon weakened.
Slow out, soon recovered to 9th on rail travelling keenly in the slow tempo, tightened after straightening 250 metres out, ran home one-paced.

Jumped awkwardly and failed to muster pace before given reminders, picked up to midfield in 6th on rail turning into back straight, saved ground turning for home but badly hampered over 250 metres out, never recovered.
Held up in mid-division along the fence, quickened up well between runners passing 250M, hit the fore near 100M, all out to hold off pursuing rivals towards the finish.
Settled down midfield along the 2-path, finished off strongly from 300M, challenged for the lead over final 100M, just held.
Taken back to the rear, 6-7Ls to make up 400M, wide into straight, closed off fastest to finish nearest at the line, just missed 2nd in a photo.
Towards the rear 3-wide, waited with until top of straight, closed off well to claim 4th, nearest finish.
Reserved behind midfield, put in a mild bid from top of straight, stayed on to go 5th near line but no threat to leaders.
From draw 11 moved up to track leaders along the 2-path, challenged for the lead early straight, flattened final 150M.
Jumped awkwardly and lost ground, recovered to a midfield spot but raced wide no cover, lay out home turn, kept on only fairly in the straight.
Never far off the pace, switched away from fence 400M, fought on at same pace, no longer a threat final 200M.
From draw 12 dropped back to the rear, 6Ls to make up 400M, closed off the race mildly but got checked near 100M, not ridden out to the line.
Emerged as leader passing 1000M, hard driven to hold its lead early straight, caught near 150M, weakened towards the finish.
Tracked leader, given every chance, kept battling early straight before fading from 150M, swamped by rivals late. (Minor lacerations to LH stifle)
Dropped back to a rearward position, not quickened on straightening, eased when no chance final 100M.

Jumped well from gate 10, raced in 5th, 2 wide, easy run to turn, not enough room early in straight, angled out and made contact 250M, cleared 200M, hit the front 150M, kept on very well to the line, easily scored.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide towards rear, 7 lengths back on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared 150M, finished off well to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Shifted in at start and made contact, raced 2 wide behind midfield, a bit closer on turn, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Jumped with them, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, hit the front 200M, peaked and headed 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 8 lengths or so back turning in, finished off very strongly to be nearest on line.
Jumped awkwardly, raced towards rear on the inside, 7 lengths back turning in, made good progress early in straight, no extra final 75M.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide towards rear, very wide into straight, made some progress in the run home.
Made contact shortly after start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, wider turning in, made contact near 250M, ran on evenly to the line.
Began smartly from gate 1, sent forward to take the early lead, headed 1150M, raced in 2nd in the middle stages, 1-1/2L back on turn, peaked on run 200M, weakened final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, no clear run final 150M.
Away well, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead 1150M, led by 1-1/2L turning in, peaked and headed 200M,
Began well from the widest draw, trapped wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back turning in, peaked and inconvenienced early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.

Moderately away, raced in midfield on the inside, angled out 550M, hard ridden after passing 300M, finished off strongly to score by a narrow margin.

Moderately away from the widest draw, sent forward to race prominently on the outside, travelled well to turn, hit the front 300M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner late. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, wider turning in, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Began fairly from gate 1, raced towards rear on the inside, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, closed off well to make frame without threatening.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4-1/2L back turning in, made some headway in straight.
Jumped well from gate 11, raced better than midfield on the inside, angled out 550M, no clear run early in straight, peaked on run 200M, ran on evenly to the line.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide towards rear, 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the outside, 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Began awkwardly, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some progress early in straight, blocked final 150M, not able to test properly.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked and headed 350M, weakened final 300M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced at rear on the outside, very wide turning in, made no impression in straight.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, wider turning in, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, very wide into straight, peaked early in straight, weakened final 250M.
Away with them, raced behind midfield on the inside, peaked 500M, weakened early in straight, finished tailed out.
Settled down behind midfield, switched away from fence 800M, gave good response top of straight, stayed on best final stages and got up inside 100M.
Reserved in midfield, moved to the 3-path passing 1200M, wide into straight, ran on well and challenged strongly for the lead 200M, out-stayed by winner late stages. Hung on 2nd in a photo.
Held up behind mid-division, swung wide home turn, ran on well final 400M to make frame, just missed out on 2nd in a photo. (Blood in trachea.)
Raced in midfield, wide no cover form 900M, pushed wider home turn, quickened to lead 300M, peaked on its run 100M, couldn't hold off rivals final stages.
Given a patient ride from draw 12, settled near last, put in a mild bid turning into straight, held by leaders in the run home.
From wide draw taken back to last about 10Ls off the pace, remained at the rear 400M, shifted ground 300M to continue forward, stayed on but no serious threat to leaders.
Reserved in midfield, moved closer to leaders when pace slackened on home turn, ran on fairly to the line, never reach contention.
Crossed to the front near 1600M, vied for lead 1100M onwards, run ended 300M, swamped by rivals mid-straight.
Led early, retrained to take cover behind leaders from 1600M, unbalanced at 1100M on own accord, failed to close off turning home, soon out of contention. (Roarer.)
Jumped fairly from wide draw, shifted across behind runners to race in a rearward position, ran past beaten horses in the straight, never threatened.
Caught wide early, moved up on the 1st turn to be racing outside leader, challenged for the lead 600M, kept on fairly early straight, no extra final 200M.
Slow to begin, recovered to a midfield position, had no clear run early straight, eased final 200M.
Caught wide no cover early stages, strode forward from 1400M to reach the fore at 900M, struggled to keep up 500M, soon weakened on straightening.
Chased leaders along the 2-path, pushed to a 4-wide spot without cover home turn, checked 250M and lost ground, nothing left final stages.
Broke smartly, settled just behind the leader, switched to 2 wide near the 600M, travelled comfortably, angled out at 400M and closed off well, won nicely.
Settled in front of midfield early, raced keenly at the 1000M then soon tracked the leader, kept on strongly until 150M then weakened slightly.
Settled at the rear 2 wide, stayed on okay to grab 3rd.
Sat in a midfield position 2 wide, just one pace when asked.
Settled worse than midfield on the rail, made minor progress. (See Incident Report)
Led and weakened at 200M.
At the rear and took time to response, made some late headway.
Had a nice run in midfield between runners. Travelled well until getting clear running near 250m, closed strongly to lead at 100m & held off late challenger.

Limited early speed & raced third last along stand side rail. Shifted inwards to get clear running from 300m to 200m before closing off strongly in late stages to charge to fast finishing 2nd (Rider questioned, see report).
Showed some speed & shared second place for most of the middle stages. Continued close to the lead all the way until the first two pulled a length clear in last 100m. Not beaten far into third.

Raced close to the speed, sharing second place when about a length behind for most of the middle stages. Moved to the lead at the 250m mark, joined by the winner at the 100m, battled on ok, only beaten just over 1L.

Showed some speed, racing third early before racing on the leaders back along the stand side rail in middle stages. Shifted inwards to get clear at the 200m mark, closed off evenly in final stages & wasn't beaten far.
Raced just worse than midfield when racing nearer to the center of the track. Was 3.5L lengths behind entering last section before making good headway in the middle of the track to be beaten only 2L.

Bumped soon after the start before racing in just worse than midfield along the stand side rail. Was held up fleetingly near the 200m mark before shifting inwards & closing off ok under little ridding in final stages.

Was outpaced after the start & raced second last. Was over 4L from the lead passing the 400m mark when continuing second last before making up a length or so when passing a couple of rivals when running onto midfield.
Raced just forward of midfield throughout. Was under 2L from the lead entering last section, hung inwards in final furling when weakening out to be beaten over 4L. (Blood in trachea post-race).

Commenced awkwardly then bumped & lost a length before mustering & getting position in midfield between runners. Was a touch keen mid-race, was only about a length behind at the furlong mark but weakened out late.
Bumped soon after the start before racing worse than midfield between runners. Emptied out at the 150m mark & gave ground quickly late.
Showed customary early speed to speed across the front of the field to lead along stand side rail. Was headed at the 250m mark & weakened out quickly late.

Raced in midfield when the closest runner to the center of the track. Was just under 3L from the lead entering final section, cane under riding soon after, was beaten at the 300m before weakening out badly in late stages.
Had no early speed & raced at the rear throughout. Weakened badly in the final section & was a long last. (Mucus in trachea post-race).
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, hard ridden 300M, finished off strongly to score.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced 3 wide, a length or so back, 2 wide from 1050M, a bit closer on turn, hit the front 200M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 50M.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover slightly behind midfield, wider after passing 650M, 3 lengths back turning in, closed off well to take a place.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide from 700M, 4 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight to make frame, nearest finish.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, finished off well without threatening the first few.
Away well, raced 3 wide with cover, 6 lengths or so back, wider on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.

Jumped well from the widest draw, raced prominently on the outside, took the lead approaching 1300M, challenged by rival turning in, peaked and headed 200M, weakened final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 8 lengths back, closer on turn but still the last, made some headway in straight.
Began fairly, raced towards rear on the inside, 2 wide from 650M, no clear run early in straight, ran on evenly thereafter.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide towards rear, 3 wide turning in, made no impression in straight.
Away with them, raced prominently on the inside, allowed rival to cross 1050M, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced behind midfield on the inside, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start, raced in midfield on the outside, no cover for the majority of the race, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter. (Mucus.)
Out with rest, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, weakened early in straight.
Broke a step slow but quickly recovered to settle behind the speed, under pressured at 350M and quickened very well, won going away.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, had some trouble obtaining clear running in the straight, but ran on well for 2nd. (See Incident Report)
Settled near the pace 2 wide, kept on okay and battled for 3rd.
Sat in front of midfield 2 wide, closed off nicely but weakened slightly in the final 50M, lost 3rd on the line.
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide, stayed on fairly. (Lame right front)
Settled near the rear on the rail, made some ground in the straight, never threatened.
Settled midfield 2 wide, only one pace when asked.
Tracked leader, weakened inside 250M.
Steadied after the start to race near the rear 3 wide, began to improve at 650M, showed some dash early in the straight but then weakened. (See Incident Report)
Caught 3 wide no cover in midfield throughout, made no impression
Raced near the rear on the rail, made no ground.
Sat last and never a threat.
Settled midfield on the rail, weakened and faded in the straight.
Led early and faded quickly at 250M. (See Incident Report) (Performance unacceptable, must trial)
Jumped fairly from the widest draw, settled just over 1L off the pace on stands rail, quickened under pressure to hit the front over 200 metres out, just held on to the line.
Moderate start from second widest draw, travelled some 1L off the pace one off stands rail, quickened well under pressure alongside winner 200 metres out, held every chance to fail only narrowly.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, failed to muster under pressure and trailed the field to 500 metres, inconvenienced for a run 200 metres out, finished off the race well under pressure closing stages.
Began well from a middle draw and soon took up running with half a length advantage, hung in and a difficult ride from half-way out drifting in sharply 150 metres out, ran home one-paced.
Settled just within 2L of pace, drifted slightly further back 600 metres out approaching course proper, came under pressure to challenge inside 350 metres but failed to quicken to threaten.
Broke well from the one draw of the small field, travelled prominently near the centre of the track, unable to sustain effort inside final 100 metres.
Soon came from a low draw to join the leaders, came under pressure coming onto course proper, yielded ground quickly inside final 300 metres.
Jostled at start and soon dropped to last few about 3L off the pace, drifted further back approaching course proper, one-paced under pressure in the run to the line.
Began awkwardly losing ground, soon recovered to join the leaders after first 200 metres, weakened noticeably inside final 250 metres.
Dropped back after the start, settled towards the rear in a slow run race, waited with until 400M, closed off strongly down inside, got up close home.
Tracked leaders, commenced to race fiercely 1400M when pace was slow, led near 300M, continued on well to the line, caught close home.
Held up 2-wide in midfield, pace slow early and middle stages, chased hard over final 300M, got up for 3rd late.
Tracked leader on outside in a slowly run race, checked 1000M, 3rd turning home, fought hard to the line, lost 3rd near line. (Jockey questioned re riding tactics.)
Restrained behind midfield early stages, made forward move when pace was very slow 1100M, led from 1000M until headed near 300M, faded final stages.
Not hurried, settled at the rear in a slow run race, held up until 350M, ran on without threat.
Settled midfield in a slow run race, 3Ls off leader 400M, put in a mild bid on straightening, steadied near 150M, held ground final stages.
Jumped only fairly, held up towards the rear racing keenly early stages, 3-wide home turn, stayed on fairly from top of straight, never a threat to leaders

Soon led, restrained to set very slow pace until rivals took over 1100M, struggled to hold position on straightening, emptied mid-straight. (Jockey questioned re the slow pace set between 1600M-1200M)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the outside, 4 lengths or so back turning in, no daylight early in straight, cleared 300M, finished off very strongly to score.
Began smartly from gate 12, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead 900M, led by 3/4L on turn, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner final 50M.
Shifted in at start and made contact, took the early lead, headed 900M, allowed rival to cross 700M, 3/4L back turning in, kept on well in straight to take a place without threatening.
Reared as stalls opened, missed break and lost many lengths, reached the back of the field 750M, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to make frame, nearest on line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, raced better than midfield on the outside, no cover on turn, made good progress early in straight, peaked on run 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped well, positioned a length behind the leader in the early stages, 2 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide on turn, kept on same pace in straight.
Bumped start, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made minor progress early in straight, peaked 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Taken back to race 2 wide behind midfield, similar position on turn, one-paced in straight.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, showed limited response early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened final 100M.
Out with rest, positioned 3 wide with cover in midfield, wider turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 250M.
Moderately away from gate 13, raced in midfield on the outside, no cover for the majority of the race, very wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out 550M, finished off very strongly to score.

Made contact with the left side of its barrier on jumping, raced at rear on the inside, 6 lengths or so back, 2 wide turning in, no clear run early in straight, cleared 200M, finished off strongly to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, made good progress after passing 250M, no extra final 50M.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, there to turn, made some progress early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced prominently on the outside, there to turn, took the lead 350M, peaked and headed 150M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced slightly better than midfield, 2 wide, crowded near 1200M, checked near 1100M, 3 lengths back turning in, made some progress early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Bumped start, raced in midfield on the outside, 3 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, finished off evenly.

Away with them, raced prominently on the inside in the early stages, allowed rival to cross 1050M, sat right behind the leader in the middle stages, showed some response early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened 100M.
Taken back to race behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some headway early in straight, peaked 150M, one-paced thereafter.

Made contact with the right side of its barrier on jumping, unable to slot in, trapped wide in midfield early, taken back after passing 1300M, raced 3 wide with cover towards rear in the middle stages, made no impression in straight.
Out with rest, raced slightly better than midfield on the outside, 3 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, crowded near 300M, made no impression final furlong.
Shifted in at start and bumped, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/4L on turn, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 3 wide from 900M, wider turning in, made no progress in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear, 6 lengths back, very wide into straight, failed to make any progress in the run home.

Bumped start, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, bumped near 200M, finished off very strongly to score. (See Racing Incidents.)
Out with rest, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off well to take 2nd, just beaten by a narrow margin.

Began well from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out 350M, showed good response in straight, hit the front 150M, kept on well but unable to hold off the first two final 50M.
Jumped well from gate 10, sent forward to take the lead, shared the lead with rival from 750M, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, weakened final 50M.
Away well, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, there to turn, made some progress early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the outside, 6 lengths back on turn, made some progress early in straight, no clear run final 200M, not able to test properly.
Hampered start, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some headway in straight.
Shifted out at start and made contact, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, very wide into straight, finished off evenly. (Bled.)
Moderately away, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, very wide into straight, bumped near 200M, kept on same pace thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear, 7 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made some progress early in straight, blocked 100M, ran on evenly thereafter.

Jumped with them, trapped wide in midfield early, sent forward after entering the back straight, shared lead in the middle stages, peaked early in straight, headed 150M, hampered 100M, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at rear on the outside, 7 to 8 lengths back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Settled well back and waited with, angled off the rail coming into straight obtaining a run 200 metres out, responded well to hit the front close to finish despite a difficult ride.
Broke best before taken 2 back to 3rd on rail, quickened under pressure to hit the front over 150 metres out only to be caught final strides.
Travelled in midfield, raced keenly middle stages, nearest at finish. (Riding questioned)

Settled in forward of midfield on the rail, just under 4L back in 5th rounding home bend, saved ground turning in, reached within 1L of lead 100 metres out but unable to sustain effort closing stages.
Ridden forward to be up with the pace, taken 2 back to 4th early in back straight, fought on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Crowded at start from a wide draw settling well behind, trailed the field into straight, ran on past well-beaten horses in the run to the line.
Settled just worse than midfield, inconvenienced over 500 metres out, one-paced under pressure in straight.
Pressed forward to lead from the widest gate, obtained rails run in the front over 850 metres out and led until headed inside final 200 metres.
Hard ridden from a wide draw to vie for lead early before settling one back in 2nd, one-paced under pressure when shifted ground over 150 metres out, never recovered.

Ridden along after moderate start before recovering to just worse than midfield in 9th, gained 8th in similar position onto home bend and saved ground turning in, found no extra inside final 100 metres.
Wide in last few early, remained well back to straight, never a factor.
Travelled 3 wide without cover in midfield, widest runner turning for home, soon weakened.
Broke well and settled in front of midfield on the rail, travelled smoothly throughout, switched out rounding the turn, responded well and won.
Settled worse than midfield on the rail, closed off well when asked, nearest finish.
Caught wide down the back straight and made a mid-race move to join the lead, kept on well early in the straight, weakened at 150M.
Travelled behind the speed on the rail, quickened okay early but only one pace afterwards. (See Incident Report)
Up with the pace early, under pressured at 800M and soon hard ridden, kept on fairly.
Sat in front of midfield 2 wide, switched out to 3 wide rounding the home turn, and did not quickened well enough. (Blood in trachea)
Broke with the field and ridden along to lead, weakened inside 200M. (See Incident Report)
Settled worse the midfield 2 wide, limited response in the straight. (See Incident Report)
Raced near the rear, made no impression
At the rear and never a threat.
Steadied after the start from a wide barrier, never in contention. (See Incident Report)
Went to the lead, hard ridden in closing stages & dug deep to continue to hold a neck advantage on line.
Had a nice run on leaders back. Moved into clear running, tried hard all the way to the line but couldn't quite get to the leader/winner who won by a neck.

Steadied soon after the start & raced in midfield along the rail. Moved into clear running soon after straightening, closed well all the way to line but couldn't get to leader. Only beaten a neck into third.

Steadied from outside barrier & cut across to race third last on rail. Improved slightly along the rail passing the 400m, shifted outwards into clear running mid-straight before closing strongly in concluding stages to 4th.

Steadied nearing first bend & raced worse than midfield when three deep with cover. Continued wide around bend, swung to be the widest runner on straightening before making good late ground down the outside, only beaten 2L.
Raced in midfield away from the rail but then lost position slightly passing the 500m. Had clear running on straightening & finished off steadily to midfield without threatening.
Was wide at the first bend & then steadied & taken back to last. Stayed along the inside on cornering when second last before making some late ground to run onto midfield from the tail.

Ridden along from gate 11 but was racing very wide around the first bend before being posted three deep without cover in midfield throughout. Was wide on straightening but made no headway & was never likely after wide trip.

Showed early speed, was three wide at the first bend before improving to race two wide & outside the leader from the 800m. Dropped a length behind the lead near the 500m, weakened out in the straight to be beaten 4.5L.
Raced outside the leader early before being crossed & racing 1,1 from the 800m. Eased wider just prior to straightening, peaked on effort mid-straight before weakening out in last furlong.
Steadied after the start & taken back to second last. Was relegated to last near the 400m mark, swung wider on cornering, never really ran on & was beaten over 5L.

Raced in midfield between runners before being shuffled back & relegated to third last near the 400m. Didn't have much room in final 100m but was too far back to be involved & failed to beat a rival home.
Average to begin, raced in midfield on the outside, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to score.
Clean jump, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner late.
Began fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, closed off well to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, angled out 350M, made some progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 wide turning in, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Began well from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, angled out 400M, no clear run early in straight, cleared 150M, finished off evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 7 lengths back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Away well, raced prominently, 2 wide, found rail approaching 700M, a length behind the leader on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, one-paced in the run home.
Away with them, tracked leaders on the outside, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from gate 10, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Broke well and showed very good early speed to lead, travelled strongly throughout, quickened well when asked, won smartly.
Settled behind midfield on the rail, angled out at 250M, closed off well, but no threat to the winner.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, ran on quite well for 3rd.
Sat just behind the speed, kept on okay for 4th.
Raced in midfield on the rail, only one pace when asked.
Broke well but steadied to obtain a midfield positon 2 wide, switched out to center track in the straight, only limited response.
Showed no early speed early, under pressured at 800M and began to improve, made some progress in the straight along the rail.
Raced 3 wide no cover in midfield, made no impression.
Settled behind midfield 2 wide, never a threat.
Tracked leader, under pressured at 550M, weakened and faded in the straight.
Detached from the field early despite hard ridden, never in contention. (Roarer)
Settled near the rear, under the whip at 800M and never travelled.

Ridden positively to be joint leaders 3-wide, gradually shifted 2 back to 4th for cover early in back straight, became 5th in similar position 700 metres out, gained upper hand about 50 metres out, won cozily.
Broke well holding narrow advantage on the rail, fought on dourly under pressure only to caught 50 metres out.
Taken back from the widest draw and waited with, saved ground turning for home, obtained clear run over 150 metres out and quickened well under pressure.
Broke well restraining just off the pace on rail, became 4th in similar position 600 metres out, plugged on under pressure in straight.
Settled just over 2L off the pace mainly in 6th on rail, saved ground turning for home, kept on steadily without quickening.
Unbalanced early and slow into stride, travelled strongly in 8th or 7th in back straight within 3L of pace, kept on steadily under pressure without quickening.
Crowded early travelling one from last, one of the widest at the back turning for home, fought on well under pressure down the centre of home straight.
Travelled towards the rear, saved ground rounding home bend, kept on well in straight in the run to the line.
Well there from a wide gate travelling wide without cover, gained 2-wide position in 2nd onto home bend, weakened noticeably after straightening.
Settled behind midfield in 9th after beginning from a wide gate, came under pressure to challenge rounding home bend, baulked for a run early in straight until the 200 metres, kept on well to finish.
Travelled keenly wide without cover in midfield from a wide gate, 4-wide rounding home bend and widest into straight, dropped out tamely inside final 150 metres.
Travelled keenly not far off the pace, went forward 3-wide from 700 metres to join the leaders rounding home bend, shifted wide into straight and fading when hampered 200 metres out, never recovered.
Crowded start, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, no clear run early in straight, bumped near 200M, cleared 150M, finished off very strongly to score.

Taken back from gate 8, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, bumped near 200M, cleared approaching 100M, closed off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Away with them, raced towards rear on the outside, 5 lengths or so back on turn, taken very wide in straight and finished off strongly to take a place.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the early lead, headed 900M, allowed rival to cross near 700M, sat right behind the leader on turn, made some progress early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Began well, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, angled out 350M, finished off evenly.
Jumped well, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Commenced well, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, allowed rival to cross near 750M, a length or so back on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Clean jump, raced prominently but trapped wide early, took the lead 900M, found rail near 700M, led by a length on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 100M, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 6 lengths or so back on turn, made no impression in straight.
Moderately away from the widest draw, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with no cover, a length or so back, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began only fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, crowded near 150M, eased final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away from gate 11, trapped 4 wide in midfield, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect.
