Moderately away from a tricky draw, raced in midfield on the inside, moved a bit closer on turn, angled out 600M, showed very good response in straight, hit the front 150M, kept on well to hold off the challengers late.

Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off strongly, just beaten by a narrow margin. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from gate 11, raced behind midfield on the inside, angled out 500M, closed off well to take a place, always just held.
Out with rest, raced 2 wide, 8 lengths or so back, 3 wide from 800M, same margin back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off well to make frame.
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced in 3rd, 2 wide, similar position on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, dropped towards rear near 500M, 5 lengths or so back turning in, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Average to begin, taken back to race 2 wide towards rear, 6-1/2L back turning in, made some headway early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Away well, raced behind midfield on the outside, 6 lengths or so back turning in, very wide into straight, made minor progress in the run home.
Made contact at start, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, challenged by rival on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide in midfield, wider from 600M, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 7 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, no daylight early in straight, ran on evenly thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began fairly, sent forward to race in 2nd, challenged the leader on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Began well from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.

Bumped at start before pushing forward to lead & crossing to rail near 1400m. Headed in the lead near the 1000m, continued second when holding rail position, regained lead at 300m before going on to win easily.

Was wide without cover around first bend before improving position to midfield off the rail in middle stages. Continued wide down back straight & around bend before closing off steadily, narrowly held non-threatening 2nd.

Raced worse than midfield along the rail for the majority. Made progress along the inside just before cornering, continued to close well in the straight & was just beaten for second on the line, albeit well behind winner.
Crowded after start & raced at the tail throughout. Stayed along the inside rail in the straight & closed off steadily in late stages to close to well beaten 4th late.

Crowded at start & raced second last early. Moved three wide near the 1000m, commenced to improve position around the field from the 700m, was the widest on straightening before finishing off only one paced to midfield.
Bumped at the start before improving position & racing third throughout. Was under 2L from lead on straightening, peaked mid-straight & gave a few lengths in final furlong.

Raced in midfield away from the rail throughout. Had no clear run near the 350m & was held up for some distance thereafter before getting clear near the 300m but then finished off only moderately when difficult to ride.

Began fast before being headed by winner in first furlong & then crossed near the 1400m. Momentarily raced on leaders back before moving off rail & improving to lead near 1000m. Headed again near 300m before weakening late.
Raced 4th along the rail throughout early & middle stages. Moved away from the rail near the 500m, straightened only just over 3L from the lead but peaked at the 200m & weakened to second last.

Crowded between runners at start & settled rearward between runners. Was relegated to a clear second last near 650m, was not travelling well approaching corner, relegated to last on straightening & tailed out to be beaten 9L.
Broke nicely and up with the pace, travelled smoothly throughout, hit the front 300M, kept on well and won comfortably.
Settled towards rear on the rail, switched out to 3 wide rounding the home turn, hardly ridden 150M for 2nd.
Settled midfield 2 wide, kept on fairly but only one pace afterwards.
Ridden along to lead, shared lead from 900M, limited response in the straight.
Jumped awkwardly and settled midfield on the rail, steadied and made minor progress in the Straight.
Sat at the rear, moved to the middle of the track in the straight, made no impression.
Caught wide to track the leader throughout, joined the leader at 900M, weakened inside 300M.
Settled 3 wide in front of midfield, under pressure in the Straight, never a threat. (See Incident Report)
Had a nice run on the leaders back throughout. Moved over heels passing the 400m, moved to the lead at the 275m before going on for a much deserved win, holding a 1L advantage on line.

Improved after first 100m, raced 4th but a wide without cover before shifting into the 1,1 near the 700m. Moved up to challenge at the 300m, looked the winner at the 250m, battled well to be beaten 1L into second.

Raced in fifth place when staying half a horse away from the rail throughout. Shifted outwards to get clear running mid-straight before closing off well in the late stages to finish a good debut third.

Shifted inwards after the start before racing in a bunch in midfield when away from the rail. Was over 3L from the lead on straightening before making some headway in the last furlong to move to 4th in final 50m.
Began very fast & pushed forward from the outside barrier to race outside the leader. Continued to be close to the lead passing the 200m mark but couldn't go with the first couple in final 150m. Ok.
Pushed forward to get soft lead in early stages. Joined & headed by the winner at the 275m before weakening a few lengths in final stages.

Badly crowded, blundered & lost ground at the start & raced rearward. Moved wider to improve passing the 900m, shifted to be the widest runner on straightening when 4.5L from lead before passing a number of runners late.

Hampered at the start & was then taken back to race at the tail. Shared last place and about 6L from the lead on straightening before passing a couple of runners when running onto midfield from a long way back.

Steadied & threw head soon after start & was taken back to race rearward along the rail. Shifted off the rail just before straightening when about 5L from the lead before a couple of tiring rivals late but never threatening.

Raced just worse than midfield between runners throughout. Forced into the three wide line but with cover from the first turn, was only 3.5L from the lead entering last section but did little in the straight & was well held.
Raced three deep with cover in midfield for the majority. Had clear running on straightening when only 2.5L from the lead but emptied at the 200m & gave ground late.

Shifted outwards & bumped at start before steadying away from heels & racing four wide without cover after the first turn. Was wide on straightening before weakening in final 300m after wide passage throughout.

Shifted inwards at start & raced very keenly when worse than midfield before racing fiercely at the first bend & losing ground. Was last & just under 6L from the lead at 400m before failing to make any headway (see report).

Hampered after start before getting position in midfield along the rail. Got close to heels & steadied near 850m, entered last section only 3.5L from lead when continuing along rail before weakening out quickly in last 250m.
Clean jump, sent forward to race prominently, led halfway, kept on very well to hold off the challengers.
Began well from gate 14, positioned a length behind the leader on the stands' side, unable to obtain clear running until final 200M, finished off well to take 2nd.
Jumped with them, raced towards rear, 2 away from the stands' rail, hard ridden from 300M, closed off well to take a place.
Average to begin, raced towards rear on the stands' rail, unable to obtain clear run until 150M, finished off strongly to make frame.
Bumped start, sent forward to take the early lead, headed halfway, hard ridden after passing 350M but only showed limited response, ran on evenly to the line.
Crowded on jumping, raced towards rear, 3 away from the stands' rail, a bit closer in the middle stages, made good progress after passing 300M, peaked on run 100M, weakened thereafter.
Bumped start, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader, hard ridden after passing 350M but only showed limited response, weakened gradually final 150M. (Roarer.)
Began well from gate 13, positioned a length behind the leader, 2 away from the stands' rail, bumped 300M, unbalanced and blundered near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away well, raced towards rear in the middle of the track, made some progress after passing 400M, peaked 200M, weakened final 100M.
Moderately away from gate 1, sent forward to race prominently, peaked on run 300M, weakened final furlong. (Sustained a laceration to the right front heel bulb.)
Bumped start, raced behind midfield, nearer to the middle track, made no progress final 400M.
Bumped start, raced behind midfield on the middle track, failed to make any progress final 300M.
Out with rest, raced in midfield, 2 away from the stands' rail, crowded near 400M, hampered 300M, made no progress thereafter.
Away with them, raced in midfield on the middle track, failed to make any progress final 400M.
Broke nicely and ridden along to be up with the pace, kicked clear at 300M, kept on well and held off all challengers.
Jump on terms and settled midfield 3 wide with cover, angled out at 400M and held together until 300M, ridden out and closed off well, just can't get to the winner. (See Incident Report)
Settled at the rear, switched out to center track and stayed on well, nearest finish.
Settled behind midfield on the rail, held up early in the straight, quickened well when into the clear, closed on nicely for 4th.
Sat midfield on the rail, ran on along the rail, and made some headway.
Settled midfield 2 wide between horses, only one pace when asked.
Steadied after the start to sit near the rear, had some trouble in the straight, but did closed off okay, best stride late.
Settled in front of midfield, hard ridden at 450M, just limited response.
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide, only able to pass weakened rivals.
Broke a step slow and ridden to be prominent, settled just behind the speed, weakened at 350M.
Broke only fairly but showed good pace to lead, weakened in the straight.
3 wide behind midfield throughout, made no impresion.
Broke slowly and sat outside the lead 3 wide, weakened and faded in the straight.
Settled 3 wide midfield, never a threat.

Began well, taken over 2L back rounding first bend, niggled at in 5th some 3L back over 1100 metres out, switched out passing 600 metres to challenge, ran on under pressure to gain upper hand close to home.

Began fairly, soon picked up handy position, keen at times in back straight, drifted 2L back to 4th approaching home bend, switched 3-wide for a run on top of home bend hitting front 500 metres out, caught close to finish.
Soon took up running attempting to make all, narrowly headed shortly after straightening, unable to sustain effort.
Began awkwardly, settled just off the pace in 4th on the rail, gained 3rd in similar one back position passing 1000 metres, failed to quicken under pressure in home straight.
Settled in rear of the small field over 4L off the pace, gained closer rounding home bend and within 2L of pace into straight, kept on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Settled at the back of the small field, kept on same pace under pressure without quickening.

Prominent and wide early, worked his way forward 3-wide around first bend to join the leaders passing 1400 metres, obtained 2-wide position over 1000 metres out, dropped away quickly after straightening.
Reserved behind midfield, had to wait for an opening early straight, closed off strongly when a gap opened up mid-straight, shot clear 100M, shifted out abruptly 50M when well in control.
Settled 3-wide towards the rear, wide into straight, finished off strongly down the outside but not getting to winner.
From wide draw dropped back to a rearward spot, niggled along 500M, closed off well final 300M, got up for 3rd near line.
Held up in midfield along the 3-path, quickened up well passing 400M, hit lead 200M, out-finished final 100M.
Caught wide early, left with no cover 1200M, moved up to press leader on outside, challenged for the lead early straight, not finishing pace of first 4 final stages.
Reserved in midfield along the fence, held up near 300M and again between 200M and 100M, could have done better.
Chased leaders on inside, put in a mild bid on straightening, no impression on leaders passing 200M.
Always prominent, tracked leader from 1100M, switched 3-wide 600M, challenged for the lead 400M-200M, flattened over final 150M.
Held up behind midfield, caught 3-wide during the race, swung wide for home, stayed on fairly from 400M, not reach leaders.
Settled down 2-wide in midfield, held up early straight, was making his run when bumped by rival 200M losing momentum, kept on same pace closing stages.
From wide draw taken back to race towards the rear, held up along the fence from 350M, not fully tested to the line.
Switched off to race at the rear 8-9Ls off the pace middle stages, kept on fairly turning into straight, never threatened.
Went forward, crossed to the lead 1100M then steadied the pace going into home turn, caught by rivals inside 250M, no extra final stages.
Settled ahead of midfield, caught wide no cover after 800M, moved up to challenge 500M, going one paced passing 250M, badly checked mid-straight, lost momentum.
Bumped start, raced behind midfield on the outside, moved closer after passing 600M, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to score, won by 1/2L.
Began well from a wide draw, raced prominently on the outside, shared lead in the middle stages, ridden after passing 300M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 50M.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced towards rear on the outside, very wide into straight, made good progress in the run home to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out 450M, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, raced at rear, 10 lengths back, closer on turn, very wide into straight, closed off well to be nearest on line.
Away with them, sent forward to take the lead, shared the lead with rival in the middle stages, peaked and headed 300M, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Crowded start, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 8, raced behind midfield on the inside, angled out approaching 500M, no clear run early in straight, made some progress thereafter.
Bumped start, raced in midfield on the outside, very wide into straight, one-paced in the run home.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 9 lengths back turning in, passed some tired runners in straight.
Out with rest, tracked leaders, 2 wide, angled out 550M, peaked early in straight, weakened and eased inside final furlong.
Jumped well, raced 3 wide with cover slightly better than midfield, travelled keenly in the middle stages, crowded near 450M, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, similar position on turn, failed to close off in straight.

Moderately away from the widest draw, unable to slot in, trapped wide in midfield early, moved closer after passing 1400M, positioned 3 wide, a length or so back in the middle stages, peaked on turn, weakened 500M, eased final 350M.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced in midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 500M, no clear run early in straight, cleared 100M, finished off very strongly to score.
Began only fairly, raced better than midfield on the inside, easy run to turn, finished off well to take 2nd, just beaten by a neck.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made very good progress in straight to take a place, just beaten by a neck.
Jumped well from gate 9, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, kept on well in straight, hit the front 75M, unable to hold off the first two close home.
Moderately away from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/2L on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 75M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Away well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide turning in, no clear run in straight, not able to test properly.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover slightly behind midfield, wider turning in, made some progress early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Shifted out abruptly at start, raced 2 wide at rear, angled out 500M, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide towards rear, 3 wide on turn, made some headway in straight.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, no clear run in straight, not able to test properly.
Bumped start, raced in midfield on the outside, no cover for the majority of the race, showed limited response early in straight, no clear run final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Started very slowly, raced at rear throughout, never a threat.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the outside, no cover on turn, made no progress in straight.

Clean jump, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3 lengths on turn, kept on well in straight to hold off the challengers.
Out with rest, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 4 lengths or so back on turn, finished off well to take 2nd.
Jumped with them, positioned on rail in midfield, angled out 400M, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Average to begin, raced in 2nd, 3 lengths or so back on turn, kept on well in straight to make frame without threatening.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, 9 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, wider turning in, finished off evenly.
Commenced well from gate 1, raced 2 wide towards rear, 8 lengths or so back on turn, very wide into straight, made little progress in the run home. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Taken back from gate 10, raced 2 wide at rear, 9 lengths or so back on turn, very wide into straight, made no impression in the run home. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began awkwardly, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened and eased final furlong.
Slow to begin, reserved towards the rear in a race run at good tempo, crept closer 650M, wide into straight, finished off well under top weight to lead 150M, won going away.
Settled ahead of midfield, moved up 450M to challenge, briefly led 200M but not going the pace of winner final stages.
Began well, tracked leaders on inside, ran on steadily to go 3rd 150M out but comfortably beaten by winner.
Switched off to race at the rear about 8Ls off leader, moved closer passing 600M, stayed on without threat.

Went forward but unable to find cover, crossed to the lead 1200M setting good pace, responded only fairly top of straight, faded 200M. (Jockey : instructed to go forward and if possible to obtain cover.)
Caught 3-wide near the rear, 7-8Ls off the good pace, stayed on fairly over final 300M, not reach leaders.
Tracked leader in a race run at good pace, driven along home turn, soon beaten and out of contention.
From draw 9 caught wide no cover chasing leaders, pushed along back-straight, moved up to 2nd home turn, run ended 250M, faded away.
Jumped with them, restrained to a midfield position, failed to pick up turning into straight, never threatened.
Taken back and raced at the rear early and middle stages, came under pressure 600M, failed to make ground in the straight. (Jockey : instructed to ride conservatively from wide draw.)
Held up in mid-division, pushed along 600M to hold its position, not quickened on straightening.
Jumped only fairly, settled behind midfield, never travelled, fell back to last 500M, eased down, finished tailed out. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Broke nicely and settled midfield on the rail, ran on well between horses in the straight, won comfortably.
Settled just behind the speed, kept on well on rail for 2nd.
Settled in front of midfield, closed off okay, held 3rd.
Sat midfield 3 wide early, moved to 2 wide at 600M, and kept on fairly for 4th.
Steadied after the start from a wide barrier to settle last, stayed on okay along the rail.
Tracked leaders, weakened inside 200M.
Hard ridden early to lead, weakened at 250M.
Broke a bit slow, settled worse than midfield on the rail, made no impression.
Settled near the rear, under pressured at 800M and hard ridden soon after, limited response.
Sat near the rear 2 wide, angled out in the straight and never a threat.
Sat worse than midfield 2 wide, never in contention.

Had a nice run in midfield in the clear for the majority. Eased three wide entering last section when just under 4L from the lead before closing strongly to strike the lead in the final 75m & go on to win.
Had a nice run 1,1 from about the 1500m mark. Dashed to the lead at the 150m & looked the winner before over-run in the final 75m, held second.

Crowded at the start before shifting behind runners to race in midfield away from the rail. Was just over 4L from the lead entering last section, swung wide on cornering before closing off strongly down the outside to be close third.
Had a soft run in midfield along the rail throughout. Moved off the rail on cornering, closed off well all the way to the line to be beaten under 2L into 4th.
Steadied & taken back towards the rear. Was near last all the way, entered last section 7L from the lead before making up many late lengths from a long way back to be beaten just over 2L on the line.
Was wide early before improving positon to race outside the leader from the 1500m. Continued close to the lead up until the 150m mark before weakening slightly in final 100m.
Pushed forward to lead. Was headed in the lead by the runner-up near the 175m before giving a few lengths in concluding stages.

Had a soft run on the leaders back throughout. Stayed along the rail in the straight, had some difficulty getting clear running momentarily mid-straight but did little once clear & weakened to be beaten 4.5L into midfield.
Got back to race just worse than midfield away from the rail. Was about 6L from the lead entering last section & made no headway in the straight, beaten a similar margin on the line.
Steadied after the start & taken back to race worse than midfield along the rail. Was hard ridden from the 500m but failed to respond & only held 7L margin in the straight.
Had no early speed as per normal & raced at the tail. Moved wider on the track & was hard ridden near the 850m when trying to improve but it amounted to little & was never in contention.

Raced wide in midfield early before being steadied & taken back to third last passing the winning post first time. Continued near the tail from after half-way, swung wide on straightening but failed to run on & finished last.
Slightly slow out and bumped, raced towards rear on the inside, angled out 400M, made contact 250M, finished off very strongly to score.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, angled out 500M, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to take 2nd. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, raced prominently on the inside, travelled well to turn, hit the front 200M, kept on well but unable to hold off the first two late.
Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead but trapped 3 wide, 2 wide from 600M, led by 1/4L turning in, peaked and headed 200M, ran on evenly to the line.
Began smartly from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear running until final 100M, made some progress thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run until final 50M, made some progress thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, allowed rival to cross 600M, 1 to 2 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Began only fairly, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide towards rear, angled out 400M, made no impression in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, wider turning in, made contact 250M, one-paced thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the outside, 8 lengths or so back on turn, made no impression in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Jumped with the field, settled midfield 2 wide, angled out rounding the Home Turn, closed off well and won smartly.
Broke alertly, settled just behind the leaders, quickened well in the straight despite shifting grounds.
Sat in a box seated position, split horses in the straight, hit the front at 200M, had every chance.
Settled worse than midfield on the rail, took time to respond in the straight and ran out of room at 100M, ran okay. (See Incident Report)
Sat midfield on the rail, angled into the clear in the straight, only one pace.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, closed off only fairly.
Settled near the rear, only able to pass weakened rivals.
Broke well and led, weakened inside 200M. (See Incident Report) (Barrier Manners unacceptable, must trial)
Ridden along from the outside barrier to join the lead, weakened in the straight.
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide, made no impression.
At the rear and never a threat.
Always at the rear, never in contention.
Settled in rear of midfield about 4L off the pace, snuck closer on rail entering home straight, obtained clear run inside 200 metres and quickened well to assert authority close to home.

Moderate start settling just some 2L back in joint 6th on the rail, gained slightly closer onto home bend and switched off heels of tiring race leader on straightening, hit the front over 150 metres out only to be headed late.
Settled towards rear in 10th some 6L off the pace, wide into home straight and responded well under pressure inside final 200 metres, did best work late.
Close up and wide early from a wide draw settling some 3L back in 7th shortly after, slightly further back in 9th into straight, fought on steadily to be nearest at finish, not much room late.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, travelled well back over 11L off the smart pace, finished off the race strongly inside final 150 metres down the centre of the track.
Well there 3-wide most of the way in back straight, shifted one back passing the 700 metres and remaining 3-wide around home bend, lost position making final turn and kept on steadily to the line.
Wide amongst leaders after beginning from a wide draw, taken 2L back 4-wide without cover passing the 700 metres, ran home one-paced.

Prominent 5-wide after beginning from the widest draw, pressed forward to gain narrow advantage briefly amongst leading trio 3-wide passing the 600 metres, unable to sustain effort inside final 150 metres.
Well there and wide early, gradually shifted back to just over 2L off the pace in 6th, baulked for a run early in straight, found no extra inside final 200 metres.
Ridden forward after moderate start, shared pace on rail before gaining slender lead rounding home bend, headed over 150 metres out and folded up quickly.
Driven to soon lead, narrowly headed passing the 600 metres, folded up quickly under pressure upon straightening.
Always well behind, never seen with a chance.
Caught 3-wide early before improving to race one-out-one-back, pressed leader 400M, led 250M, continued on well late to hold off pursuing rivals.
Chased leaders on inside, responded well turning in, challenged winner over final 150M but always held.
Tracked leaders in a steadily run race, had every chance from 350M, fought hard and got up for dead heat 2nd last stride.
From outside draw shifted across behind runners, settled behind midfield along the inside, had difficulty obtaining clear running 150M, did best work late to claim 4th, nearest finish.
Soon led from draw 1, took them along at even tempo, pressed by rival 400M, fought on well under top weight before grudgingly gave way final 100M.
Held up along the fence in midfield, put in a mild bid turning home, always held by leaders in the run to the line.
In mid-division, caught 3-wide no cover during the race, kept on same speed from top of straight, no impression on leaders final 200M.
Unhurried, waited with towards the rear in a steadily run race, swung wide for home, stayed on without threatening.
Held up behind midfield, found less than expected when driven out top of straight, never threatened. (Jockey : raced too keenly with the slow pace and left without a finishing effort.)
Settled at the rear, still 7Ls to make up 400M, gave limited response only. (Jockey : instructed to ride conservatively. Difficult to make up ground from 500M due to slow pace)
From draw 11 eased to race at the back, settled 7Ls off the pace, wide into straight, failed to run on.
Settled in mid-division, left flat-footed turning into straight, soon out of contention, weakened to last.
Average to begin, raced better than midfield on the inside, easy run on turn, showed very good response in straight, hit the front approaching 100M, kept on strongly to the line, easily scored.

Moderately away from gate 9, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed approaching 100M, weakened gradually thereafter, finished 2nd.
Away well, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, wider turning in, bumped near 250M, finished off well to take a place.

Taken back to race behind midfield on the inside, 5 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, angled out 350M, no clear run early in straight, cleared 150M, closed off well to make frame without threatening.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced in midfield on the outside, very wide into straight, made some progress in the run home.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, angled out 300M, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made some progress.
Began well from a wide draw, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, peaked on turn, crowded near 250M, weakened gradually thereafter. (Blood in trachea.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced prominently on the outside, a length back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 7 lengths back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, raced behind midfield on the outside, no cover for the majority of the race, very wide into straight, made no progress in the run home.
Slowly away, raced 2 wide at rear, peaked on turn, eased early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)

Began well from gate 1, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, a bit closer in the middle stages, 2 wide turning in, finished off very strongly to score.
Average to begin, raced in midfield on the inside, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, angled out 550M, closed off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.

Away well, tracked leaders on the inside, 2 wide after passing 600M, hit the front 400M, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 150M, ran on evenly to the line. (Lame right front leg next day morning.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the inside, slightly improved along the rail on turn, angled out early in straight, made some progress thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide towards rear, angled out 450M, passed some tired runners in straight.
Moderately away from the widest draw, raced at tail, hard ridden after passing 500M, made good progress early in straight, no extra final 150M.
Taken back from gate 10, raced at rear on the outside, commenced move 500M, very wide into straight, made some progress early in straight, peaked 200M, ran on evenly to the line. (Roarer.)
Began well, raced prominently on the outside, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Taken back to race 3 wide towards rear, 4 wide turning in, made no impression in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the outside, moved closer on turn, very wide into straight, made no impression in the run home.
Began well from a wide draw, raced 2 wide in midfield, unable to maintain position on turn, showed nothing in straight.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, wider turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Out with rest, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide from 850M, moved a bit closer after passing 700M, wider turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, challenged by rivals turning in, peaked and headed 400M, weakened 250M, eased final furlong.
Well there from a wide draw, held narrow advantage rounding home bend, drew clear under pressure inside final 300 metres.
Well there early from a wide draw, drifted back to 2L 6th before re-gaining closer position to 5th 4-wide onto home bend, fought on steadily from similar position into straight, never threatening.
Wide in last few travelling keenly around home bend, one of the widest entering straight, ran on steadily without threatening.
Moderate start and soon dropped to last few, trailed the field onto home bend, ran on inside final 200 metres to be nearest at finish.
Always prominent, one-out-one-back rounding home bend, jostled between runners when keen about 550 metres out, unable to quicken under pressure to threaten in straight.
Began fairly, soon recovered to one back position on rail, baulked in similar position turning into straight, unable to quicken under pressure.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, soon taken across for rails run trailing at the back, improved to 11th onto home bend 900 metres out, steadied for a run 250 metres out, kept on steadily to the line.

Began well from a wide draw, soon taken back behind midfield wide without cover in back straight, drifted to last over 500 metres out, fought on steadily without quickening down centre of home straight. (Tactic questioned)
Settled some 2L back in 6th, in similar position into straight, soon faded. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Slowly away, soon recovered to midfield along the rail some 3L back, saved ground turning for home, one-paced under pressure.
Soon dropped behind midfield, lost position when crowded 950 metres out, ran home one-paced under pressure. (Jockey reported racing keenly early and middle stages.)
Held narrow advantage 4-wide onto first corner, shared pace 2-wide around home bend, folded up quickly inside final 300 metres.
Travelled wide in midfield, found nothing under pressure in straight.
Settled midfield on the rail, travelled comfortably, tracked the leaders at 400M, quickened well at the final 150M to win.
Jumped only fairly, sat towards rear, kept on well, no clear run final 150M, not quite able to challenge. (See Incident Report)
Ridden hard to lead, stayed on okay for 3rd.
Sat towards rear on the rail, began to improve inside 250M, just limited response.
Settled behind midfield 2 wide, switched out at the Straight, but only one pace.
Slow to begin, sat rear, and made no impression. (Bled)
Ridden hard to chase the lead 2 wide until 500M, faded quickly at 200M.
Sat handy on the rail, chased the leader throughout, and weakened at 250M.
Pushed forward from second widest gate & got nice run in third away from the rail throughout. Moved to the lead approaching the 250m mark & had enough up sleeve to win by 0.75L.
Had a nice run in midfield away from the rail. Was ridden up from the 550m, made continual ground to move to second near the 200m & finished off well but fell 0.75L short on line.

Crossed soon after start & was then crowded & steadied near the 1100m & raced a clear last. Was over 6L behind entering last section before closing off strongly between runners to charge to fast finishing third, see report.
Had a nice run in midfield away from the rail. Entered last section just over 3L from the lead before shifting outwards at the 350m & then closing off steadily in final stages.

Outpaced after start & raced 3rd last between runners. Shifted outwards passing the 500m, was the second widest on straightening when just under 6L behind before making some late headway down the outside from a long way back.
Had a soft run in midfield along the rail throughout. Entered last section only 2.5L from the lead before finishing off only steadily to the line to be beaten 3L into midfield.

Ridden along at start to hold position when racing just worse than midfield along rail. Moved away from the inside on straightening when about 4.5L behind before finishing off only moderately to midfield without threatening.

Had a soft run in midfield along the rail. Stayed along rail on straightening when 3.5L behind, was held up near the 300m & again between 150m & 100m when having something to offer before race passed by final 100m, excuse.

Improved between runners after the first furlong to race just worse than midfield. Was steadied & raced keenly when close to heels near 600m, moved into clear running on straightening, one paced in straight & was no threat.

Got back after the start & raced second last along the rail. Continued near the rear & about 6L from the lead on straightening before making no headway into deficit in the run to the line. Well beaten.

Showed early speed to lead but was unable to cross to the rail. Was joined & shared the lead from the 500m, passed by the winner approaching the 250m mark before weakening quickly in last 150m to be well beaten.
Was trapped racing three wide without cover in midfield throughout. Began losing ground from before straightening & gave a further few lengths in the straight to be well beaten.

Showed customary speed after the start & raced second when holding the rail position. Went through to share the lead form the 500m mark, was beaten early in the straight & weakened to long second last.

Had no speed early & allowed to drift back from the outside gate to race near the tail when three wide with cover. Forced 4 wide passing the 600m, was the widest on cornering before weakening badly to long last in straight.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, took the lead 300M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Made contact at start, sent forward to race prominently on the inside, took the lead 900M, travelled well to turn, headed 300M, kept on well to take 2nd.
Shifted out at start and made contact, raced 3 wide behind midfield, a bit closer on turn, finished off well to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Jumped with them, raced prominently but trapped 4 wide early, found a 2 wide spot near 650M, 1 to 2 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Bumped start, tracked leaders on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Moderately away, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on same pace in straight.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 to 6 lengths back turning in, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 10, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Inconvenienced at start, sent forward to race prominently on the outside, 3 wide on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.

Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently but trapped very wide, unable to maintain position from 1000M, dropped towards rear in the middle stages, eased final 450M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Broke nicely and ridden along to be prominent, settled just behind the speed, ran on well along the rail, kicked clear and won easily.
Settled near the rear on the rail, improved along the rail in the straight, made good progress to grab 2nd. (See Incident Report)
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide between horses, got hampered at 400M when angling out, and stayed on well.
Up with the pace, kept on fairly well for 4th.
Settled midfield 2 wide, lay in under pressure at 300M, only one pace afterwards. (See Incident Report)
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, did not quickened well enough when asked.
Sat at the rear, stayed on fairly.
Settled midfield on the rail, made minor progress in the straight.
Showed good early speed to lead, weakened inside 200M. (Rider dropped his rein)
Sat in front of midfield on the rail, slightly held up in the middle part of the straight, never impress.
Tracked leaders, weakened inside 250M.
Caught 3 wide no cover, weakened in the straight.
Steadied after the start to settle near the rear, never a threat. (See Incident Report)
Caught wide near the rear throughout, never in contention.
Began well from the one draw settling one back off the pace on rail, obtained a run inside 300 metres, fought on steadily under pressure to just get up on line.
Jumped awkwardly settling one from last in 8th on rail, forced to switch for a run over 150 metres out and fought on well to the line. (Tactic in straight questioned)
Settled just over 2L off the pace in 5th near mid-division of small field, shifted wide for a run entering home straight, fought on under pressure to hold every chance throughout.

Travelled mainly 3-wide prominently, not far off in 4th most of way in back straight, commenced move wide rounding home bend hitting front briefly inside 300 metres, unable to sustain effort closing stages.

Travelled keenly in rear of midfield in 6th on rail, unbalanced for a stride 700 metres out, came to challenge under pressure in straight, badly hampered inside 200 metres, fought back well closing stages.
Travelled wide towards rear of small field in 7th, in similar position turning into home straight, fought on under pressure past well-beaten horses.
Trailed the field most of way, ran past well-beaten horses closing stages.
Pressed forward from the widest gate to reach 2nd 2-wide approaching back straight, found no extra from similar position into home straight.
Soon took up running, obtained rails run approaching back straight and held narrow lead until headed inside 300 metres. (Mucus)
Moved to the front 1500M, allowed uncontested lead at a slow tempo, opened up 2L lead mid-straight, kept on well to the line.
Held up 2-wide behind mid-division, picked up well passing 300M under top weight, made good gains late to finish nearest at the line.
Jumped awkwardly, moved up to track leader in a slowly run race, tried hard but couldn't get closer to winner in the run home, held on 3rd at the line.
Led early before easing off to race behind leader, fought on steadily in the straight but never going the pace to challenge winner.
Dropped back after the start, waited with near last, had difficulty obtaining clear running 400M-200M, did best work late.
Settled midfield along the 2-path, 4Ls off leader in a slowly run race, fought on one paced when driven out in straight, claimed 6th in a blanket finish for minor placings.
Held up in mid-division, saved ground on inside, moved up to 4th mid-straight, held ground final stages.
Restrained to the rear for cover 9Ls off the pace, made limited progress final 400M. (Jockey was told he had made an error of judgement by continuing to restrain his horse when pace was slow.)
Began awkwardly, restrained to race near the rear in a slowly run race, responded fairly from 400M, never dangerous.
Tracked leaders in a slowly run race, driven 500M out, couldn't finish off.
Settled behind midfield, 5Ls to make up 400M, not quickened on straightening, never reach contention.
Jumped well, raced better than midfield on the outside, moved a bit closer on turn, finished off very strongly to score by a neck.
Jumped with them, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner on line.
Began smartly, sent forward to race prominently on the outside, there to turn, kept on well in straight to take a place, always held.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, found rail approaching 700M, angled out 450M, closed off well to make frame without threatening.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out 500M, finished off evenly.
Jumped awkwardly, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the outside, 7 lengths back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Slowly away, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, wider on turn, made no impression in straight.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced at rear on the outside, 6 lengths back on turn, made no progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, raced 2 wide towards rear, 5 lengths or so back on turn, made no progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the inside, 5 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Commenced well, positioned 1 out 1 back, unable to maintain position 500M, weakened gradually in straight, eased final 150M.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide better than midfield, similar position on turn, showed good response in straight, hit the front 150M, kept on well to the line.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out early in straight, finished off well to take 2nd, nearest finish. (See Racing Incidents.)
Crowded start, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Out with rest, raced 2 wide towards rear, 6 lengths or so back, there to turn, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to make frame.
Shifted out at start and made contact, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 6 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Inconvenienced at start, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, very wide into straight, made good progress in the run home without threatening.
Away well, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared 300M, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently on the inside, took the lead 1100M, led by a length turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, weakened gradually final 100M.
Slowly away, raced in midfield on the inside, 3 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared 250M, finished off evenly.
Made contact at start, raced 3 wide with cover, 4 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, finished off evenly.
Made contact at start, sent forward to take the early lead, headed 1100M, a length back on turn, bumped early in straight, showed limited response thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover slightly better than midfield, wider 500M, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong. (Mucus.)

Moderately away from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, travelled keenly in the early stages, saved ground on turn, bumped early in straight, peaked 300M, weakened inside final furlong.
Moderately away from a wide draw, tracked leaders on the outside, no cover throughout, weakened early in straight when hard run took toll.

Jumped with them, raced slightly better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off very strongly to score.
Away well, raced prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, kept on well in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.

Away with them, raced 3 wide better than midfield in the early stages, sent forward after passing 900M, took the lead 800M, led by 1/4L turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 100M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, similar position on turn, made some headway in straight to make frame, no threat to the first few. (See Racing Incidents.)
Out with rest, raced 2 wide behind midfield, found rail near 550M, saved ground on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Bumped start, took the early lead, headed approaching 800M, sat right behind the leader on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to 100M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped well, raced in midfield on the outside, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 3 wide towards rear, 2 wide from 600M, 6 lengths back turning in, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide better than midfield, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 8 to 9 lengths back on turn, made no impression in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Bumped start, raced towards rear on the inside, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.

Showed dazzling early speed to come across the face of the field from gate 10 to lead. Held around a 2L advantage at half-way, continued clear of rivals in the straight & held off late closers in fast time.

Slightly outpaced after the start & raced worse than midfield on the rail. Moved away from the rail & into clear running on straightening before finishing strongly in late stages to move to fast finishing second late.
Pushed forward before getting nice position 1,1 from the first bend. Battled on well all the way to the line to only be beaten 1.25L into third.
Raced third along the rail after being crossed by the leader. Stayed along the inside on straightening, was hard ridden but only battled on for well beaten fourth (blood in trachea post-race).
Pushed forward but didn't have the speed of the leader. Raced second, and about 2L behind around the bend. Battled on before peaking on run passing the 150m, passed for minor money in last 100m.
Drifted back after start & raced third last away from the rail. Was a fair way behind on straightening before making significant late ground to run onto midfield from a long way back.

Outpaced after the start & raced worse than midfield between runners. Was just under 4L behind approaching the corner, shifted second widest before making some headway when running onto non-threatening midfield finish.

Outpaced after the start & niggled along down the back straight to hold position second last along rail. Stayed along the rail on straightening before passing one or two tiring rivals late (mucus in trachea, lame next day).
Raced in midfield away from the rail throughout. Was 5L behind approaching the corner before doing little in the straight & weakening to be beaten 6L.
Raced in midfield along the rail throughout. Was just over 5L from the lead entering last section but came under pressure early in the straight & weakened to be third last.

Steadied after the start & taken back to race at the tail. Was ridden along to hold position approaching the first bend, was 9.5L from the lead when continuing last at the 400m before doing little in the straight.
Was trapped racing three wide without cover when worse than midfield. Was over 6L from the lead at the 400m, was forced very wide on cornering before weakening to long last in the straight.
Jumped from a wide draw, sat behind midfield on the rail, stayed on well, began to improve inside 300M and closed off strongly.
Settled midfield, angled out at 100M, finished off well to take 2nd, but not quite able to challenge (See Incident Report).
Ridden hard to track the lead 2 wide, kept on okay, made some progress at 150M (See Incident Report).
Settled handy on the rail, took time to response inside 250M, had every chance.
Showed good early speed to lead, weakened in the early part of the Straight.
Ridden along to chase the lead 2 wide, kept on pace, only limited response.
Sat behind midfield, switched out to 3 wide to improve rounding the Home Turn, made minor progress in the Straight.
Settled rear until 1100M, kept on fairly, just one pace.
Sat worse than midfield 2 wide, crowded and steadied at the early Straight, not able to be fully tested (Lame left hind).
Settled midfield 2 wide, travelled well until 400M, weakened thereafter.
Sat rear, never in contention
Settled in front of midfield 3 wide no cover, improved track the leader, faded out at the Straight.

Veered inwards & bumped before striding forward from widest gate to take lead at winning-post first time. Crossed to rail when leading at 1200m, was just over a length clear of rivals on straightening & dug deep late to win.

Raced along rail on first bend before shifting into 1,1 position near the 1100m. Eased wider to improve near 450m, was 2.5L behind at 400m mark, closed strongly in final stages but couldn't get to leader.

Raced midfield along rail early before being shuffled further back after half-way. Moved off rail near 450m, entered last section under 4L behind, raced in restricted room momentarily near 200m before closing strongly late.

Bumped at start before being steadied & taken back to race second last. Continued rearward on straightening before closing strongly down the outside in the final stages to move to fast finishing 4th late.

Badly crowded at start & consequently lost ground before shifting down to the rail when racing last. Continued last & over 6L behind on cornering before making significant late ground from a long way back, beaten under 2L.

Led early before being crossed & racing on the leaders back from the 1200m. Continued along the rail following leader in middle stages. Stayed near inside in straight but weakened in the last furlong (blood in trachea).
Raced in midfield along the rail throughout. Entered last section 3L form the lead, stayed along rail in straight but could only maintain deficit all the way to the line.

Taken rearward after start but was then trapped three wide without cover from the 1000m. Commenced to improve around the field down back straight, moved to second at 400m before wide passage took its toll in final 250m.

Steadied early before racing in midfield away from the rail. Shifted wider on the track around the 650m bend, was very wide on cornering when continuing in second half, never really ran on in final stages.
Improved position after the start & settled second away from the rail from the 1000m. Came under pressure near the 450m mark before weakening out in the final 250m & was beaten 5.5L.
Raced in midfield away from the rail throughout. Moved into the three wide line passing the 600m, was forced wide on cornering before doing nothing in the straight & weakening to long second last.

Steadied as gates opened & was taken across behind runners to race worse than midfield along rail. Was relegated to second last near 750m, came under hard riding near the 500m mark & weakened to finish a long last (bled).
Began well, sent forward to race in 2nd, travelled well to turn, hit the front 200M, kept on well to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Commenced well, raced better than midfield on the inside, moved closer along the rail on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off well to take 2nd.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced slightly behind midfield on the outside, moved a bit closer after passing 600M, 3 lengths back turning in, finished off strongly to take a place, nearest on line.
Away well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, closed off well to make frame without threatening.
Reared just before stalls opened and started slowly, raced 2 wide towards rear, 3 wide on turn, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line. (Roarer.)
Taken back from gate 11, raced at rear on the outside, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, very wide into straight, made some progress in the run home.
Bumped start, raced in midfield on the outside, moved a bit closer after passing 600M, no cover throughout, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped well from gate 9, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L, peaked and headed 200M, weakened thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, 3-1/2L back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened inside final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began awkwardly, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, one-paced in straight.

Slightly slow out, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (Lame left front leg.) (Sustained an injury to the left front fetlock next day.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Broke well and ridden to be prominent, slotted into a position behind the leaders, travelled comfortably throughout, angled out in the straight, quickened well, battled on gamely and won.
Broke smartly, showed good early speed to lead, kept on well and fought on for 2nd.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, split horses in the straight and closed off well, just lost 2nd on the line.
Settled midfield on the rail, stayed on well.
Steadied from the outside barrier to settle at the rear, showed a strong dash early in the straight, only one pace after 100M.
Taken back near the rear from a wide barrier, stayed on okay.
Broke nicely and sat up with the pace, unable to quicken in the straight. (See Incident Report)
Settled near the rear 2 wide, made some late headway.
Settled in a box seated positon, weakened inside 150M.
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide, made no impression.
Settled midfield 2 wide, never a threat.
3 wide no cover throughout, weakened and faded in the straight.
Settled one back on the rail, saved ground turning for home, hit the front under pressure inside the 100 metres, won readily.

Ridden forward from a wide draw to lead 2-wide passing the 900 metres, narrowly headed inside the 600 metres but re-gained lead briefly 250 metres out, unable to sustain effort and headed again 100 metres out.
Settled towards rear in 10th, saved ground turning for home, ran on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground remaining well behind, switched wide for a run rounding home bend and the widest at the back into straight, ran on well down the centre of the track.
Ridden and wide in first few, gradually drifted over 2L back to 5th early in back straight remaining wide without cover, lost position entering home straight and kept on one pace without quickening.
Moderate start, trailed the field to 150 metres, produced good late impression closing stages.
Began well from the one draw to lead early, ceded advantage passing the 900 metres before re-gaining lead 600 metres out, headed again by eventual runner-up and soon faded.
Travelled keenly mainly in midfield on the rail, snuck closer rounding home bend before briefly baulked entering straight, one-paced under pressure in the run to the line.
Settled 2-wide in midfield in 7th, came under pressure rounding home bend shifting wider into straight, kept on same pace without quickening.
Settled towards rear in 9th on rail, baulked for a run entering home straight at 350 metres, unable to sustain effort inside final 200 metres.
Began well from the widest draw, wide in prominent position before taken back to midfield early in back straight, remained wide throughout running wider into straight, made no further impression.
Well there before settling one out one back in 4th, in similar position into straight and soon weakened.
Reserved at the rear, 7Ls to make up 400M, finished determinedly through final 300M, got up close home for 5th win of the season.
Positively ridden from draw 11, crossed to race behind leader, led from 250M, continued on willingly to the line only to be caught by winner late.
Settled down midfield, pushed to a 3-wide position without cover after 800M, wide into straight, closed off well over final 300M, narrowly missed 2nd.
In 4th spot never far off from the pace, kept on steadily along the fence in the straight but always held by leaders.
Restrained in midfield along the 2-path, swung wide for home, tried hard on straightening but couldn't threaten first three over final 100M.
Jumped only fairly, held up towards the rear, stayed on mildly over final 300M, not reach leaders.
Unhurried after the start, was steadied 800M and shuffled back to near the rear, swung wide for home but lacked a rally thereafter, never threatened.
Went forward from wide draw, crossed to track leaders in 3rd on settling, responded well on straightening initially before flattening over final 150M.
Held up behind midfield, kept on fairly turning into straight, never going the pace to challenge.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners early stages, settled at the back 8-9Ls back, gave limited response on straightening, never involved.
Moved up to lead passing 1100M setting good pace, headed 250M, soon no extra and weakened to finish near last.
Away well, close up behind leaders early stages, checked 800M and shuffled back to midfield, came up empty on straightening, soon out of contention.
Began well from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, easy run to turn, finished off strongly to score.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, closed off well to take 2nd.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, very wide into straight, finished off well to take a place, nearest on line.
Clean jump, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, 3/4L back on turn, kept on well in straight to make frame, always held.
Began smartly from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 50M, weakened thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, 4 to 5 lengths back, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Made contact at start, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 4 lengths back, same margin back on turn, very wide into straight, made good progress in the run home.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 2 wide in midfield, difficult to settle in the early stages, 3 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Slightly slow out and inconvenienced, raced behind midfield on the inside, 4 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, ran on evenly thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear, 6 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, made some progress in the run home.
Made contact at start, raced better than midfield on the outside, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, same margin back on turn, showed some response early in straight, no clear run near 100M, eased thereafter.
