Bumped shortly after start, positioned on rail slightly better than midfield, 2 wide turning in, finished off strongly to score by a neck.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 2 wide behind midfield, commenced move 550M, very wide turning in, finished off well to take 2nd, always just held.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, angled out 500M, finished off strongly to take a place.

Away with them, raced better than midfield on the inside, travelled keenly in the early stages, sat right behind the leader on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared 250M, closed off well to make frame, always held.
Began well, tracked leaders on the outside, 3 wide turning in, took the lead near 200M, peaked and headed 150M, weakened gradually final 50M.
Made contact at start, taken back to race 2 wide towards rear, angled out 500M, no clear run early in straight, cleared 150M, made minor progress thereafter.
Inconvenienced shortly after start, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some progress early in straight, not enough room 250M to 150M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out 500M, made some headway early in straight, peaked on run 200M, kept on evenly to the line.
Made contact at start, raced at rear on the outside, very wide into straight, made some progress early in straight, no extra final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped shortly after start, raced slightly behind midfield on the outside, similar position on turn, made no progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began smartly, raced prominently on the outside, there to turn, took the lead 300M, peaked and headed 200M, weakened thereafter. (Bled.)
Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked early in straight, headed near 250M, weakened final furlong.
Crowded start, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Began well from a wide draw, raced better than midfield on the outside, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 250M, eased thereafter. (Bled.)
Began well to be up with early leaders before sitting back to race ahead of midfield, quickened up smoothly to lead 250M, continued on well to the line for a comfortable win.
Jumped only fairly, soon taken across behind runners and settled in a 2-wide spot towards the rear, made good progress from 350M, got up for 2nd near 50M, held by winner final stages.
Chased leaders, had every chance turning home, not finishing pace of winner mid-straight, hung on for 2nd until near 50M.
Settled ahead of midfield, brought wide to challenge 350M, stayed on mildly for non-threatening 4th.
Hard driven out the gate, moved up to press leader on outside, hung out throughout the majority of race, kept on same pace in the straight. (Racing manners unacceptable.)
Tracked leaders, checked 350M when going for a narrow passage, inclined to shift ground when placed under pressure and failed to make up ground after. (Jockey expressed concern with its action.)
In midfield but unable to slot in, no closer than 3-wide throughout, ran on fairly passing 400M, never a serious threat.
Jumped only fairly, took up a midfield position along the 2-path, driven along 450M but never going the pace to challenge leaders.
Worked to the lead, set pace from 900M while under pressure from a rival on outside, lacked further response after being headed 300M, weakened towards the line.
From widest draw dropped back to race at the back, had no clear running early straight, ran on fairly when switched out passing 300M. No threat on leaders.
Began awkwardly, obtained running in midfield, pushed along 500M but failed to reach contention.
Unhurried after the start, dropped back to race at the rear, became detached passing 800M, didn't respond to urging, never in the picture.
Broke nicely, settled midfield, 3 off the stand's rail, began to improve inside 250M, responded well to win.
Sat towards rear, travelled smoothly, quickened well at 250M for 2nd.
Sat handy, chased the leader throughout until weakened at 150M, held 3rd.
Travelled strongly to lead 3 off the stand's rail until 450M, made minor progress in the Straight.
Sat towards rear, was crowded and held up at 250M, could not be fully tested (See Incident Report).
Ridden hard to sit handy, center of the track, limited response in the Straight.
Settled behind midfield, 4-off the stand's rail, just one pace. (See Incident Report).
Sat in front of midfield, center of the track, never a threat.
Jumped only fairly, sat midfield 2-off the stand's rail, weakened inside 200M. (See Incident Report) (Performance unacceptable, must trial)
Ridden along to track the leader, faded quickly at 400M.
Slow to begin, angled out at 550M, no impression.
Pushed forward to lead. Set only moderate sections in front, kicked strongly all the way down the straight & went on to win by over a length.

Drifted back & shared last place when racing away from the rail. Continued rearward, shifted to be the widest runner on straightening when 5L from the lead before finishing strongly down the outside to move to second late.
Raced just worse than midfield, three wide with cover before moving 4 wide with cover from 650m. Dashed well mid-straight & looked winning threat before finishing steadily in last 100m to be third.
Pushed forward before racing outside the leader. Was only half a length from the lead on straightening, tried hard but couldn't challenge the leader in the last 100m, caught for a minor placing late.

Bumped at start before racing in midfield between runners. Entered last section 2.25L behind, raced tight & was close to heels mid-straight, was steadied near 150m & not fully tested last 100m, not beaten far & had excuse.
Got nice position 1,1 after start. Eased three wide passing the 600m, was only 1L from the lead on straightening, peaked at the 100m before weakening a bit late.
Raced third along the rail for the majority. Straightened only 1.25L form the lead, stayed along the rail in the straight but only battled, weakening to be beaten 3L into midfield.

Raced in midfield along the rail throughout. Straightened only 2.25L from the lead in a compacted field, raced tight & had limited room for the majority of the straight & went to the line without being tested.

Slow to begin & was shifted behind runners, racing second last early & then third last along the rail. Straightened just under 4L from the lead before finishing off steadily when not much room in final stages.

Was slow to begin & then shifted across behind runners from outside barrier to race at the tail. Continued at the tail on straightening when 5.5L form the lead before passing few tiring rivals when finishing off along the rail.

Bumped at the start before racing worse than midfield between runners. Was 4.5L from the lead on straightening, shifted outwards near 350m before doing little thereafter & proving no threat when finishing eleventh.

Drifted back & raced worse than midfield when three wide with cover. Was ridden along on straightening when 4.5L from the lead before doing little in the straight & beating only two rivals home (lame next day).

Was trapped racing four wide without cover in midfield throughout. Moved closer to the led when improving after the 700m, straightened only 1L from lead before wide run took its toll & weakened out quickly final 250m.

Raced three wide in midfield but was left without cover in that position from about the 1100m. Was just over 3L from the lead on straightening but weakened out in the straight after wide passage & was last.
Moderately away, raced in midfield on the outside, moved a bit closer on turn, showed good response in straight, hit the front 250M, kept on well to hold off the challengers late.
Began fairly, raced at rear on the outside, very wide turning in, finished off strongly to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Jumped well from gate 13, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 wide turning in, closed off well to take a place, always just held.
Began only fairly, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off well to make frame, always just held.

Began well from a wide draw, raced behind midfield on the outside, no cover in the early stages, found rail near 800M, very wide turning in, kept on well in straight, not quite able to challenge. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slowly away, raced 2 wide at rear, 3-1/2L back turning in, not enough room early in straight, finished off well to be nearest on line.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared 300M, made good progress thereafter to be nearest on line.
Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, travelled well on turn, peaked early in straight, headed 250M, weakened gradually final 150M.
Began only fairly, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened thereafter.
Moderately away, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on the inside, saved ground throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced in midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 650M, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Jumped well, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Began well from gate 1, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, 3 wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Broke well from the inside barrier, ridden along and showed great early speed, moved across to the stands' rail, broke the field apart and opened a sizeable lead, kept on well and won easing down.
Broke nicely, settled midfield on the stands' rail, switched to the inside for clear running, ran on okay for 2nd.
Slow away and moved towards the stands' rail, settled near the rear, kept improving on the stands' side, closed off okay.
Settled worse than midfield 5 from the stands' rail, moved to center track to improve, made good progress.
Up with the race on the stands' rail, travelled strongly until 300M, only one pace when asked. (See Incident Report)
Settled worse than midfield 3 from the stands' rail, made some progress.
Settled in front of midfield 3 from the stands' rail, hard ridden at 550M, made no impression.
Settled near the rear, made some late headway.
Settled at the rear 4 off the stands' rail, switched to center track to improve, showed some dash at 250M but weakened in the final 50M.
Raced with the leading group, weakened at 200M. (See Incident Report) (Racing Manner unacceptable, must trial amongst runner)
Sat in front of midfield 4 from the stands' side, weakened and faded at 250M.

Fractious in barrier, jumped okay, raced prominently, weakened at 200M and faded. (See Incident Report) (Roarer) (Mucus in Trachea) (Minor laceration to the tongue) (Barrier Manners and Performance unacceptable, must trial)
Settled midfield 2 off the stands' rail, never a threat. (Lame right front leg the next morning)
Broke slowly, never in contention.
Soon took up running setting a sedate pace early stages, held over 2L advantage most of the way in straight, won comfortably.
Jumped awkwardly settling one from last in 8th on rail, not much room behind runners early in straight, responded well inside 200 metres to grab 2nd over 50 metres out.
Well there on rail before restraining just off the pace in 3rd, remained travelling keenly rounding home bend, baulked for a run early in straight, kept on same pace under pressure.
Close up early before taken some 3L back in 5th, dropped further back to 6th onto home bend, switched 4-wide entering straight, kept on same pace under pressure.
Settled at the back in 9th, widest runner swinging for home, produced good late impression inside final 200 metres.
With leaders 4-wide, obtained one back 2-wide position onto home bend, kept on before fading under pressure inside final 100 metres.
Taken back to 7th from a poor draw, 4 wide rounding home bend and into straight, kept on well under pressure.
Broke well before taken 2L back 2-wide in 4th, 3-wide entering home straight and soon faded under pressure.
Settled in 6th within 3L of pace on rail, steadied for a stride before gaining 5th rounding home bend, briefly baulked early in straight, one-paced when hampered and lost position inside 200 metres.
Showed early speed, crossed to the lead from draw 14, gave good response when urged 300M, drew clear mid-straight, was strongly challenged late, just lasted.
Settled ahead of midfield, never far off 3Ls off the pace, headway on leader from 300M, produced a strong late challenge, just failed.
Held up in midfield along the fence, kept to inside on straightening but not much room from 300M-200M, closed off well late stages to take 3rd. (Jockey questioned re his riding in the straight.)
From wide draw shifted across behind runners, raced behind midfield 5-6Ls off leader middle stages, switched away from fence 450M and finished off the race reasonably well.
From draw 12 slotted into a 2-wide position towards the rear, took a while to get going on straightening, closed off nicely over final 250M.
Urged along to be tracking leader on inside, battled on same pace on straightening, faded final 100M.
Positioned ahead of midfield along the 2-path, had every chance on straightening, kept on same pace final 200M posing no threat to leaders.
Pushed along from draw 11, pressed leader on outside, failed to quicken on straightening, couldn't hold his position from 200M, faded towards the line.
Settled down midfield, 5Ls make up 400M but failed to make progress in the run home, never threatened. (Jockey : inclined to race keenly and found it difficult to make up ground in the straight.)
Fractious in the stalls then began awkwardly, dropped back to race towards the rear, couldn't pick up speed turning home, never involved.
Prominent behind leaders, couldn't go on passing 300M, weakened rapidly.
Jumped fairly, held up 3-wide in midfield, wide into straight, found nothing under top weight, never a factor.
Checked on jumping, ended up racing at the rear, plenty to do top of straight but came up empty. (Blood in trachea.)
In mid-division, unable to slot in, caught 3-wide no cover from 800M, dropped away passing 400M, finished tailed out. (Lame RF leg.)
Clean jump, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4-1/2L back, same margin back on turn, finished off strongly to score.
Taken back to race 2 wide towards rear, 3 wide from 600M, 6 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield early, found rail near 900M, a bit closer in the middle stages, 4 lengths back turning in, closed off well to take a place without threatening.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back turning in, no clear run early in straight, cleared 250M, finished off very strongly to make frame, nearest on line.
Jumped well from gate 12, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, challenged by rival turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, weakened gradually final 50M.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced behind midfield on the outside, very wide turning in, made some headway in straight.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide slightly behind midfield, 2 wide from 900M, 5-1/2L back turning in, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)

Jumped well from the widest draw, raced better than midfield on the outside, moved a bit closer after passing 950M, 2 wide on turn, very difficult to ride in straight, not able to test properly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from gate 1, raced in 2nd, challenged the leader turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Slightly slow out, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, finished off evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 9 lengths back, still well back on turn, passed some tired runners in straight.
Shifted out at start and bumped start, raced slightly better than midfield on the inside, 3 lengths back on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Began only fairly, taken back to race at rear on the inside, 7 lengths back on turn, one-paced in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Away well, raced slightly better than midfield on the inside, saved ground to turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off very strongly to score.
Began well, raced in 3rd, 3 lengths back turning in, finished off strongly to take 2nd without threatening the winner.

Quickly into stride, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, travelled comfortably to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, weakened gradually thereafter, finished 3rd.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide in midfield, 5 lengths or so back, there to turn, made some headway in straight to make frame.
Began fairly from gate 1, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, 6 lengths or so back, saved ground throughout, made some progress in straight.
Away with them, unable to slot in, trapped wide slightly behind midfield in the early stages, found a 2 wide spot near 800M, 7 lengths back turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Moderately away, raced behind midfield on the inside, 8 lengths back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Began well, raced better than midfield on the outside, 4 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Made contact at start, sent forward to race in 2nd, a length back on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong. (Bled.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, still well back on turn, made no impression in straight.
Began awkwardly, raced towards rear on the inside, 9 lengths back turning in, made no impression in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.

Bumped start, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, same position on turn, hit the front 200M, kept on strongly to the line, won by 1-1/4L.
Began well from a tricky gate, trapped 3 wide with no cover in midfield early, 2 wide from 1100M, 3 lengths back turning in, closed off well to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Away well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably in the middle stages, led by 1/2L turning in, peaked and headed 200M, ran on evenly to the line. (Lost left front plate at start.)
Taken back from gate 8, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame, nearest finish.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 2 wide better than midfield, a bit closer on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the outside, 7 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off well to be nearest on line.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Slightly slow out, raced slightly better than midfield on the inside, saved ground to turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Began well from gate 1, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, showed limited response early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped with them, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, one-paced in the run home.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the inside, 8 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made no impression in straight. (Lame right front leg next day morning.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the outside, 6 to 7 lengths back, same margin back turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Settled well behind and waited with, switched widest into straight, ran on well down the centre of the track to assert authority inside 50 metres despite hanging in.

Close up early on rail, gradually drifted back to joint 5th some 4L back early in back straight, gained slightly closer passing the 700 metres and saved ground turning for home, fought on steadily under pressure to be nearest at finish.
Driven forward from a wide gate before settling one back 2 wide, came to challenge under pressure upon straightening but unable to quicken to threaten.
Broke well settling one back in 3rd on rail, came to challenge under pressure rounding home bend, unable to quicken to threaten in straight.
Soon took up running attempting to make all, led until overhauled inside final 50 metres.
Settled in rear of midfield, went wide into home straight, inconvenienced over 100 metres out, produced good late impression closing stages.
Slowly away, soon crossed to the rail at the back before picking up to 9th towards the rear, made up good ground between runners in straight but never threatening.
Settled at the back, gained one closer 700 metres out, saved ground turning for home, ran on steadily without threatening. (Lame next day)
Settled in rear of midfield after moderate start, saved ground turning for home, gradually faded under pressure inside final 150 metres.
Settled in forward of midfield in 5th or 6th, soon weakened under pressure after straightening.
Soon picked up from moderate start to 4th just over 2L off the pace, gradually faded after straightening.
Taken well back from the widest gate, trailed the field into home straight, found nothing. (Tactic questioned)
Jumped okay, settled midfield on the rail, and stayed on well to win.
Broke smartly, travelled smoothly to share the lead until 700M, and ran on evenly thereafter.
Ridden along to sit handy, made some progress inside 200M, but just not quickened enough.
Settled behind midfield, caught wide and made minor progress in the Straight, only one pace after 200M (See Incident Report).
Jumped well, travelled comfortably to share the lead until 700M, and kept on okay.
Jumped only fairly, steadied and sat rear, began to improve inside 600M, just limited response.
Sat towards rear on the rail, showed some dash in the early in the straight and soon difficult to ridden out (See Incident Report).
Sat midfield, made no impression.
Settled in front of midfield 3 wide no cover, ridden hard from 950M to be prominent, weakened at 250M (See Incident Report).
Sat in front of midfield 2 wide, never a threat.
Jumped only fairly, settled behind midfield, weakened inside 150M (substantial amount of blood in the horse's trachea).
Jumped only fairly, caught wide throughout, never in contention.
Had a soft run third on the rail throughout. Had clear running on straightening, closed steadily to strike the lead in the final few strides & won narrowly.

Pushed forward to lead & crossed to rail leaving straight first time. Kicked away from immediate challengers before straightening, continued to hold lead until passed in the final few strides. Just beaten.

Had a soft run in midfield along the rail throughout. Was just under 4L form the lead entering final section, stayed near the inside in straight, closed off steadily all the way to the line & was only beaten half length.

Steadied shortly after the start before racing in midfield along the rail throughout. Was just over 5L from the lead entering final section, shifted outwards mid-straight when making ground before closing well late to only be beaten 2L.

Steadied on jumping & shifted behind runners from the outside gate to race at the tail. Shifted wider near the 500m, was forced very wide on cornering, raced tight on straightening, closed off ok from a long way back.

Began awkwardly before getting back to race worse than midfield away off rail. Moved into the three wide line & improved position from 550m, forced wider on cornering before making some late ground when running onto midfield.

Steadied after start & drifted back to race rearward. Shared last place from the 900m, entered last section 7L from the lead before making same late ground between runners when running onto midfield from a long way behind.

Crowded at the start before getting back to race worse than midfield along the rail. Was just under 7L from the lead entering final section, stayed close to the rail in the straight, only battled away in concluding stages.
Raced in midfield away from the rail throughout. Was 4L form the lead entering final section but could only maintained that margin & was passed by better finishers in the concluding stages.

Obtained a nice position 1,1 from about the 1300m. Shifted outwards sharply to avoid heels near the 450m, entered last section under 3L from lead, emptied shortly after straightening & weakened poorly (bled).

Steadied after start & drifted back to race third last away from the rail. Entered last section with only 3 runners behind & 6L from lead before shifting wide & racing tight on straightening, before doing little in last 250m.

Jumped awkwardly & lost ground before improving position to race second away from the rail in the middle stages. Came under pressure & began losing ground from before cornering, weakened poorly in straight to be last.
Crowded start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to score.
Average to begin, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off well to take 2nd.
Out with rest, raced better than midfield on the outside, 2-1/2L back on turn, closed off well to take a place without threatening.
Bumped start, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made good progress to make frame.
Began awkwardly and made contact, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 100M, headed and weakened 50M.

Began well from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some progress early in straight, raced tight 100M, awkwardly placed in the closing stages. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the outside, 7 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Taken back from the widest draw, 8 lengths or so back on turn, very wide into straight, made good progress in the run home.
Jumped with them, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, a length back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 50M.
Away with them, positioned right behind the leader on the inside, same position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Shifted out at start and made contact, raced in midfield on the outside, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Bumped start, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped on terms, showed no early speed and settled near the rear on the rail, angled out at 350M and closed off strongly to win.
Settled behind the speed on the rail, under pressured at 350M, took the lead at 200M, had every chance.
Steadied after the start to settle at the rear, made good progress near the rail, ran on well. (See Incident Report)
Settled midfield on the rail, held up early in the straight, closed off fairly.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide between horses, under pressured at 650M to keep its position, made some progress late.
Up with the pace, limited response in the straight. (See Incident Report)
Raced ungenerously in the early stages, then caught 3 wide in midfield, made no progress.
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide, made no impression.
Steadied after the start, raced near the rear 2 wide, didn't quickened.
3 wide no cover in front of midfield early, then improved to challenge the lead at 800M, weakened in the straight.
Settled worse than midfield 3 wide after being hampered in the early stages, never a threat. (See Incident Report) (Performance unacceptable, must trial)
Broke well and assumed the lead, weakened and faded quickly in the straight. (See Incident Report)
Broke well settling one out one back, gained slightly closer alongside race leader 900 metres out, hit the front shortly after straightening and soon drew clear, won cosily.
Taken back from a wide draw, made swift progress on the rail to 7th early in back straight, switched wide to challenge turning for home, finished off the race well down the centre of the track.
Soon recovered from poor start along the rail to reach 6th some 5L back into back straight, gained slightly closer to 5th rounding home bend and sustained headway closing stages to snatch 3rd late.
Broke well settling over 3L back in joint 4th early in back straight, gained close to pace over 800 metres out, came under pressure rounding home bend, one-paced straight.
Soon took up running, obtained rails run turning into back straight, headed by eventual winner shortly after straightening and weakened under pressure.
Began well from the one draw settling just off the pace in 3rd, remained similar into home straight, unable to sustain effort inside final 150 metres.
Close up early but travelled somewhat ungenerously and soon drifted back to 8th, ridden along in back straight and the widest of all turning for home, made no further impression.
Taken back to last few from a wide gate, saved ground turning for home, one-paced.
Travelled wide in last place after moderate start, never seen with a chance. (Tactic questioned) (Lame next day)
Ridden along early in joint 4th some 3L back, became 5th in similar position 900 metres out, saved ground on the rail turning for home, soon weakened under pressure.
From draw 1 jumped well to lead early stages before sitting back behind leaders, finished off willingly on straightening to lead inside 150M, well in control over final stages.
Showed speed from draw 3 and vied for command on inside, continued on well under top weight to establish narrow lead 250M, couldn't hold off winner 150M, held on for 2nd just.
Sent forward from outside draw, vied for the lead 2-wide down the back-straight, kept battling turning for home, ceded to first 2 final 150M. Finished clear form rest.

Awkwardly away and lost ground, raced keenly towards the rear, responded fairly when placed under pressure 400M, stayed on to finish a distant 4th. (Jockey : felt something amiss concluding stages. / Roarer.)
From wide draw dropped back off the pace, waited with at the rear until top of straight, closed off mildly over final 300M but never a threat to first three.
Began fairly, moved up to chase leaders from 900M, couldn't keep up with first three top of straight, faded final stages.
Taken across from wide draw, dropped back to the rear 7Ls off the pace, made limited progress on straightening, never a threat to leaders.
Jumped awkwardly and blundered soon after, near the rear and further back than anticipated to avoid racing wide, ran on fairly final 300M, never involved. (Jockey questioned re riding position.)
Positioned ahead of midfield, caught racing wide no cover until 500M, not quickened when pushed along 400M, never reach contention.
Raced keenly in midfield, came under pressure 500M, lacked further response on straightening.
Settled down 3-wide behind midfield, came up empty turning for home, never going the pace to challenge.
Jumped only fairly, raced behind midfield, pushed along 600M to keep up with rivals, soon beaten top of straight. (Mucus.)
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, a bit closer after passing 700M, 2nd on turn, finished off strongly to score by a neck.

Average to begin, raced 3 wide with no cover in midfield early, sent forward 1100M, took the lead 950M, led by a length in the middle stages, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner close home.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide towards rear early, 2 wide behind midfield in the middle stages, very wide turning in, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide in midfield, a bit closer in the middle stages, finished off evenly. (Blood in trachea.)
Made contact at start, raced better than midfield on the inside early, dropped to midfield in the middle stages, 2 wide on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Began fairly, raced towards rear on the inside, commenced move 400M, very wide turning in, made some headway in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths back, a bit closer in the middle stages, 3 wide turning in, finished off evenly.
Jumped well, took the early lead, headed 950M, sat right behind the leader on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Taken back from gate 12, raced at rear, 8 lengths or so back on turn, made minor progress in straight.

Away with them, sent forward to race prominently on the inside, steadied off heels 1000M, raced better than midfield on rail in the middle stages, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final 150M.

Began well from gate 1, positioned in midfield on the inside early, raced behind midfield in the middle stages, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened closing stages.
Moderately away, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.

Began well from a wide draw, raced 2 wide better than midfield early, found rail 700M, angled out 500M, made contact 450M, hard ridden 350M, hit the front 200M, kept on strongly to the line.

Jumped with them, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner. (Sustained a laceration to the right hind leg.)
Crowded start, raced at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back turning in, closed off well to take a place, nearest on line.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3-1/2L back, carried wider 600M, same margin back turning in, finished off well without threatening.
Jumped awkwardly, raced slightly better than midfield on the inside, angled out 600M, made contact 450M, showed good response early in straight, no extra final 150M.

Crowded start, raced towards rear on the outside, 6 lengths or so back, very wide into straight, short of room and slightly inconvenienced near 450M, made some progress in the run home. (Rider dropped whip 100M.)
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out 550M, made minor progress in straight.
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length turning in, peaked and headed 200M, weakened final 150M.
Slightly slow out, raced towards rear, 7 lengths back turning in, made some headway in straight.
Bumped start, raced in midfield on the outside, very wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced at rear on the outside, very wide turning in, made no progress in straight.
Began only fairly, raced towards rear on the inside, 6 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start, sent forward to race prominently on the outside, a length back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final 250M.
Crowded on jumping, raced prominently on the outside in the early stages, found rail 600M, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Pushed forward & improved to lead near the 1100m. Had a pretty soft time in front, kicked well all the way to line to win by a short margin.
Went forward from outside gate before getting lovely position 1,1. Moved up to second approaching the 200m, tried hard all the way but couldn't get to the leader who held a Shd advantage on line.

Raced on the leaders/winners back for the majority. Was awkwardly placed close to the leaders heels near the 300m & again near the 150m when racing tight with second before closing well late to only be beaten 0.75L into 3rd.

Slightly slow to begin & got back to race worse than midfield along the rail. Was just under 6L from the lead on straightening before making good late ground along the inside in final stages to only be beaten 1L into 4th.

Rider was unbalanced on jumping & was then taken back to race 4th last away from rail. Was 5L from the lead on straightening before shifting outwards at the 350m & closing strongly down the outside late to be close behind.

Slow to begin before improving to midfield along rail. Just over 2L from the lead on straightening, held up between 300m & 150m, shifted outwards near 150m before closing off well late stages to be close behind.
Led early before racing second, outside the leader from the 1100m. Continued second until peaking near the 200m, weakened slightly in late stages.
Was trapped racing three wide without cover in midfield throughout. Straightened 3L from the lead before battling on well to be beaten just over 2L after a wide passage throughout.
Raced in midfield away from the rail throughout. Was 3.5L from the lead entering final section, battled away fairly in late stages to only be beaten 2.5L but never really threatened & was 9th.

Got back after the start to race second last away from rail. Shifted wider on the track on straightening when 7L from lead before making some late ground to only be beaten 2.5L but inly beat 4 rivals home in a bunched finish.

Didn't have the early speed of others & raced worse than midfield along the rail before improving in middle stages to race in midfield. Entered last section 4.25L from lead, stayed along rail but never challenged.

Veered outwards & bumped soon after start before improving to be prominent before steadying near the 1200m & racing in midfield from the 1000m mark. Was only 2.5L from lead at 400m weakening out in last 150m.
Was crowded & lost ground soon after the start & raced at the tail. Was over 7L behind on straightening & made no headway & was second last. (Rider questioned  see report).

Was bumped & taken outwards soon after start before steadying & racing just worse than midfield away from the rail. Eased wider on the track passing 500m, was just under 6L behind at 400m but did little & weakened to last.
Sat in front of midfield on the rail, travelled smoothly, under pressured at 200M and quickened well to win.
Broke smartly, ridden along to lead 2 wide, just held 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Settled in front of midfield, made some progress in the Straight, close off okay.
Ridden hard to sat midfield 2 wide, steadied when making the Home Turn, kept on okay over the final 100M.
Sat towards rear 3 wide, angled out in the Straight, and showed some dash inside 100M.
Ridden along throughout to track the leader, remain prominent until 150M, weakened over the final 50M.
Jumped only fairly, settled worse than midfield, was crowded until 150M, and kept on fairly.
Settled towards rear very wide, made no impression.
Jumped nicely, sat handy, only one pace in the Straight.
Settled midfield, unable to obtain clear run throughout the Straight, not fully tested.
Sat rear, held up at the Straight (See Incident Report).
Sat behind midfield, no impression (See Incident Report).
Sat towards rear 2 wide, never in contention.

Placing: FE
Comment: Ridden along to sat midfield 3 wide, crashed the running rail and dislodged its rider near 400M (Bled).
Had a nice run in midfield away from the rail. Moved into the 1,1 position approaching half-way. Moved up to lead near 350m mark, continued on well all the way to the line to win by just over 1L.

Raced in midfield along the rail. Moved away from the rail near the 500m, raced tight on straightening when 1.5L from lead, held up near the 300m before shifting inwards at 225m & finishing well but unable to reel in winner.

Steadied & taken back to race at the tail. Was a clear last on corner, entered last section just under 7L from the lead, shifted to be the widest runner near 350m before making significant late ground to fast finishing 3rd.
Raced in midfield away from the rail throughout. Raced tight on straightening when only 1.5L from the lead before moving to second near the 300m mark before being over-run for third in final strides.

Wasn't ridden after start & was allowed to drift back to race third last. Continued back & wide & was relegated to second last near 700m. Was 5.5L behind on straightening before making steady late ground to not be beaten far.

Was trapped racing three wide in midfield & was left in that position & without cover from about the 1000m mark. Was ridden along approaching the corner, straightened just under 3L from lead before holding similar margin to line.

Steadied & lost ground on jumping before racing worse than midfield early. Improved position to midfield between runners around bend, was held up on straightening, had clear running from 350m but finished moderately late.

Crowded & unbalanced after the start and consequently raced rearward along the rail. Shifted away from the rail on straightening, entered last section just under 5L behind before passing a few tiring rivals late.

Steadied from outside gate & taken back to race second last. Straightened just over 4L from the lead, shifted outwards at 250m & became unbalanced when under pressure before finishing moderately late.
Bumped at the start before racing worse than midfield when three wide with cover. Entered last section just over 4L from the lead before weakening a few lengths in the run to the line.

Obtained a good position in third behind the leading pair. Improved to race on the leaders back from the 650m, briefly held up behind the leader when racing along the rail near the 350m before weakening badly in final 250m.
Pushed forward to lead. Was joined & passed by the winner at the 350m mark before weakening out poorly in the final 250m to be well beaten.
Improved steadily after the start to race in midfield along the rail. Straightened only 3L from the lead but was a beaten horse early in the straight & weakened poorly to long second last
Pushed forward to race outside the leader. Was beaten on straightening & dropped out of contention very quickly & was very long last. No vet abnormalities, must trial.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the early lead, headed approaching 1000M, retook the lead 750M, led by a length turning in, kept on very strongly to the line.
Out in line, raced 2 wide better than midfield, found rail near 700M, angled out 550M, showed good response early in straight, peaked on run 150M, ran on evenly to the line, finished 2nd.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide towards rear, 5 lengths or so back turning in, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Jumped with them, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out 500M, made some progress in straight to make frame.
Out with rest, raced in midfield, 3 lengths or so back turning in, finished off evenly.
Began well from gate 1, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Began only fairly, raced slightly behind midfield on the outside, 4 lengths or so back turning in, made no impression in straight.
Away with them, sent forward to race prominently on the outside, took the lead approaching 1000M, headed 750M, 2nd on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 300M.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, there to turn, made no impression in straight.
Began awkwardly, raced at rear on the inside, 6 lengths back turning in, showed limited response early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Jumped with them, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, allowed rival to cross near 850M, peaked on turn, weakened final 300M.
Broke nicely and settled just behind the leaders, angled out at 400M and ran on well, always doing enough.
Broke slowly and settled worse than midfield on the rail, navigated through traffic and stayed on strongly, always held.
Raced in front of midfield 3 wide with cover, closed of well early in the straight, only one pace afterwards.
Steadied after the start from a wide barrier, sat last early, began to improve near 1200M, went around the field rounding the home turn, stayed on okay.
Settled near the rear, held up early in the straight, switched out to center track, stayed on fairly.
Settled midfield between horses, made little progress.
Up with the pace 3 wide no cover, kept on only fairly.
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide, made no progress
Sat near the rear, made no impression. (Blood in trachea)
Settled midfield 3 wide, did not quickened.
Hard ridden early but showed little speed, raced behind the leaders, weakened in the straight. (See Incident Report)
Showed good early speed to lead, weakened and faded quickly near 200M.
Tracked leaders, under pressured at 650M, no response and faded.
Settled midfield on the rail, ridden along at 600M and gave ground abruptly, eased down near 300M.(Bled and lame right front leg)
Ridden forward before settling one back in 2nd, quickened to hit the front over 200 metres out, won readily.
Soon took up running setting a steady pace, narrowly headed over 200 metres out, unable to peg back the winner closing stages.
Broke well, settled over 2L back in 3rd becoming 4th in a similar position on top of home bend, fought on steadily without threatening in straight.
Jumped awkwardly, settled in last of the small field of 5, soon came to challenge entering straight but never threatening.
Some 3L back in 4th on the rail, gained closer up rounding home bend, soon faded from 1L 3rd into straight.
Dropped back from wide draw, over 10Ls behind early stages before going forward 1200M, in touch at 400M, fought on gamely and wrestled the lead 100M out, narrowly clinched the Derby.
From draw 1 moved forward to track leaders in 3rd, remained close up to home turn, challenged along the inside over final 250M, came close to win the Derby but narrowly denied at the post.
Settled just behind leaders in a slowly run race, loomed top of straight, established narrow lead 200M, dug in late when challenged but couldn't fend off first 2 late, just missed out on Derby glory.
Emerged as leader entering first turn, was allowed to set a very slow pace in the front, challenged by rivals early straight, lost command near 200M but fought on determinedly to hold 4th.
Held up behind midfield, saved ground on inside throughout, kept on mildly on straightening, comfortably held by leaders in the sprint home.
Restrained in mid-division, held up for clear running top of straight, failed to gain ground on leaders over final 200M. (Jockey reminded to ride out to the finish.)
Settled down midfield along the fence, remained close enough to leaders passing 500M, battled on one paced in the straight, always held by first few.
Behind mid-division, raced wide no cover and inclined to race keenly early stages, under pressure from 600M, found less than expected on straightening, closed off the race only fairly.
Always prominent behind leader in a slowly run race, couldn't hold off rivals when race turned into a sprint inside 400M, faded mid-straight.
Jumped awkwardly, restrained in mid-division along the 2-path, waited with until 350M but gave limited response when driven, never going the pace to challenge.
Jumped only fairly, settled behind midfield, raced keenly early stages when pace was slow, unable to go with rivals passing 400M, soon out of contention.
Unhurried after the start, raced keenly towards the rear, taken out to 3-wide spot 1100M, swung wide home turn but came up empty on straightening.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners, held up near last in a slowly run race, failed to finish off when driven out 400M. Never involved.
Dropped back from wide gate, raced keenly at the rear in a slowly run race, driven along 600M and swung wide for home, failed to close off the race.
Bumped start, raced behind midfield on the outside, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly, easily scored.
Average to begin, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, made contact near 1000M, same margin back on turn, finished off well to take 2nd, good debut.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Began only fairly, raced towards rear on the outside, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Began smartly, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, there to turn, kept on well early in straight, no extra final 150M.
Began well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, trapped wide in midfield, a bit closer on turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked on run 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Average to begin, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear run early in straight, kept on same pace thereafter.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened gradually final 100M.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, no clear run in straight, not able to test properly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact at start, raced behind midfield on the outside, very wide turning in, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began awkwardly, raced at rear on the inside, 6 lengths or so back, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, one-paced in straight.
Bumped start, raced at tail, 8 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, very wide into straight, made no impression in the run home.
Jumped with them, raced behind midfield on the inside, travelled keenly in the early and middle stages, angled out 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Out with rest, raced 3 wide, a length or so back, checked near 1000M, no cover on turn, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect. (See Racing Incidents.) (Mucus.)
Moderately away, positioned 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off strongly to score.
Away well, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, there to turn, hit the front 300M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, angled out 650M, 3 wide turning in, hard ridden approaching 250M, finished off evenly.
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced slightly behind midfield on the outside, wide into straight, finished off well to make frame without threatening.
Jumped only fairly, sat right behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked 150M, ran on evenly thereafter.

Made contact with the left side of its barrier on jumping, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths back turning in, no clear run early in straight, cleared approaching 100M, finished off well to be nearest on line.
Began well from a wide draw, raced slightly better than midfield on the outside, no cover for the majority of the race, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Began only fairly, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made some progress.
Taken back from gate 12, raced at rear on the outside, very wide into straight, made some headway in the run home.
Slowly away, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear run in straight.
Commenced well from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, 3 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Began well from gate 9, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/2L turning in, peaked and headed 300M, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced towards rear on the outside, very wide into straight, peaked 300M, weakened and eased final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)

Taken back from gate 9, raced towards rear on the outside, 6 lengths or so back on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off very strongly to score.
Began only fairly and made contact, raced in midfield on the inside, angled out 550M, very wide into straight, hit the front 200M, kept on very well but unable to hold off the winner on line.
Began well from a wide draw, raced 2 wide better than midfield, angled out 400M, showed good response early in straight, peaked 150M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Crowded start, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear run early in straight, cleared approaching 100M, finished off well to make frame.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Made contact at start, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Commenced well from gate 1, raced slightly better than midfield on the inside, 3 lengths back, angled out 400M, raced tight near 200M, no extra final furlong, not clear run final 75M.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, commenced move 500M, very wide into straight, made some progress early in straight, no extra final 150M.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the outside, found rail 450M, last turning in, 8 lengths or so back, no clear run early in straight, cleared 100M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Made contact at start, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, raced tight near 200M, weakened and eased final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well, raced 2 wide in midfield, wider 550M, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, set a fast tempo in the early stages, led by a length in the middle stages, peaked early in straight, headed 250M, weakened thereafter.
Driven forward and soon crossed to the lead, set good pace up front, kicked clear mid-straight, kept on late stages just holding off 2nd.
From draw 1 settled along the fence in midfield, soon into clear top of straight, did best work final 200M, just failed to reel in the long time leader.
Obtained a midfield spot, raced keenly 800M, checked 500M, directed to inside passing 250M to challenge, closed off well for 3rd.
More prominently ridden, tracked leaders on inside, tried hard on straightening but lacked the needed response, inclined to lay in and had to be steadied close home.
Away fast then restrained to find cover behind leaders, switched wide on straightening, closed off moderately without threatening first three.
Failed to muster early speed, caught wide no cover in midfield from wide draw, kept on fairly final 300M., no impression on leaders.
Unhurried after the start, held up towards the rear, gave limited response on straightening, never going the pace to challenge..
Moved up to track leaders, swung wide into straight for his challenge, couldn't go on passing 250M, faded towards the line. (Lame RH leg.)
Fractious in the stalls, dropped back to race near last, raced keenly middle stages, passed tired rivals in the straight, never threatened.
Dropped back to near the rear, gave no response exiting home turn, never involved.
From wide draw moved forward gradually to race outside leader, couldn't sustain run 250M, weakened away.
Began slowly, always at rear, never in the picture.
Jumped okay, showed some early speed to sit handy, kept on well over the final 150M to win.
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide, had trouble obtaining clear running until 100M, and closed off strongly.
Sat in front of midfield on the rail, began to improve inside 400M, kept on okay to hold 3rd.
Settled midfield, showed some response in the Straight, only one paced afterwards (Small laceration to left hind leg).
Sat rear on the rail, travelled smoothly, and stayed on okay.
Settled towards rear 2 wide, had no clear run in the Straight, finished off evenly.
Ridden hard to lead 2 wide, weakened inside 250M.
Ridden along to sit in front of midfield 2 wide, no impression in the Straight.
Sat rear 2 wide, made some ground late.
Settled midfield 3 wide no cover, never a threat.
Settled towards rear on the rail, never in contention.
Battled early for the lead, faded quickly in the straight. (Bled).
Raced in midfield along the rail. Stayed along the rail in straight, had clear running along the inside & closed well to steal the lead in the final stages, going on to win by a neck.
Pushed forward to lead. Held lead all the way until passed by winner along the inside in final stages. Beaten only a neck.
Raced in midfield along the rail. Shifted off the rail near the 400m & raced tight for a short distance before straightening, closed well all the way & was only narrowly beaten into third.

Taken back after the start & raced third last away from the rail. Swung to be the widest runner on cornering when continuing rearward before making significant late ground down the outside to only be beaten 0.75L into fourth.

Raced just worse than midfield away from the rail. Entered last section 4L from lead, held up fleetingly on straightening, got clear passing 300m before finishing off steadily to be beaten 3L, rider questioned (see report).
Pushed forward & raced second away from the rail. Continued second & 1L from the lead on straightening before emptying mid-straight & giving a few lengths to midfield late, beaten 4L on line.
Had a nice run 1,1 for the majority. Peaked on effort soon after straightening & weakened in last furlong to be beaten 4.5L into midfield.

Veered outwards & bumped on jumping before being steadied & taken back to second last along the rail. Had clear running on cornering when just under 7L behind before passing only one or two tiring rivals late. Never likely.
Shifted behind runners after the start & raced 4th last along the rail. Had clear running along the inside in the straight but did little & was beaten 5.5L.
Raced in midfield away from the rail throughout. Eased wider on cornering but weakened in the straight to be beaten 7L.
Raced third along the rail throughout. Was beaten soon after straightening & weakened out quickly in the last furlong to finish a well beaten second last.
Raced at the tail throughout. Came under hard ridding near the 500m before becoming detached near the 400m mark & weakening out to long las (bled).
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably to turn, kept on well in straight to hold off the challengers. (See Racing Incidents.)
Commenced well, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, there to turn, finished off well, always just held.
Knuckled on jumping, raced slightly behind midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to make frame, nearest finish.
Began well, positioned 1-3/4L behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, very wide turning in, finished off evenly.
Slightly slow out and hampered, raced at rear on the inside early, 2 wide from 850M, found rail 550M, kept to inside after straightening and finished off evenly.
Moderately away from the widest draw, raced better than midfield on the outside, 2 lengths or so back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began fairly from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, 3 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Taken back from gate 10, raced towards rear on the outside, 7 lengths back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.

Shifted out at start and bumped, raced behind midfield on the inside, unable to maintain position 800M, last on turn, showed nothing in straight. (Mucus.) (Abnormal respiratory noise.) (Lame left front leg next day.)
Broke okay, settled in front of midfield 2 wide, travelled comfortably throughout, angled out at 500M, quickened well in the straight and won.
Settled midfield 2 wide, closed off well in the straight, no threat to winner. (See Incident Report)
Settled worse than midfield on the rail, stayed on okay for 3rd.
Broke well and ridden along to assume the lead, kept on well early and weakened inside 150M.
Sat just behind the speed, only one pace when asked.
Caught 3 wide no cover into the first turn, improved outside the lead, kept on fairly.
Settled near the rear, made some progress late. (See Incident Report)
Settled close to the pace 2 wide, hard ridden at 400M, limited response.
Broke slowly and settled at the rear, made no impression.
Sat worse than midfield 2 wide, made no progress.
Settled midfield on the rail, never a threat.
Settled near the rear, made a run at 700M, weakened and faded in the straight.

Broke well from the one draw settling just off the pace and becoming some 3L back in 4th passing the 900 metres, remained similar on rail position saving ground turning in, gained upper hand 50 metres out.

Drived forward to lead over 950 metres out after moderate start from a wide draw, travelled keenly in front to straight when shifted ground, came under pressure to hold advantage until headed inside 50 metres.
Prominent from middle draw, became 3rd some 2L back over 900 metres out, went wider into home straight, kept on steadily under pressure without quickening.
Settled in 5th near midfield, gained closer to pace rounding home bend and one of the widest turning in, fought on well down the centre of the track.
Ridden to lead early before taken over 950 metres out, trailed the pacemaker to home straight holding place chance until finding no extra inside final 50 metres.
Soon taken back to midfield in 7th, commenced move rounding home bend to reach within 3L of race leader into straight, kept on same pace.
Slowly away before recovering quickly to 10th, improved steadily down back straight to reach 8th 750 metres out, kept on same pace.
Failed to muster and soon dropped towards rear, came under pressure upon straightening, produced late impression but without threatening.
Settled near midfield in 6th, saved ground turning for home, had no more to give after straightening.
Settled in last from a wide draw, commenced move rounding home bend and went widest into straight, produced some late impression 200 metres out.
Taken back from the widest draw settling wide without cover in worse than midfield, found nothing in home straight.
Jumped awkwardly and tightened dropping well behind, checked on heels passing 600 metres, saved ground turning for home but never seen with a chance.
Settled ahead of mid-division, quickened up well between runners passing 300M, led inside 150M, kept to task final stages holding off late challenge of 2nd and 3rd.
Reserved behind midfield, waited with until passing 300M, closed off well down the outside to be nearest at the finish.
Held up towards the rear in a fast run race, still 6Ls off the pace at 400M, closed off best in the straight, nearest finish.
Reserved in midfield 5-6Ls off the fast pace, did best work final 200M, shifted ground 150M to secure clear running, just missed a minor placing.
Chased leaders in 4th, remained within striking distance home turn, fought on steadily passing 300M, comfortably held by first few final stages.
Tracked leader on outside with pace fast middle stages, driven along from 400M challenging for the lead, out-stayed by rivals final 100M.
Soon led, set fast pace from 1200M, under siege 200M, fought hard until giving way final 100M.
Always prominent behind leader in a fast run race, challenged up the fence from 350M, couldn't get past leaders, no extra final stages.
Settled down 2-wide in midfield, niggled along 450M, lacked a closing response.
From wide draw switched off to race in last 10Ls off the fast pace, swung wide on straightening, found lacking in the home run.
Jumped awkwardly and lost ground, raced towards the rear in a fast run race, struggled to keep up home turn, soon in last place and out of contention.
Began only fairly, raced in midfield on the inside, 6 lengths back on turn, finished off very strongly to score by a neck.
Began well from a wide draw, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, a length back on turn, showed good response in straight, hit the front 150M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner late.
Began smartly, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, angled out 350M, finished off well to take a place, always held.
Away well, raced better than midfield, 4 lengths or so back on turn, made some headway in straight to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Quickly into stride, took the lead easily, led by a length on turn, peaked and headed 150M, weakened gradually final 100M.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, taken wide in straight and made minor progress.
Shifted in at start, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, ran on evenly thereafter.
Taken back to race behind midfield on the inside, 7 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, made little progress in straight.
Made contact shortly after start, raced towards rear on the outside, 8-1/2L back on turn, made little progress in straight.
Made contact shortly after start, raced at rear on the inside, still well back on turn, made some progress early in straight, no clear run final 50M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the inside, 9 lengths back, saved ground on turn, showed limited response in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the outside, 10 lengths back, still well back on turn, made no progress in straight.
