Average to begin, raced towards rear on the inside, 4 lengths back on turn, no daylight early in straight, cleared 200M, showed very good response, hit the front 75M, kept on strongly to the line.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/2L on turn, ridden 250M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 75M, finished 2nd.
Made contact at start, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared 300M, finished off well to take a place.
Began smartly from gate 1, positioned 1-3/4L behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Jumped only fairly, raced at tail, 6 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Bumped start, raced in midfield on the outside, no cover for the majority of the race, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover towards rear, 5 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, passed some tired runners in straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced prominently on the outside, 1/2L back on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 200M, crowded 150M, weakened thereafter.
Began only fairly, raced better than midfield on the outside, 2 wide from 850M, 1-3/4L back on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.

Shifted out on jumping and bumped, raced 2 wide behind midfield, wider turning in, showed limited response early in straight, weakened inside final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.) (Blood in trachea.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the outside, 4 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, raced awkwardly and only showed limited response early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Settled wide in last few, one of the widest turning for home, ran on down the centre of the track to gain upper hand 50 metres out, won cosily.

Settled in midfield in 7th on rail, closer to pace in similar position rounding home bend, baulked briefly upon straightening, responded well to hit the front 170 metres out only to be headed close to home.

Settled 3-wide in rear of midfield, commenced move 500 metres out approaching home turn, hung in and awkwardly placed behind horse in straight until over 300 metres out and then near the 200 metres, finished off the race well.
Ridden forward after moderate start from a wide draw settling some 2L off the pace on the rail, hung in a difficult ride early in straight, found no extra inside 100 metres.

Settled behind midfield on the rail, snuck up to within 3L of pace making home turn, baulked briefly after straightening, responded under pressure inside the 200 metres, made no further impression closing stages.
Slowly away, soon recovered to worse than midfield in 9th, did not find much room early in straight, finished off the race quite well.

Broke well from a wide draw gradually settling one out one back, switched 3 wide in 3rd rounding home bend, drew level under pressure early in straight but unable to sustain effort inside final 250 metres.
Began well from a wide draw but soon taken back to rear for rails run, steadied on heels 800 metres out, saved ground turning for home, fought on steadily in the run to the line.
Began well settling in forward of midfield in 6th, came within 2L of pace on home bend 600 metres out, kept on under pressure until finding no extra 150 metres out.
Inconvenienced at start, niggled along wide in last from a wide draw, trailed the field until running on past beaten runners down the centre of the straight.
Settled 3 wide without cover in 5th from a wide draw, went wider into straight, soon weakened.
Soon taken well behind and never seen with a chance.
Improved gradually along the rail to gain narrow advantage 1000 metres out, led until headed about 300 metres out, folded up quickly.
Ridden forward after moderate start to lead early stages, narrowly headed passing 1100 metres, soon weakened after straightening.
Broke well and showed good early speed to lead, battled on gamely from the 350M to the post and won.
Sat just outside the leader, fought hard in the straight, just can't get by the winner.
Steadied after the start from a wide barrier, stayed on well to grab 3rd. (See Incident Report)
Settled worse than midfield on the rail, took some time to respond when under pressure, and stayed on late.
Settled just behind the leaders, only one pace when asked.
Settled midfield 2 wide, travelled keenly throughout, and made minor progress.
Caught 3 wide in midfield, didn't handle the turn particularly well, made some progress late.
Settled 3 wide near the rear, made no impression.
Up with the pace, weakened at 300M.
Sat close to the pace 3 wide no cover, weakened in the straight.
Settled near the rear, held up in the straight, not fully tested. (See Incident Report)
At rear, never in contention.
Raced three wide with cover in midfield throughout. Was just over 4L from the lead on straightening, made continual ground to move to narrow lead at the 75m mark & held narrow advantage on line.

Got back to race second last along the rail after start. Moved off the rail near 700m, was last & 5.5L from lead on straightening, was the widest runner in the straight & made continual ground down the outside, just beaten.

Was trapped racing wide just behind the leaders & was then left without cover from about the 850m. Was only 1.5L from the lead entering last section, moved to lead near 200m, over-run late, only beaten 1L on line.

Raced in midfield between runners early & then drifted slightly further back around bend. Raced tight passing the 500m, was 5L behind entering last section before closing off ok in final furlong to be beaten under 2L on line.

Raced in midfield along the rail before drifting slightly further back around bend. Stayed along rail on straightening when 4L behind before shifting outwards near 200m & closing off steadily between runners late.

Was taken back from outside gate & raced a clear last after the start. Was over 5L from the lead entering last section, was held up for clear running until the 175m before closing off late to midfield.

Showed speed to lead after start before being headed approaching 1100m & then racing just behind the leading group. Was just over 3L from the lead entering last section & maintained margin to the line when finishing midfield.

Pushed forward & raced wide near the lead early before improving to take the lead near the 950m mark before crossing to the rail when leading near the 750m. Headed in lead approaching 200m & weakened out in late stages.
Raced in 1,1 for the majority. Eased into clear running near the 400m mark when 3L from the lead before peaking at the 300m & weakening out to be beaten 5.5L.

Raced outside the leader early, took narrow lead momentarily near the 1100m before being headed at the 950m & racing on the leaders back from the 750m. Continued just behind before weakening out quickly in the last 150m.

Raced in midfield along the rail throughout. Moved off the rail approaching the 500m, was close to heels & steadied at the 400m when just over 4L from the lead before shifting outwards at the 300m but failing to run on late.
Raced three wide outside the lead early before racing third from about the 950m. Continued close until emptying at the 300m mark & weakening out poorly in the last furlong.

Began awkwardly & lost ground at start before improving quickly after first 100m to race in midfield away from the rail. Eased wider approaching corner, straightened only 3L behind but weakened out badly to be well beaten.

Placing: FE
Comment: Got back to race third last away from the rail. Was taken wider on the track near the 500m before clipping a heel soon after and falling.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, finished off strongly to score by a neck.
Away well, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, found rail near 700M, easy run to turn, hit the front 250M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner close home.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced slightly better than midfield on the outside, 3 lengths back turning in, showed good response early in straight, peaked 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Moderately away from gate 1, tracked leaders on the inside, saved ground throughout, kept on well early in straight, no extra final 150M.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out after passing 500M, made some progress early in straight, no further impression final furlong.

Commenced well, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield early, found rail near 900M, 2 wide turning in, not enough room early in straight, made minor progress 300M to 200M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Made contact at start, raced 3 wide towards rear, 2 wide from 900M, 7 lengths back turning in, made some progress in straight.
Taken back to race 2 wide towards rear, found rail 700M, still well back on turn, passed some tired runners in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began awkwardly, raced towards rear on the inside, still well back on turn, passed some tired runners in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail early, 12 lengths back, a bit closer after passing 650M, still 11 lengths back turning in, made no impression in straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced slightly better than midfield on the outside, 2 lengths or so back, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Began awkwardly and crowded, raced at rear on the outside, difficult to settle in the early stages, 9 to 10 lengths back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Made contact and unbalanced at start, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length on turn, peaked early in straight, headed 250M, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Crowded start, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter. (Lost left hind plate at the start.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide, angled out in the straight, closed off strongly and won going away. (See Incident report)
Settled midfield on the rail, improved along the rail rounding the home turn, switched out at 350M, quickened nicely, but can't hold off the winner.
Settled midfield 2 wide early, moved to 3 wide rounding the turn to improve, lay in and got bumped in the straight, ran on okay.
Settled near the rear, stayed on fairly well.
Settled at the rear, closed off nicely, best stride late.
Sat at the rear on the rail, made some progress.
Ridden along early to lead, kept on okay early and weakened inside 150M.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, angled out in the straight but did not quickened. (See Incident Report)
Settled worse than midfield on the rail, made no impression.
Sat in front of midfield 2 wide, raced greenly rounding the turn, got hampered in the straight, weakened and faded soon after. (See Incident Report)
Sat outside the lead, got badly crowded in the straight and soon faded. (See Incident Report)
Broke well before settling just over 2L off the pace in 4th, came to challenge from entering straight and responded well to assert authority over 100 metres out.
Settled in 3rd on rail within 2L of pace, shifted off rail for a run entering straight, hit front under pressure briefly 200 metres out and soon headed.
Settled in worse than midfield in 7th, switched out to challenge on straightening, ran on well under pressure down the centre of the track.
Settled just worse than midfield on rail, came under strong pressure early in straight, produced good late impression inside final 150 metres.
Taken back from the widest draw, trailed the field until forward move 3-wide from the 750 metres, finished off the race strongly from wide into straight.
Gradually taken back from a wide draw, finished off the race well inside final 250 metres.
Settled in 6th 2-wide in midfield, came under pressure approaching home turn, kept on steadily without quickening.
Soon took up running from moderate start, led until joined into straight, unable to sustain effort inside final 150 metres.
Travelled some 4L back in 5th on rail, in similar position turning into home straight, found no extra inside final 100 metres.
Settled well behind after moderate start, trailed the field rounding home bend and into straight, made no further impression.
Ridden to prominent position from middle draw, settled in 2nd just outside leader from the 1000 metres, disputed lead into straight, weakened under pressure inside final 200 metres.
Always in last few and never seen with a chance.
Jumped only fairly, waited with towards the rear along the stand's rail, ran on powerfully passing 300M, produced the fastest 400M finish of the day to nail the leader near line.
Sped to the lead and soon crossed to the stand's side, built a clear margin halfway, kept on well under 7lb claimer only to be nailed by winner close home.
Chased the clear leader, roused along 350M but lacked the needed response, battled on to take a non-threatening 3rd.
Gradually moved forward to be 3rd on settling, waited with until 250M but found less than expected, soon no threat to first 2, just missed 3rd in a photo finish.
In 4th place 3-4Ls off the runaway leader, kept on same pace final 400M, failed to threaten first two.
Not hurried after the start, reserved at the rear 7Ls off the pace, stayed on mildly over final 400M and never dangerous.
From draw 14 moved up along the stand's rail to race in midfield, battled on one paced final 400M, never a serious threat. (Bled.)
Settled behind midfield, 7Ls off leader at 400M, made limited progress only.
Held up behind midfield, failed to run on passing 400M, never reach contention.
Settled towards the tail of the field, found little when placed under pressure mid-way, never threatened.
Always near the rear, hung in over final 400M and proved difficult to ride, failed to progress.
Towards the rear down center of the track, not quickened passing 400M, failed to factor.
Badly crowded for room at start, restrained towards the rear, failed to keep pace passing 400M, weakened. (Jockey : no cover during race being the reason for disappointing run.)
Badly crowded for room at start, raced towards the rear, outpaced middle stages, soon out of contention passing 400M, finished tailed out. (Jockey : failed to travel at any stage.)
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 lengths or so back turning in, finished off strongly to score by a neck.

Moderately away from gate 1, raced midfield on the inside, a bit closer on turn, showed good response early in straight, hit the front approaching 200M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner close home.
Taken back from gate 9, raced behind midfield on the outside, a bit closer on turn, made good progress early in straight, no extra final 150M.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, slightly hampered near 450M, made some headway in straight to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Slowly away and made contact, raced 2 wide towards rear, 5 lengths back turning in, made some progress in straight.
Jumped awkwardly, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, steadied off heels near 900M, 6 lengths back turning in, made some headway in straight, slightly inconvenienced near 125M.
Began smartly from the widest draw, raced in midfield on the outside, very wide into straight, made some progress early in straight, peaked 200M, made contact 125M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began awkwardly and made contact, raced at tail, 6 lengths back turning in, made some progress in straight on the inside.
Jumped well, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leaders on the inside, 2 wide from 500M, 1/2L back turning in, took the lead 300M, peaked and headed 200M, weakened thereafter.
Made contact at start, positioned 2 wide, 1-1/2L back, wider turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Bumped start, raced towards rear on the inside, 5 lengths back turning in, showed some response early in straight, not clear 200 to 100M, one-paced thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, angled out after passing 600M, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Began well, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/2L turning in, peaked and headed 300M, weakened final furlong.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 3 wide behind midfield, checked near 900M, 5 lengths or so back turning in, failed to make any progress in straight.
Began well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length on turn, kept on well in straight to hold off the challengers.
Commenced well, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on the inside, a bit closer on turn, finished off well to take 2nd, just beaten by a head.
Slightly slow out, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, slightly improved on turn, finished off well to take a place.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back turning in, no clear run early in straight, cleared 200M, finished off strongly to make frame, nearest on line.

Jumped well from the widest draw, raced better than midfield on the outside, found a 2 wide spot near 900M, 1 to 2 lengths back turning in, showed limited response early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 6 lengths back on turn, taken wide in straight and made good progress to be nearest on line.
Began well, positioned 2 wide in 2nd, a length back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide towards rear, 3 wide on turn, made some progress early in straight, no extra final 200M.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, eased final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began awkwardly and slightly crowded, raced towards rear on the inside, hampered near 1150M, saved ground on turn, made no impression in straight.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Made contact at start, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (Roarer.)
Out with rest, raced in midfield on the outside, no cover after passing 900M, a bit closer on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened quickly final 300M. (Roarer.)

Horse No: Comments on Running is not available for this race.
Horse Name: Comments on Running is not available for this race.
Jockey: Comments on Running is not available for this race.
Gear: Comments on Running is not available for this race.
Comment: Comments on Running is not available for this race.
Began fairly from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off well to score by a narrow margin.
Clean jump, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably to turn, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner on line.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, crowded near 700M, 4 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Out with rest, sent forward to race in 2nd, a length or so back on turn, kept on same pace to the line.
Jumped only fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, similar position on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening the first few.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced towards rear on the inside, closer on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off evenly.
Held up in midfield, battled on at same pace turning into straight, never dangerous.
Taken back from gate 10, raced at rear on the inside, still well back on turn, passed some tired runners in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear, 7 lengths back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off evenly.
Began only fairly, raced 3 wide, a length or so back, checked near 700M, 2 wide from 650M, 3 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Shifted out at start, raced slightly better than midfield on the outside, no cover for the majority of the race, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact at start, raced behind midfield on the outside, very wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter. (Blood in trachea and a continuous displacement of the soft palate.)

Raced in midfield along the rail throughout. Came under hard ridding near 550m, came off the rail early in the straight before finishing strongly down the outside to charge to lead inside final 50m before drawing clear late.

Pushed forward & shared the lead until improving to the lead near the 700m. Was just over a length clear of nearest rival on straightening, continued in the lead until passed by fast finishing winner in last 50m. Held second.

Raced prominently after start before being crossed near the 800m & racing on the leaders back. Moved off the rail when continuing third near the 650m, was about 1.5L behind on straightening & tried hard all the way to line.

Got back to race third last away from the rail after start. Improved between runners entered last section when 7L behind, held up on momentarily on straightening before shifting outwards & closing strongly down the outside.

Began well but drifted back to race in midfield away from the rail. Continued between runners, entered last section 6L from the lead before making continual late ground to only be beaten 2.5L into fifth.

Didn't have early speed & shifted behind runners to the rail before racing worse than midfield along the inside. Moved off the rail passing the 500m, closed off steadily nearer the inside when running on to halve margin late.

Began fast before being headed & racing 1,1 from near the 900m. Lost his position around the bend when dropping back to be about 4L from the lead. Was passed by fast closing rivals in last furlong when weakening to midfield.

Taken outwards at start & raced at the tail. Was a clear last & over 10L from lead at 400m, was beginning to finish off strongly before being checked near 125m before picking up again late. Clearly would have finished closer.

Improved after the start to share the lead before being headed near the 700m & racing second along the rail thereafter. Was about 1.5L form the lead on straightening, only battled in last 250m & was beaten 4L on line.
Jumped only fairly before racing in midfield away from the rail. Tracked three wide from about the 500m before weakening out in the last 300m to be well beaten (substantial mucus in trachea).

Drifted back after the start & raced second last. Tracked three wide with cover around the bend when continuing rearward, was just under 10L from the lead entering last section & made no headway in the straight.

Began fast from widest gate but couldn't cross & raced 4 wide in midfield after start. Continued wide & began losing ground from the 600m, was relegated to third last near 450m & weakened out badly to long last in straight.

Jumped on terms, settled worse than midfield 2 wide, switched out to 3 wide to improve at 1000M, angled further out rounding the home turn, closed off strongly and won handily. (Lame right front leg the next morning)
Broke well and settled in front of midfield on the rail, moved out to 2 wide at 600M and under pressured, ran on well, had every chance.
Settled near the rear 2 wide, got hampered at 600M and badly crowded at 400M, stayed on well after regaining balance.
Sat at the rear, hard ridden at 550M, made a wide run rounding the home turn and kept on.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, under pressured at 800M, only one pace when asked.
Settled worse than midfield on the rail, closed off fairly.
Settled near the rear on the rail, made some progress
Settled behind the speed on the rail, kept on fairly early and weakened inside 150M.
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide, hard ridden at 600M, made some late progress.
Caught wide early and improved outside the leaders, weakened in the straight.
Broke well and led, weakened at 400M. (See Incident Report) (Roarer)
Settled midfield on the rail, made no impression. (Roarer) (Mucus in trachea)
Sat midfield 2 wide, weakened and faded in the straight.
Ridden vigorously early and caught 5 wide in the first turn, up with the pace and faded quickly rounding the home turn. (Performance unacceptable, must trial)

Raced in midfield along the rail. Moved off the rail into clear running near the 600m, was over 5L from the lead entering last section, finished strongly down the outside to charge to the lead in final 100m & drew clear late.

Showed customary early speed to share lead early before improving to outright lead near 900m. Raced 3L clear of nearest rival on straightening, passed by fast finishing winner in last 100m but was 2L clear of third on line.
Raced in midfield away from the rail. Was just under 8L from the runaway leader on straightening before closing off steadily all the way to move to non-threatening third near the 125m.

Raced in midfield early but lost position from about the 900m mark before being ridden along from the 800m to hold position. Continued to drift back to be over 9L form the lead on cornering before making late headway to 4th.

Began awkwardly, crowded at the start & raced last. Was just under 10L behind at the 400m before being held up around the bend until about the 300m. Made good late ground nearer the inside late (rider questioned, see report).

Got back to second last after the start & continued to race rearward throughout. Shared last place on cornering before making up a few lengths to run onto well beaten midfield finish from a long way back.
Had a nice position in midfield away from the rail throughout. Was forth & just under 5L behind runaway leader on straightening before peaking on his effort mid-straight & weakening out.

Pushed forward to race outside the leading pair when wide before shifting to be two wide without cover from the first bend. Was second & just over 3L from the lead behind runaway leader before weakening quickly last furlong.

Showed speed to share lead early before being headed near the 900m & racing behind the leader. Drifted slightly further back around the bend, shifted outwards when under pressure after straightening before weakening late.

Drifted back after the start & raced third last after start. Continued rearward when racing wider on the track before hanging outwards around the bend. Was last & the widest on straightening but never improved.

Hard ridden at start before sharing second place when away from the rail & about 1 length behind in first 400m. Continued to share second on cornering when just over 3L from lead before weakening very quickly in final 250m.
Was about a length slow to begin before racing along the rail when worse than midfield. Was 9L from the lead entering last section before weakening out very poorly in the straight to be long last.
Out with rest, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, commenced move 450M, finished off very strongly to score.
Away well, raced slightly better than midfield on the outside, there to turn, showed good response in straight, hit the front 200M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 100M.

Moderately away from the widest draw, raced in midfield on the outside, commenced move after passing 750M, took the lead 500M, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 200M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Began fairly and made contact, raced 2 wide towards rear, similar position on turn, closed off well to make frame without threatening the first few.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, a bit closer on turn, kept on same pace to the line.
Jumped with them, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground to turn, no clear run early in straight, ran on evenly thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped awkwardly, raced towards rear on the outside, 3 to 4 lengths back turning in, made no impression in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, angled out 600M, very wide into straight, made some progress early in straight, no extra final furlong.
Slightly slow out and bumped, raced towards rear on the inside, 2 wide turning in, no clear run early in straight, cleared 200M, made no progress thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Shifted in at start and made contact, raced at rear on the outside, a bit closer on turn, very wide into straight, made no progress in the run home.
Began well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 wide from 900M, closer on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (Lame left front leg next day morning.)
Began fairly and slightly crowded, raced in midfield on the inside, unable to maintain position on turn, eased early in straight.
Began well from gate 1, raced prominently on the inside, took the lead 1100M, headed 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well, took the early lead, headed 1100M, 2nd in the middle stages, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Settled just behind the leader, switched out in the straight, travelled comfortably, quickened well when asked, won easily.
Broke well and settled in front of midfield on the rail, closed of fairly well.
Settled midfield on the rail, stayed on fairly.
Raced worse than midfield, made some progress early in the straight, but only one pace inside 150M.
At rear, made decent progress near the rail in the straight.
Broke nicely and led, kept on okay early but weakened inside 150M.
Settled midfield 2 wide, did not quicken in the straight.
Tracked leaders, weakened in the straight.
Settled near the rear, never in contention.
Sat in front of midfield 2 wide, never a threat.

Began from a wide gate, gingerly shifted across to 3-wide in 2L 4th, 2-wide rounding home bend and switched out to challenge on straightening, hit the front 300 metres out and just held on from runner-up's strong challenge.
Gradually improved to forward of midfield in 6th mainly over 4L back, commenced move passing the 500 metres, quickened well in 5th from behind eventual winner to just fail to get up on line.
Settled towards the rear 3-wide in 9th, gained closer to 4L 7th wide home bend, fought on steadily to reach 3rd over 100 metres out but never threatening.
Ridden positively disputing lead early stages, taken one-out-one-back onto home bend, renewed effort to gain slender advantage briefly entering home straight, soon found no extra.
Niggled along worse than midfield on the rail, came under stronger pressure rounding home bend, switched off heels on straightening, produced moderate late impression closing stages.
Taken back from the widest gate, trailed the field along the rail and saved ground turning in, kept on steadily past well beaten ones.
Ridden early from the one draw, gradually drifted back near midfield some over 3L back in 5th, baulked for a run early in straight, kept on steadily inside final 220 metres.
In front briefly before settling one back in 3rd coming onto home bend, baulked for a run early in straight, found no extra inside final 250 metres.
Travelled wide in last few, even wider rounding home bend, made moderate impression under pressure down the centre of the straight.
Settled in last few, came under pressure after straightening, ran home one-paced.
Driven forward from a middle gate, took up running 3-wide over 900 metres out, steadied up the pace in front around home bend, folded up quickly inside final 300 metres. (Blood in trachea)
Checked at start, never better than midfield, weakened in straight.
Chased leaders, quickened up nicely top of straight, led nearing 100M and successfully repelled the runner up late stages.
Jumped awkwardly, shifted across behind runners early stages before moving up to race in midfield, responded well passing 350M, chased leader strongly final stages, just held.
Chased leaders on inside, kept battling in straight, couldn't get near to first two final 200M, held on for 3rd just.
Dropped back to a rearward position, ran on and did best work final 200M, just missed 3rd but no threat to first two.
Quickly into stride, shared lead on inside under 7lb claimer, fought on well early straight, caught near 100M, no extra late stages.
Held up in midfield along the fence, ran on moderately passing 400M, no threat to leaders.
From wide draw taken back to race in last, 7Ls behind leaders home turn, pushed along 550M but lacked a response, never going the pace to challenge.
Settled 3-wide in the group chasing leaders, wide into straight, responded only fairly, no threat to leaders over final 200M.
Settled towards the rear along the inside, gave limited response in the straight, ran past beaten horses only.
Up with the pace, not quickened when driven out 350M, gave ground rapidly mid-straight. (Jockey : unable to sustain its run to the finish after setting strong pace early stages. / Roarer.)
Went forward, caught 3-wide no cover outside leaders, emptied passing 300M, weakened rapidly.
Failed to show sufficient pace to cross runners to its inside, obliged to race without cover, weakened top of straight and finished tailed out. (Jockey : raced in a disappointing manner.)

Began well from a wide draw, taken back to race 2 wide towards rear, angled out 500M, finished off very strongly to score.

Began only fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, made contact near 550M, 3 wide turning in, showed very good response in straight, took the lead 125M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner close home.
Taken back from gate 13, raced at rear on the outside, 8 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made very good progress in straight to take a place, nearest on line, good debut.
Blundered shortly after start, unable to slot in, trapped very wide early, a length or so back, 3 wide on turn, kept on well early in straight, no extra final 150M.
Began well, raced in midfield on the outside, 4 lengths or so back, no cover on turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked 150M, ran on evenly thereafter.

Made contact shortly after start, raced 3 wide, a length or so back, moved a bit closer after passing 800M, took the lead 650M, led by 1-1/2L turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 125M, weakened thereafter.
Bumped start, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, similar position on turn, showed some response early in straight, no extra final 150M.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out 650M, 4 lengths back turning in, no clear run in straight, not able to test properly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began only fairly and crowded, positioned 5 lengths behind the leader on rail, angled out and made contact near 550M, same margin back turning in, made no impression in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear, 8 lengths back turning in, made little progress in straight.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced better than midfield on the inside, 2 wide on turn, showed some response early in straight, checked off heels 250M, weakened final furlong.
Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead 1000M, headed 650M, peaked turning in, weakened early in straight.
Began well from gate 1, took the early lead, headed 1000M, allowed the leader to cross near 800M, unable to maintain position from 600M, weakened early in straight.
From wide draw restrained to race towards the rear, 7Ls to make up top of straight, finished off strongly final 400M, got up close home.
Quickly crossed from draw 10 and enjoyed uncontested lead, opened up a sizable lead mid-straight, caught close home. Clear from remainders.
Unhurried after the start, dropped back to race behind midfield, kept on moderately passing 400M, got up for 3rd last stride but never a threat to first two.
Held up 3-wide in midfield, put in a mild bid top of straight, moved up to 2nd 300M out, peaked on its run 100M, lost 3rd late. (Jockey : lay in when placed under pressure in the straight.)
From wide draw taken back to last, 9Ls off the pace passing 400M, took a while to get going, did best work final 200M.
Began awkwardly from draw 9, raced keenly in a rearward position, made some progress over final 300M without troubling first two.
Always in touch behind leaders, battled on same pace in straight, out of contention for minor placings passing 200M.

Settled ahead of midfield, found less than expected in the finish, no threat to leaders from 200M. (Jockey reported whilst hampered on several occasions in the straight he could offer no additional excuse.)
Raced in midfield along the fence, had difficulty obtaining clear running early straight, ran on fairly over final 250M, never threatened.
Held up behind mid-division, gave limited response on straightening, never dangerous.
Chased the pace, obliged to race wide without cover for the majority of the events, failed to finish off under top weight, eased 100M when no chance.
Settled down 2-wide in midfield, responded fairly turning in, never going the pace to challenge.
Tracked leader, struggled to keep up passing 400M, soon weakened to last.
Jumped only fairly, settled behind midfield 2 wide, began to improve from 700M, stayed on well to win.
Sat in front of midfield 2 wide, travelled smoothly, showed some response inside 250M, finished 2nd.
Ridden along to chase the leader 3 wide, raced keenly in the early stages, close off nicely to grab 3rd.
Settled towards rear, travelled okay, lay in and stopped riding inside 100M.
Travelled comfortably to lead, remained prominent until 300M, weakened under pressure at 150M.
Jumped okay, ridden along to sit handy, steadied in the early Straight, soon weakened.
Sat rear, one-paced, never a threat (See Incident Report).
Sat back in the barriers as the start was effected, jumped awkwardly, settled midfield on the rail, never in contention.
Showed speed to race close to the lead early. Assumed the lead near the 400m mark before drawing away to win very easily.
Raced in midfield, one horse in from the stand side rail. Improved between runners to dash to second near the furlong pole & finished off ok but was no match for easy winner.
Raced in midfield throughout. Improved to share third place by about half-way, battled on well to hold third.

Bumped at the start before racing worse than midfield early. Improved to midfield approaching half-way after shifting inwards to be nearest to the center of the track, battled away well to just miss third.
Raced in midfield along the stand side rail. Raced in restricted room & hampered near the 400m mark before finishing off steadily late.
Began awkwardly & was slightly crowded after the start & settled in the second half. Raced a touch keenly in the middle stages when just worse than midfield. Finished off only fairly in last section.

Drifted back to race in the final quartet when coursing along the stand side rail. Finished off only fairly in the last section when holding well beaten midfield finish. (Rider questioned, see report).
Ridden forward & responded well to stride to lead early. Joined & headed by the winner entering the final section before weakening out quickly in concluding stages.
Showed early speed to race second along the stand side rail after the start. Was under 2L form the lead entering the final section before peaking on effort & weakening in final 250m.

Raced just forward of midfield when racing nearer to the center of the track without cover. Came under hard riding near the 400m mark when about 3L from the lead before weakening out in the last furlong to be well beaten.
Jumped outwards & bumped & lost ground before racing near the tail. Did little in the last section & was well beaten.
Raced in midfield between runners throughout. Weakened badly in the final 300m to be well beaten.
Knuckled and then bumped at the start & raced at the tail. Did nothing in the last section & was a well beaten second last.

Jumped awkwardly & lost ground at start & raced rearward when coursing nearer to the center of the track. Weakened badly in the final furlong to be a very long last. (Substantial mucus in trachea, roarer, lame next day).
Commenced well, positioned 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off strongly to score.
Jumped with them, raced in midfield on the outside, angled out 450M, finished off well to take 2nd, just beaten by a narrow margin.
Made contact shortly after start, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, wider turning in, closed off well to take a place.
Began well from a wide draw, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, same position on turn, hit the front 300M, peaked and headed 125M, ran on evenly to the line.
Bumped on jumping, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off well without threatening.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide turning in, made some progress in straight.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some progress in straight.
Average to begin, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, kept on evenly thereafter.
Made contact shortly after start, raced better than midfield on the outside, no cover throughout, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the outside, 6 lengths back turning in, passed some tired runners in straight.
Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/4L turning in, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide towards rear, 5 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, made no impression in straight.
Taken back from gate 12, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Broke a step slow, shifted across towards the rail early and settled last, made a mid-race move down the back straight and led the race from 1000M, kept on strongly in the straight and won.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, angled out rounding the home turn, closed off nicely for 2nd.
Sat close to the pace 2 wide, kept on fairly for 3rd.
Settled worse than midfield on the rail early, got shuffled back down the back straight, stayed on okay.
Broke well and assumed the lead until 1000M, kept on one pace.
Settled midfield on the rail, made minor progress.
Raced in front of midfield 2 wide, moved to 3 wide at 800M, did not quicken.
Settled near the rear, circled the field rounding the home turn, made no impression in the straight.
Caught 3 wide no cover near midfield, limited response in the straight.
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide, made no ground.
Settled midfield 3 wide, never a threat.
Raced near the rear, never in contention. (See Incident Report) (Performance unacceptable, must trial)
Settled midfield 2 wide, under pressured at 850M and gave ground. (See Incident Report)
Settled in last few and waited with, commenced move 300 metres out quickening well inside final 200 metres to take command shortly after.
Close up early, gradually settled in 6th just some 3L off the pace, gained 2L 5th rounding home bend, made modest progress under pressure inside final 200 metres but never threatening.
Settled in worse than midfield 3-wide, slightly wider entering home straight, fought on steadily under pressure down the centre of the track, never threatening.
Settled 3-wide in rear and waited with, commenced move shifting widest entering home straight, fought on steadily under pressure down the centre of the straight.
Soon dropped to clear last despite niggling along, trailed the field into straight, fought on steadily under pressure closing stages.
Jumped awkwardly from the widest gate, travelled wide without cover prominently, disputed lead 3-wide rounding home bend, kept on until overhauled inside final 150 metres.
Niggled along obtaining rails run in front over 1100 metres out, ceded advantage for 4th passing the 1100 metres, baulked behind runners in straight until the 150 metres, found nothing.
Travelled mainly in rear of midfield, given reminders approaching home turn, baulked for a run between the 300 and 150 metres, ran home one-paced.
Well there early before settling 2 back in 5th on rail, became 6th in similar position rounding home bend saved ground turning in, kept on steadily in straight without threatening.
Well there from a wide draw travelling keenly one back in 3rd, came to share the pace approaching home turn, unable to sustain effort inside final 150 metres.
Improved steadily from moderate start to take up running 1000 metres out, led on rail until joined on top of home bend, folded up quickly under pressure inside final 150 metres.
Settled towards rear wide without cover, made headway to 4L 7th 3-wide onto home bend, remained wide into straight, made no further impression.
Crowded at start settling in last few on rail, switched out to challenge entering straight, baulked for a run until the 150 metres, made no further impression.
Travelled mainly in rear of midfield on the rail niggling along rounding home bend, soon weakened after straightening.
Restrained to race in 3rd on settling, held up briefly 250M, came through narrow passage to challenge for the lead before gaining upper hand final 50M.
Strolled to the lead, set very slow pace middle stages, quickened up 450M, battled on well when pressed by rivals final 200M, held on for 2nd.
Jumped awkwardly, never far off leaders in a slowly run race, responded well on straightening, drew alongside leader inside 200M, fought hard but couldn't hold off winner late.
Settled near last in a slowly run race, 7Ls to make up top of straight, closed off final 400M to go 4th late stages but never a threat to first three.
Jumped only fairly, reserved in midfield, driven 450M but never going the pace to challenge leaders, kept on mildly for non-threatening 5th.
Not hurried after the start, waited with in a position behind midfield, stayed on moderately under top weight without threatening first three.
Tracked leader in a slowly run race, steadied 250M when crowded between rivals, outpaced final 150M.
From wide draw dropped back in search of cover, raced towards the rear 6-7Ls in a slowly run race, responded fairly passing 400M. No impression on leaders.
From wide draw switched off to race in last, 8Ls off the pace passing 400M, made limited progress down outside.
From draw 6 ended up in a 3-wide spot in midfield without cover, failed to quicken on straightening, never dangerous.
Slow to begin, restrained to race towards the rear in a slowly run race, couldn't go on passing 400M, never involved.
In mid-division, saved ground along the inside but lacked a finishing response on straightening, soon gave way.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the inside, slightly improved along the rail on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared 150M, finished off strongly to score.
Average to begin, positioned a length behind the leader on the inside, easy run to turn, made contact near 400M, hit the front 250M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner close home.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out after passing 550M, no clear run early in straight, cleared 200M, finished off strongly to take a place, nearest finish.
Began well from a wide draw, raced in midfield on the outside, no cover throughout, very wide into straight, closed off well to make frame, just missed 3rd.
Made contact shortly after start, taken back to race towards rear on the outside, very wide turning in, finished off well to be nearest on line.
Away well, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, 3 wide turning in, made good progress early in straight, no extra final 150M.
Taken back from gate 12, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, very wide into straight, made some progress in the run home.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide towards rear, 4 lengths or so back turning in, made some progress early in straight, no extra final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out 550M, made some progress early in straight, peaked on run 150M, weakened gradually final 100M.
Began smartly from gate 1, raced prominently on the inside, took the lead 650M, led by a length turning in, showed limited response early in straight, headed 250M, weakened final furlong.
Began only fairly and crowded, raced in midfield on the inside, 2 wide turning in, no clear run early in straight, weakened thereafter.

Made contact shortly after start, sent forward to race prominently on the outside, took the lead 1000M, headed 650M, 2nd turning in, made contact early in straight, peaked 300M, weakened final 200M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced towards rear on the outside, 5 lengths back turning in, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to score.
Moderately away from gate 11, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, challenged the leader turning in, took the lead early in straight, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 50M.
Out with rest, raced at tail, 8 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, very wide into straight, made very good progress in the run home to take a place.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, angled out 500M, kept on well early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, angled out 500M, made some headway in straight.
Made contact at start, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed good response early in straight, not enough room near 200M, cleared 150M, made some progress thereafter.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out 500M, finished off evenly. (Mucus.)
Moderately away from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, angled out 500M, showed some response early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened thereafter.
Average to begin, raced better than midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 500M, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M.
Shifted out at start and made contact, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, angled out 500M, very wide into straight, made some progress early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened thereafter.

Average to begin, raced in midfield on the outside, 3 to 4 lengths back, difficult to settle in the early stages, similar position on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Began awkwardly and made contact, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some progress early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Quickly into stride, sent forward to take the lead, challenged by rival from 550M, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened final 200M.
Commenced well from a wide draw, raced better than midfield on the outside, a bit closer on turn, carried wider 500M, weakened early in straight, eased final 300M.

Away with them, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, sent forward after passing 1100M, took the lead 950M, led by 1/2L on turn, kept on very well to the line and scored.
Commenced well from gate 1, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, angled out after passing 500M, 3 wide turning in, finished off well to take 2nd, always held.
Jumped with them, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground to turn, angled out 350M, closed off well to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 2 wide towards rear, 3 wide after entering the back straight, angled out 400M, very wide into straight, passed some tired runners in the run home.
Out with rest, took the lead, led by 1/2L, headed 950M, 2nd on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slowly into stride, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground throughout, made some progress early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Out in line, raced 2 wide in midfield early, 3 wide from 1000M, no cover from 800M, 4 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight. (Lost right front plate near 1000M.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the outside, 6 lengths or so back on turn, made no impression in straight.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, gradually dropped towards rear after passing 1000M, 5 lengths back turning in, showed no response early in straight, eased inside final furlong.

Moderately away, raced better than midfield on the outside early, moved closer after passing 1650M, positioned 3rd in the middle stages, weakened 500M, eased early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Driven forward from the widest draw, held running off the rail before obtaining rails run approaching home bend, held 1L advantage turning into straight, hung on well under pressure.
Always thereabouts settling one back in 3rd from 800 metres, slightly further off the pace rounding home bend, fought on dourly to be nearest at finish.
Ridden positively from the two draw, settled one back behind eventual race winner passing 600 metres, unable to quicken under pressure to threaten in straight.
Travelled in forward of midfield in 6th, finished off the race well inside final 100 metres.
Hard ridden from a wide draw before settling 3-wide in 4th some 2L back, drifted over 3L back in 5th approaching home bend, one-paced in straight.
Jumped well before taken two back to joint 4th, became further off the pace passing 600 metres, one-paced under pressure in straight.
Jumped awkwardly settling well behind, commenced move passing 400 metres swinging wide into straight, produced good late impression in the run to the line.
Began very awkwardly settling in midfield in 7th, similar turning for home, made no impression in straight.
Settled in rear of midfield, came under pressure passing 500 metres, found nothing.
Soon dropped to last few from a wide draw, saved ground on rail turning for home, made no show in straight.
Niggled along at the back, never seen with a chance.
Awkward start before hampered, travelled keenly wide without cover in 9th just worse than midfield, found nothing in straight.
Jumped okay, sat handy 2 wide, began to improve inside 650M, travelled strongly to close off.
Settled behind midfield 2 wide, travelled smoothly, showed some dash over the final 75M to hold 2nd.
Sat towards rear 3 wide, angled out at 450M, made some progress at the Straight but weakened inside 100M.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, not clear run until 150M, not able to fully tested.
Jumped awkwardly, settled rear, stayed on okay.
Jumped awkwardly, sat towards rear 2 wide, switched out in the Straight, not clear run over the concluding stages.
Sat rear 3 wide, ridden hard from 450M, only one pace (See Incident Report).
Jumped awkwardly, sat midfield on the rail, showed limited progress in the Straight.
Settled midfield 3 wide, ridden along to chase the leader from 700M, weakened at 125M.
Sat worse than midfield on the rail, one pace throughout, no impression.
Slow to jump, sat towards rear on the rail, never a threat.
Ridden along to lead, weakened early in the Straight to last (Substantial amount of blood in the horse's trachea) (See Incident Report).

Raced on the leaders back early before a pair further back from the 900m. Moved off the rail sharply passing the 800m & hampered rivals before racing 1,1 thereafter. Improved along the rail to steal lead at 125m & drew away late.

Raced at the tail after the start. Improved around runners near the 750m & avoided interference. Raced wide with cover in midfield, hampered & taken wider by rival from the 450m before making late ground to close to second.

Raced 1,1 early before improving to race second from the 800m when coursing one horse off the rail. Was a length from the lead on straightening, battled on all the way to the line to hold non-threatening third.

Shared lead early before improving to near the 950m mark & crossing to rail soon after. Was over a length clear on straightening when continuing in lead before joined & passed by winner at 125m before tiring quickly in last 75m.

Shifted out at start before mustering to race in midfield. Badly crowded, checked & lost ground passing 750m. Made up lost ground around bend, 4th on straightening, finished off one paced in straight (irregular heart rhythm).

About a length slow to begin before racing rearward along rail. Crowded & steadied near the 700m & raced second last thereafter. Was a long way back on straightening, passed a few tiring rivals late, well beaten in midfield.

Steadied soon after start & taken back to race third last. Steadied to avoid heels approaching the 700m & raced last thereafter. Last & a long way back on straightening before passing a few tiring rivals late, well beaten.

Trapped racing wide with cover in midfield. Was forced 4 wide without cover to avoid trouble near the 750m. Hung outwards & lost ground around the bend & was consequently next to last on straightening & never ran on (lame).

Raced in midfield between runners in early stages before being bumped heavily, crowded & losing ground approaching the 700m. Never really travelled after the incident, failed to run on & was well beaten.
Was trapped racing three wide without cover in midfield throughout. Began losing ground when hanging outwards from about the 550m, weakened badly in the straight to be very long second last.
Pushed forward & shared the lead early before being headed near the 950m & crossed soon after. Began losing ground from the 650m & weakened badly to be a long last. Poor.
Began well from gate 1, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, same margin back on turn, 2 wide turning in, finished off strongly to score by a neck.
Jumped with them, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, a bit closer on turn, finished off strongly to take 2nd, just beaten by a neck.
Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the first two close home.
Out with rest, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, there to turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide at rear, 4 lengths or so back, angled out approaching 350M, made good progress early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Commenced well, positioned 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, wider on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 9, raced towards rear on the outside, there to turn, very wide into straight, made little progress in the run home. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began awkwardly and made contact, raced at rear on the inside, 4 lengths or so back, saved ground throughout, one-paced in the run home.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, 3 wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Broke nicely and settled in front of midfield 2 wide, moved onto the rail at 600M, angled out in the straight and closed off strongly to win.
Settled midfield 2 wide, stayed on well for 2nd, best stride late.
Settled midfield on the rail, responded well in the straight, just one pace inside 50M.
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide, closed off okay
Raced behind midfield on the rail, saved ground rounding the turn, made good progress in the straight.
Settled near the rear, under pressure from 800M, stayed on okay.
Sat last and switched to center track in the straight, only able to pass weakened rivals.
Settled near last on the rail, made some late headway.
Settled behind the lead 2 wide, limited response in the straight. (See Incident Report)
Broke well and led, weakened inside 200M.
Caught 3 wide no cover in front of midfield, ridden along throughout and weakened in the straight.
Sat just behind the speed on the rail, under the whip at 350M and no response. (See Incident Report) (Performance unacceptable, must trial)

Began from a wide draw settling some 5L back in midfield in 5th, gained closer when pace slackened on home bend and snuck up further entering straight, obtained run over 250 metres out and just got up on line.
Settled worse than midfield in 7th, commenced move 600 metres out swinging one of the widest into straight, gained narrow advantage over 200 metres out only to be pipped at post.
Settled in rear and waited with, remained similar into straight, did not find much room until over 200 metres out, fought on steadily without threatening.
Broke well, settled one back 2-wide most of the way, commenced move over 400 metres out, tight inside runners and a difficult ride early in straight, made no impression closing stages.
Held up in 3rd over 3L back in back straight, became closer 800 metres out, saved ground on rails turning for home, unable to sustain effort inside final 150 metres.

Settled just better than midfield in 4th some 4L off the pace, closer to lead passing the Rock, commenced move 3-wide home bend gaining every chance into straight, unable to sustain effort inside final 180 metres.
Moderate start, making headway behind midfield when crowded on top of stables bend, travelled 3-wide with cover towards rear in back straight, given reminders wide around home bend but found nothing.

Shared early lead 3-wide before obtaining rails run in front on top of first bend, set fast pace early in back straight before steadying up past the Rock, soon headed after home turn and folded up quickly.
Began well from a wide gate, close up in joint 3rd 3-wide before taken back to midfield remaining wide without cover in back straight, remained similar until yielding ground from over 400 metres out.
Soon dropped to rear and trailed the field throughout, never seen with a chance.
Began well then restrained to race in a rail position ahead of midfield, angled out to challenge top of straight, quickened up strongly to lead 150M, well in control final stages.
Settled down 3-wide in midfield, finished off well in the straight to go 2nd near 50M, not reach winner.
Reserved towards the rear racing along the 3-path, 5Ls to make up top of straight, stayed on moderately to go 3rd just before line but never a threat to first two.
Chased leaders in 3rd, kept on steadily in the straight but not going the pace to challenge first two. Claimed 4th in a photo.

Went forward vying for lead on outside, emerged as leader 700M, fought on early straight but unable to hold off winner near 150M, faded late stages to finish 5th. (Jockey : lay in in the straight, difficult to ride out.)
Jumped only fairly, held up 2-wide in midfield, responded fairly turning for home and never going the pace to challenge.
Vied for early lead along inside, in 2nd spot making home turn, fought hard for the lead early straight, couldn't sustain run passing 200M, faded towards the line.
Unable to slot in from draw 12, chased leaders 3-wide, no cover after 700M, kept on same pace on straightening, never pose any threat.
Unhurried after the start, settled behind midfield, driven along nearing 400M but failed to muster a rally.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners, towards the rear 7Ls off the pace, came up empty on straightening, never involved.
Slow to begin, settled down behind midfield along the fence, came under pressure home turn, soon weakened out of contention.
Dropped back, ended up in last, scrubbed along halfway but couldn't muster, lost touch with rivals home turn, never in the picture. (Jockey : reluctant to stretch out middle stages.)
Bumped start, raced towards rear on the outside, 6 lengths back, commenced move 500M, very wide turning in, finished off very strongly to score.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, angled out 400M, finished off strongly to take 2nd, just beaten by a narrow margin.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the first two final 50M.
Away well, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, 2 wide turning in, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 11, raced at tail, 6 to 7 lengths back turning in, very wide into straight, made very good progress in the run home to be nearest on line.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, 4 lengths back, saved ground on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Moderately away from the widest draw, positioned 3 wide with cover, 4 lengths back, very wide turning in, finished off evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the inside, 6 lengths back, there to turn, made some progress early in straight, no clear run 200M to 100M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Average to begin, raced prominently, travelled keenly in the early and middle stages, peaked 400M, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.) (Lame left front leg next day morning.)
Away with them, raced 3 wide with no cover, slightly better than midfield, moved closer after passing 700M, 2nd on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened and eased thereafter.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, 3 wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter. (Bled.)
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
