Average to begin, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, challenged the leader turning in, hit the front 300M, kept on strongly to the line.
Began well from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, closed off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Taken back to race towards rear on the outside, 4 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Taken back to race at tail, 5 lengths or so back, same position on turn, hard ridden after passing 300M, made some progress to make frame.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, challenged by rival turning in, peaked and headed 300M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced in midfield on the outside, 3 lengths or so back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter. (Blood in trachea.)
Slightly slow out, raced behind midfield on the inside, 4 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)

Chased leader 2-wide in a very slow run race, driven near 400M to challenge for the lead before gaining upper hand final 100M. Ridden out to prevail. (Trainer : suited today by racing outside the lead in a slowly run race.)
Soon led, allowed to dictate proceedings with a very slow pace, tried hard on straightening to fight off pursuing rival, grudgingly gave way final 100M.
Tracked leaders in a slowly run race, held up for a few strides near 200M, kept on well late under top weight to claim 3rd just in time but was comfortably held by first two.

Reserved in mid-division, raced keenly middle stages in a very slowly run race, looked threatening mid-straight when driven out to challenge leaders, flattened final 100M losing 3rd place last stride.
Jumped awkwardly and lost ground then taken across behind runners to race in last, pace very slow throughout, 4-5Ls to make up 400M, closed off fastest to be nearest at the line.
Dropped back to near the rear, pushed wide entering home turn, kept on fairly final 300M, not reach leaders.
Jumped only fairly, obtained a midfield spot in mid-division along the fence, couldn't go on passing 300M, never threatened.
Caught 3-wide no cover in a slowly run race, crept forward halfway to be tracking leaders making the home turn, couldn't sustain run passing 300M, faded towards the line.
Shifted across behind runners, raced towards the rear in a very slow run race, driven along 450M but not going the pace to challenge.
In 4th place on settling, pace very slow, driven along 450M but failed to respond, dropped to last place 200M from home.
Ridden along to lead on the stands' rail until 750M, travelled smoothly, kept on well to win.
Slow to begin, sat midfield one off the stands' rail, angled in inside 200M, closed off nicely to hold 2nd (See Incident Report).
Sat worse than midfield on the stands' rail, travelled well, switched in and made some ground over the final 100M, finished off okay.
Sat handy one off the stands' rail, made some progress inside 150M, finished off evenly (See Incident Report).
Chased the leader and led after 750M, but one pace after 350M (See Incident Report).
Settled towards rear 4 off the stands' rail, no clear run and held up until 200M, could not be fully tested (See Incident Report).
Jumped awkwardly, sat towards rear center of the track, made some progress early of the Straight, closed off fairly (Blood in the horse's trachea).
Sat rear center of the track, just one pace, never a threat.
Sat rear 2 off the stands' rail, showed some response at 200M, but just not quick enough.
Jumped awkwardly, settled midfield 2 off the stands' rail, limited response in the Straight, never going the pace to challenge.
Settled midfield 4 off the stands' rail, travelled evenly, weakened at 150M.
Jumped fairly, sat midfield center of the track, gave ground and weakened inside 100M.
Sat in front of midfield 3 off the stands' rail, eased after 150M after being hampered, not tested (Performance unacceptable, BT) (See Incident Report).
Settled handy 3 off the stands' rail, no impression (Heart Irregularity).

Steadied & taken back to second last. Was relegated to last near the 750m. Was lest entering final section, eased outwards to be second widest before sprinting strongly to dash to lead near 150m before going on to win easily.

Raced three wide early before steadying & getting position 1,1 from about the 1200m. Shared lead fleetingly near 175m before passed by winner, battled hard & was a little wayward when fighting on to hold second.
Raced third last away from the rail. Had clear running when just over 3L from the lead on straightening before closing off steadily down the outside to just be beaten for second on line.

Began only fairly & was ridden along after the start & improving along rail to race in midfield in middle stages. Held up early in straight before getting clear & closing strongly between runners late.
Raced in midfield away from the rail throughout. Eased three wide at the 500m, closed steadily all the way to the line & wasn't far behind second when holding midfield finish.
Improved after the start to eventually share lead from about the 1200m. Was joined near the 175m, passed quickly by winner soon after before over-run for minor prizemoney in the final 50m.

Steadied & taken back to a clear last after the start. About 3L behind second last after first section before improving along rail to be second last from the 750m. Battled on to hold deficit in straight but was never likely.
Raced on the rail following the leader for the majority. Moved off the rail after straightening, was still close at the 250m before weakening a few lengths in the last 150m.

Held lead momentarily after start before over-racing when being steadied & sharing lead from 1200m. Was a length behind on straightening before weakening badly from 350m & finished a distant second last (mucus in trachea).

Raced four wide when only 1L from the lead up until the 1200m before being steadied & drifting back to midfield from the 1000m. Was the widest runner on cornering before weakening badly in the straight to be very long last.
Slightly slow out, raced towards rear on the inside, angled out approaching 450M, finished off strongly to score.
Slowly away, raced at tail, 6 lengths or so back, commenced move 500M, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to take 2nd, nearest finish.
Jumped well, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared 200M, finished off well to take a place without threatening.
Began only fairly, raced behind midfield on the outside, a bit closer on turn, wide into straight, showed good response early in straight, peaked on run 200M, ran on evenly to the line.
Average to begin, raced prominently, 2 wide, shared lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Shifted in at start and bumped, unable to slot in, trapped wide, a length or so back, similar position on turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Commenced well, raced behind midfield on the inside, 3 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared 150M, made no progress thereafter.
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 lengths or so back, angled out 400M, unable to obtain clear run until approaching final 100M, one-paced thereafter.
Began well from gate 9, trapped very wide in midfield, very wide turning in, showed some response early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Away with them, positioned 1 out 1 back, similar position on turn, unable to obtain clear run early in straight, made no progress thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, 3 wide, shared lead on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M.
Moderately away from gate 1, sent forward to race prominently on the inside, shared lead on turn, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened and eased thereafter.
Broke on terms, showed sufficient pace early to sit handy and behind the lead, travelled strongly throughout, quickened very well and kicked clear, impressive.
Broke a tad slow and settled at the rear 2 wide, angled out rounding the Home Turn, closed off well, but no threat to winner. (See Incident Report)
Caught 3 wide in front of midfield throughout, under pressure from the 600M, ran on okay.
Jumped on terms and ridden along to lead, weakened inside 150M.
Settled midfield on the rail, only one pace when asked.
Settled at the rear on the rail, made decent progress along the rail, ran out of room last 50M and not fully tested.
Broke alertly but was soon steadied to be near the rear 2 wide, made no impression
Settled worse than midfield on the rail, did not quickened in the Straight. (Blood in trachea)
Settled worse than midfield 3 wide, weakened in the straight.
Settled midfield 2 wide, never a threat.

Moderate start, rushed up on rail to within 3L of pace and travelling keenly, similarly positioned rounding home bend and obtained clear run over 350 metres out, gained upper hand inside final 100 metres.
Well there, taken back to 3rd tracking race leaders around home bend, came to challenge on straightening and hit the front over 200 metres out, unable to sustain effort and headed 100 metres out.

Taken back from wide draw for rails run from last to 9th some 6L off the lead, similarly positioned rounding home bend angling out for a run on straightening, ran on well inside final 200 metres to be nearest at finish.
Gradually taken back from a wide draw and waited with, went for an inside run on straightening and ran on well final 200 metres to be nearest at finish.
Moderate start travelling well behind on the rail, snuck closer to 5L 8th entering home straight, fought on steadily without quickening.

Jumped well but soon taken back to 5th just over 2L off 3-wide without cover, improved to dispute lead rounding home bend and hit the front 500 metres out, led until headed 200 metres out and weakened.

Travelling keenly in 2L 4th when snatched back to 5th 1000 metres out, produced modest impression under pressure early in straight until finding no extra inside final 150 metres. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Began well but soon taken back to last few, commenced move very wide around home bend and remained in rear into straight, made up late ground inside final 150 metres. (Tactic questioned)
Taken back from a wide draw to reach last before home bend, widest in last turning for home, produced good late impression inside final 150 metres.
Soon took up running holding narrow advantage to the 500 metres, hung on under pressure in first few until overhauled inside final 150 metres.
Travelled keenly in last few, saved ground turning for home, kept on well without threatening.
Soon recovered from moderate start to 1L 3rd on rail, became 2L 4th coming onto home bend, kept on before fading under pressure closing stages.
Settled in midfield, hung in away from whip early in straight, made no impression inside final 200 metres.
Travelled in midfield and keenly in back straight, lost position making home turn, made no further impression.
Soon moved to the front setting a slow tempo in early and middle stages, kept giving when placed under pressure on straightening, all out late stages to hold off pursuing rivals.

Taken back from wide draw, settled towards the rear in a slowly run race, made good headway passing mid-straight, briefly held up 100M before hitting the line well to take 2nd close home. Nearest line.
Tracked leaders in a slowly run race, tried hard to get close to leader on straightening, still 1.5L behind at 100M before doing best work late to be nearest at the finish.
Jumped awkwardly, strolled forward to be tracking leader on outside, fought on steadily in the straight but not getting closer to the leader, held 2nd spot until 50M.
In 4th place never far off from the pace, well placed to strike turning home, had every chance but was well held by leaders over final 200M.

Began fairly, obtained a midfield spot along the fence, raced keenly middle stages in a slow run race, kept on steadily in the straight but was held up 150-100M. Could have finished closer to 4th and 5th.

Heavily retrained in midfield, into clear 350M, kept on mildly towards the line, had to ease from a rival late and not ridden out close home. (Jockey : his mount not suited by slow early pace. / Lame next day.)
From wide draw drifted back to race at the rear, 4.5L to make up top of straight after running a slow 800m, was making headway until final 150M when held up and couldn't be tested to the finish.
Dropped back to last, raced keenly middle stages in a slowly run race, found less than expected in the finish. (Jockey : his mount's action shortened over final 200M / Mucus.)
Caught 3-wide in midfield, lost cover going into the bend, kept on same pace in the straight, never in contention.
Hampered on jumping, raced behind midfield 5Ls back, under pressure 550M but didn't respond to riding. Never a factor.
Began only fairly, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, hit the front 250M, kept on very well to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared 150M, finished off well to take 2nd.
Shifted in at start and made contact, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out after passing 700M, very wide turning in, closed off well to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Began only fairly, raced towards rear on the outside, very wide turning in, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Began smartly from gate 1, raced prominently on the inside, 2 wide on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the inside, 5 to 6 lengths back turning in, kept to inside after straightening and made some progress.
Shifted out at start and bumped, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked and headed 250M, weakened inside final furlong.
Bumped start, taken back to race towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened thereafter.

Out with rest, raced 2 wide behind midfield, commenced move 600M, very wide into straight, made some progress early in straight, peaked on run 200M, weakened thereafter. (Lost left hind plate near 500M.)
Made contact at start, raced towards rear on the outside, 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, no clear run and raced tight early in straight, made no progress thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 1-1/2L back, 3 wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final 250M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away, positioned 2 wide, 3 lengths back, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final 250M.
Slightly slow out, raced behind midfield on the inside, 2 wide after passing 600M, no clear run and raced tight early in straight, made no progress thereafter.
Began well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, trapped very wide, 1-1/2L back, similar position on turn, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect.

Bumped shortly after start, raced 2W behind midfield early, 3W from 1100M, a bit closer in the middle stages, 3 lengths back turning in, showed very good response in straight, hit the front 200M, kept on strongly to the line.
Made contact at start, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length on turn, hard ridden 300M, peaked and headed 200M, ran on evenly to take 2nd.
Taken back from gate 12, raced at tail, 6 lengths or so back on turn, wide into straight, finished off strongly to take a place, nearest finish.

Average to begin, positioned 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, no daylight early in straight, cleared 200M, made some progress thereafter to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide towards rear, 5 to 6 lengths back turning in, made some progress in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Began well from a tricky gate, raced in midfield on the outside, a bit closer on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Average to begin, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.

Made contact at start, positioned a length or so back on the outside in the early stages, found a 2 wide spot near 1100M, 2 lengths or so back turning in, showed limited response early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back on turn, angled out 450M, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.

Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide towards rear, angled out after passing 450M, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to score. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 3 wide after passing 750M, a bit closer in the middle stages, 3 lengths back turning in, closed off well to take 2nd.

Bumped start, positioned 5 lengths behind the leader on the inside, angled out after passing 450M, same margin back turning in, made good progress early in straight, no clear run 200M to 100M, finished off well to take a place.
Away well, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, unable to obtain clear running until final 100M, finished off well to make frame.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide slightly better than midfield, no cover after entering the back straight, 2 lengths back turning in, showed limited response in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began fairly, raced at rear on the outside, 6 lengths back turning in, very wide into straight, made good progress in the run home.

Shifted out at start, took the lead, headed 1150M, sat 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader in the middle stages, saved ground on turn, not enough room early in straight, cleared 200M but only showed limited response, one-paced final 50M.

Began fairly, trapped wide, slightly better than midfield, moved closer after passing 1050M, 2nd in the middle stages, challenged the leader turning in, took the lead early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, weakened 100M.
Began awkwardly, raced at rear on the inside, angled out 550M, very wide turning in, passed some tired runners in straight. (Lost left front plate near the 700M.)

Began well, raced prominently on the inside, difficult to settle in the early stages, inconvenienced 1300M, took the lead 1150M, led by 3/4L, challenged by rival turning in, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened final furlong.

Began well, raced 3 wide, a length or so back, 2 wide from 1100M, 2 lengths behind in the middle stages, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped awkwardly, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened and eased final 100M.
Began well before settling in midfield, commenced move wide into home straight, responded well inside final 150 metres to assert authority shortly after.

Broke well before taken back in midfield, raced keenly on rail gaining steadily to 6th 700 metres out, saved ground on home turn and switched out for a run early in straight, quickened inside final 100 metres.
Soon came from a wide draw to join the leaders, gained slender advantage 600 metres out coming onto home bend, led until swamped inside 100 metres.
Taken back from a wide draw, remained in last few to straight, did not find much room early on, produced moderate late impression inside final 150 metres.
Pressed forward from a wide draw to take up running on rail turning into back straight, led the field until narrowly headed 600 metres out, saved ground in 3rd turning for home, one-paced.

Not far off early stages, dropped to 5th some 2L back passing 800 metres, raced keenly in middle stages, badly bumped making final turn but recovered well and made modest progress in straight until the 100 metres.
Travelled wide without cover the majority of race and mainly in midfield, widest runner turning for home, ran on past well-beaten runners.
Began well from the one draw and soon taken some 2L back to 4th on rail, shifted out for a run making final turn bumping others and unbalanced, kept on same pace without quickening under pressure.
Began awkwardly losing ground travelling in last few on rail, gained to 9th over 900 metres out and racing keenly, switched inside for a run early in straight, ran home one-paced.
Taken well behind from the widest draw, saved ground making home turn, kept on well. (Riding questioned)
Broke well but quickly taken back to one from last, dropped to last into straight, made no further impression. (Jockey reported saddle shifted)
Moderate start, improved steadily wide in back straight to join race leaders 3-wide inside 800 metres, remained similar into straight but folded up quickly inside final 200 metres.
Settled in front of midfield, travelled smoothly, showed some progress under pressure inside 150M, closed off nicely.
Jumped only fairly, sat behind midfield on the rail, was crowded at the early Straight, responded well at the final 50M to grab 2nd.
Broke nicely, ridden hard to sit handy on the rail, showed some response inside 200M but just not quick enough.
Jumped nicely, ridden along to lead on the rail, ran on evenly (Lost left front plate).
Sat midfield on the rail, was crowded in the Straight, stayed on well.
Settled towards rear 2 wide, angled out in the Straight, showed some dash over the concluding stages.
Sat worse than midfield 3 wide, held up in the early Straight, not fully tested (See Incident Report).
Sat worse than midfield, began to improve at 550M, but one pace thereafter.
Sat rear, showed limited response under pressure in the Straight, made no progress.
Settled towards rear 2 wide, no impression.
Jumped awkwardly, settled in front of midfield 3 wide, hung out in the Straight, never a threat (See Incident Report).
Sat handy 2 wide, eased after 150M (Heart Irregularity).
Had a nice run in midfield along the rail. Moved away from the rail near the 400m when 3L from lead, closed strongly to steal strike lead at 150m & went on to win by soft 0.5L.

Raced just off of midfield away from the rail throughout. Was over 4L from the lead at the 400m, held up for a short distance on straightening before closing strongly in the last 150m to steal fast finishing second on line.

Raced in midfield in the clear in first half. Eased four wide when 2.5L behind at the 400m, closed to second passing the 150m before being caught for runner-up placing in final stride & was only beaten half-length on line.
Pushed forward, raced third early before being 4th along the rail from half-way. Was under 2L from lead on cornering & battled away ok to be beaten a similar margin on line.
Raced in midfield away from the rail throughout. Moved wider on the track to improve near the 450m, was the widest on cornering before finishing off steadily down the outside to not be beaten far.

Shared lead early before racing on the leaders back from the 1200m. Came off the rail approaching the 650m bend, was under 1L from the lead on straightening before weakening slightly late to be beaten 2.5L into midfield.
Pushed forward to lead. Was passed by the winner at the 150m before weakening a few lengths in final stages.
Raced 4th early before improving to third near the 1000m mark when coursing away from the rail. Improved to be three wide no cover approaching the 650m, peaked at the 175m & gave a few lengths late.

Steadied at start & taken back to race at the rear. Moved three wide passing the 600m, improved position approaching corner, shifted outwards to be the widest after straightening, made some late ground but was too far back.
Steadied & taken across behind runners from the outside gate & raced rearward. Was last & over 7L form the lead on cornering, made up a few lengths but was too far back & still only beat two home.
Raced worse than midfield along the rail throughout. Was over 6L behind at the 400m & made no real ground, second last.
Had no early speed & was steadied between runners soon after start & raced third last throughout. Was relegated to second last passing the 500m & never got involved in the straight. Last.
Began smartly, raced prominently on the inside, allowed rival to cross near 600M, sat right behind the leader on turn, finished off well, won by a head.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length turning in, kept on very well in straight, just unable to hold off the winner close home.
Bumped shortly after start, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off strongly to take a place.
Began only fairly, raced in midfield on the outside, 4 lengths or so back on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame, nearest on line.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced behind midfield on the outside, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to be nearest on line.
Bumped shortly after start, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, made some progress early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Average to begin, raced in midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 450M, made some progress early in straight, peaked on run 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Crowded start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, made contact and unbalanced near 600M, 5 lengths back turning in, showed limited response in straight. (Mucus.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Shifted out at start, raced slightly better than midfield on the outside, wide into straight, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Began awkwardly, raced towards rear on the inside, 7 lengths or so back on turn, made good progress early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Began well from a wide draw, tracked leaders on the outside, 1-1/2L back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Began only fairly, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Settled midfield 2 wide, travelled comfortably throughout, angled out at 350M and closed off strongly, battled gamely, always doing enough.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, struck the front at 150M, and could not hold off the winner.
Jumped with the field and settled on the rail worse than midfield, stayed on okay, no threat to the top 2.
Settled behind the speed, only one pace when asked.
Shifted across towards the rail after the start, settled 2 wide near the rear, circled the field rounding the Home Turn, and closed off fairly.
Settled at the rear on the rail, navigate through traffic in the straight and made good progress between horses.
Stalked leader, kept on evenly. (rider dropped his rein)
Settled midfield on the rail, made no impression.
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide, made no ground. (See Incident Report)
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, had difficulties obtaining clear running, never fully tested.
Jumped well and ridden along to lead, weakened inside 200M.
Settled last, never stretched out and eased down. (See Incident Report)
Jumped best before taken some 3L back to 5th, remained similar onto home bend, angled off rail for a run on straightening, hit the front over 200 metres out for comfortable victory.
Began well before settling in worse than midfield niggling along at times in back straight, saved ground turning for home, fought on steadily without threatening.
Travelled keenly towards rear wide without cover, made steady headway from over 600 metres out to be widest into straight, fought on under pressure to reach 3rd late.
Settled in rear, crowded and lost position 600 metres out, went very wide into straight, made up good ground down the centre of track.
Settled at the back, commenced move 3-wide 700 metres out to reach 5L 9th onto home bend, briefly baulked on straightening, fought on steadily closing stages.

Broke well travelling some 4L back in 6th, carried backward and lost position over 600 metres out while racing ungenerously, saved ground and within 3L of pace turning for home, unable to sustain effort in straight.
Travelled prominently wide without cover, restrained over 2L back in 4th in back straight, went wide for a run into home straight, made no impression.
Pressed forward from a wide draw, led 3-wide over 900 metres out and obtaining rails run 600 metres out, led until headed by eventual winner over 200 metres out. (Tactic questioned)
Settled in last few on rail, saved ground turning for home, one-paced in straight. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Ridden to lead on rail, ceded advantage over 900 metres out, weakened under pressure shortly after straightening.
Settled in midfield, drifted backward to last few over 700 metres out, made no further impression. (Mucus in trachea)
Ridden forward after moderate start to soon reach 1L 3rd , folded up quickly after straightening.
Chased leader 2-wide, challenged strongly for the lead early straight, led near 150M, continued on well to the line.
Restrained to a rearward position after jumping from draw 10, 3-wide making the turn for home, closed off well down outside of straight, nearest finish.
Went forward for the lead, slowed things down 700M, kept on well turning in, headed by winner near 150M before losing 2nd close home.
Reserved in midfield 4Ls off the pace, ran on under top weight passing 300M, just missed 3rd.
Settled in 4th, always in touch, put in a mild bid passing 400M, peaked on its run 100M from home.
From draw 1 moved up to track leaders, lacked a finishing kick passing 300M, always held by leaders in the run home.
Dropped back towards the rear, raced keenly early and middle stages, ran on fairly over final 300M, not reach contention.
Unhurried after the start, unable to slot in from draw 11, raced 3-wide without cover in midfield, not quickened passing 350M, faded final 200M.
Crossed to race along the rail in mid-division, fought on one paced turning in, steadied 150M and quickly out of contention.
Settled towards the rear, 6Ls off the pace 400M, failed to make much progress on straightening. Never a factor.
Failed to muster speed despite ridden along, fell back to last 600M, soon left behind top of straight. (Jockey : failed to stretch out and raced in a disappointing manner.)
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced 2 wide in midfield, bumped 550M, 4 lengths back on turn, finished off very strongly to score.
Began fairly from gate 1, raced slightly better than midfield on the inside, angled out 400M, closed off well to take 2nd.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide better than midfield, very wide into straight, finished off well to take a place, not quite able to challenge.
Began fairly, raced towards rear on the inside, 5 to 6 lengths back, saved ground throughout, finished off well to make frame without threatening.
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1-1/2L on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 100M, weakened final 50M.
Commenced well, sat right behind the leader on rail, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 8, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back, same margin back on turn, very wide into straight, made some headway in the run home.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 7 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made some progress in straight. (Lame left front leg next day morning.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the outside, 6 lengths back, similar position on turn, made no impression in straight.
Jumped with them, sent forward to race in 2nd, a length or so back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Burst out of stalls, raced in midfield on the outside, bumped near 550M, 4 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.

Jumped well from gate 11, raced in midfield on the outside, moved closer after passing 700M, 4 wide turning in, hit the front 200M, kept on very well to the line and scored.
Began well from gate 1, raced slightly better than midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 800M, 3 wide turning in, no clear run early in straight, cleared 300M, finished off well to take 2nd.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 wide from 900M, a bit closer on turn, showed good response early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced behind midfield on the inside, angled out after passing 600M, 3 to 4 lengths back turning in, finished off well to make frame without threatening.
Taken back from gate 13, raced towards rear on the inside, 4 lengths or so back turning in, finished off well without threatening.
Out with rest, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, challenged the leader turning in, took the lead 300M, peaked and headed 200M, weakened final 100M.
Away with them, raced 2 wide towards rear, 5 to 6 lengths back turning in, made some progress in straight.
Commenced well, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Slow to begin, raced at tail early, sent forward after passing 1250M, raced in midfield on outer in the middle stages, very wide into straight, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Began fairly, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Away well, sent forward to take the lead, challenged by rival turning in, peaked and headed 300M, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped awkwardly, raced towards rear on the outside, moved closer on turn, very wide into straight, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.

Taken back from gate 14, raced at rear on the inside, angled out after passing 1100M, raced 3 wide at rear in the middle stages, very wide turning in, failed to close off in straight. (Blood in trachea.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, wider after passing 600M, 5 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter. (Blood in trachea.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Had a nice run on the leaders back. Moved into clear running passing the 400m, closed strongly to go past the leader very quickly at the 100m before drawing away to win easily.

Bumped & hampered at the start before racing just off midfield in the clear. Was the widest runner on cornering when around 4.5L from the lead before closing well down the outside to second final few strides.

Pushed forward to race outside the leader. Cruised to the lead under no riding at the 375m, asked for full effort passing the 200m & commenced to race very greenly, passed by winner near the 100m before tiring late.

Steadied & taken back to race third last after start. Continued with only three rivals behind on cornering when 5L from the lead before making some late progress to move to well beaten 4th in final 125m.

Steadied & taken back from the outside gate to race at the rail. Was 6L from the lead on straightening, shifted outwards at the 300m before passing a number of rivals when running onto well beaten midfield finish.
Raced three wide with cover in midfield. Raced tight passing the 500m & again entering the last section when 4L behind before finishing off only one paced to be well beaten in midfield on the line.

Crowded soon after start & consequently lost ground before improving to race in midfield along the rail. Was just over 3L from lead entering final section before finishing only one paced to be well beaten over 7L in midfield.

Jumped awkwardly & lost ground before mustering speed & improving position to race 1,1 from about the 1000m. Was only 2.5L from the lead entering final section but weakened in final furlong to be beaten over 7L.

Pushed forward from wide gate before racing three wide without cover just forward of midfield. Was only just over 1L from the lead entering final section but wide passage took its toll & weakened out in final furlong.
Showed good early speed to lead. Headed by the third place-getter soon after straightening before weakening out quickly in final 100m. Well beaten.
Raced in midfield between runners. Was 4.5L from the lead entering final section before doing little in the straight & weakening to be beaten 8.5L.

Steadied & got head up after the start & was taken back worse than midfield. Hung outwards around the bend & consequently straightened in last place before failing to do anything in the straight & was well beaten third last.
Raced wide in midfield & was left 4 deep without cover from after the first bend. Bumped at the 400m mark when 4L from the lead before weakening out sharply in last 250m to be beaten about 11L.

Was slow to begin, conceding about 4L before crossing down to the rail & racing second last. Stayed along the rail on straightening when over 6L behind but did nothing in the straight & weakened to be a long last.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, travelled smoothly, showed some dash over the concluding stages, finished off strongly.
Chased the leader 2 wide, travelled strongly, made some progress in the Straight, could not hold off the winner.
Sat midfield 3 wide without cover, travelled nicely, stayed on well to hold 3rd.
Jumped only fairly, sat towards rear 3 wide, closed off okay.
Settled midfield on the rail, had difficulty obtain clear running in the Straight, not fully tested.
Jumped with the field, settled midfield 2 wide between horses, only one pace when asked.
Settled worse than midfield 4 wide, showed minor progress in the Straight, ran on evenly.
Sat handy on the rail, limited response when asked over the final 200M.
Ridden hard to lead 2 wide, weakened gradually over the final 300M (See Incident Report).
Sat towards rear 3 wide, never a threat.
Jumped awkwardly, sat worse than midfield on the rail, stayed on fairly early in the Straight but soon faded
Sat rear, made no impression.
Reared as the start was effected, sat towards rear.
Sat towards rear 2 wide, never a factor.

Raced 4th along the rail before coming away from the rail when the pace steadied near 750m. Moved up to share the lead near the 225m, before over-powering the immediate challenger in final 100m & pulling away to win well.

Raced third away from the rail before improving to race outside the leader when the pace slower passing the 750m. Took the lead early in the straight, shared lead from 225m but was over-powered last 100m. Good effort.

Raced just behind midfield early before improving to midfield around the bend when galloping between runners. Moved into clear running at the 400m when just over 2L behind before finishing off one paced to third.

Raced in midfield along the rail in early & middle stages. Came away from the rail near the 500m, was 2.5L from the lead entering final section before closing off steadily to move to 4th in final 150m.

Was steadied & taken back from the outside gate to race a clear last. Was 6.5L from the lead in straightening before shifting outwards & making eye-catching late ground down the outside from a long way back.

Crowded at the start & consequently lost ground & raced second last. Steadied away from heels between 900m-800m when pace slowed. Was 4.5L from the lead on straightening before making late ground between runners to midfield.

Raced in midfield away from the rail. Was then three wide but with cover from about 750m, was slightly awkward on straightening when just over 3L from the lead but made no headway in the straight & held position to the line.

Was trapped racing three wide without cover in midfield after the start. Moved closer to the lead & forced 4 wide passing 750m when pace slowed, was still just behind at 200m before wide passage took its toll, weakening late.

Steadied at the start & taken back to race worse than midfield when wide with cover. Improved to midfield around the 800m bend when continuing wide, was the widest on straightening before finishing only moderately late.
Pushed forward before racing on the leaders back. Was hampered near the 700m when close to leaders heels. Was under 2L behind on straightening but weakened out to be beaten 8.5L.
Drifted back to race worse than midfield along the rail. Moved away from the rail just before straightening, was 4.5L from the lead entering final section but did nothing & weakened to be beaten 9L.
Pushed forward to lead. Joined & headed in the lead early in the straight before weakening poorly to be beaten just under 10L.
Bumped at the start before racing third last away from the rail. Continued near the tail on straightening, was over 6L behind entering last section but did nothing & was a long last.
Began well, raced in 2nd, a length back on turn, hit the front 350M, kept on very strongly to the line, easily scored.
Taken back to race at tail, 4 lengths or so back, commenced move 450M, finished off very strongly to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Away well, raced in 3rd, 2 wide, briefly crowded near 800M, a length or so back turning in, hard ridden from 200M but only showed limited response, ran on evenly to the line.
Began fairly from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed some response early in straight, no extra final 150M.
Began well, raced 3 wide behind midfield, 2-1/2L back turning in, made no impression in straight.
Slowly away, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made no impression in straight.
Average to begin, positioned 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length on turn, peaked and headed 350M, weakened final 300M.
Jumped on terms, settled near the rear 2 wide, switched out at the 500M, responded very well when asked, closed off strongly to score.
Caught 3 wide behind midfield with cover, took some time to respond, quickened nicely to grab 2nd.
Settled midfield 3 wide, angled out at 600M to improve, and made good progress early in the straight, but only one pace after 150M.
Broke only fairly and settled at the rear, stayed on well inside 300M, best stride late.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, made limited progress.
Ridden along early to sit outside the lead, kept on okay.
Settled at the rear on the rail, held up early in the straight and got hampered near 100M, never fully tested. (See Incident Report)
Sat behind the speed on the rail, made minor progress.
Sat worse than midfield on the rail, unable to obtain clear running until 300M, was inconvenienced near 100M, and ran on ordinarily.
Raced worse than midfield 2 wide, made no impression.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, had trouble in running for the majority of the straight, not tested.
Broke well and ridden to be prominent, sat 2 wide behind the leaders, weakened inside 150M.
Caught 3 wide no cover, never a threat.
Hard ridden in the early stage to lead, weakened and faded inside 250M.

Obtained cover over 2L back in 3rd 1300 metres out, gained closer 2-wide about 1L back inside the 1000 metres, further closer in 3rd rounding home bend and hit the front shortly after straightening, hung on well under pressure.
Settled in 5th just worse than mid-division of the small field, commenced move 3-wide 600 metres out, ran on steadily under pressure inside final 300 metres to reach 2nd late.
Broke well from a wide draw to lead 2-wide establishing a quick tempo, narrowly headed over 700 metres out and re-gained lead briefly entering straight, lost 2nd under pressure 50 metres out.

Travelled 3-wide some 1L back in 3rd, improved 3-wide around home bend and hit the front briefly 700 metres out, kept on from 3rd into straight until losing it over 150 metres out. (Jockey warned for riding tactic early stages)
Slow to begin settling in rear and waited with, commenced move on straightening reaching within 3L of pace in 6th early in straight, fought on steadily but never threatening.
Soon taken back to rear of small field, came within 3L of pace on straightening, unable to sustain effort inside final 200 metres. (Blood in trachea)
Began fairly but soon dropped to 6th and over 5L back in back straight, gained closer to within 3L of pace 3-wide rounding home bend, wider into straight and soon weakened.
Travelled keenly in 2nd on the rail early stages, became 4th over 1L back onto home bend, saved ground turning into straight and folded up quickly.
Settled in 3rd, moved up to challenge nearing top of straight, led 300M and soon driven clear. Well in command final 150M.
Slow to begin, given a waiting ride at the rear, no clear running early straight, did best work final 250M to claim 2nd close home, not reach winner.
Held up behind midfield, put in a mild bid passing 400M, stayed on for 3rd but couldn't get closer to winner.
Allowed uncontested lead, set slow pace throughout, headed near 300M, fought on to hold 2nd until concluding stages.
Settled midfield, pushed along 600M, never going the pace to challenge. (Jockey : the pace was too slow.)
Held up near last in a slowly run race, responded fairly from top of straight, never reach contention.
Tracked leader in a slowly run race, failed to respond passing 400M, weakened to finish last.
Clean jump, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L turning in, kept on well in straight to hold off the challengers. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, similar position on turn, finished off well to take 2nd.
Away well, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, 3 wide from 700M, a bit closer turning in, kept on well in straight to take a place, not quite able to challenge.
Jumped with them, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, closed off well to make frame without threatening.
Began only fairly from gate 1, positioned 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, 2 wide turning in, finished off evenly.

Made contact with the right side of its barrier and lost ground, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths or so back, 3 wide on turn, angled out 500M, no clear run early in straight, made good progress thereafter to be nearest on line.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced behind midfield on the outside, very wide into straight, kept on same pace in straight.
Jumped with them, sat right behind the leader on rail, raced keenly throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began fairly, raced slightly behind midfield on the outside, no cover after passing 1050M, a bit closer in the middle stages, made no impression in straight.
Moderately away, positioned 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide turning in, peaked early in straight, one-paced thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced behind midfield on the inside early, 2 wide from 900M, 4 lengths back turning in, made no progress in straight.
Taken back from gate 12, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide from 900M, 4 lengths back turning in, no clear run early in straight, made no progress thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Bumped start, raced at rear on the outside throughout, never a factor. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, raced in midfield on the outside, 4 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, finished off strongly to score.
Jumped with them, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length on turn, kept on very well in straight, just unable to hold off the winner late.
Moderately away, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on the inside early, angled out 1000M, 3 wide from 800M, a bit closer on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place without threatening.
Bumped start, raced behind midfield on the outside, very wide turning in, made very good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Began well from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some progress in straight.
Bumped start, raced slightly behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back turning in, very wide into straight, made some progress in the run home.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the early lead, headed near 1200M, positioned a length behind the leader in the middle stages, kept on evenly in straight.
Bumped start, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, there to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, wider turning in, showed some response early in straight, blocked near 250M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Moderately away, raced towards rear on the inside, angled out after passing 600M, 5 lengths back turning in, made some headway in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 5 to 6 lengths back turning in, made good progress early in straight, peaked 200M, ran on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the outside, 5 to 6 lengths back turning in, one-paced in the run home. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Bumped start, raced better than midfield on the outside, moved closer after passing 800M, 4 wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened and eased final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)

Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, commenced move 800M, took the lead 550M, led by 1-3/4L turning in, kept on well to the line and scored.
Away well, raced 2 wide, 1-1/2L back, similar position on turn, finished off well to take 2nd, not quite able to challenge.

Began well, raced slightly better than midfield on the inside, dropped towards rear in the middle stages, 2 wide from 600M, 6 lengths back turning in, finished off strongly to take a place, nearest on line.
Made contact at start, raced in midfield on the outside, moved closer after passing 1000M, 4 lengths back turning in, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 9, raced towards rear on the inside, angled out 700M, 6 lengths back turning in, made some progress in straight.
Moderately away, raced behind midfield on the outside, 5 lengths back turning in, very wide into straight, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced behind midfield on the inside, angled out 700M, 7 lengths back turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Made contact at start, raced towards rear on the outside, 6 lengths back turning in, very wide into straight, made no impression in straight.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, 2 wide after entering the back straight, wider turning in, made no progress in straight.
Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, headed near 550M, peaked on turn, weakened final furlong.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, found rail near 500M, 5 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.

Placing: DNF
Comment: Jumped well, positioned a length behind the leader on rail early, dropped to 4th from 800M, unable to maintain position shortly thereafter, eased 600M. (Bled.) (Irregular Heart Rhythm.)
Restrained in midfield along the fence, driven along 300M, did best work final 200M to get up just in time.
Ridden prominently, track leader into straight, responded well turning home, wrestled the lead near 50M but caught by winner just before line.
Soon led, took them along at a steady pace, kept on well to maintain its lead on straightening, headed by first 2 near 50M, held on for 3rd just.
Taken back to the rear, held up early straight before finishing well, almost claimed 3rd. (Bled 2nd time / Compulsory retirement.)
Broke well from draw 1 tracking the pace, fought hard on straightening but always held by leaders, raced in restricted room final 50M.
Taken hold of after the start, settled behind midfield and raced keenly in middle stages, wide into straight before closing off steadily over final 300M.
From draw 12 caught wide no cover chasing leaders throughout, ran on one paced in the straight. (Jockey : contemplated going forward and leading but was reluctant to do so carrying 134lb.)
Slow to begin, ended up racing at the rear, very wide into straight, closed off reasonably well final 300M.

Jumped awkwardly, settled towards the rear further back than intended, held up making the home turn, finished off only fairly. (Jockey : not suited by the early pace being run slightly slower than standard.)
Up with early pace before taking up a position ahead of midfield, not going the pace to challenge top of straight, soon beaten.
Held up towards the rear, never travelled, hard pressed home turn but lacked a finishing kick. Never involved.
Settled 3-wide near the rear, wide into straight, couldn't finish off.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, improved nicely through the rail from the 600M, angled out into the clear at 300M, saved every ground and kicked clear late, always doing enough.
Settled midfield on the rail, closed off nicely along the rail, just held 2nd.
Settled midfield 2 wide, switched out at 350M, ran on nicely, just lost the battle for 2nd.
Hard ridden along early to lead, kept on fairly.
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide, held up early in the Straight, made little progress late. (See Incident Report)
Settled behind midfield on the rail, ran on ordinarily.
Settled near the rear on the rail, under pressure from 600M, showed minor progress late.
Sat just behind the leader early, weakened inside 250M.
Prominently placed, hard ridden at 500M but no response, weakened and faded soon after.
Caught 3 wide no cover midfield, never impress.
Settled last, detached from the field at 500M, never in contention
Settled near the rear, never travelled and eased down. (Performance unacceptable, must trial)
Pushed forward, led momentarily in early stages before racing second in the clear. Moved to the lead at the 225m, hard ridden in the late stages to hold off fast closers to win narrowly.
Raced three deep without cover in midfield throughout. Was 4L form the lead approaching the corner before closing strongly in final stages to charge to fast finishing second when narrowly beaten.
Raced third along the rail throughout. Moved off the rail on straightening before closing strongly in late stages to be narrowly beaten into third.

Steadied & raced worse than midfield after start. Was checked away from heels near 600m consequently shifting outwards & losing ground. Was the widest on straightening, bumped in the straight before finishing strongly late.

Bumped at the start before being steadied & being taken back towards the rear. Was relegated to last near 650m, continued near the tail on straightening before staying nearer the inside & making good late ground.

Bumped at the start before being steadied at first bend & racing at the rear. Raced tight between runners passing the 500m when continuing rearward, raced tight on straightening, finished off only one paced in last furlong.
Raced in midfield along the rail. Was 5L behind entering final section before finishing off only steadily in the straight to hold midfield finish on line.

Jumped only fairly & raced worse than midfield along the rail. Moved off the rail approaching the 400m when 6L from the lead, got close to heels near the 200m before shifting outwards but finishing only moderately late.
Showed customary early speed to move to the lead soon after the start. Joined & passed by the winner approaching the 200m mark before weakening out in last 150m.

Bumped at start, was last early before being caught three wide near the back. Was unbalanced & taken wider when rival horse was checked near 600m, was last & wide on straightening & was never in contention (rider questioned).
Bumped on jumping before racing in fourth place away from the rail. Was ridden along approaching the 400m mark when 3L from the lead before weakening out quickly in the final 250m to be well beaten.

Jumped only fairly before racing ungenerously in the early stages when racing in midfield. Lost ground near the 600m when continuing to be steadied off heels when racing between runners. Weakened poorly in the straight, last.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide in midfield, commenced move 500M, finished off very strongly to score by a narrow margin. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well, sent forward to race in 2nd, 1/2L back on turn, hit the front 150M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner on line.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 wide turning in, made some progress in straight to take a place, no threat to the first two.

Average to begin, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/2L on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, weakened gradually final 100M. (Mucus in trachea.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced behind midfield on the outside, moved a bit closer on turn, made some headway in straight.
Out with rest, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out 350M, made some progress in straight.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Slightly slow out and bumped, raced 2 wide towards rear, 5 lengths back turning in, kept on same pace in straight.
Jumped awkwardly, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground to turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, raced at rear on the inside, 2 wide from 700M, 7 lengths back turning in, failed to make any progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began fairly, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (Blood in trachea.)
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Jumped with the field, settled midfield 2 wide, closed off strongly to score.
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide, stayed on well, best stride late.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, had some trouble obtaining clear running in the Straight, ran on well despite having some trouble obtaining clear running in the Straight.
Ridden along and showed good early speed to lead, travelled comfortably throughout, and looks the winner until weakened inside the final 25M.
Settled midfield on the rail, only one paced when asked.
Settled behind midfield on the rail, made some progress. (See Incident Report)
Broke alertly and settled in a box seated position, showed some dash early but weakened inside 100M.
Pushed forward from a wide barrier to stalk leader, under pressure rounding the Home Turn, weakened inside 200M, a bit green.
Settled near the rear 3 wide, made no impression.
Settled last, never a threat.
Settled at the rear, never in contention.

Gradually settled in midfield after moderate start, dropped further back to 9th over 4L back 600 metres out, briefly baulked early in straight, quickened well inside final 200 metre out to assert authority over 50 metres out.

Settled at the back from the widest gate and waited with, trailed the field to straight, quickened well between runners inside final 200 metres to hold every chance only to be denied by a narrow margin.
Settled in last few after inconvenienced at start, shifted wide into straight, baulked behind runners early on, produced good late impression inside final 200 metres.

Ridden to lead from a middle draw, obtained rails run inside race leader passing the 750 metres, travelled keenly with narrow advantage coming onto home bend, led until overhauled inside final 70 metres.
Amongst early leaders 4-wide, gradually shifted some 3L back to 6th in back straight, came under pressure to challenge on straightening, fought on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Travelled wide without cover in midfield, widest runner into straight, fought on steadily down the centre of the track without threatening.

Ridden along 3-wide in first few from the 3 draw, obtained cover in 3rd one off the rail 800 metres out, switched 3-wide for a run on top of home bend, unable to sustain effort inside final 150 metres.
Mainly in 5th on rail about 2L off the pace, gained 4th over 500 metres out, gradually weakened inside final 150 metres.
Slowly away, soon recovered along the rail to 9th some 4L off the lead, gained closer to 8th 700 metres out, switched out to challenged entering straight but hung in and a difficult ride, fought on.
Soon dropped to last few and never seen with a chance.
Prominent and very wide without cover, came 3-wide to hit the front briefly inside the 900 metres, became 2nd coming onto home bend, folded up quickly inside final 250 metres.
Prominent and wide in early stages, gradually settled 3-wide without cover in 4th in back straight, lost position from top of home bend. (Bled)
From wide draw pressed forward, tracked the pace from 1300M, readily responded on straightening, took lead near 100M and held sway from the persistent 2nd final stages.
Never far off leaders, swung wide for home 400M, responded well under pressure, challenged for the lead final 150M but always held by winner.
Slow to begin, reserved towards the rear in a steadily run race, 5Ls off the pace home turn, stayed on well to go 3rd near line.
Crossed to the lead 1250M, pressed by rival 800M, fought well on straightening, headed near 100M, edged out to 4th late.
Began well, restrained to track leaders along the fence, held up 250M-150M before closing off the race mildly.
Unable to slot in, caught wide no cover in midfield until moving up to share the lead 500M, stayed in contention until 150M, faded towards the line.
Settled 2-wide in midfield, lacked a finishing kick passing 300M, always held by leaders.
Held up in 3-wide in mid-division, raced keenly 1400M, ran on one paced passing 300M, not reach leaders.
Settled near last early stages, switched to 3-wide 1100M, moved closer to midfield entering home turn, lacked a finishing effort on straightening.
From wide draw dropped back to the rear, remained as the back-marker 400M, gave limited response on straightening, never dangerous.
Began awkwardly then shifted across behind runners, settled towards the rear 5-6Ls off the pace, couldn't go on final 300M.
Jumped only fairly, held up midfield on inside, struggled to keep up 550M, gave ground top of the straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, commenced move 400M, very wide turning in, finished off very strongly to score.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, commenced move after passing 450M, 3 wide turning in, finished off well to take 2nd.
Taken back to race 2 wide towards rear, 6 lengths back, angled out 350M, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to take a place, nearest finish.
Moderately away from the widest draw, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead 900M, led by a length on turn, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the first few final 50M.
Jumped well from gate 1, raced better than midfield on rail, 2 wide from 350M, unable to obtain clear run until final 50M, made some progress thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from a wide draw, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, there to turn, kept on well early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Moderately away, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, unable to obtain clear run in straight.
Clean jump, took the early lead, headed near 900M, sat right behind the leader in the middle stages, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened final 50M.
Slowly away, raced towards rear on the inside, angled out after passing 400M, 5 lengths back turning in, finished off evenly.
Jumped awkwardly, raced in midfield on the outside, very wide into straight, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Slow to begin, raced at tail, 7 lengths back turning in, made some progress early in straight, weakened final 100M. (Blood in trachea.)
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong. (Irregular heart rhythm.)
