Began well, positioned a length behind the leader on the stands' side, ridden after passing 450M, hit the front 150M, kept on very well to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well, positioned a length behind the leader on the stands' rail, hard ridden after passing 400M, finished off well to take 2nd.
Average to begin, positioned a length behind the leader, 2 away from the stands' rail, hard ridden from 300M, closed off well to take a place without threatening.
Shifted in at start and made contact, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/2L, hard ridden after passing 350M, peaked and headed 150M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact at start, tracked leaders, nearer to the middle track, ridden from 500M but only showed limited response, one-paced to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from gate 1, sent forward to race prominently, hard ridden after passing 400M but only showed limited response, weakened final 150M.
Jumped with them, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.

Began very awkwardly, raced towards rear on the middle track, a bit closer in the middle stages, hard ridden from 450M, showed limited response, weakened final 300M. (Mucus in trachea.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Settled one back in 4th before carried backward to 3L 4th approaching first bend, saved ground turning for home, quickened well to lead over 200 metres out and soon drew clear.
Led early, ceded advantage for 3rd approaching first bend travelling over 2L off the pace, kept on at the one pace from a similar position into straight.

Began well from the widest draw gradually shifting back to midfield and wide without cover, drifted further behind over 900 metres out remaining in similar position into straight, ran on steadily down the centre of the track.
Settled in midfield on the rail, saved ground turning in, fought on steadily under pressure in straight.
Ridden forward out wide to join the leaders, gained narrow advantage about 1200 metres out and rails run over 900 metres out, held 2L break into straight but headed over 200 metres out.
Travelled keenly in last few on the rail, angled out for a run approaching home turn over 550 metres out, did not find much room until the 250 metres, finished off the race well.
Crowded at start, travelled keenly just worse than midfield, baulked for a run early in straight until the 300 metres, fought on under pressure.
Settled in midfield, in similar position into straight, kept on one pace.
Crowded shortly after start and soon dropped to the rear travelling keenly in last few, inconvenienced briefly 300 metres out, kept on well closing stages.
Jumped fairly and gradually settled towards the rear, inconvenienced and switched 200 metres out, made no further impression.
Ridden to join the leaders, taken one back off the rail coming onto home bend, weakened after straightening. (Tactic questioned)
Settled just better than midfield in 5th 3-wide without cover, in similar position into straight, weakened under pressure inside final 200 metres.
Soon dropped to last despite niggling along, one of the widest at the back rounding home bend, found nothing in straight.
Jumped awkwardly travelling 3-wide behind midfield, wider turning into home straight, soon faded under pressure.
Jumped on terms, settled nicely midfield 3 wide with cover, under pressure at 500M, angled out into the clear in the Straight, and ran on strongly to score.
Caught 3 wide in front of midfield, hit the front at 200M, and just weakened inside final 25M.
Sat midfield 2 wide between horses, made some good progress in the Straight, no threat to top 2.
Sat last from the main group, stayed on fairly well.
Settled near the rear 2 wide, closed off okay.
Settled just behind the leader, unable to quicken in the Straight.
Sat near the rear on the rail, only able to pass weakened rivals.
Sat close to the pace 2 wide, weakened in the Straight.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, made no impression.
Broke nicely and ridden along to lead, nothing in the Straight.
Settled midfield on the rail, limited response in the Straight.
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide, nothing in the Straight. (Performance Unacceptable, must trial)
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, never a threat. (Heart Irregularity)
Broke slowly and detached from the field, never in contention. (Barrier Manners and Performance Unacceptable, must trial)

Steadied going out of the straight first time before racing in midfield away from the rail. Raced tight & forced wide on cornering before making continual steady ground to steal lead in final stride. First two clear of third.
Raced outside the lead throughout. Moved to the lead early in the straight, held advantage all the way until being caught in the final few strides. Well clear of third.

Improved around the first bend, raced three deep outside leaders before steadying near 1400m & shifting to race on the leaders back. Moved into clear running on straightening, battled on bravely to hold well beaten third.

Shifted back to race second last away from the rail after the start. Improved between runners approaching the corner, shifted wider on straightening before finishing off steadily down the outside to finish a well held 4th.
Raced 4th in the clear early before racing 1,1 from the 1200m. Eased three wide near the 550m, was only 1.25L from the lead at the 400m mark before giving ground to be well beaten in midfield.
Raced in midfield along the rail. Came off the rail approaching the 600m, raced tight with winner on cornering & again at the 350m before weakening to be well beaten.

Hampered start & had no early speed & consequently raced last. Shifted four wide passing the 600m, was very wide on straightening, 7L from lead before failing to finish off (not comfortable with track conditions  rider).
Raced third last along the rail. Was about 5L from the lead on straightening when only having two runners behind but did little in the straight & weakened to be beaten over 10L.

Pushed forward to lead. Joined & headed soon after straightening before weakening out badly in the straight to be long second last (failed to handle track  rider. substantial blood in trachea post-race).

Steadied on jumping & dragged back to race three deep without cover near the rear. Continued to cover additional ground in middle stages when wide. Was beaten before straightening & was a distant last.
Made contact at start, taken back to race 3 wide with cover at rear, very wide turning in, finished off very strongly to score.
Jumped with them, sent forward to take the early lead, headed 1200M, 2nd in the middle stages, hit the front 350M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 50M.
Out with rest, taken back to race at tail, slightly improved after passing 800M, very wide into straight, made good progress in the run home to take a place.

Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening, made good progress early in straight, no clear run 200M to 150M, closed off well to make frame.
Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide towards rear, angled out 550M, no clear run early in straight, made good progress final 300M, no threat to the first few.
Began well, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Shifted out at start, raced in midfield on the outside, 2 to 3 lengths back turning in, showed some response early in straight, peaked 200M, ran on evenly thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well, raced prominently on the outside, took the lead 1200M, found rail near 950M, led by 1/2L on turn, peaked and headed 300M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, raced better than midfield on the outside, 2 lengths or so back, no cover throughout, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong.

Shifted in at start, sent forward to race prominently on the inside, allowed rival to cross 950M, sat right behind the leader on rail, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Began fairly from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, 2 wide turning in, no clear run early in straight, made no progress thereafter, eased final 150M.
Crowded start, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, very wide turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, no clear run early in straight, weakened final 300M.
Moderately away, positioned 2 wide better than midfield, angled out 550M, peaked 400M, weakened thereafter, unacceptable performance.
Jumped with the field, steadied early to obtain cover near the rear 3 wide, and stayed on well to win. (See Incident Report)
Stalked leader, travelled comfortably throughout, kept on well for 2nd.
Settled 3 wide with cover in front of midfield, closed off okay.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, made some progress.
Sat last and switched out in the Straight, took time to respond but stayed on strongly late. (See Incident Report)
Settled near the rear 2 wide, showed some dash early but one pace afterwards
Settled midfield 2 wide, only one pace when asked. (See Incident Report)
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide between horses, limited response in the Straight.
Caught 4 wide up with the pace, weakened inside 350M. (See Incident Report)
Broke slowly, then ridden along to sit midfield on the rail, found nothing in the straight.
Up with the pace 3 wide, weakened in the Straight.
Settled worse than midfield on the rail, lay out rounding the Home Turn and soon weakened.
Broke nicely and led, being pressured throughout, weakened and faded in the Straight.
Settled behind midfield 2 wide, never a threat.

Began well from a wide draw and soon taken back to midfield in 6th wide without cover, gained steadily around home bend to 4L 4th into straight, quickened well down the centre to assert authority over 150 metres out.
Settled some 3L off the pace in 3rd, fought on steadily under pressure in straight but never threatening.
Ridden positively from a wide draw, obtained rails run in front over 950 metres out, led until finding no extra over 250 metres out.
Jumped fairly, improved gradually along the rail to 2nd just some 2L back, hit the front briefly from tiring pacemaker over 200 metres out, soon found no extra.
Settled mostly in remote 4th over 4L off the pace, saved ground making home turn, found no extra inside final 150 metres.
Jumped awkwardly and crowded, settled just worse than midfield in 6th most of the way, saved ground near rails turning for home, faded under pressure inside final 200 metres.
Gradually settled towards the rear in 7th travelling wide on better ground, kept on steadily in straight without quickening.
Ridden along just behind midfield on the rail, gradually dropped further back to last few onto home bend, made no impression in straight.
Jumped awkwardly and soon taken well behind from the widest draw, travelled off the rail on better ground throughout, ran home one-paced.
Settled well behind after moderate start, never seen with a chance.
From wide draw moved up to take the lead, quickened up well top of straight on rain affected surface, held on comfortably from runner up towards the finish.
Tracked leader (eventual winner), fought on well from top of straight, but always held by winner.
Caught wide no cover towards the rear, went wide into straight, responded well down outside of track, nearest finish.
From wide draw taken across behind runners, restrained at the rear, swung widest home, stayed on well along stand's rail to be nearest at the line.
From draw 13 moved up to track leader, tried hard on straightening but couldn't get closer to leader, flattened final 150M.
Dropped back to the rear 6Ls off the pace, gave mild response under top weight passing 400M, stayed on without threatening first few on rain-affected ground. (Lame next day.)
Given a waiting ride towards the rear, swung wide into straight, responded only fairly over final 400M, not reach contention.
Settled just ahead of midfield, kept on same pace turning home, posed no threat to leaders final 200M.
Held up in mid-division, kept on only fairly passing 400M, never able to challenge. (Lame next day.)
Tracked leaders, raced keenly 900M, remained in touch top of straight but couldn't run on, out of contention 200M.
Settled down 3-wide in midfield, had 4Ls to make up 400M, failed to quicken on ran-affected track. Never dangerous.

Jumped fairly, held up towards the rear, saved ground on inside turning for home, moved up to 4th 200M before weakening final stages. (Jockey : concerned with the respiratory noise that his horse had made / Roarer.)
Restrained in midfield along the 3-path, failed to quicken on rain affected ground turning for home, no extra final 200M.
Began very awkwardly and lost ground, held up behind midfield, weakened fast turning into straight, soon left behind by rivals.

Made contact at start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, moved closer after passing 1100M, a length back on turn, showed good response in straight, hit the front 200M, kept on well to the line and scored.

Jumped with them, sent forward to take the early lead, headed near 1700M, 2nd in the middle stages, retook the lead 750M, led by 3/4L turning in, headed near 200M, ran on well to take 2nd, just beaten by a neck.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide towards rear, commenced move 700M, very wide turning in, kept on well in straight to take a place, not quite able to challenge.
Began well, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, kept to inside after straightening and finished off well to make frame.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, a bit closer in the middle stages, angled out 700M, very wide turning in, kept on same pace in straight.
Made contact at start, raced behind midfield on the inside, angled out 600M, made some progress early in straight, peaked on run 200M, ran on evenly to the line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, angled out approaching 600M, very wide turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Moderately away, raced 2 to 3 wide at rear, commenced move 600M, very wide into straight, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong. (Roarer.)

Clean jump, raced better than midfield on the outside early, took the lead 1700M, travelled well in the middle stages, headed near 700M, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 wide from 1000M, wider turning in, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final 300M.
Away well, raced slightly behind midfield on the outside, commenced move 1200M, positioned 4 wide, a length or so back on turn, peaked and crowded 500M, weakened thereafter. (Mucus in trachea.)
Bumped shortly after start, raced at rear on the outside, eased final 500M. (See Racing Incidents.) (Lame right front leg next day morning.)
Out with rest, raced towards rear on the stands' side, 3 lengths or so back, a bit closer in the middle stages, hit the front 150M, kept on very well to the line and scored.
Jumped well from gate 11, positioned a length behind the leader on the stands' side, hard ridden after passing 350M, finished off strongly to take 2nd, always just held.
Jumped with them, positioned 2-1/2L behind the leader on the stands' side, unable to obtain clear run until 150M, finished off well to take a place.

Bumped start, raced behind midfield, 2 away from the stands' rail, a bit closer in the middle stages, checked near 200M, unable to obtain clear run until final 100M, made some progress thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)

Jumped well from gate 14, raced prominently on the stands' rail early, positioned a length behind the leader in the middle stages, hard ridden after passing 350M and made some progress, no extra final 150M.

Away with them, raced in midfield, 3 away from the stands' rail, made some progress after passing 400M, bumped 200M, peaked on run 150M, ran on evenly thereafter. (Mucus in trachea.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length in the middle stages, made contact 200M, peaked and headed 150M, weakened gradually final 50M.
Bumped start, raced towards rear, nearer to the middle track, 4 lengths back in the middle stages, finished off evenly.
Shifted in at start and bumped, positioned a length behind the leader on the middle track, hard ridden after passing 300M but only showed limited response, weakened final 150M.
Made contact at start, positioned a length behind the leader, 2 away from the stands' rail, hard ridden from 350M but only showed limited response, crowded 200M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped well, raced behind midfield, 3 away from the stands' rail, hard ridden from 400M but only showed limited response, weakened final furlong.
Away well, raced in midfield on the middle track, hard ridden from 400M but only showed limited response, weakened final 150M.
Slightly slow out, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Made contact at start, raced towards rear on the middle track, hard ridden after passing 400M, showed no response, weakened final furlong.
Raced three wide in midfield after start. Had some cover before being left wide without cover from about the 700m. Dashed to lead passing 300m, drew away to win by 2.5L.

Bumped at start before racing three wide with cover in midfield when following the winner. Was under 2L from the lead on straightening before closing off well to move to second near the 75m mark but was no match for winner.

Raced in midfield between runners early before drifting slightly further back after the 800m mark when racing keenly. Entered the final section sharing last place before coming wider & closing off well down the outside late.

Pushed forward to dispute lead early before being headed & racing third away from the rail. Moved up to the lead near the 400m mark, was joined by the winner at the 300m, fought hard but could offer no more in final 150m.

Ridden forward to challenge lead when racing wide before continuing on to take outright lead passing 900m. Stayed away from the rail around bend, was headed in the lead at 400m, battled away but was beaten 4L into midfield.

Raced in midfield along the inside throughout. Shifted back inwards passing the 300m but finished off only moderately in the last furlong & was below expectation (not entirely comfortable on surface  rider).

Got back to race third last away from the rail. Shifted wider on the track passing the 550m, was second widest and near the back but under 3L behind at the 400m, passed one or two tiring rivals but was beaten 6L.

Steadied & taken back to share last place. Moved wider on the track near 650m when still last, was the widest runner on straightening but under 3L behind before passing a few tiring rivals but never challenging from the back.
Bumped at the start before drifting back to race at the tail. Stayed nearer the inside on straightening, was last but only 3L behind entering last section but never really ran on & was well beaten.

Showed some speed to hold narrow lead momentarily after start before getting position in midfield between runners in middle stages. Came under riding on straightening before weakening to be beaten over 10L.

Got back to race worse than midfield near the inside. Stayed nearer to the inside on straightening when only 2.5L from the lead before weakening to be well beaten (hung inwards & not comfortable on affected track  rider).

Was slow to begin but mustered speed & improved to share lead near 1200m. Improved to narrow lead before being headed at 900m & racing second thereafter. Was close behind on straightening before weakening poorly to long last.

Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on strongly in straight, easily scored.
Made contact at start, raced 3 wide behind midfield early, found rail near 800M, a bit closer in the middle stages, 2 wide from 500M, finished off strongly to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Commenced well, positioned 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked on run 200M, ran on evenly to the line.
Made contact at start, raced at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame without threatening.
Shifted out abruptly at start, sent forward to race prominently, shared lead on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Crowded start, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on same pace in straight.
Began only fairly and made contact, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide turning in, one-paced in straight.
Crowded start, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, 4 wide turning in, made no impression in straight.
Began fairly from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the outside, 7 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped with them, raced behind midfield on the outside, 5 lengths back turning in, failed to make any progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact at start, raced prominently on the outside early, positioned 3 wide, a length or so back in the middle stages, peaked 400M, weakened early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)

Jumped fairly before racing three wide with cover in midfield throughout. Was just over 3L from lead on straightening before closing strongly down the outside to steal narrow lead in final stride in close three way finish.

Shifted behind runners from wide draw & raced near the tail. Moved wider on the track near 650m, was the widest runner on cornering when just under 4L from lead before closing strongly down the outside to be narrowly beaten.

Showed speed after the start to stride to lead after 150m before being headed & passed near the 750m & racing second thereafter. Regained the lead at 300m before being caught in the final stride in a very close 3 way finish.

Didn't have the early speed of others, raced third last along the rail. Was held up making the home turn, got clear running near the 300m before finishing strongly along the inside late to be only beaten half length.
Knuckled on jumping, ridden forward to be close to lead when wide before continuing to charge to the lead at the 750m. Headed in the lead at the 300m, battled away to be beaten 3L into midfield.

Slow to begin before being crowded & racing at the tail. Was again crowded near the 650m when continuing along the inside. Was held up on cornering when 4L from lead before making up a length late when running onto midfield.

Ridden forward to be prominent before racing three wide without cover when about 2L from the lead in the middle stages. Was only about 2L from the lead on straightening before weakening a few lengths to midfield late.

Knuckled on jumping & bumped before racing worse than midfield away from rail. Checked to avoid tiring runner near 650m & consequently lost ground. Was last of the main field on straightening, only held 5L deficit to line.

Bumped on jumping before racing on the leaders back early before sharing third place from the 750m. Continued along the rail & straightened only about 2L from the lead before weakening poorly in final 300m to be beaten 9L.

Ridden hard at the start before between runners when just behind the lead in middle stages. Was niggled along to hold position around the bend, was beaten & began yielding ground before straightening, weakened to long last.

Placing: FE
Comment: Raced in midfield away from the rail in early stages. Began losing ground quickly from the 750m before going amiss and falling near the 500m (irregular heart rhythm & bled).
Ridden along to lead on the rail, travelled smoothly throughout, kept on well to win (See Incident Report).
Sat towards rear 3 wide, travelled strongly, made some progress under pressure inside 150M to grab 2nd.
Sat in front of midfield on the rail, showed some response inside 200M, not quite able to challenge (Lost its right hind plate).
Chased the leader 2 wide, only one pace when asked.
Sat rear, no clear running in the early Straight, response nicely inside 150M, stayed on okay.
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide, made minor progress in the Straight, finished off evenly.
Sat in front of midfield 2 wide, weakened at 200M, closed off fairly.
Settled worse than midfield 3 wide, ran on evenly.
Sat towards rear 2 wide, angled out to the center of the track at 400M, limited response when asked.
Settled midfield, weakened at 250M and faded.
Sat worse than midfield on the rail, no clear running in the early Straight, could not be fully tested.
Jumped only fairly, sat towards rear on the rail, never a threat.
Settled midfield 2 wide, no impression.
Sat towards rear 2 wide, never a factor (Roarer).

Raced in midfield along the rail throughout. Was hard ridden from 600m, straightened just under 4L from the runaway leader, was still 3L behind at 150m before charging in the final stages to steal lead in final few strides.

Strode to the lead approaching the winning post first time. Raced over 2L clear passing the 600m, was still about 3L clear at 150m before being charged down in the final few strides by fast closing winner, big gap to 3rd.

Raced on the leaders back from about the 1300m. Moved to second passing the 600m. Tried hard to hold about 2L deficit until about the 300m mark before getting tired late but having enough advantage to hold well beaten third.

Pushed forward to race second away from the rail. Was just under 5L from the lead on straightening before battling away in a one-paced fashion in the straight to hold off challengers for well beaten fourth place.

Raced worse than midfield two wide early before moving three wide with cover near 1000m. Shifted wider on the track to improve passing 500m, passed a couple of tiring rivals in straight when running onto well beaten fifth.

Jumped awkwardly & bumped before racing just worse than midfield along the rail. Was 7L from the lead entering final section before finishing off only moderately near the inside in the straight & was never a threat.
Had a nice run 1,1 for the majority. Was 5L from the lead entering final section before finishing off only moderately in the straight to be beaten just over 6L in midfield.

Had no early speed & raced rearward before being relegated to a clear last 1200m. Shifted out widest on cornering when about 9L from the lead before making up a few lengths late to run onto well beaten midfield finish.
Raced in midfield away from the rail throughout. Was a touch keen in the middle stages. Was just under 7L from the lead entering final section & made no ground in straight (lame next day).
Allowed to drift back from the wide draw & raced rearward throughout. Was 8L from the lead on straightening when continuing rearward & never made any headway in the straight & was beaten over 10L.

Jumped awkwardly & lost ground and consequently raced last early. Improved after first bend & raced three deep with cover in midfield from 1100m. Shifted wider 600m before weakening out in the straight to be beaten 12L.
Drifted back to race third last along the rail. Was relegated to last near the 550m mark before doing nothing in the straight & weakening poorly to be long second last.
Was trapped racing three deep without cover just forward of midfield for the majority. Began yielding ground from the 600m & weakened out badly to be a very long last (must trial).
Out with rest, raced at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, there to turn, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to score.
Began only fairly, raced 3 wide, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, finished off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Shifted out at start and made contact, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, travelled comfortably to turn, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the first two final 50M.
Fast into stride, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, made some progress in straight to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Taken back to race towards rear on the outside, 5 to 6 lengths back, very wide into straight, made some headway in the run home.
Shifted in at start and made contact, raced in midfield on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, made good progress early in straight, no extra final 150M.
Crowded start, difficult to settle in the early stages, raced 2 wide behind midfield, found rail 500M, no clear run early in straight, ran on evenly thereafter.
Began only fairly from gate 1, raced towards rear on the inside, 6 lengths back turning in, made some progress early in straight, blocked near 200M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Away well, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Started very slowly, showed no early speed, raced at tail, 9 lengths or so back, still well back on turn, made no impression in straight.
Began well, raced better than midfield on the outside, peaked 400M, weakened gradually in straight. (Bled.)
Knuckled over on jumping and became unbalanced, recovered to race 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M.
Broke a step slow, ridden along until the 800M to assume the lead, travelled nicely throughout, kept on well to win.
Jumped with the field, tracked leader, unable to pass the winner.
Sat towards the rear 2 wide, angled out in the Straight, and stayed on strongly.
Settled midfield 2 wide between horses, closed off nicely.
Up with the pace early, only one paced when asked.
Settled worse than midfield on the rail, made some progress in the Straight.
Sat midfield on the rail, made no impression. (See Incident Report)
Caught 3 wide midfield throughout, nothing in the Straight.
Settled behind midfield 2 wide, under pressure at 500M, made no progress.
Broke slowly and sat last, lost touch with the field from 600M despite hard ridden, never a threat.
Ridden along early to be prominent, weakened and faded in the Straight.
Tracked race leader in 2nd or 3rd, dropped slightly backward to 2L 5th passing 900 metres, switched 4-wide to challenge entering straight, hit the front 300 metres out and soon drew clear.

Jumped awkwardly losing considerable ground, soon recovered 3-wide between runners reaching within 3L of pace in 6th in back straight, came under pressure turning for home, fought on steadily to snatch 2nd final stages.
Settled at the back on rail after slow start, trailed the field to straight, made up good ground down the centre of the track and did best work late.
Settled well behind, improved slightly closer to 11th about 800 metres out, remained 3-wide with cover rounding home bend, responded well to challenge inside final 300 metres.
Well there early from a wide draw, pressed forward wide around first bend joining race leader 1100 metres out, disputed lead into home straight but soon found no extra.
Gradually taken back from the widest draw, improved to midfield 3-wide in back straight, remained similar turning for home, fought on steadily and never nearer.
Ridden to lead from a middle draw obtaining rails run 1400 metres out setting a quick pace in back straight, led until finding no extra 300 metres out, swamped for a placing closing stages.
Crowded at start settling in midfield, slightly worse 800 metres out, saved ground on inside turning for home, fought on steadily under pressure.
Dropped gradually to last few despite niggled along on rail, fought on quite well in straight, never nearer.
Not far off in 5th or 4th on rail, chased leaders into straight, baulked early on and unable to sustain effort inside final 250 metres.
Wide in midfield early stages, improved along back straight to 1L 3rd 3-wide 950 metres out, similar rounding home bend and into home straight, soon weakened.
Travelled keenly in 4th early stages, gradually shuffled back to 7th about 850 metres out, renewed effort entering home straight but bumped and unbalanced 300 metres out, made no further impression.
Began well from the one draw gradually settling in midfield on rail, saved ground turning into home straight, faded gradually.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, towards rear most of way and never seen with a chance.
Tracked the pace early stages, moved up to be vying for lead down the back straight, took over 350M and soon opened up a commanding lead, kept on well final 150M for a hat-trick of wins.
Settled down in midfield, into clear passing 400M, ran on well to claim 2nd near 100M, held by winner closing stages.
Tracked leaders on inside, held up 350M-250M, kept on steadily final 200M, no threat to winner, held on for 3rd at the line.
Given a waiting ride towards the rear, driven nearing 400M, made steady progress on straightening, claimed 4th just before line.
Moved up to press the pace, caught 3-wide no cover throughout, kept battling early straight, held 2nd to 200M, couldn't sustain run late stages.
Never far off leaders, within striking distance turning for home, continued on moderately early straight, no extra final 100M.
Shifted across behind runners after the start, towards the rear early stages before moving up to midfield passing halfway, kept on final 400M without serious threat to leaders.
Held up at rear 8Ls off the pace, made limited progress on straightening, never a threat to leaders.
From wide draw moved up chasing leaders along 3-path, had cover but raced keenly in the middle stages, tried hard to stay in contention early straight, peaked on its run 200M, faded towards the line.
Restrained to race behind midfield, driven along 500M but failed to respond, never a factor.
Soon led, pressed by rivals middle stages, headed top of straight, no extra and weakened rapidly. (Mucus in trachea).
Settled midfield along the fence, came under serious pressure home turn, weakened badly from top of straight, finished tailed out. (Unacceptable Performance / Lame RH leg.)

Clean jump, in touch, 2 wide, angled out after passing 550M, showed very good response in straight, hit the front 200M, kept on well to the line and scored.

Began well from the widest draw, raced slightly better than midfield on the outside early, moved closer after passing 1100M, 3rd on turn, kept on well in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Began only fairly, sent forward to take the early lead, headed 1500M, retook the lead 1150M, led by 3/4L turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 200M, ran on evenly to the line.
Quickly into stride, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead 1500M, headed 1150M, 2nd on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Began only fairly, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some progress in straight.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, dropped to midfield in the middle stages, wider turning in, made some progress early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Made contact at start, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, kept on same pace to the line.
Taken back from gate 7, raced towards rear on the inside, 2 wide from 950M, 5 lengths back turning in, one-paced in the run home. (Lame left front leg next day.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Out with rest, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 3 wide from 800M, 5 lengths back turning in, kept on same pace in straight.
Jumped awkwardly, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, one-paced in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slightly slow out, raced towards rear on the outside, very wide turning in, made no progress in the run home.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear throughout, never a factor. (Lame right front leg next day.)
Began fairly from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, angled out 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from gate 11, raced behind midfield on the outside, moved closer after passing 1000M, peaked 500M, weakened early in straight.
Began fairly, urged along to take up a midfield position, quickened up well from 350M, pressed leader from mid-straight, gained upper hand inside 100M.
Quickly away from draw 1, led early before settling back in 4th, travelled well into straight, quickened to lead 250M, joined by rival passing 200M, fought hard but got outrun late stages.
Lost ground at start, soon detached from field, raced greenly early and middle stages, over 10Ls to make up 400M, ran on powerfully from last to take 3rd near line. (Jockey questioned.)
Settled down midfield, 5Ls off the pace 400M, ran on steadily without reaching first two, lost 3rd last stride.
Jumped well, up with early pace before holding back to race in midfield, put in a mild bid on straightening, no threat to first two final 200M.
Held up towards the rear, 8Ls to make up 400M, stayed on past beaten horses in the straight. No impression on leaders.
Driven forward to be vying for lead on inside, fought hard to stay in contention early straight, run ended 200M, faded towards the line.
Settled down behind mid-division, pushed along 550M, ran home one paced, never able to challenge.
Pressed forward from wide draw, 3rd on settling, short-lived effort early straight, faded 200M.
Away with them, up with early pace before holding back passing 900M, stayed in touch with leaders home turn but failed to pick up on straightening, no extra 200M.
Rushed forward to be vying for lead on outside, headed by rivals 250M, weakened rapidly. (Blood in trachea.)
Dropped back to near last after the start, struggled to keep up with rivals from 900M, over 10Ls behind turning for home, never a factor.
Ridden along to lead, traveled strongly, made some progress inside the final 200M, kept on well to the line.
Sat towards rear 3 wide, angled out early in the Straight, responded well under pressure, closed off nicely to take 2nd.
Jumped okay, sat handy, traveled smoothly throughout, kept on nicely.
Sat in front of midfield on the rail, closed off okay.
Sat in front of midfield 3 wide, began to improve and chase the leader at 800M, slightly weakened inside 250M.
Jumped only fairly, settled worse than midfield 3 wide, showed minor progress in the Straight (Barrier Manners unacceptable, must stalls test).
Sat towards rear 2 wide, closed off evenly.
Fractious in barriers, slow to jump, settled towards rear on the rail, one pace only (Barrier Manners unacceptable, must stalls test).
Settled midfield, showed limited response when asked.
Sat worse than midfield 2 wide, weakened and faded at 250M, no impression (Lost its left front plate).
Sat worse than midfield on the rail, never a threat.
Sat rear, never in contention (Racing Manners unacceptable, must trial)
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well in the middle stages, hard ridden from 250M, kept on well to hold off the challengers.
Began well, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on the stands' rail, unable to obtain clear run until 200M, finished off well to take 2nd, just held.
Quickly into stride, sent forward to race prominently, hard ridden 400M, kept on same pace to the line, no threat to the first two.
Jumped with them, raced behind midfield on the stands' side, 3 lengths or so back, hard ridden after passing 400M, made some progress thereafter, no threat to the first few.
Clean jump, positioned a length behind the leader on the stands' side, hard ridden from 250M but only showed limited response, ran on evenly thereafter.
Slightly slow out, raced in midfield nearer to the middle track, made some progress after passing 350M, peaked on run 150M, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Out in line, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader, nearer to the middle track, hard ridden 350M, peaked 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Reared as stalls opened and started very slowly, raced at rear on the stands' side, made some progress after passing 350M, no extra final 100M. (Roarer.)
Crowded shortly after start, raced at rear nearer to the middle track, hard ridden from 400M but only showed limited response, weakened gradually final 150M.
Jumped with them, raced behind midfield on the stands' side, made no progress final 400M.
Away with them, raced prominently on the stands' side, peaked 300M, weakened thereafter.
Began only fairly, raced at rear, 4 lengths or so back, hard ridden 400M but showed no response, weakened final furlong.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, angled out 500M, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly, easily scored.
Began well from gate 9, positioned 3 wide, a length or so back, 2 wide from 850M, angled out approaching 500M, closed off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Bumped start, raced 2 to 3 wide towards rear, very wide turning in, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Average to begin, raced behind midfield on the outside, very wide turning in, made good progress in straight to make frame without threatening.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, angled out 450M, made some progress early in straight, no extra final 50M.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced towards rear on the outside, very wide into straight, made some progress in the run home.
Began smartly, raced better than midfield on the outside, moved a bit closer after passing 900M, no cover throughout, showed limited response early in straight, ran on evenly thereafter.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 100M, weakened thereafter.
Slow to begin, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some progress early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, there to turn, kept on well early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out 500M, made minor progress early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M.
Taken back from gate 13, raced at rear on the outside, very wide into straight, made no progress in the run home.
Made contact at start, raced behind midfield on the inside, angled out 500M, showed limited response early in straight, weakened inside final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slightly slow out and crowded, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out 500M, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped with the field, raced in a prominent positon near the rail, quickened well in the Straight, won comfortably.
Settled worse than midfield wide with cover, moved towards the stands' rail in the Straight, closed off nicely for 2nd.
Broke well and raced close to the pace, kept on fairly well near the stands' rail.
Broke alertly and shared the lead, ran on okay and just weakened inside final 75M.
Settled near the rear, stayed on okay late.
Up with the pace, only one paced when asked in the Straight. (See Incident Report)
Sat at the rear, made some progress in center track.
Sat last and made some ground on the stands' rail late.
Caught wide in front of midfield, never quickened.
Ridden along to lead, found nothing in the Straight.
Jumped awkwardly and settled worse than midfield, never in contention.
Settled midfield, raced keenly down the back straight, weakened in the Straight.
Settled in front of midfield early, under pressured at 850M and never travelled.
Sat midfield close to the rail, weakened and faded at 500M.
Taken back to wide in midfield from a wide draw, improved passing 1100 metres out to 3rd onto home bend, soon came to challenge on straightening and gained upper hand 150 metres out.
Crowded at start, gradually settled in forward of midfield, drifted slightly back to 8th over 4L back rounding home bend, ran on in straight and did best work late.
Disputed lead on rail most of way, held 2L advantage from eventual winner entering straight but caught over 150 metres out, lost 2nd late.
Travelled wide from a wide draw gradually shifting backward to midfield after good start, commenced move 800 metres out and wide onto home bend, fought on steadily in straight but never threatening.
Taken back to last few from a wide draw and waited with, very wide rounding home bend and widest into straight, fought on steadily under pressure on stands side.
Taken back from the widest draw for rails run near last, saved ground rounding home bend but inconvenienced on top of straight, fought on steadily down the centre of the track without threatening.
Niggled along in last few, made steady headway on the outside rounding home bend, ran home one-paced.
Moderate start, soon improved on rail to reach within 5L of pace in 9th, ran home one-paced.
Not far off in back straight, drifted back to 6th some 3L back rounding home bend, made no impression in straight.
Slightly slow out settling in last few, made no impression in straight.
Led or disputed lead 2-wide, folded up quickly after straightening.

Began well but soon taken back to near midfield, pulled forward keenly to within 2L of pace in 5th briefly over 900 metres out, shifted back to over 3L back in 7th onto home bend, found nothing in straight.
Never better than midfield dropping to last few on home bend.
Began well settling in 3rd, became 4th on rail rounding home bend, folded up quickly upon straightening. (Irregular heart rhythm)

From draw 1 stayed close to the pace, remained racing on the inside turning for home while his rivals swung wide to center of track, continued on well to win by comfortable margin on rain affected ground.
Caught wide chasing leaders, gave good response on straightening, came home well down outside of track to take 2nd.
Crowded on jumping between rivals, held up behind midfield, responded well from 400M on rain affected ground, kept on steadily for 3rd.
Dropped back to race at the rear, swung widest for home, made good progress final 400M down outside of track, got up for 4th 50M.
Held up midfield, kept on mildly down center of track, never a serious threat.
Raced wide behind midfield, swung to outside of track on straightening, stayed on without threatening.
Up with the pace 3-wide, outpaced passing 300M, soon out of contention.

Up with leaders, raced keenly throughout, found less than expected when asked top of straight, no extra 150M. (Jockey : unable to obtain cover, responded only fairly when placed under full pressure in home straight.)
Settled midfield, failed to quicken on rain affected ground passing 400M, never dangerous.
Led along the 4-path on rain affected track, found no extra and weakened on straightening, soon out of contention.
Held up towards the rear, came under pressure home turn, came up empty passing 400M, never involved.
Began awkwardly from wide draw, taken back to race in the rear, failed to respond on straightening, never in the picture.
Average to begin, raced behind midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off strongly to score.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced behind midfield on the outside, very wide turning in, made good progress in straight to take 2nd, nearest finish.
Began only fairly, raced at rear on the outside, very wide into straight, made good progress in straight to take a place, nearest on line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, challenged the leader 500M, kept on well early in straight, no extra final 50M.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the outside, very wide into straight, made good progress early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Began well from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, challenged by rival from 500M, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began well from a wide draw, raced better than midfield on the outside, 2 lengths or so back turning in, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly thereafter.
Slightly slow out, raced in midfield on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail in the middle stages, peaked early in straight, one-paced thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, peaked 450M, ran on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Fast into stride, raced 4 wide slightly better than midfield, similar position on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually in the closing stages. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced in midfield on the outside, moved a bit closer on turn, very wide into straight, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Jumped awkwardly, raced 3 wide slightly better than midfield, 2 wide on turn, angled out 500M, made no progress in straight.
Jumped with them, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Out with rest, raced in midfield on the outside, 2 to 3 lengths back turning in, finished off very strongly to score.
Average to begin, raced behind midfield on the outside, very wide turning in, finished off very strongly to take 2nd, nearest on line.

Commenced well, raced in midfield on the inside, moved a bit closer on turn, made very good progress early in straight, hit the front 200M, kept on well but unable to hold off the first two final 50M.
Taken back from gate 10, raced at rear on the outside, very wide turning in, made good progress in straight to make frame without threatening.
Jumped well from the widest draw, took the early lead, headed near 1100M, 2nd on turn, retook the lead early in straight, peaked and headed 200M, ran on evenly to the line.
Began very awkwardly, raced at rear on the inside, 2 wide from 600M, 5 to 6 lengths back turning in, made some headway in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back to race 3 wide towards rear, 5 lengths or so back turning in, made some progress in straight.
Slightly slow out, raced slightly behind midfield, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Away with them, tracked leaders, made contact near 450M, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide behind midfield, 2 wide from 950M, similar position on turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, raced slightly better than midfield, made contact near 450M, 1 to 2 lengths back turning in, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away, raced towards rear on the inside, 5 lengths back turning in, showed limited response early in straight, weakened inside final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from gate 1, travelled very keenly, took the lead near 1100M, led by 1/2L in the middle stages, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)

Placing: DNF
Comment: Taken back from gate 9, raced 2 wide at rear, unable to maintain position near 700M, eased final 600M. (Bled.)

Began well from gate 1, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, saved ground to turn, finished off very strongly to score.
Commenced well, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, travelled comfortably to turn, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner close home.
Began fairly, raced in midfield on the inside, 3 lengths or so back, saved ground throughout, finished off well to take a place without threatening.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Out with rest, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide towards rear, 7 lengths or so back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 7 to 8 lengths back, still well back on turn, very wide into straight, made some progress in the run home.
Jumped with them, positioned 3 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, kept on same pace in straight.
Made contact at start, raced better than midfield on the outside, no cover for the majority of the race, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Crowded start, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made no progress in straight.
Made contact at start, raced towards rear on the outside, 7 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Settled mainly in forward of midfield in 5th, came to challenge upon straightening and gained upper hand inside the 100 metres, won cosily.

Soon led, increased tempo 1100 metres out gaining a 4L break early in back straight, maintained over 1L advantage onto home bend, similar early in straight but only to be headed inside the 100 metres, fought on for 2nd.

Not far off the pace in 4th on rail, further back when tempo quickened early in back straight, gained under pressure to 1L 2nd over 600 metres out, held some chance in straight until outsprinted 100 metres out.
Settled in midfield in 6th on rail, commenced move over 600 metres out reaching 4th some 3L back on rail making home turn, kept on early in straight until finding no extra inside final 100 metres.

Ridden forward to be up with the pace, some 4L back in joint 3rd in quick tempo early in back straight, came under pressure 3-wide some 2L back onto home bend but dropped to 6th very wide into straight, kept on at the one pace.
Inconvenienced at start and soon taken back to last few, remained well back into straight, produced good late impression inside final 100 metres.
Inconvenienced at start losing ground settling in last few, came under pressure home bend and saved ground making final turn, ran home at the one pace down the inside of the track.
Jumped awkwardly from the widest draw losing ground, trailed the field on rail to straight, fought on well past well-beaten horses.
Badly bumped at start and soon dropped to last few, commenced move 3-wide rounding home bend and remained well back into straight, ran past well-beaten horses without threatening.
Pressed forward from a wide draw to obtain midfield position in 7th, remained in similar position despite coming under pressure 550 metres out, weakened noticeably 100 metres out.
Jumped awkwardly and soon came to vie for lead wide onto first bend, settled over 3L behind fast leader losing rails run 700 metres out, gradually weakened from 3rd rounding home bend.
Never better than midfield, gave ground under pressure from approaching home bend. (Roarer as reported previously)
Broke nicely, ridden along to lead, travelled strongly, kept on well to win.
Settled midfield 3 wide, began to improve inside 750M and chased the leader, slightly weakened from 250M, just held 2nd.
Sat rear 3 wide, angled out at 400M, responded well when asked, closed off nicely to grab 3rd.
Jumped only fairly, settled midfield on the rail, travelled okay throughout, made minor progress in the Straight.
Sat towards rear on the rail, showed some response in the Straight, but just not quick enough.
Sat handy, limited when asked, ran on evenly.
Settled worse than midfield 3 wide, weakened over the final 200M.
Sat towards rear 3 wide, switched out inside 400M, one pace.
Sat worse than midfield 2 wide, failed to respond when asked, never a factor.
Jumped okay, settled better than midfield 2 wide, weakened and faded in the Straight, made no impression.
Settled rear on the rail, never a threat.
Sat rear 2 wide, never seen with a chance.
Strode forward to lead. Raced a couple of lengths clear on straightening & maintained that advantage all the way to the line to win well.
Bumped soon after the start before racing in midfield along the rail. Stayed nearer the inside on straightening before closing off well to narrowly hold well beaten second on line (mucus in trachea).

Outpaced early & raced near the tail. Was 7.5L from the lead entering final section, shifted out to be the widest on straightening before closing very strongly down the outside in final stages to just miss second.
Had a nice run 1,1 for the majority. Was 3L from the lead on straightening before finishing off steadily all the way but being caught for a minor placing late.

Steadied & threw head after the start before getting position in midfield along the rail. Was just over 5L from lead entering final section, shifted outwards mid-straight before making up a length or two in last furlong.
Pushed forward from widest gate to race second at the leaders flanks. Dropped a couple of lengths behind on straightening weakening a length or so to midfield late.
Raced in midfield but was caught three deep without cover throughout. Drifted further back approaching the 400m, was wider on straightening before finishing off steadily to midfield late.
Got back to race worse than midfield away from the rail. Shifted outwards & raced tight at the 300m mark before finishing only steadily to midfield.

Bumped soon after the start before racing on the leaders back. Raced keenly in the early & middle stages. Bumped on straightening when continuing to share second place before emptying at the 200m & weakening late.
Raced third last along the rail. Was ridden along to travel better near the 750m, was just under 7L from the lead at the 400m & made no headway when racing along the rail in the straight.
Raced in midfield between runners for the majority. Was 4.5L from the lead entering final section, came under pressure before straightening and did little in the straight weakening to second last.
Hampered on jumping before getting back to last. Was ridden along from the 550m, continued last on straightening before failing to make any headway and being beaten 9L.
Began smartly from gate 1, raced in 2nd, a length or so back, same positon on turn, hit the front 150M, kept on strongly to the line and scored. (Bled.)
Bumped shortly after start, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, finished off well to take 2nd.
Began well from the widest gate, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1-1/2L on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, ran one evenly to the line.
Bumped shortly after start, raced better than midfield on the inside, 2 wide on turn, finished off well to make frame without threatening the first few.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced in 3rd, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, made some progress early in straight, no extra final 150M.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 12 lengths back in the middle stages, aided by pace but set an impossible task, made very good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Shifted out at start, raced 3 wide with cover towards rear, 9 lengths back on turn, made some headway in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Crowded on jumping, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some progress early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Hampered start, raced 2 wide at rear, 11 lengths back on turn, made little progress in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield early, found rail near 600M, saved ground on turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped well, raced in midfield on the outside, very wide turning in, made no progress in straight.
Shifted in at start and made contact, difficult to settle in the early stages, made contact near 700M, 7 lengths back turning in, weakened early in straight.
Hard ridden to lead, kept on well to score.
Up close to the pace, made some ground in the straight, no threat to winner.
Sat just behind the leader, kept on okay, just lost 2nd on the line.
Settled near the rear 2 wide, stayed on well the grab 4th.
Settled midfield 3 wide no cover, closed off okay.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, only one pace when asked. (See Incident Report)
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide, made some late headway. (See Incident Report)
Sat towards to rear on the rail, made little progress.(See Incident Report) (Epiglottic Entrapment)
Sat last on the rail, saved ground and made no impression.
Settled behind midfield on the rail, never a threat.
Settled midfield 2 wide, hung out around the Home Turn, never in contention.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, weakened and faded in the straight. (See Incident Report)
Amongst leaders early gradually settling in 3rd , improved 3-wide in back straight to 2nd 900 metres out hitting front into straight, just fended off runner-up's strong late challenge.
Settled in midfield, commenced move 3-wide rounding home bend going wider into straight, ran on dourly to just fail to get up on line.
Settled in midfield on rail, snuck closer entering home straight and continue to run on under pressure down inside without threatening.

Settled better than midfield 3-wide in 5th onto first bend, remained similar in back straight, came under pressure home bend, switched in for a run early in straight, ran on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Settled just worse than midfield in 8th, in similar position into home straight, finished off race well down the centre of the track.
Moderate start, took up running passing winning post the first time, led setting a sound pace to straight, soon found no extra.

Amongst leaders early settling one back in 2nd onto first bend, travelled ungenerously over 950 metres when held back to 3rd, one-out-one-back home bend, one-paced under pressure in straight. (Jockey warned)

Moderate start, gradually settled in last few, steadied behind runner 900 metres out, saved ground turning for home, produced good late impression inside final 200 metres.(Jockey warned for not riding out.)
Settled in 4th on rail over 2L back, came under pressure rounding home bend, switched off rail into straight, faded gradually.
Slow to begin, taken across at the back from the widest draw niggled along on rail from 750 metres, made no impression in the run to the line.
Slow to begin and then crowded, towards rear throughout, never seen with a chance.
Jumped awkwardly, never a factor.
Not hurried early stages, settled towards the rear 8-9Ls off the pace, swung wide for home, ran on strongly and got up just before the line.
Settled ahead of midfield, responded well turning for home, came close to score his 5th win was just denied at the line.
From draw 1 moved forward to be vying for lead along the inside, drifted out on straightening, kept on well to line but couldn't hold off first 2 late.
Moved up to chase leaders, responded well from top of straight to be challenging for the lead, couldn't hold off first 2 late and just missed out on 3rd.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners, 10Ls off the pace on settling, came wide home turn, made some progress in the straight, went 5th near line.
Pressed the lead on outside, batted on one paced in the straight, out of contention final 100M.
Jumped awkwardly, at the rear early stages racing keenly, moved up to midfield home turn, stayed on without threatening final 300M.
Settled towards the rear, 7Ls to make up 400M, made non-threatening progress final 300M.
Driven forward to be chasing leaders 2-wide, not picked up pace under top weight, no extra 200, faded towards the line.
Dropped back to race at the rear, failed to quicken in straight, never a factor. (Jockey : did not travel well at any stage with the genuine pace, raced in a disappointing manner.)
Held up towards the rear, outpaced from 500M to be last turning in, hard driven but didn't respond to riding.
Driven along to hold a midfield position on inside, found nothing when asked, weakened rapidly passing 200M.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, led by 2-1/2L turning in, kept on very well in straight, easily scored.
Jumped with them, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2-1/2L back on turn, kept on well in straight without threatening the winner.
Slightly slow out, raced at tail, 10 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, made very good progress in straight to take a place.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off well to make frame without threatening.
Jumped well from gate 11, raced 3 wide better than midfield in the early stages, 2 wide from 700M, 5 lengths back turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear, 9 lengths or so back, still well back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to be nearest on line.
Made contact at start, raced in midfield on the outside, similar position on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 3 wide from 450M, taken wide in straight and finished off evenly.
Out with rest, raced 2 wide in midfield, 7 lengths back on turn, made no impression in straight. (Lame left front leg next day morning.)
Average to begin, raced 2 wide towards rear, 9 lengths back turning in, made no impression in straight.
Started slowly, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Away with them, raced better than midfield on the inside, 4 lengths back on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
