Slightly slow out, showed no early speed, raced behind midfield on the inside, 2 wide turning in, no clear run early in straight, cleared 200M, finished off very strongly to score.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide better than midfield, wider from 550M, made contact 400M, finished off strongly to take 2nd, just beaten by a narrow margin.
Average to begin, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, took the lead 250M, kept on well but unable to hold off the first two close home, just beaten by a head.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced at rear on the inside, angled out 650M, no clear run early in straight, cleared approaching 150M, finished off well to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, headed near 1100M, 3rd in the middle stages, kept on evenly in straight.
Bumped start, raced at rear, hard ridden from 600M, very wide into straight, closed off well without threatening.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, angled out 550M, made contact early in straight, peaked on run 200M, weakened gradually final 100M.
Crowded start, raced 2 wide towards rear, moved closer after passing 700M, very wide into straight, made minor progress early in straight, peaked 200M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out 700M, very wide into straight, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out approaching 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened and eased final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.) (Blood in trachea.)

Bumped start, unable to slot in, trapped very wide, 2 lengths or so back early, sent forward after passing 1300M, took the lead near 1100M, challenged by rival turning in, headed 250M, weakened final furlong.
Away well, sent forward to race prominently, challenged the leader turning in, peaked 250M, weakened thereafter. (Mucus.)
Taken back from gate 9, raced at rear throughout, never a factor, unacceptable performance.
Driven and crossed to the lead, fought on well turning into straight, still 2Ls in front at 200M, ran out of steam late but gamely prevailed by a nose at the line.
Dropped back on jumping from a wide draw, settled down 3-wide in midfield, ran on well from 300M charging home late, just missed by a nose.
Began awkwardly, driven forward to track leader on inside, fought on steadily turning home, found extra late stages to be nearest at the line.
Caught wide no cover chasing leaders, tried hard from 400M, briefly went 2nd mid-straight, outran late to finish 4th but beaten less than 1L.
Dropped back to race at the tail of the field, swung wide for home, closed off well for 5th but not able to challenge first few.
Chased leaders in 4th early stages, shuffled back to midfield entering home turn, kept on mildly over final 300M, never a winning chance.
Jumped only fairly from wide gate then dropped back to race at the rear of the field, stayed on final 300M without threatening.
Jumped fairly, soon moved up to track the pace, in 2nd spot top of the straight, weakened from 200M. (Jockey could offer no excuse for the disappointing performance.)
Settled towards the rear, steadied near 1000M and 700M, into clear running 400M but ran on only fairly.
Refused to jump with the field and lost a significant amount of ground, 7Ls back in detached last turning for home, ran past a few beaten horses towards the line. (To consecutive barrier trials.)
Fractious as the start was effected, jumped awkwardly and lost ground, settled behind midfield along the fence, couldn't go on passing 300M.
Began fairly, held up midfield early stages before moving closer to leaders home turn, failed to pick up early straight, no extra 200M, faded to last.
Broke nicely, sat midfield 2 wide, travelled strongly, responded well under pressure inside 250M, kept on well to win.
Chased the leader, kept on okay until 200M, slightly weakened thereafter.
Settled midfield, showed some dash inside 150M, closed off nicely.
Sat rear, made some progress over the final 50M, finished off okay.
Jumped okay, ridden along to lead, travelled smoothly until the early Straight, unable to quicken after 250M.
Settled towards rear 2 wide, never in contention.
Had a nice run in midfield away from the rail. Straightened about 3L from the lead when just behind the leading trio before closing strongly in last furlong to charge to lead in final few strides.

Began well and went to the lead. Travelled well on straightening when about a length clear, challenged at the 200m, dug deep to fend off immediate challengers before over-run in final few strides by fast finishing winner.

Shifted across behind runners from gate 13 before settling worse than midfield between rivals. Had clear running on straightening when 5L behind before making strong late ground in last furlong to steal third in last stride.

Pushed forward to race outside the leader early before steadying & racing a length behind from the 900m. Moved up to share the lead near 200m before just battling away in last 75m when being over-powered for minor place late.

Raced just behind leaders before hanging outwards, checking off heels & losing ground near the 850m bend. Hung outwards again near the 650m. Was ridden quietly before sharing lead near 250m before peaking 100m (must trial).

Began moderately before being steadied from outside gate & racing near the tail throughout. Was nearly 7L from lead on straightening before making up significant late ground in the concluding stages when charging home late.

Raced in midfield away from the rail throughout. Moved into clear running on straightening when just over 4L form the lead before finishing off only one paced in the dash to the line to be beaten a similar margin.
Raced in midfield along the rail throughout. Was just over 4L from the lead on straightening, stayed nearer the rail in straight before weakening a length or so to be beaten 5L in midfield.

Began well but was steadied after start & taken right back to race near the tail when four wide without cover. Continued very wide around bend, was widest & 7L behind on straightening & did reasonable job to maintain margin.

Got back after start but raced three wide when worse than midfield. Had limited cover around first bend when continuing wide. Shifted wider passing the 500m, was just over 6L behind on straightening but failed to improve.

Shifted across behind runners after the start & raced worse than midfield along the rail. Stayed along the rail on straightening when 6L from the lead but weakened a further few lengths to be well beaten.

Steadied after first 100m & taken back to race three wide near the rear in the middle stages. Was last and just 8L from the lead on straightening but did little in the straight & weakened to be well beaten.

Reared at the start and lost significant ground before ridden hard to catch up to the body of the field near the 900m. Weakened out in the straight to be beaten over 10L but had excuse after bungling the start.

Was racing 4th away from the rail when badly hampered & taken out very wide by rival runner when making 850m bend, consequently lost a few lengths. Began losing ground before straightening & weakened out to be long last.
Began well from a wide draw, raced in 2nd, a length or so back, 3 wide turning in, made contact early in straight, finished off strongly to score.
Jumped awkwardly, raced towards rear on the inside, travelled keenly in the early and middle stages, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off well to take 2nd.
Began smartly from gate 12, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped with them, raced in midfield on the outside, 3 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Shifted in at start and made contact, raced 3 wide better than midfield, angled out 550M, made contact early in straight, kept on same pace to the line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced behind midfield on the outside, very wide into straight, finished off well to be nearest on line. (Roarer.)
Began well from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, kept on same pace in straight.
Bumped start, raced better than midfield, 2 wide, moved a bit closer after passing 650M, kept on well early in straight, no extra final 150M.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced towards rear on the outside, very wide into straight, closed off well without threatening. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, raced behind midfield on the inside, moved closer on turn, showed limited response early in straight, one-paced thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, a bit closer on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 250M.
Slightly slow out and crowded, raced 2 wide at rear, found rail near 700M, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Out in line, raced better than midfield on the outside, very wide into straight, peaked 450M, weakened early in straight.
Broke well and settled into a box-seat position, angled out in the straight and ran on, doing enough to just holding on.
Jumped with the field then steadied towards the rear, settled 3 wide worse than midfield with cover throughout, closed off strongly, just missed out.
Settled in front of midfield 3 wide no cover, made good progress in the Straight, but no match to the top 2.
Tracked leader, kept on fairly well early in the Straight, just weakened inside final 75M.
Ridden along early to be prominent, slotted in just behind the speed, travelled a bit keen throughout, only one pace in the Straight.
Settled midfield 3 wide, ran on only fairly.
Raced in front of midfield 2 wide between horses, held up early in the Straight and made little impression.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, did not quickened in the early part of the Straight, but did stayed on late inside final 150M.
Broke a step slow but showed very good early speed to lead, weakened inside 250M.
Raced 4 wide towards the rear, made some late headway.
Settled behind midfield on the rail, made no impression.
Jumped quite well but steadied towards last, never a threat.
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide, nothing in the Straight.
Settled last and never in contention. (See Incident Report) (Blood in Trachea) (Roarer) (Small abrasion to the left front cannon)
Tracked leaders, commenced move early in straight and took command over 100 metres out, won readily.
Soon took up running holding slender advantage, narrowly headed rounding home bend, re-gained lead briefly over 300 metres out only to be worn down 100 metres out.
Prominent 3-wide from a wide draw settling some 3L back in 5th 2-wide to home bend, fought on steadily in straight to reach 3 rd closing stages.

Travelled in rear of small field in 7th on rail and hanging in at times, gained slightly to 4L 6th 600 metres out, did not find much room behind runners until the 200 metres, fought on steadily to the line.
Broke well from the wide draw, settled just outside leader before hitting front narrowly rounding home bend, headed early in straight and ran home one-paced. (Tactic questioned)
Settled in last few from a wide draw, never seen with a chance.
Moderate start, soon recovered to just over 2L off the pace in 4th on rail, found no extra and faded shortly after straightening.
Trailed the field throughout and never a danger.
Travelled smoothly behind leaders, cruised to the lead 150M and soon had the race won. Completed hat trick of wins with extreme ease.
Reserved behind midfield, stayed on well final 200M to go 2nd, made some gains on winner late but that rival had been eased already.
Settled ahead of mid-division, kept on steadily down the inside, got up for 3rd late stages without troubling first two.
Vied for lead along the inside, shook off rivals to lead early straight, headed by the easy winner 150M out, no extra late stages and faded to 4th.
From wide draw caught 4-wide outside the lead, tried hard on straightening, not finishing pace of leaders final 200M.
Always prominent, up with leaders throughout, battled on one paced under top weight, faded 200M from home.
Jumped awkwardly then taken back to last, 6Ls off the pace home turn, stayed on fairly passing beaten rivals only.
Settled down midfield, 4Ls to make up 400M, couldn't go on in the straight.
Raced in mid-division along the 3-path, hung out in the middle stages whilst making the turn from 800M, never going the pace to challenge.
Hard driven forward but failed to show sufficient pace to cross his rivals, caught wide no cover when vying for the lead, found no extra 250M and gave ground rapidly.
From wide draw dropped back to race near the rear, didn't quicken when pressed along 500M, never involved.
Restrained to a rearward position, raced keenly early stages, driven 600M but failed to pick up pace. Never in contention.
Commenced well, raced slightly better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off strongly to score.

Made contact at start, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner close home. (Sustained a small laceration to the right hind heel bulb.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, a length or so back, there to turn, kept on well in straight to take a place, always just held.
Commenced well from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept on well early in straight, no clear run and snatched up final 50M.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide behind midfield, 2 wide from 650M, 4 lengths back turning in, made some progress in straight.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced in midfield on the outside, there to turn, made some progress early in straight, no extra final 150M. (Roarer.)
Began only fairly, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Bounded on jumping and lost ground, raced towards rear on the inside, 6 lengths back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Began smartly from the widest draw, raced 2 wide better than midfield, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at rear on the outside, very wide into straight, made no impression in the run home.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths back turning in, finished off evenly.
Slowly away, raced towards rear on the outside, 8 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Taken back to race 2 wide towards rear, 8 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Jumped awkwardly, raced at rear throughout, never a factor. (See Racing Incidents.)
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced 2 wide better than midfield, no daylight early in straight, cleared approaching 200M, hit the front 150M, kept on strongly to the line, easily scored.
Taken back from gate 9, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, made good progress thereafter to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, there to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 100M, stayed on evenly to take a place.
Away well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, weakened gradually final 50M.
Began well from a wide draw, trapped wide in midfield early, moved closer after passing 1000M, kept on evenly in straight.
Clean jump, raced 3 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 6 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Taken back from gate 11, raced behind midfield on the outside, similar position on turn, finished off evenly.
Crowded shortly after start, raced towards rear of midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some progress early in straight, short of room in the closing stages. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, sat right behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, kept on same pace in straight.
Taken back to race 2 wide at rear, 4-1/2L back turning in, finished off evenly.
Jumped awkwardly, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, made no impression in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Out with rest, raced 2 wide towards rear, there to turn, made no progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover towards rear, very wide into straight, showed limited response early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.

Jumped with them, raced slightly better than midfield on the outside, moved closer after passing 750M, took the lead 600M, shared the lead with rival on turn, kept on very well in straight, won by 1-1/4L.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 3 wide from 700M, slightly improved on turn, closed off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, angled out 600M, 4 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight to take a place, nearest on line.

Crowded shortly after start, raced at rear on the inside, moved a bit closer after passing 600M, angled out 450M, made good progress early in straight, not enough room from 100M, snatched up close home.

Jumped awkwardly and bumped, raced behind midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 650M, carried wider 450M, very wide into straight, closed off well to be nearest on line, no threat to the first few. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped shortly after start, raced towards rear in the early stages, sent forward after passing 800M, raced in 3rd on turn, 3 wide, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Average to begin, tracked leaders, 2 wide, found rail 500M, shared the lead on turn, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M.
Taken back from gate 10, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.

Commenced well, raced better than midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 800M, 3 wide after passing 600M, 3 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, headed near 1000M, positioned a length behind the leader in the middle stages, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.
Out with rest, raced towards rear, moved a bit closer after passing 700M, very wide into straight, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (Blood in trachea.)
Moderately away from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead 1000M, peaked and headed 600M, weakened thereafter, eased final 400M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Broke well from the one draw, ceded advantage for one back position over 950 metres out, angled out 2-wide into straight, asserted authority under pressure over 150 metres out.
Crowded at start settling in midfield on rail, gained closer turning in, angled out off heels 250 metres out, fought on under pressure without threatening.
Began quickly, took up running on rail about 950 metres out, led until headed under pressure over 150 metres out.
Settled in last few, saved ground turning for home, fought on steadily under pressure.
With leaders early, shifted one-out-one-back entering back straight, became 2L 4th about 650 metres out, lost position when wide into straight, kept on same pace.
Settled in midfield 2-wide, switched widest into straight, hung in early and kept on steadily to the line.
Settled towards rear, one of the widest into straight, kept on steadily under pressure without quickening.
Settled well behind, saved ground turning for home, baulked for a run over 150 metres out, made no further impression.
Crowded at start settling well behind, trailed the field into straight, fought on late and never nearer.

Slightly slow out from the widest draw, ridden forward to midfield just over 3L off in 5th 800 metres out, 3-wide without cover before wider into straight, unable to sustain effort inside final 150 metres.
Moderate start from a poor draw and lacked early pace, travelled behind midfield in 8th 3-wide without cover, carried wider into straight and soon weakened. (Lame)
Ridden forward from a poor draw to soon join race leader, unable to sustain effort inside final 400 metres. (Lame)
Broke nicely, ridden along to sit handy on the rail, responded well when asked making the Home Turn, kept on well to win.
Jumped only fairly, settled midfield on the rail, angled out and improved inside 500M, made good progress in the Straight, just missed narrowly on the line.
Sat behind midfield, travelled smoothly, closed off okay.
Ridden hard to lead, slightly weakened in the Straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Settled behind midfield 2 wide, took some time to respond after being under pressure at 500M, made minor progress inside 150M.
Sat midfield 2 wide, travelled strongly in the middle stages, but limited response when asked over the final 200M.
Fractious in the barriers, jumped awkwardly, settled in front of midfield on the rail, finished off fairly.
Ridden along to sit in front of midfield 2 wide, switched out approaching the 850M to share the lead, weakened inside 150M (See Incident Report).
Sat rear, slightly improved inside 600M, never a threat.
Settled handy 2 wide, travelled okay until weakened inside 550, no impression over the concluding stages.
Sat towards rear on the rail, never in contention. (lame left front the next day)
Sat towards rear 2 wide, eased down in the Straight (Bled).
Had a nice run on the leaders back. Moved over the heels of the leading pair on straightening, moved to the lead near the 100m mark & had enough in hand to hold off late closer to win by half length.

About 1L slow to begin & was ridden along to muster before getting position worse than midfield along rail. Stayed along the inside on straightening before closing strongly to move to 2nd at 100m & beaten only half-length.
Raced in midfield along the rail after first bend. Raced tight on straightening, shifted outwards to get clear at the 225m before closing off ok to move to third in final few strides.

Steadied approaching first bend & raced just worse than midfield away from rail. Was a touch keen when improving to midfield near the 800m. Shifted wider near 400m before making up late ground down the outside to be 4th.

Showed early speed to dispute the lead before steadying after first bend & racing outside the leader thereafter. Moved to the lead near the 225m before being joined by winner approaching 100m before weakening a length late.
Had a nice run 1,1 from after the first bend. Hung outwards on cornering when under pressure before being overtaken by better finishers in the last furlong.
Raced in midfield away from the rail. Was 4.5L from the lead at the 400m, raced tight between runners on straightening and again at the 225m before finishing only moderately late.

Was trapped racing three wide without cover when just worse than midfield throughout. Was just under 7L from lead entering final section when continuing to cover extra ground before being only able to make up a length late.

Steadied after jumping & was taken back to race worse than midfield between runners. Raced keenly from the 900m to about the 700m before being steadied from heels. Only held margin in the straight & was beaten 6L on line.
Pushed forward to share lead early before taking outright lead after first bend. Raced a length clear passing the 700m, was joined and headed near the 225m before weakening quickly in last furlong.
Steadied & taken to the tail. Was about 10L from the lead at the 400m when continuing last & made no headway into that margin finishing a long second last.

Steadied when racing wide around the first bend before being taken back to second last from the 1000m mark. Was under hard ridding from the 400m when over 8L from the lead before weakening further to be long last.

Bumped start, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 3Ls back turning in, no clear run early in straight, cleared after passing 150M, finished off strongly to score. (Sustained a minor abrasion to the left front leg.)
Average to begin, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared 100M, finished off strongly to take 2nd, just beaten by a narrow margin.
Moderately away from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, led by 1/2L turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the first two close home.
Jumped only fairly, raced at tail, 9 to 10 lengths back, closer on turn, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to make frame, nearest on line.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced in midfield on the outside, 3 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, very wide into straight, closed off well without threatening.
Moderately away from a wide draw, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, 1/2L back, same position on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide towards rear, 6 lengths back, a bit closer after passing 600M, angled out 500M, made some progress in straight.
Average to begin, raced towards rear, 7 to 8 lengths back, closer on turn, no clear run in straight, not able to test properly.
Made contact at start, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run in straight, not able to test properly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, wider on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Began well from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, angled out approaching 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened final 150M. (Blood in trachea.)
Broke well and showed good speed to sit behind the speed, travelled nicely throughout, angled into the clear rounding the Home Turn, quickened well, won going away.
Jumped on terms, slotted into 2 wide position in front of midfield, closed off nicely in the Straight, always held.
Broke well, tracked leader throughout, and kept on fairly well, no match for top 2.
Jumped nicely and ridden along to lead, just weakened inside final 50M, lost 3rd on the line.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, only one pace when asked.
Settled worse than midfield on the rail, took time to respond in the Straight, stayed on late, still racing a bit green.
Raced worse than midfield 2 wide, made some progress.
Settled midfield 2 wide, limited response in the Straight.
Broke a bit slow, settled near the rear 2 wide, made no impression.
Steadied after the start and moved across from a wide barrier, nothing in the Straight.
Settled towards the rear, never in contention.
Settled midfield on the rail, never a threat.

Settled in last few and waited with, commenced move rounding home bend and widest into straight, quickened well inside final 250 metres down the centre of the track to take charge inside the 150 metres.
Travelled towards rear and keenly in back straight, baulked 350 metres out before sneaking up between runners on the inside, reached 2nd inside the 100 metres, found winner too strong.
Settled towards rear 3-wide from a middle draw, commenced move 4-wide rounding home bend, ran on steadily down the centre of the straight to be nearest at in finish.
Attempted to make all from the one draw setting a quick tempo in first half of race, held 2L advantage into straight but swamped by fast-finishing winner 150 metres out, found no extra near finish.
Settled in midfield on rail, saved ground turning for home, unable to quicken under pressure and weakened under pressure inside final 100 metres.
Moderate start from a middle draw, ridden forward to be up with the pace before settling one back in 3rd on rail, kept on before fading under pressure inside final 100 metres.
Crowded at start travelling well back, saved ground turning for home, fought on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Began well but steadied and shifted back to midfield early stages, came under pressure rounding home bend and very wide into straight, one-paced.
Settled well back from the widest draw, saved ground home turn, fought on steadily without threatening.
Well there on rail, settled just over 3L off the pace in 5th in back straight, came to challenge under pressure turning for home but found nothing.
Broke well settling some 3L back in joint 4th 2-wide, wide rounding home bend, made no show in straight.
Pressed forward from a wide draw, obtained 2-wide position in 2nd rounding first bend, dropped out tamely after straightening.
Tracked the pace from draw 1, moved strongly into contention, wrestled the lead from leader 100M, well in command closing stages.
Showed speed to lead, set good pace upfront, pressed by rival 200M, fought hard but couldn't hold off challenge final 100M. Clear from rest.
Began fairly, settled midfield, pushed along 450M, did best work late to claim 3rd, no threat to first two.
Obtained a midfield position, raced ungenerously in the early and middle stages, ran on moderately final 300M. No impression on first two.
Jumped well, up with early pace before holding back to settle in 5th spot, never going the pace to challenge leaders in the straight, kept on one paced to the line.
Restrained after the start, settled at the rear, 9Ls to make up 400M, closed off best but had too much to do. (Jockey reminded to ride out to the finish.)
Chased leaders 2-wide, fought on under top weight passing 400M, briefly went 3rd mid-straight, no extra late stages and lost several places near line.
From wide draw jumped only fairly, shifted across behind runners to be 6Ls towards the rear, stayed on final 300M without seriously threatening.
Moved up to press leader on outside, couldn't sustain run passing 200M, faded towards the line. (Bled.)
Away with them, soon niggled along but struggled to keep up with rivals, soon left behind turning for home.
Began well, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead near 1000M, enjoyed the easy lead in the middle stages, kept on well in straight to hold off the challenger.
Average to begin, raced in midfield on the inside, easy run to turn, finished off strongly to take 2nd, nearest finish.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced in midfield on the outside, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight to take a place, nearest on line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, 7 lengths back turning in, made very good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Quickly into stride, took the early lead, headed near 1000M, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader in the middle stages, kept on evenly in straight.
Slightly slow out, raced at rear, 8 lengths back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to be nearest on line.
Jumped with them, raced towards rear on the outside, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made some progress in the run home.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced behind midfield on the inside, 5 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, kept on same pace in straight.
Bumped on jumping, raced better than midfield, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened and eased final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back, same margin back on turn, one-paced in the run home.
Jumped well, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)

Jumped well, positioned 2 wide, 1-1/2L back, commenced move 600M, 3 wide turning in, hit the front 250M, kept on well to hold off the challengers.
Made contact at start, raced behind midfield on the outside, hard ridden from 550M, finished off strongly to take 2nd, just beaten by a narrow margin. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide towards rear, 3 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, closed off well to take a place.
Made contact at start, taken back to race at tail, 4 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, made good progress early in straight, no clear run final 100M.
Average to begin, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked and headed 250M, ran on same pace to the line.
Jumped only fairly, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line. (Blood in trachea.)
Moderately away, tracked leaders, 3 wide, 2 wide after entering the back straight, 3/4L back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened inside final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)

Strode forward and shared the lead in middle stages when racing closest to the center of the track in a line of 4 on speed. Moved to narrow outright lead passing 250m before continuing on to win by a length.

Raced in midfield not far from the stand side rail. Shifted inwards passing the 300m to get clear running before closing strongly in last furlong to improve to second at 75m & get within a length on the line.

Didn't have the early speed of others and raced just worse than midfield nearer to the center of the track. Closed strongly in final 300m to be beaten just over a length when getting closest to lead on line.
Showed customary early speed to lead before sharing the lead in the middle stages. Continued not far behind all of the way until over-run for a minor placing in the final 50m, close behind.
Showed speed to share the lead when galloping between runners in a line of four at the front. Continued close before emptying at the 75m mark & just being over-run late but wasn't beaten far.

Bumped at the start & drifted back to race rearward. Was relegated to last near half-way. Was over 4L from lead at the 400m before doing best work in last furlong when making late ground between runners to only be beaten 2L.

Bumped at the start before drifting back to race last along the stand side rail early. Was second last at half-way, got close to heels & steadied near 350m before making up a length late, beaten under 3L in midfield.
Raced in midfield when galloping near to the center of the track. Was ridden along passing the 400m mark before weakening a length in the last section to be beaten just over 3L.
Slow to begin by about a length & raced near the rear when galloping closer to the center of the track. Gave a few lengths in last section & was beaten just over 6L.
Raced in midfield in the early and middle stages. Was niggled along from half-way & began yielding ground from the 450m, eventually weakening out to be beaten about 11L (bled).

Showed speed to share the lead when galloping between runners at the front. Came under pressure quickly passing the 250m before weakening badly in late stages to be long last (respiratory noise, substantial blood in trachea).
Sat handy 4 wide off the stand's rail, travelled strongly, made good progress over the concluding stages, kept on well to win.
Ridden along to lead, travelled smoothly, weakened inside 100M to hold 2nd.
Jumped awkwardly, settled midfield center of the track, showed some response when asked approaching the 100M, closed off okay.
Sat midfield 3 wide off the stand's rail, ran on evenly, slightly weakened over the last few strides.
Jumped awkwardly, settled towards rear 3 wide off the stand's rail, no clear run from 300M, cannot be fully tested.
Jumped only fairly, sat towards rear 2 wide the stand's rail, ran on fairly, limited responded when asked.
Jumped awkwardly, sat towards rear 4 wide off the stand's rail, one pace, no impression.
Sat rear, weakened inside 200M, never a threat.
Had a nice run in fourth along the rail. Bumped multiple times when racing tight after straightening before improving to take narrow lead near 50m mark & continue on to win narrowly.

Had a nice position in midfield away from the rail. Eased three wide near the 600m, straightened just under 3L from the lead before closing strongly all the way to the line to just miss in a bob of the heads on the wire.

Raced just worse than midfield early before improving along the rail to race in midfield on middle stages. Stayed close to the inside on straightening, closed well all the way to the line to move to third in final 25m when beaten under 1L.
Began very fast and came across from gate 14 to lead. Continued to lead until being passed quickly by the first two inside the last 75m, boxed on well to only be beaten 1.25L on line.

Raced just worse than midfield between runners. Eased wider passing the 550m, was the second widest on straightening when around 4.5L from the lead before making late ground down the outside to only be beaten 2.25L into fifth.

Drifted back to race in a rearward along the rail. Stayed along the inside, held up on straightening, was making steady ground along rail before being crowded, checked & losing ground near the 200m before finishing ok late.

Pushed forward, raced third early before improving to race outside the leader from the 900m. Peaked on effort at the 250m when about a length behind before weakening out in last furlong to be beaten over 5L in midfield.

Began awkwardly & lost a few lengths before racing rearward. Shifted outwards after straightening when over 5L behind before managing to pass a few tiring rivals when running onto midfield but only maintaining margin.

Pushed forward, raced second, crossed by leader near 1100m, moved off rail & raced 1,1 from about the 900m. Raced tight & bumped a few times on straightening before weakening out pretty poorly in final 250m.

Blundered after start before being steadied & taken back to race in a bunch at tail. Was a clear last on straightening when 7L behind before shifting to be the widest, passed a few tiring rivals without making any ground.

Got back to race worse than midfield when three wide with cover. Was forced wider passing the 600m, was the widest runner on straightening when just under 6L from the lead before weakening a length in the run to the line.

Was trapped racing three wide without cover in midfield in early & middle stages. Shifted out to be five wide on cornering & came under immediate pressure before weakening to be beaten 8L (roarer again).

Raced midfield between runners for the majority. Straightened just under 4L from the lead, was finishing off only moderately & was no factor before being slightly short of room in final 150m & not ridden out thereafter.

Drifted back after the start to race in a bunch at the tail of the field from the 1100m. Continued rearward on straightening, was just under 6L behind entering final section & did nothing in the straight, weakening to last.
Out in line, raced towards rear on the inside, 2 wide from 850M, wider turning in, showed very good response in straight, hit the front 100M, kept on well to hold off the challenger late.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at rear on the outside, 2 wide on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off strongly to take 2nd, just beaten by a narrow margin.
Began well from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, angled out 450M, made some progress in straight to take a place, no threat to the first two. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, wider turning in, made some progress early in straight, no extra final 100M.

Began well, raced slightly better than midfield on the outside, moved closer after passing 900M, took the lead 500M, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 100M, weakened thereafter. (Lame right front leg next day.)

Made contact at start, raced better than midfield on the inside, angled out after passing 600M, kept on well early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.) (Blood in trachea.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final 100M.

Out with rest, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, took the lead 800M, headed near 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong. (Sustained a laceration to the left hind leg.)
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide from 900M, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.) (Blood in trachea.)
Shifted out at start and made contact, sent forward to take the lead, headed near 800M, peaked 500M, weakened early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from a wide draw, raced in midfield on the outside, peaked 550M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped awkwardly, raced 2 wide towards rear, 3 wide from 900M, peaked on turn, weakened thereafter. (Bled.)
Jumped with the field, settled midfield 2 wide, closed off nicely, always have the measure of the race.
Settled just behind the speed 2 wide, angled out into the clear in the Straight, quickened nicely, always held.
Broke slowly, settled midfield on the rail, had some difficulty finding clear run early in the Straight, ran home okay last 200M.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, held up early in the Straight, ran on evenly.
Settled worse than midfield on the rail, stayed on fairly.
Settled near the rear on the rail, made some progress in the Straight.
Settled behind midfield 2 wide, one pace when asked.
Tracked leader, weakened inside 250M.
Broke well and ridden along to lead, weakened and faded inside 200M.
Caught 3 wide no cover around midfield, nothing in the Straight.
Jumped nicely but steadied to settle at the rear from a wide barrier, never a threat.
Showed no early speed and sat at the rear, never in contention.
Jumped in midfield, ridden forward to within 1L of leaders shortly after, carried backward to 3L 5th over 1000 metres out, responded well inside final 300 metres to assert authority 100 metres out.
Ridden along to join the leaders from a poor draw, restrained in 2nd some half a length off the pace, hit the front under pressure over 250 metres out only to be caught at the 100 metres.
Moderate start, travelled keenly amongst leaders early, remained one-out-one-back rounding home bend, kept on steadily without quickening.
Broke well travelling keenly with narrow advantage on rail, headed over 250 metres out and swamped for a placing late.
Settled towards rear on rail, gained closer to midfield to 6th rounding home bend, ran on steadily early in straight but tightened a couple of times inside final 75 metres.
Settled in last few but travelling keenly onto home bend, made good progress under pressure in the run to the line but never threatening. (Blood in trachea)
Settled in rear on rail from a poor draw, made steady headway rounding home bend to reach 4L 7th into straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, travelled keenly just over 2L back in 5th on rail, gained slightly closer to 4th onto home bend, unable to quicken under pressure in straight.
Restrained to rear from a wide draw, saved ground on rail turning in, fought on steadily without quickening under pressure inside final 200 metres.
Close up early from a wide draw but gradually dropping back towards rear, remained 3-wide around home bend, produced good late impression in straight, nearest at finish.
Soon taken back from a wide draw, remained wide in last few, dropped to tail-end and given reminders rounding home bend, fought on well past well-beaten runners inside final 100 metres. (Bled)
Travelled in midfield in 8th some 4 to 5L back, found nothing under pressure in straight.
Close up early, gradually drifted back to 6th and steadied inside 1000 metres, wide without cover in midfield around home bend before yielding ground into straight, made no further impression.
From draw 1 obtained running in midfield along the fence, pushed along 600M, responded well on rain affected ground, kept finding under pressure final 200M and just prevailed at the line.
Towards the rear, no closer than 3-wide throughout the trip, stayed on well passing 400M on rain affected ground, just held at the line.
Taken back from wide draw, waited with at the rear along inside, held up for clear running making the home turn, finished fastest final 400M, held by first 2 towards the line.
Always prominent, in 2nd spot turning for home, led early straight before joined by rivals inside 200M, faded to 4th late.
Not hurried after the start, dropped back to race at the rear, wide into straight, closed off steadily to be nearest at the finish.

Raced wide no cover in midfield early stages, moved up to track leaders approaching home turn, swung wide for home, responded well to take lead mid-straight but run ended near 100M and lost several places near line.

Began only fairly, held up towards the rear, had difficulty obtaining clear running home turn, kept on mildly early straight before fading away final stages. (Jockey : settled further back than anticipated.)
Behind mid-division along the 3-path, kept chasing leaders early straight, couldn't sustain run final 200M.
Restrained to race in midfield, over-raced in early stages, kept on fairly turning home, never dangerous.
Settled towards the rear, 5Ls to make up 400M, lacked a finishing kick, never threatened. (Blood in trachea.)
Jumped only fairly, sent forward to lead, headed inside 400M, weakened rapidly. (Jockey : may not have appreciated heavy track conditions.)
Chased leader, failed to respond passing 400M, soon out of contention.
Settled 3-wide in mid-division, came up empty on straightening, eased when no chance.
Raced behind midfield, came under pressure home turn, soon weakened away and finished tailed out (Unacceptable Performance.)
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, headed approaching 800M, retook the lead 550M, kept on well in straight to hold off the challengers late.
Made contact shortly after start, raced slightly behind midfield on the outside, very wide turning in, finished off very strongly to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Made contact shortly after start, raced in 3rd, 3 wide with no cover, same position on turn, hard ridden after passing 300M, closed off well to take a place, always held. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, there to turn, angled out early in straight, finished off well to make frame.
Made contact shortly after start, raced prominently, took the lead 800M, headed near 550M, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide at rear, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Bumped start, positioned 3 wide with cover, 2 lengths back, wider turning in, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at rear on the outside, very wide into straight, made minor progress in the run home.
Away with them, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, there to turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Commenced well, positioned 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Began well, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, same position on turn, finished off strongly to score by a narrow margin.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/2L, travelled comfortably to turn, kept on very well in straight but unable to hold off the winner on line.
Away well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Commenced well, positioned 3 wide, 1-1/2L back, no cover throughout, kept on same pace in straight.
Moderately away, raced at rear on the inside, 4 lengths back turning in, made good progress early in straight, peaked on run 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, commenced move 500M, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly thereafter.
Slow to begin, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Began only fairly, raced behind midfield on the outside, very wide into straight, kept on same pace to the line.
Jumped awkwardly and lost ground, raced at rear on the outside, very wide turning in, showed limited response early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Slowly away, raced 2 wide towards rear, angled out 550M, no clear run in straight, not able to test properly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Shifted in at start, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Began well from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.

Jumped well, raced better than midfield on the inside, 4 lengths or so back, moved a bit closer along the rail in the middle stages, hit the front 250M, ran on strongly to the line, won by 3-1/2L.
Began well from a wide draw, raced in 2nd, 2 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, kept on well in straight without threatening the winner.

Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled keenly in the early stages, led by a length on turn, peaked and headed 250M, ran on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out after passing 400M, very wide into straight, closed off well to make frame.
Commenced well from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Out with rest, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, 3 wide from 700M, a bit closer on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, similar position on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slightly slow out, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on same pace in straight.
Average to begin, raced towards rear, 5 lengths or so back on turn, very wide into straight, no clear run early in straight, ran on evenly thereafter.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide from 700M, moved closer on turn, very wide into straight, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Away with them, raced towards rear on the outside, very wide into straight, failed to make any progress in the run home.
Slowly away, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Held up behind midfield, waited with until 450M, responded strongly passing 300M, got up near line.
Took early lead before taking a step back behind leader 1300M, moved up to join leader again 600M, fought on well to lead 150M out, caught by winner final few strides.
Settled down midfield, saved ground on inside, closed off steadily final 300M, went 3rd close home.
Given a waiting ride towards the rear, dropped to last passing 700M, brought wide in the straight, did best work final 200M, nearest finish.
Vied for early lead before emerging as leader 1300M, pressed by rivals 600M, fought hard in the straight, caught near 150M, faded late to finish 5th.
4th on settling, crept closer to leaders 600M, kept on steadily towards the finish, not beaten far at the line.
Settled behind midfield along the inside, held up home turn, responded to pressure when driven early straight, had no clear running over final 150M, could have done better.
Reserved behind midfield, caught wide entering back straight, driven along 650M but failed to pick up under top weight, never a threat to leaders.
Went forward, tracked leaders from 1300M, remained close enough turning, fought hard to hold its position, no extra 150M.
Taken back to race at the rear, made mid-race move 850M to be pressing leader 3-wide, had nothing left passing 250M, weakened.
Settled in midfield, pushed along 450M, kept on fairly turning home, weakened 150M.
Dropped back to near the rear, taken wide back straight, came under pressure home turn, soon no extra on straightening.
Ridden along to lead on the rail, travelled strongly, made good progress in the Straight, kept on well to win.
Sat in front of midfield on the rail, travelled comfortably, showed some response when asked inside 250M, closed off nicely.
Settled behind midfield on the rail, began to improve approaching the 450M, ran on evenly to the line.
Sat in front of midfield 3 wide, peaked at 150M but weakened thereafter.
Broke nicely, ridden hard to sit handy but steadied from 700M, one pace when asked in the Straight.
Sat midfield 2 wide, lay in near the 600M, finished off okay (Racing manners unacceptable).
Sat towards rear 2 wide, no clear running in the Straight, could not be fully tested.
Settled behind midfield 3 wide, improved from 500M, made minor progress in the Straight.
Jumped only fairly, sat behind midfield 2 wide, raced keenly in the middle stages, weakened inside 150M.
Ridden along to chase the lead 2 wide, weakened quickly over the final 100M, never a threat.
Was fractious in the barriers, jumped awkwardly, settled towards rear on the rail, limited response when asked (Roarer).
Jumped okay, sat rear 3 wide, no impression.

Raced third last when galloping in the clear. Moved wider at 600m, shifted very wide on straightening before letting go with a dazzling turn of speed to charge to lead at the 100m & despite laying in win impressively.

Raced just worse than midfield along the rail. Stayed close to the rail on straightening when about 5L from the lead before closing off well to move to second passing the 100m mark but being unable to match impressive winner.

Showed speed to lead before being crossed & racing on leaders back from the 800m. Moved into clear running on straightening when second before being passed quickly by the winner at the 100m & then battling to hold third.

Showed speed at the start & improved to share lead on first bend before improving to outright lead near the 1000m. Was over 1L clear on straightening before passed at the 125m before battling away to hold well beaten 4th.

Steadied after the start & shifted behind runners to race second last. Continued rearward & about 6L from the lead on straightening before passing a few rivals when running onto well beaten midfield finish.

Was trapped racing three deep in midfield before being left without cover from about the 700m. Was forced wider on straightening when just over 3L from the lead before only battling away to hold well beaten midfield finish.

Steadied from outside gate & shifted behind runners to last before being ridden along at the tail. Was last & over 6L from the lead on straightening before passing a few tiring rivals when running onto midfield out wide.

Began fairly before improving along the rail to race prominently before being crossed at the first bend & racing in midfield. Was 3.5L from lead entering final section before weakening a few lengths in straight (Must trial).

Bumped at the start, improved to race close to lead early before steadying & being crossed & racing 1,1 from about the 700m. Was under 3L from the lead on straightening before weakening poorly to be beaten 6L (see report).

Bumped at the start, raced wide around first bend when in midfield before being ridden forward to improve position & race outside the leader from the 700m. Niggled when 2L behind on straightening before weakening in straight.

Raced in midfield between runners throughout. Drifted slightly further back after the 600m bend, was about 4L behind on straightening before doing nothing in the straight and failing to beat a runner home. Last.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length on turn, kept on very well in straight, won by 2-1/4L. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide in midfield early, moved closer after passing 900M, 2nd in the middle stages, a length or so back, kept on well in straight without threatening the winner.
Commenced well, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off well to take a place without threatening. (Lame left front leg next day morning.)
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, wider turning in, finished off evenly.
Out with rest, positioned 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well, raced in 2nd in the early stages, 3rd in the middle stages, kept on well early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M.
Away with them, raced at tail, 6 lengths or so back on turn, finished off evenly.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced towards rear on the inside, angled out 450M, 5 lengths back turning in, made no impression in straight.
Taken back to race towards rear on the outside, 3 lengths or so back, no cover throughout, made no progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Broke nicely, showed good early speed to sit just behind the speed, travelled nicely throughout, quickened nicely in the Straight to score
Hard ridden early, sat outside the lead, kept on okay, never a threat to the winner. (laceration to the right front pastern)
Jumped on terms, steadied from the wide barrier and raced at the rear, stayed on very well late.
Broke a step slow, settled behind midfield on the rail, under pressure at 500M, closed off only fairly.
Ridden along early to lead, kept on okay early in the Straight and weakened inside 150M. (See Incident Report)
Jumped nicely and settled midfield on the rail, only one pace when asked.
Crowded at the start, went near the rear on the rail, and made some progress in the Straight.
Showed good early pace to be prominent, under pressure at 500M, weakened near 250M.
Caught 3 wide no cover worse than midfield, made no impression.
Settled behind midfield 2 wide between horses, made no progress.
Settled towards the rear, never in contention.
Settled midfield 2 wide, never a threat.

Settled just off the pace in 5th, drifted further away over 3L back in back straight, commenced move home bend switching wide into straight, responded well inside final 150 metres to take command over 50 metres out.
Settled in rear of midfield in 7th on rail, hugged rail turning for home, snuck up under pressure to reach 2nd final strides. (Tactic questioned)
Ridden to hold 1L advantage into back straight, narrowly headed over 700 metres out, re-gained lead making final turn only to be overhauled over 50 metres out, lost 2nd late.
Settled in midfield in 6th some 5L back, came under pressure rounding home bend, sustained progress under pressure inside final 150 metres and did best work late.
Gradually taken back to last few from a poor draw, travelled 3-wide without cover most of way, remained similar turning for home, ran on under pressure to be nearest at finish.

Recovered quickly from moderate start to be up with the pace, restrained some 2L back to 4th early in back straight, 3rd in similar one-out-one-back position 700 metres out, one-paced when tightened 150 metres out.
Dropped to tail-end after moderate start, remained well behind into straight, produced good late finish inside final 150 metres.
Taken back from the widest draw reaching last over 800 metres out, given reminders rounding home bend and widest into straight, finished off race well down the centre of the track .
Began well from the one draw, gradually settled one back on rail early in back straight, remained similar turning for home, kept on before weakening inside final 50 metres.
Restrained to midfield from a poor draw settling towards rear with cover in 8th, came under pressure from 550 metres out but could only keep on at the same pace without quickening.
Always in last few and never seen with a chance, travelling keenly in early stages.
Broke well from a poor draw, swung 4-wide into back straight and gradually improved to lead over 700 metres out, headed on straightening and weakened. (Sustained injury)
From draw 11 quickly shifted across behind runners, settled behind mid-division, held up on home turn, ran on strongly final 250M, got up near 50M.
Chased leaders 2-wide, took over 400M, kept on well early straight, led to near 50M, held on 2nd just.
Settled towards the rear 10Ls off the pace, saved ground along the inside, ran on nicely to be nearest at the finish.

Reserved in a 2-wide position behind midfield, pushed along 550M swinging wide into straight, responded well but lay in under pressure, not fully tested late when being corrected by its jockey, nearest finish.
Chased leaders on inside, travelled well into straight, fought on steadily along the fence over final 300M but always held by leaders towards the finish.
Raced in mid-division along the 2-path, moved closer home turn, kept on moderately final 300M, held by leaders final 150M.

Jumped only fairly, shifted across to race along the fence in mid-division, close enough turning home, responded well initially but run ended mid-straight. (Jockey: up in class did not finish the race strongly over final 200M.)
Restrained to a rearward position, inclined to race keenly early stages, 9th at 400M, gave limited response turning home, never threatened.
From draw 12 take across behind runners, held up at the rear over 10Ls off the fast pace early stages, kept on only fairly turning home, never a threat.
Tracked the pace early stages, moved up to press leader 900M, couldn't go on passing 400M, soon out of contention. (Sustained wounds to LF cannon.)
Dropped back after the start, at rear over 10Ls off the pace early stages, crept closer 600M but failed to respond turning for home, never involved.
From draw 1 strolled to the lead, set fast pace first half of race, came under pressure 450M, weakened badly on straightening.

Began well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, trapped 3 wide, 2 lengths or so back, commenced move after passing 600M, took the lead 450M, kicked clear early in straight, ran on strongly to the line, won by 4-3/4L, impressive.
Commenced well from gate 1, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, angled out 350M, finished off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Shifted out at start, positioned 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, hard ridden after passing 500M, closed off well to take a place without threatening.
Blundered on jumping, raced in midfield on the inside, 3 lengths or so back, saved ground throughout, kept on well early in straight, peaked 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced towards rear on the outside, 4-1/2L back turning in, made some progress in straight, never dangerous.
Crowded start, raced behind midfield on the inside, 4 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, kept on same pace in straight.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at tail, 6 lengths back on turn, passed some tired runners in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths back, angled out after passing 400M, very wide into straight, made no impression in straight.
Taken back to race 2 wide towards rear, 6 lengths back turning in, made no impression in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well in the middle stages, headed near 450M, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Moderately away from a wide draw, positioned 3 wide with cover, 3 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, very wide into straight, weakened final 300M.
Away well, raced prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, peaked 450M, weakened and eased thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
