Began smartly from gate 1, raced prominently in the middle of the track, ridden approaching 200M, took the lead 150M, kept on very well to the line, easily scored.
Bumped on jumping, sent forward to take the lead on the stands' side, ridden after passing 300M, headed 150M, kept on well to the line.
Jumped awkwardly, raced in midfield on the middle track, finished off well to take a place without threatening the first two.
Average to begin, raced prominently, nearer to the middle track, peaked on run 300M, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Shifted in at start and bumped, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on the stands' side, peaked 400M, weakened gradually final 300M.
Jumped well from gate 10, raced prominently on the stands' rail, peaked 350M, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slowly away, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on the stands' side, hard ridden after passing 450M but only showed limited response, weakened final 250M.
Commenced well, raced in midfield on the middle track, peaked 400M, weakened from 300M.
Slightly slow out, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader, peaked approaching 400M, weakened final 300M.
Began awkwardly, raced at rear on the stands' rail, detached from the main group 500M, finished tailed out, unacceptable performance.
Settled in 4th on rail about 3L off the pace, switched 3-wide coming onto home turn, ran on under pressure to hit front over 100 metres out, won readily.
Never far off, fought on steadily under pressure but found winner too strong. (Lame)
Soon dropped to last few, saved ground and snuck up to 6L 6th turning in, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Ridden to lead from a wide draw, obtained rails run in front over 800 metres out, unable to sustain effort and headed over 100 metres out.
Jumped well before settling in 6th in forward of midfield, given reminders 500 metres out, made no impression in straight. (Blood in trachea)
Settled in midfield from moderate start, further behind into straight, ran home one-paced. (Tactic questioned)
Soon dropped to midfield despite ridden along out wide, improved steadily to some 3L 4th 3-wide onto home bend, faded into straight.
Soon dropped wide towards rear from a poor draw, remained similar into straight, ran home one-paced.
Crowded at start losing ground but soon recovered to rear of midfield, ridden slightly closer 4-wide onto home bend, found nothing in straight.
Ridden along 2-wide in joint 2nd about 2L off the pace, dropped out tamely upon straightening.
Broke well but lacked pace and soon dropped well behind, given reminders rounding home bend, found nothing.
Lacked pace and soon dropped well behind, never seen with a chance.
Broke smartly, ridden along to lead 2 wide, travelled comfortably, made some progress inside 200M, closed off nicely (See Incident Report).
Sat handy on the rail, travelled strongly, made contact with a runner in a number of occasions in the Straight, kept on well.
Settled behind midfield 2 wide, response okay when asked inside 150M, nearest finish.
Slow to begin, settled worse than midfield on the rail, travelled okay, slightly weakened inside 75M.
Sat rear, raced greenly and lay in the Straight, stayed on well.
Settled behind midfield 3 wide, ran on evenly, one pace when asked.
Jumped awkwardly, sat towards rear on the rail, no clear run in the early Straight, closed off fairly.
Ridden hard to lead, weakened near 250M, never a danger.
Jumped awkwardly, sat handy 2 wide, no impression in the Straight (See Incident Report).
Sat midfield, raced wide, weakened and faded inside 300M.
Sat midfield, travelled wide throughout, raced greenly and lay in under pressure, never a threat (See Incident Report, Unacceptable Performance).
Settled in front of midfield, raced wide and without cover, never in contention.

Showed speed after the start to lead. Travelled strongly in middle stages, dashed clear under no riding after straightening, was still 3L clear at the 150m before being allowed to cruise to the line impressively.

Raced worse than midfield away from the rail. Had clear running on straightening when 3.5L from the lead before making strong late ground to close to second passing the 75m mark before reducing margin to under 1L late.
Had a soft run in midfield along the rail. Stayed along the rail on straightening, entered last section 3L from the lead before closing well to move to second at 200m before holding third on line.
Began fast & raced outside the leader. Couldn't go with the leader/winner on straightening before battling away to be beaten 3L into fourth.

Raced in midfield between runners. Raced a touch keenly passing the 850m, was afforded clear running on straightening when just over 2L from the lead before battling away fairly to be beaten just over 3L in midfield.

Lifted feet at the start & consequently got back to race at the tail. Continued last on cornering when staying along the rail before making up a length or two when running onto midfield from the back but never threatening.

Didn't begin fast & got back to race second last soon after the start. Continued rearward & 5L from the lead entering final section before passing only a few tiring runners when holding deficit to finish in midfield.
Raced in midfield along the rail. Moved away from the rail approaching the final corner, was 4L from the lead entering last section before doing little in the straight & weakening to be beaten 8L.
Got back after the start to race third last when galloping three wide with cover. Was last and just under 6L from the lead entering final section before weakening poorly to be beaten 12L.

Was trapped racing four wide without cover in midfield before steadying around the first bend & shifting to be three wide with cover from about 750m. Was ridden along from the 550m before weakening badly to be well beaten.

Ridden at start to be prominent before racing on the leaders back for the majority. Was only about 2L from the lead on straightening before weakening badly in the straight to be very long second last.

Was trapped racing three deep without cover in midfield before improving to be outside the leaders from 650m when still wide. Hung outwards passing 600m & on straightening before weakening & then not tested last 300m (lame).
Average to begin, raced prominently on rail early, sat right behind the leader in the middle stages, kept to inside after straightening, finished off strongly to score.

Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/2L, found rail near 900M, travelled comfortably in the middle stages, kept on well early in straight, peaked 150M, headed 100M, ran on evenly to take 2nd.
Moderately away from a wide draw, positioned 3 wide, 2 lengths or so back, 2 wide from 900M, same margin back on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place without threatening.
Began well from a tricky draw, raced prominently on the outside, 1/2L or so back, there to turn, kept on well in straight without threatening.
Jumped awkwardly, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Out with rest, raced slightly behind midfield on the outside, 3 lengths or so back turning in, made good progress early in straight, no extra final 150M.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, dropped to midfield in the middle stages, wider turning in, bumped 450M, no clear run in straight, unable to test properly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slowly away, raced behind midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 500M, bumped 450M, not enough room early in straight, peaked 150M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Hampered start, raced at rear on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, kept on same pace in straight.
Moderately away from the widest draw, raced better than midfield on the outside, 2 lengths or so back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths or so back, found rail near 600M, same margin back turning in, made no progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the outside, very wide turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from gate 12, raced at tail, 8 lengths or so back, very wide into straight, made no progress in the run home.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, dropped towards rear 700M, struggled from 500M, eased final 250M. (See Racing Incidents.) (Lame right front leg next day.)
Broke nicely and settled in a box seat position, angled out in the Straight and quickened nicely, battled hard and just done enough.
Broke a step slow and settled midfield on the rail, held up early in the Straight and ran on strongly after the 250M, just missed narrowly on the line.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, made good progress early in the Straight, just one pace after 150M.
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide, stayed on okay, no threat to top 3.
Raced near the rear on the rail, made decent progress along the rail.
Steadied after the start from a wide barrier to sit at the rear, under pressure at 800M, circled the field and stayed on nicely until weakened in the final 100M.
Settled near the rear 2 wide, held up most of the Straight, never seriously tested.
Broke nicely and showed good early speed to lead, weakened in the Straight.
Settled midfield 2 wide between horses, nowhere to go in the early part of the Straight, made little impression.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, nothing in the Straight. (See Incident Report)
Ridden along early, caught wide down the back Straight and improved to sit outside the lead at 900M, weakened and faded in the Straight. (See Incident Report)
Settled behind the speed, under pressured at 500M and gave ground.
Caught 3 wide with cover in midfield, never a threat. (See Incident Report)
Raced 3 wide without cover in front of midfield, never in contention.
Well there but soon taken one back, commenced move rounding home bend and hit the front into straight, drew clear under pressure inside final 200 metres.
Lost ground at start dropping to last early, gained slightly closer on rail rounding home bend, snuck up under pressure after straightening, fought on steadily to reach 2nd over 50 metres out.
Close up early gradually drifting backward to midfield approaching first bend, fought on steadily after straightening without threatening.
Moderate start gradually settling in last few, commenced move out wide rounding home bend, one of the widest turning in, fought on steadily down the centre of the track but never threatening.
Soon took up running on rail, narrowly headed 950 metres out, hugged rail turning into straight and found no extra.
Settled well behind from a poor gate, trailed the field from over 1200 metres out, made up good ground down the centre of straight and did best work late.
Broke well gradually settled wide without cover in last few, made steady headway around the field rounding home bend and widest runner into straight, ran home one-paced under pressure.
Improved steadily from the widest draw, obtained lead 2-wide 950 metres out but headed by the winner into straight, weakened badly inside final 200 metres. (Tactic questioned)
Ridden along in rear of midfield, reached 4th under pressure some 3L back briefly about 300 metres out, inconvenienced closing stages.
Prominent early before dropping to worse than midfield passing 1100 metres, remained similar into straight when hampered over 400 meres out, ran home one-paced.
Soon taken back to last few, saved ground turning for home, did not find much room and checked early in straight, never recovered.
Soon picked up to 6h within 3L of pace, saved ground on rail turning for home, dropped out tamely shortly after straightening.
Began well but soon dropped back to midfield, recovered steadily to joint 5th coming onto home bend and just behind leaders into straight, folded up quickly upon straightening. (Mucus)
Jumped fairly from a poor draw, ridden forward to be up with the pace, 3-wide without cover rounding home bend and unable to sustain effort from over 500 metres out. (Tactic questioned)
Prompted the pace on outside, driven to challenge for the lead mid-straight, dueled final 200M, just prevailed.
Soon led, set steady pace, joined by rival 200M, tried hard to fight off challenger, went down by a head at the line.
Tracked leaders, tried hard on straightening but always held by first two in the run home.
Held up in midfield along the fence, kept on moderately passing 300M, not reach first two.
Chased leaders 2-wide, had every chance turning home, held ground over final 200M.
Shifted across behind runners, 4Ls off the pace 400M, awkwardly placed passing 200M, failed to make headway final stages.
Settled towards the rear, 5Ls to make up 400M, stayed on without posing much threat.
Settled behind midfield, kept on fairly passing 400M, always held by leaders.
Caught wide no cover in midfield, driven along 550M, kept on one paced and no threat to leaders mid-straight.
Dropped back to race at the rear 5Ls off the pace, failed to respond when driven along 400M, soon left behind, never in the picture.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, moved a bit closer on turn, showed very good response in straight, hit the front 200M, kept on very well to the line and scored.
Began well, raced better than midfield on the outside, moved closer on turn, ridden to lead 300M, peaked and headed 200M, ran on evenly to the line.
Slightly slow out, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, a bit closer on turn, not enough room early in straight, cleared approaching 200M, finished off evenly.
Jumped awkwardly and lost ground, raced at rear, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, closed off well to make frame without threatening.
Began fairly, raced behind midfield on the inside, 3 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced behind midfield on the outside, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, 1-1/2L back on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Average to begin, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, 3rd turning in, peaked on run 300M, weakened quickly final furlong.
Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked and headed 250M, weakened quickly final furlong.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.

Slightly slow out and crowded, raced at rear on the outside early, moved a bit closer after passing 900M, 3 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from a tricky draw, taken back to race 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths back, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Shifted out at start and made contact, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Taken back from gate 11, raced towards rear on the inside, 2 wide from 550M, no clear run early in straight, cleared 300M, hit the front 150M, kept on strongly to the line, easily scored.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, 3 wide from 600M, taken wide in straight and finished off well to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Moderately away, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, hard ridden approaching 300M, kept on well until no extra final 50M.
Bumped start, positioned 2 wide, 1-1/2L back, angled out 550M, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Began smartly from gate 1, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead approaching 800M, led by a length turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, weakened final 100M.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths or so back, commenced move 550M, very wide into straight, made good progress in the run home without threatening.
Out with rest, unable to slot in, trapped wide, 2 lengths or so back, no cover for the majority of the race, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Bumped on jumping, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, no clear run early in straight, cleared 200M but only showed limited response thereafter, weakened gradually close home.

Moderately away from a wide draw, raced at rear on the outside, found rail 650M, 5 lengths back turning in, made minor progress early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened gradually thereafter, eased final 50M.
Began fairly, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 250M.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths or so back, angled out after passing 550M, peaked early in straight, weakened and eased final furlong.

Began smartly from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, 2 wide, headed near 800M, a length back turning in, weakened early in straight, eased thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.) (Lame both front legs next day.)

Raced worse than midfield away from the rail. Shifted wider just prior to cornering, straightened about 3.5L from lead before closing strongly down the outside to charge to the lead at 100m & go on to win well.

Raced in midfield along the rail early before shifting off the rail near the 900m. Eased wider passing the 500m, straightened only 2L from lead, moved up to take narrow lead at 175m before over-run in last 100m, clear of 3rd.

Crowded on jumping before shifting behind runners to the tail. Improved along rail to race third last after 400m. Stayed along the rail in straight, was held up for a run near 300m before closing strongly to steal 3rd late.

Shared lead early before being crossed & racing on the leaders back from the 1100m. Moved over the heels of the leader near 500m, moved to narrow lead at 350m, battled hard to be close until the 100m before over-run late.
Raced third, away from the rail without cover from about the 1100m. Was under a length from the lead on straightening before peaking at the furlong mark & giving a few lengths in late stages.

Was steadied & taken back to the tail. Continued last on straightening when 4.5L form the lead before doing best work in the concluding stages when passing a number of rivals when running onto midfield from the back.

Pushed forward, shared lead early before improving to lead & then crossing to rail near 1100m. Joined in the lead near the 350m before weakening out in the final furlong to be beaten 5.5L in midfield.

Got back after the start to race worse than midfield before being relegated to third last near 900m. Raced second last passing the 700m, was just under 5L from the lead at the 400m before failing to run on in the straight.
Had a soft run in midfield along the rail. Was only 1.5L form the lead entering final section before finding little passing the 250m mark & weakening poorly in the concluding stages.

Raced in midfield away from the rail before improving after the 1000m mark to race 1,1. Eased wider passing 550m mark, was only 1.5L from the lead at the 400m but found little passing the 300m & weakened poorly late.

Didn't begin fast but improved along the rail to race in midfield. Moved away from the rail passing the 550m, was under 3L from the lead entering final section but found little near the 300m & weakened poorly in last furlong.

Had no early speed & raced three wide without cover near the tail of the field throughout. Continued back & wide around the bend, was last & 5.5L from the lead at 400m but found nothing & weakened to be long second last.

Got good position in midfield away from the rail. Was forced into the three wide line passing the 850m & was the left wide & without cover around bend. Forced very wide passing the 500m before weakening badly in the straight.

Out with rest, sent forward to race prominently on the inside, took the lead near 950M, led by 3/4L turning in, hard ridden from 300M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out 650M, 4 wide turning in, hard ridden from 300M, finished off strongly to take 2nd, always held.
Taken back from gate 13, raced behind midfield on the outside, 4 to 5 lengths back, very wide into straight, made very good progress in the run home to take a place, nearest on line.
Average to begin, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no daylight early in straight, cleared 250M, closed off well to make frame without threatening. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from gate 9, raced at rear on the inside, slightly improved along the rail on turn, unable to obtain clear run early in straight, made some headway thereafter.
Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to take the early lead, headed near 950M, 2nd in the middle stages, 2 wide, kept on well early in straight, peaked 200M, ran on evenly to the line.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide at rear, travelled keenly in the early and middle stages, 4-1/2L turning in, no clear run early in straight, cleared 200M, made reasonable progress thereafter.
Moderately away from gate 1, sat 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, wider from 550M, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Began well from a wide draw, raced 2 wide better than midfield, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong. (Lame right front leg next day morning.)
Commenced well from gate 12, raced 3 wide with no cover, a length or so back, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 6 lengths or so back turning in, very wide into straight, made no impression the run home.
Slightly slow out, raced behind midfield on the inside, angled out after passing 550M, no clear run early in straight, failed to make any progress thereafter.
Commenced well, raced in midfield on the outside, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.

Drifted back after the start & raced second last away from the rail. Continued rearward on straightening when 6.5L from the lead before finishing very strongly down the outside to charge to the lead at the 75m & win well.
Raced midfield away from the rail. Eased wider just before straightening, dashed up to take the lead passing the 200m mark before over-run by strong closing winner in last 75m.
Raced in midfield away from the rail. Eased three wide passing the 600m mark, moved up to share lead fleetingly near the 200m before over-run by first two in last 150m, battled well to hold third.

Steadied after the start & taken back to last. Was a clear last and just under 8L from the lead on straightening before shifting out to be the widest runner & making good late ground from a long way back to finish 4th.
Raced just worse than midfield away from the rail. Was 5.5L from the lead entering last section & made up a few late lengths when running onto midfield.

Raced in midfield along the rail for the majority. Moved off the rail just prior to straightening, didn't have much room passing the 300m mark before getting full running approaching the 200m & finishing off ok late.
Pushed forward to lead. Travelled well approaching the corner before being joined & headed passing the 200m mark & then weakening pretty moderately to midfield late.

Slow to begin & was then crowded before having to be used to get position third last along rail. Continued rearward & was 6.5L from lead on straightening before passing a few tiring rivals but making no headway into margin.
Raced in midfield along the rail. Moved off the rail sharply on straightening, bumped rival before peaking on effort at the 250m & weakening poorly in late stages.
Had a nice run on the leaders back. Was niggled along passing the 600m before doing nothing in the straight & weakening poorly to be beaten over 10L.
Pushed forward to race outside the leader. Came under hard riding passing the 600m before weakening poorly in the final 250m to be beaten over 11L.
Was slow away, losing about 3L before improving position to race worse than midfield along the rail in the middle stages. Did nothing in the straight & weakened badly to be long third last.
Had a nice run 1,1 for the majority. Bumped on straightening when only 3L from the lead before emptying passing the 300m & weakening poorly thereafter to be long second last.

Was trapped racing three deep without cover when just forward of midfield throughout. Was only about 2L from the lead on straightening but did nothing in the straight & weakened very poorly to be a long last.
Jumped okay, sat better than midfield, traveled smoothly, made some progress in the Straight, closed off nicely.
Settled midfield, responded well under pressure, finished off strongly.
Chased leader 2 wide, kept on well to hold 3rd.
Jumped awkwardly, sat rear, showed some dash over the final 100M but just not quick enough.
Sat towards rear, angled out making the turn, peaked inside 100M, closed off okay (See Incident Report).
Ridden along to lead, raced a bit keenly in the early stages, weakened and faded inside 300M.
Pushed forward, led early before racing outside the leader from the 1100m. Moved up to share lead again at 150m mark & was just too strong for immediate challengers in the final stages.

Drifted back & raced rearward throughout. Moved into the four wide line but with cover near the 800m, was the widest on straightening when 4L from behind before closing strongly to charge to second in final few strides.
Showed speed after the start to lead. Joined at the 150m by the winner, tried hard but couldn't match rival in final stages but did well to be beaten under a length into third.
Raced in midfield between runners. Obtained clear running on straightening when about 3L from the lead before making continual steady ground all the way to the line to be beaten just over 1L.
Had a nice run 1,1 for the majority. Eased into clear running passing the 550m, was only about a length behind entering final section before peaking at the 100m and just tiring a length or so late.

Raced in midfield along the rail. Moved away from the inside passing the 550m, was only 2L from the lead entering final section before being unable to go with rivals in last furlong & weakening to be beaten 5L.

Was worse than midfield & wide before racing keenly & shifting wider passing the 1000m & racing 4 deep without cover thereafter. Was 3L from the lead entering final section before weakening a few lengths after wide passage.

Was wide in midfield before improving positon after the 1100m but was then left three wide without cover from about the 900m. Hung outwards around the bend before peaking at 250m & weakening a few lengths thereafter.

Was steadied & taken back towards the tail. Shifted wider but with cover around the first bend, was the widest on straightening when still about 5.5L from lead before making no headway into that margin & never threatening.

Was steadied & shifted back to race rearward. Was last on straightening when 5.5L from the lead before effectively maintaining that deficit all the way to the line when only passing a few tiring rivals.

Began only moderately before being ridden along to improve position after start when settling in midfield between runners. Drifted further back & was relegated to third last near the 800m before doing nothing in the straight.

Shifted across behind runners to find the rail after start before being niggled to hold position third last after the 1100m. Stayed along the rail on straightening when just under 4L behind but did nothing in the straight.

Pushed forward before shifting down to the rail & getting a nice run on the leaders back thereafter. Was under 2L from the lead on straightening but did nothing in the final section, weakening to be second last.

Raced three deep with cover in midfield in the early stages before drifting slightly further back around bend. Was under pressure before straightening, began yielding ground from the 500m before weakening out to long last.
Began awkwardly, taken back to race behind midfield on the outside, checked near 1000M, a bit closer on turn, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to score.

Jumped well, raced 2 wide in midfield early, 3 wide from 1400M, moved a bit closer after passing 1100M, 3 wide turning in, hit the front 250M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 100M.
Made contact shortly after start, raced better than midfield on the inside, dropped to midfield halfway, saved ground throughout, closed off well to take a place without threatening the first two.
Jumped with them, raced in midfield on the outside, moved closer after passing 850M, 4 wide turning in, kept on well early in straight, no extra final 150M.

Moderately away, raced 3 wide in midfield early, moved closer after entering the back straight, took the lead approaching 1000M, headed 850M, 2nd on turn, retook the lead 500M, peaked and headed 250M, ran on evenly thereafter.

Out with rest, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, headed approaching 1000M, positioned a length behind the leader on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Made contact shortly after start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 wide from 600M, peaked early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Made contact shortly after start, raced 2 wide behind midfield in the early stages, 3 wide and get a bit closer after passing 1000M, wider turning in, made no impression in straight.
Commenced well, positioned on rail in midfield early, dropped towards rear after passing 1200M, 2 wide from 750M, wider 500M, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Away with them, sent forward to race prominently on the inside, allowed rival to cross 1350M, dropped to midfield 900M, 2 wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Began fairly from gate 1, showed no early speed, raced at tail, 9 lengths back in the middle stages, 7 lengths back turning in, weakened early in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced towards rear on the inside, commenced move 800M, very wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Began well from a wide draw, tracked leaders on the outside, moved closer after passing 1200M, took the lead 850M, peaked and headed 500M, eased early in straight.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide at rear, peaked 700M, weakened thereafter, eased final 500M, unacceptable performance.
Broke with the field, settled midfield 2 wide, and closed off strongly to score.
Settled in a box seat position, angled out in the Straight, hit the front at 200M but got ran down.
Broke well but was steadied from a wide barrier to sit at the rear, stayed on well, best stride at the post.
Caught 3 wide no cover early, improved to sit outside the lead, weakened inside 200M. (See Incident Report)
Broke nicely and tracked leader, soon headed and sat behind the speed, only one pace when asked.
Sat last on the rail, made minor progress late.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, nothing in the Straight.
Settled worse than midfield on the rail, never a threat.
Jumped nicely and led, under pressure at 400M, soon weakened and faded.

Broke well and gradually restrained to one back position off the rail, shifted some 2L back to 3rd inside the 1300 metres, commenced move 3-wide around home bend and hit the front over 300 metres out, won readily.

Settled in rear of the small field after moderate start, trailed the field and inconvenienced over 900 metres out, switched 3-wide rounding home bend and wider in last into straight, finished off the race well.

Settled within 3L of pace in 4th on the rail, in similar position but became 5th rounding home bend, did not much room behind runners early in straight until the 250 metres, ran on under pressure late to be nearest at finish.

Began well and soon took up running off the rail after first 100 metres, obtained rails run over 1300 metres out setting in a sedate pace, led until headed about 300 metres out, kept on under pressure.
Travelled some 4L off the pace in last few, commenced move to gain closer rounding home bend, fought on steadily without threatening.
Settled in rear of small field, commenced move 1000 metres out circling the field 4 wide rounding home bend, just over 1L back into home straight and soon weakened.
Prominent and wide, one back 2-wide from over 1200 metres out, amongst leaders into straight, folded up quickly inside final 200 metres.
Driven forward from draw 14, crossed to the lead 800M, continued on well under pressure on straightening, firmly held off rivals final stages.
Moved up to track leader, had every chance on straightening, tried hard to the line but was always held by winner.
Began well from draw 1, soon restrained to a midfield position, made steady headway final 250M, just missed out on 2nd place.
Restrained behind midfield, over-raced early and middle stages, held up near 350M before running on moderately to the finish.
Jumped with them, dropped back to the rear passing 1000M, 6Ls to make up 400M, closed off fastest to be beaten 2L, nearest finish.
In touch, briefly went 3rd mid-straight, peaked on its run 150M, always held by leaders towards the finish.
From draw 13 unable to slot in, caught wide no cover chasing leaders, run ended 200M, no threat thereafter.
Caught racing 3-wide towards the rear, offered limited response on straightening, never a threat.
Held up in midfield 3-wide, responded mildly early straight but run ended 200M. (Jockey : his mount was disadvantaged by being obliged to race three wide carrying top weight.).
Settled down in midfield along the 2-path, held up early straight, kept on one paced to the finish, never a winning chance.
Slow to begin then shifted across to race along the fence, at rear 6Ls off the pace, failed to go on passing 400M, never threatened.
Jumped awkwardly, raced towards the rear, failed to respond passing 400M, soon out of contention. (Roarer / Lame next day.)
Up with early pace before easing off to track leader, no extra passing 200M, weakened to last.

Began well from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, easy run in the middle stages, angled out after passing 550M, showed very good response in straight, hit the front 150M, kept on strongly to the line, easily scored.
Commenced well, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, kept on well in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide, 1-1/2L back, 3 wide turning in, kept on well in straight to take a place without threatening.

Jumped with them, sent forward to race prominently on the inside, took the lead near 750M, led by 3/4L turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the outside, still 8 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Out with rest, raced behind midfield on the outside, 6 lengths back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide towards rear, wider from 500M, 7 lengths back turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Began well from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, headed near 750M, 2nd on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 300M.
Average to begin, raced behind midfield on rail, saved ground on turn, made no progress in straight.
Began very awkwardly and made heavy contact, raced towards rear on the inside, 2 wide turning in, made no impression in straight.
Shifted in at start and made heavy contact, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, wider from 550M, failed to close off in straight.
Slowly away, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (Lame right front leg next day morning.)
Commenced well, raced in midfield on the outside, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M. (Blood in trachea.)
Jumped well from a wide draw, tracked leaders on the outside early, saddle slipped back and commenced to buck near 1000M, soon restrained and completely tailed off. (See Racing Incidents.)
Crowded start, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, there to turn, hard ridden from 300M, hit the front 200M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Began well, raced in midfield on the outside, no cover throughout, very wide into straight, closed off well to take 2nd, not quite able to challenge.
Shifted out at start and made contact, sat right behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off well to take a place, always held.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the outside, very wide turning in, made good progress early in straight, hampered near 100M, kept on well to make frame.
Clean jump, positioned 3 wide slightly better than midfield early, 2 wide from 900M, angled out 550M, made some progress in straight.
Hampered start, raced towards rear on the inside, 2 wide from 700M, wider turning in, no clear run early in straight, cleared 250M, made some progress thereafter.
Made contact at start, taken back to race 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide from 650M, very wide turning in, made some progress early in straight, no extra final 150M.
Crowded on jumping, raced at tail, 8 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn but still the last, very wide into straight, made some headway in the run home.

Shifted out at start and made contact, tracked leaders on the outside, moved a bit closer 1100M, 2nd in the middle stages, peaked 300M, weakened final 100M. (Lost left hind plate near 1200M.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Shifted in at start, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out 500M, no clear run early in straight, showed limited response thereafter.
Crowded start, raced in midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 500M, showed some response early in straight, not enough room near 200M, made no progress thereafter.
Shifted out at start and made contact, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/2L turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 200M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began only fairly, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Shifted in at start and made contact, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, found rail 900M, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M. (See Racing Incidents.)

Jumped with them, taken back to race 2 wide towards rear, commenced move 700M, took the lead 500M, kept on well in straight, just able to hold off the challenger in a ding-dong battle.
Out in line, raced 2 wide in midfield, hard ridden after passing 600M, 3 wide turning in, finished off very strongly, just beaten by a narrow margin.

Commenced well, raced prominently early, badly hampered near 2050M, raced at tail in the middle stages, moved a bit closer after passing 600M, very wide into straight, closed off well to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, sat right behind the leader from 600M, kept on same pace in straight.
Taken back from gate 7, raced towards rear of midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Out with rest, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, challenged by rivals from 550M, headed 500M, weakened early in straight.
Away with them, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, there to turn, weakened early in straight, finished last.
Jumped awkwardly, held up behind midfield early stages, shuffled back to near the rear home turn, still plenty to do 250M, stayed on strongly late, led close home.
Reserved in midfield along the fence, pushed along 500M, ran on well to lead 50M out, caught by fast finishing winner late.
Settled down midfield, switched 3-wide back straight, held up making the Home Turn before switching wide top of straight, stayed on well under top weight to go 3rd near line.
Sped to the lead taking them along at good pace, battled on well in the straight, caught 50M, edged out to 4th at the line.
Slow out, raced at the back about 6Ls off the pace, did best work final 200M, nearest finish.
Forwardly placed, tracked leader entering first turn, had every chance but was comfortably held by leaders towards the finish.
Caught 3-wide early stages before moving up to race outside leader, came under pressure to hold its position early straight, out-stayed by rivals passing 150M.
Raced towards the rear, pushed along back straight, came wide home turn, kept on fairly to the line.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners in the early stages, held up at rear, struggled to pick up pace when driven home turn, never a threat to leaders.
Positioned ahead of midfield early stages, niggled along passing 600M but lacked a finishing effort. Never threatened.
Up with early pace, tracked leaders from 1400M, swung wide into straight, failed to go on. (Blood in trachea / Roarer.)
Settled in a 3-wide position midfield, raced wide and without cover for the majority of the event, pushed along to join leaders 600M, soon came up empty turning home.
Jumped okay, ridden along to lead 2 wide, traveled smoothly, made minor progress inside 150M, kept on well to win (See Incident Report).
Sat worse than midfield on the rail, could not obtain clear running in the early Straight until 100M, just missed.
Settled better than midfield 3 wide, began to improve and chase the leader from 900M, closed off nicely.
Sat midfield 3 wide, traveled comfortably throughout, response okay when asked inside 100M but just not quick enough.
Settled behind midfield 3 wide, improved from 400M, showed some dash at the concluding stages, stayed on well.
Sat in front of midfield on the rail, one pace when asked.
Settled behind midfield 2 wide, switched out making the Home Turn, ran on evenly.
Jumped only fairly, sat in front of midfield, slightly weakened at 750M, no clear run at the Straight, could not be fully tested.
Sat handy, ridden hard in the early and middle stages, raced tight inside 150M, could not be ridden out to the finish (See Incident Report).
Settled midfield on the rail, crowded over the concluding 150M, could not be ridden out to the finish.
Sat rear, limited response under pressure, no impression.
Sat towards rear, never seen with a chance.

Settled third last after start. Moved three wide near 600m bend, was four wide & improving from the 500m, was widest on straightening before sprinting quickly to charge to lead at 150m & win impressively (blood in trachea).

Had a nice run in midfield on the rail. Moved away from the rail when improving between runners at the 400m, passed quickly by winner at the 175m before improving to second soon after & holding that placing by over a length.
Raced in midfield along the rail. Stayed along the rail on straightening before working home steadily to move to well beaten third in final 50m.

Pushed forward from gate 10, disputed lead early before improving to outright lead near the 1000m & then crossing to the rail near the 700m. Battled hard until passed quickly by winner at 150m before caught for third late.

Steadied & taken back to last. Was a clear last on cornering when still a fair way off the lead before shifting outwards at the 175m and making some late ground to finish in a well beaten midfield placing.

Showed speed to dispute the lead early before being headed near the 1000m & then eventually crossed near the 700m & racing on the leaders back thereafter. Just battled away until giving a few lengths in final 100m.

Steadied & taken back to race near the tail. Shifted wider on the track on straightening when still rearward before passing a couple of tiring rivals when running onto well beaten midfield finish out wider on the track.

Raced prominently after the start before steadied at the 1000m & racing third before being crossed & racing 1,1 from about 650m. Was pushed wider on straightening but didn't do much in the straight, giving ground to midfield.

Was trapped racing wide without cover around first bend before improving position to get outside the leader from 650m. Was crowded near the 150m when still close to lead before not tested late (rider questioned see report).

Raced in midfield between runners throughout. Lost a length around 500m bend before entering last section 4.5L from lead. Had no clear galloping room in last 100m but was a long well off the lead at that stage (roarer again).
Was trapped racing wide in midfield but had cover early before being left without cover form about the 650m. Was beaten before straightening & weakened to be a long second last.

Got back to worse than midfield before being relegated to third last near 750m when along rail. Stayed close to the inside on straightening when 6L behind before weakening poorly in the straight, long last (blood in trachea).
Began only fairly, raced behind midfield on the inside, angled out 450M, raced tight near 300M, not enough room until 200M, finished off very strongly to score.
Clean jump, raced 2 wide in midfield, hard ridden from 500M, very wide into straight, raced tight early in straight, made good progress thereafter to take 2nd.

Slightly slow out and crowded, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear run early in straight, cleared 100M, finished off well to take a place without threatening.
Jumped with them, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the first few final 50M.
Jumped awkwardly, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 wide from 450M, made good progress early in straight, bumped 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Began fairly, raced in midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 450M, no clear run early in straight, cleared 100M, made some progress thereafter.
Began well from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed some response early in straight, raced tight and bumped near 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 8 lengths back on turn, made some progress thereafter.
Away with them, raced 2 wide towards rear, 7 lengths back turning in, very wide into straight, made minor progress in straight.
Bumped start, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Shifted in at start and made contact, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, wider turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Broke nicely, settled in front of midfield, ran on nicely to the line to score.
Settled midfield on the rail, closed off okay along the rail, had every chance.
Broke well and travelled strongly, led a long way rounding the Home Turn, weakened inside 50M, just held 3rd. (See Incident Report)
Badly crowded at the start, settled worse than midfield along the rail, stayed on well.
Sat last, had some trouble obtaining clear running in the Straight, closed off nicely, best stride late.
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide, made some progress in the Straight.
Raced just behind the pace, under pressure at 450M, limited response.
Badly crowded at the start, settled towards the rear, ran on fairly.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, made no impression. (See Incident Report)
Caught 3 wide midfield with cover, weakened in the Straight.
Settled at the rear, never in contention.
Caught wide in front of midfield 3 wide no cover, faded in the Straight. (Performance unacceptable, must trial)
Broke well, gradually settled in midfield, swung wide into straight, fought on well down the centre to just get up on line.
Settled in midfield, held up on home turn, fought on under pressure on the rail to hit the front momentarily just short of the line.
Ridden along after crowded at start, carried backward passing 500 metres, renewed effort 4-wide rounding home bend, hit the front over 200 metres out only to be collared close to finish.
Lost ground at start from a wide draw and settled well behind, trailed the field to straight swinging wide for a run, ran on well under pressure to narrowly placings.
Travelled wide in last few, commenced move and went widest into straight, ran on under strong pressure.
Moderate start, recovered to join last few in 9th, wide into straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Led early, shifted one back behind leaders on rail into back straight, did not find much room early in home straight and steadied 200 metres out, kept on well to the line.
Jumped well, soon dropped to last few along the rail, hard ridden into straight, only ran past well-beaten horses closing stages.
Pressed forward from a poor draw to join the leaders, hit the front briefly on straightening, folded up quickly inside final 150 metres. (Roarer)
Ridden positively to be up with the pace and mainly one-out-one-back, badly buffeted on straightening and did not find much room afterwards.
Improved steadily from a poor draw to lead narrowly on rail about 800 metres out, headed into home straight and folded up quickly inside final 150 metres.
Crowded at start travelling mainly 3-wide without cover in midfield, commenced move out wide at about 700 metres reaching within 1L of pace turning for home, soon found nothing.
Soon crossed to the lead, led steadily early stages before quickening up 700M, continued on well in the straight building up an unassailable lead 200M, won comfortably.
Restrained to a position behind midfield 5Ls off the pace, swung wide home turn, stayed on well to claim clear 2nd, not reach winner.
Jumped only fairly, settled behind midfield along the inside, ran on mildly passing 300M, got up for 3rd late but never a threat to the runaway winner.
Obtained a midfield spot, saved ground along the fence throughout, kept on steadily final 300M but lacked a strong finishing effort.
Chased leaders in a 3-wide position without cover, pushed along 550M but lacked the needed response, fought on one paced to the line.
Held up in mid-division, 4Ls to make up 400M, responded mildly when asked, never going the pace to challenge.
Chased leaders on inside, went 2nd from top of the straight, not able to challenge leader, swamped by rivals final 150M.
Positioned ahead of midfield, never far off the pace 3Ls behind leader, responded fairly under top weight final 250M, never a threat.
Tracked leader, came under pressure 400M, hung early straight, made no progress and came up empty 200M, faded towards the line. (Jockey could offer no explanation for the disappointing performance.)
From wide draw shifted across behind runners, raced as the back-marker 8Ls off the pace, failed to close off in the straight.

From wide draw taken back to near the rear, bustled along 600M but failed to respond to riding, never involved. (Jockey : was asked to ride in a conservative manner to avoid racing wide in anticipation of genuine early pace.)
Jumped awkwardly and lost ground, settled towards the rear, couldn't go on passing 400M, made no impact on his first visit to Happy Valley.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, 2 wide from 500M, showed very good response in straight, hit the front 150M, kept on strongly to the line.
Shifted in at start, raced 2 wide in midfield, same position on turn, finished off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made good progress in straight to take a place, nearest on line.
Began fairly from the widest draw, raced at rear on the outside, 8 lengths or so back on turn, finished off strongly to make frame, nearest finish.
Average to begin, positioned 5 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground to turn, made minor progress in straight.
Commenced well, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, found rail 700M, travelled well on turn, took the lead 300M, peaked and headed 150M, weakened final 100M.
Clean jump, raced 2 wide in midfield, very wide turning in, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Jumped awkwardly, raced at rear on the inside, 7 lengths or so back, saved ground to turn, made no impression in straight.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Crowded start, raced at tail, 11 lengths back on turn, switched wide entering straight, kept on evenly in the run home.
Began well, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/2L in the middle stages, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began only fairly, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.

Moderately away from gate 1, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground to turn, finished off very strongly to score.
Away with them, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably in the middle stages, led by a length turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner final 100M.
Out in line, raced in midfield on the inside, angled out 500M, finished off well to take a place without threatening the first two.
Crowded start, raced at rear, 9 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame without threatening.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths or so back, angled out after passing 600M, very wide into straight, made good progress in the run home, nearest finish.
Out with rest, raced better than midfield on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, positioned slightly behind midfield on the inside, angled out after passing 500M, no clear run early in straight, ran on evenly thereafter.

Made contact shortly after start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, angled out approaching 500M, showed limited response early in straight, ran on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Shifted in at start and made contact, raced at rear on the outside, very wide turning in, passed some tired runners in straight.
Commenced well, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Began awkwardly, raced behind midfield on the outside, very wide into straight, showed limited response early in straight, kept on same pace to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began fairly, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, angled out 500M, same margin back turning in, made no impression in straight.

Crowded start, sent forward to race prominently but trapped very wide, peaked on run 500M, weakened early in straight when hard run took toll. (Lost left hind plate at the start.) (Sustained an abrasion to the left hind heel.)

Moderately away, sent forward to race prominently, 3 wide, slightly taken back after passing 900M, positioned 2 wide better than midfield on turn, angled out 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M.
Began well from a poor draw, ridden positively to obtain rails run passing the 900 metres holding 2L advantage into straight, kept on well under pressure.
Always thereabouts after beginning from a poor draw, joint 2nd into straight, unable to quicken pressure to threaten. (Tactic questioned)
Ridden positively to be up with the pace early stages, taken one back on rail rounding home bend, ran home one-paced.
Slowly away, recovered quickly to just better than midfield in 5th over 1000 metres out, about 3L off the pace in 4th into straight, made no further impression.
Soon recovered from moderate start to midfield on rail in 6th, in similar position rounding home bend, kept on same pace without threatening.
Settled in last few, saved ground turning for home, ran on steadily under pressure to be nearest at finish.
Well back to straight, ran on steadily down the centre of the track, never nearer.
Settled in last few, hampered coming out of back straight, kept on steadily without quickening.
Settled in last few, made modest headway in straight, never nearer.
Ridden along in first few, lost position just over 1000 metres out dropping behind midfield in 7th rounding home bend, found nothing in straight.
Settled at the back from the widest draw, widest runner into straight, made no impression.
Towards rear throughout and never seen with a chance.
Moderate start, improved 3-wide steadily to be joint 4th into straight, soon weakened.

Placing: TNP
Comment: Refused to jump as the start was effected and took no part in the event. (Required to perform satisfactorily at a minimum of three consecutive barrier trials.)
Sat behind midfield on the rail, traveled comfortably, switched out to 2 wide making the turn, made very good progress in the Straight, finished off well.
Settled handy 4 wide, responded nicely when asked inside 200M, kept on well to hold 2nd.
Jumped awkwardly, sat towards rear 2 wide, closed off nicely, best stride late.
Ridden along to chase the leader, ran on evenly to the line.
Slow to jump, sat rear, no clear running in the early Straight, responded well under pressure after 200M.
Jumped fairly, settled midfield 2 wide, made decent progress early in the Straight, peaked at 100M, one pace only afterwards (Substantial mucus in trachea, See Incident Report).
Sat in front of midfield 2 wide, raced keenly in the early stages, ran on okay.
Ridden hard to lead, weakened approaching 250M.
Sat midfield 2 wide, made some progress in the early Straight but one pace thereafter.
Sat better than midfield on the rail, limited response when asked, weakened and faded after 200M (Lost right hind plate, See Incident Report).
Sat towards rear, no impression.
Settled worse than midfield, one pace, never a threat.
Sat better than midfield 3 wide, slightly weakened in the early Straight and faded.
Jumped awkwardly, sat worse than midfield, went amiss after passing the winning post.

Raced 4th in the clear for the first half. Improved onto the leaders back from the 800m when the field bunched. Moved off the rail near the 750m to get around weakening leader, got clear at the 350m & dashed strongly to win.

Raced third in the clear for first half behind fast early speed. Improved to be three wide in a line of four at the front near 750m, assumed lead on straightening before being joined near 300m & fighting on well to hold 2nd.

Raced in midfield in a fast run first half. Continued in midfield galloping between runners from the 900m when field bunched. Shifted wider prior to straightening, dashed to share lead at 300m & fought well late to hold 3rd.

Raced in midfield along the rail but a long way from the lead in a fast run first half. Moved off the rail passing the 700m, was only 2L from the lead at the 400m, shifted outwards soon after & closed off well to be 4th.

Raced 5th in the clear in first half. Shifted wider to improve near 950m before being forced wider at 800m. Improved to be the widest in a line of four at the front. Peaked passing the 250m before giving a length or two late.

Badly crowded & lost ground at the start & consequently raced near the tail throughout. Stayed near the inside after straightening before passing a few runners when closing off to midfield in the final stages.

Shifted back to race just worse than midfield. Relegated to third last near 950m when field bunched, crowded away from heels near 550m & relegated to last before passing a couple of tiring rivals when running onto midfield.

Raced in midfield away from the rail but a long way from lead in fast first half. Moved three wide near 1000m to improve, pushed four wide near 900m, only 2L behind on straightening but failed to finish off in final section.

Raced in midfield away from the rail throughout. Moved into the three wide line with cover near the 1000m. Was ridden along near 600m, was just under 4L from the lead on straightening but failed to challenge in the straight.

Bumped at the start & then steadied and taken rearward. Relegated to last passing the 900m, shifted out to be the second widest on straightening when just over 4L from lead before failing to make any headway in run to line.

Steadied from the widest gate & taken back to race rearward. Moved four wide but with cover after the 1000m when field bunched. Blundered just prior to straightening, straightened 3.5L behind but weakened to be well held.

Crowded & lost ground at start before settling last. Moved three wide in back straight, commenced to improve around field from 1200m before being forced four wide near 1000m. Was very wide on cornering before weakening out.

Shared lead early before being headed at the 1600m & then crossed soon after in a fast run early section. Moved up outside leader in a line of four at the front at 750m, was headed on straightening before weakening poorly.

Ridden forward to be prominent before improving to lead at 1600m & crossing to rail near the 1400m when going way too fast early. Joined in a line of four at 750m before weakening out badly from the 700m (rider questioned).
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably in the middle stages, hard ridden approaching 300M, kept on very well to the line and scored.
Began well from gate 12, raced behind midfield on the stands' side, crowded near 750M, a bit closer in the middle stages, made good progress final 300M to take 2nd without threatening the winner.

Taken back from gate 1, raced at rear, 5 lengths or so back, a bit closer in the middle stages, 4 lengths behind the leader at 400M, made good progress after passing 250M, no extra final 50M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well from gate 13, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on the stands' side, made contact near 350M, hard ridden 300M, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, raced in midfield, 2 away from the stands' rail, 3 away from the stands' rail from 500M, made some progress after passing 300M, peaked 150M, one-paced thereafter.
Away well, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on the stands' rail, made contact 350M, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped with them, raced slightly behind midfield, nearer to the middle track, made some progress after passing 400M, peaked on run 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Clean jump, sent forward to race prominently, 2 away from the stands' rail, peaked 450M, weakened final furlong.
Out with rest, raced towards rear, 4 lengths or so back, hard ridden from 300M but only showed limited response, one-paced thereafter.
Reared as stalls opened, missed break and lost a considerable amount of ground, still 12 lengths back at 400M, passed some tired runners thereafter.
Commenced well, raced prominently on the stands' side, peaked 350M, weakened final furlong.
Jumped awkwardly, raced behind midfield on the middle track, hard ridden 350M, showed limited response, weakened final 150M.
Began fairly, raced in midfield, 3 away from the stands' rail, peaked 500M, weakened and eased final 200M.
Began only fairly, raced towards rear on the stands' side, peaked 400M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped with the field, settled worse than midfield 3 wide, angled out towards center track, closed off strongly to score, always doing enough.
Broke nicely and settled just behind the speed on the rail, switched out at 350M and ran on nicely, always held inside final 100M.
Steadied after the start from a wide barrier, settled at the rear, navigated through traffic in the Straight and stayed on well, ran strongly to the line for 3rd.
Jumped slowly and ridden along to sit worse than midfield on the rail, made decent progress along the rail, no threat to top 3.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide between horses, only one pace when asked.
Caught 3 wide no cover on pace, kept on only fairly.
Settled midfield on the rail, did not quickened in the Straight. (See Incident Report)
Tracked leader, kept on nicely until the 150M, then soon weakened.
Settled last, had difficulties finding clear run in the Straight, ran nicely despite trouble passage. (See Incident Report)
Sat just behind the leaders, limited response in the Straight.
Showed good early speed to lead, weakened inside 350M.
Settled midfield 2 wide, made no impression.
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide, never a threat.
Settled towards the rear 3 wide, under the whip at 550M, never in contention.
Crowded at start, soon recovered to forward of midfield wide without cover, commenced move on straightening and hit the front under pressure inside final 200 metres.
Jumped fairly before travelling keenly one back in 2nd on the rail, became 3rd within 2L of pace coming onto home bend, snuck closer entering the straight and fought on dourly to snatch 2nd late.
Always thereabouts, travelling keenly off the rail without cover most of the way, quickened to hold some chance early in straight but unable to sustain effort closing stages.
Attempted to make all holding about 1L advantage most of the way until overhauled inside final 200 metres.
Settled in midfield or slightly better on the rail, did not find much room early in straight, kept on steadily without quickening closing stages.
Soon dropped to one from last, made steady headway from the 1050 metres to reach rear of midfield on the rail home bend, kept on steadily under pressure without quickening.
Travelled keenly about 2L off the pace on the rail, commenced move about 500 metres out holding some chance briefly early in straight, found no extra inside final 300 metres.
Crowded at start, never better than midfield, bumped and lost position approaching the 1200 metres before travelling keenly 3-wide to straight, unable to quicken to threaten.
Lacked early pace and soon dropped well behind from a poor draw, saved ground turning in but made no impression in the straight.
Gradually taken back from a wide draw to last few, lost position at about the 1050 metres dropping to last, went wide around home bend and into straight, made no further impression.
Gradually drifted backward from the widest draw, slightly worse coming onto home bend, lost position over 800 metres out, towards the rear into straight, found nothing.
Settled in last few and never seen with a chance.
Ridden forward from moderate start to rear of midfield, yielded ground steadily under pressure from approaching the straight.
Settled just worse than midfield, improved from the 1050 metres to reach 4th just over 2L back 3-wide rounding home bend, folded up quickly shortly after straightening.
Never far off behind leaders, travelled strongly, gave instant response when niggled along 350M, led near 200M, shook clear from rivals to complete hat-trick of wins comfortably.
Showed customary speed to go forward, vied for the lead along stands' rail, took over inside 400M, kept on well enough but no match for the odds-on favourite DREAM WINNER, held on for 2nd.
In touch, driven out 350M, not pace to challenge winner, kept on evenly to secure 3rd.
In mid-division, 3Ls behind leader 400M, closed off mildly final stages, just missed 3rd.
Settled towards the rear along the stands' rail, stayed on moderately from midway for a non-threatening 5th.
Jumped awkwardly, recovered to race in midfield, kept on one paced over final 400M, never a winning hope. (Mucus).
Jumped awkwardly, held up behind midfield, 4Ls to make up 400M, stayed on without posing serious threat to leaders.
Hampered after the start, ended up racing at the back, ran on mildly passing 400M down center of track, never a winning threat.
Settled midfield, raced down the center of track, gave limited response when driven 400M, no extra 100M.
Behind midfield early stages, struggled to hold its position mid-way, never threatened thereafter.
Settled in mid-division towards the outside of the group, didn't respond when asked 400M, faded away.
Led as expected, struggled to keep up passing 350M, soon out of contention. (Jockey : travelled well in the lead but gave ground over 300M and raced in a disappointing manner.)
Not far off from leaders early stages, gave ground passing 500M, eased when no chance. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Began well from gate 1, raced in 2nd, travelled comfortably to turn, hit the front 300M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 12 lengths or so back, commenced move 500M, still 9 lengths back turning in, finished off very strongly to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide better than midfield early, found rail near 900M, saved ground on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place, always held.
Commenced well, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, kept on well in straight to make frame, always held.

Away with them, trapped wide slightly behind midfield, 2 wide from 800M, 6 lengths back turning in, took some time to balance up in straight, ran home reasonably well. Short of room late stages. (See Racing Incidents.)
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced at rear on the inside, 9 to 10 lengths back turning in, made very good progress in straight without threatening.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, there to turn, kept on same pace in straight.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out 500M, finished off evenly.
Away well, raced 3 wide behind midfield early, 2 wide from 950M, found rail 800M, 7 lengths back turning in, made little progress in straight.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 2 wide, 8 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made no impression in straight.
Jumped well from gate 11, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length on turn, peaked and headed 300M, weakened final 200M.
Bumped start, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made no progress in straight.
Jumped awkwardly, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from gate 13, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Began well, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, travelled comfortably to turn, hit the front 250M, kept on very well to the line and scored.
Clean jump, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked and headed 250M, kept on evenly to take 2nd.
Began well from a wide draw, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, 3 wide from 700M, pressed leaders from 500M, kept on well in straight to take a place without threatening.
Taken back from gate 9, raced towards rear on the inside, 5 lengths or so back turning in, angled out 450M, made good progress in straight to make frame without threatening.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, kept on same pace in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear, 8 lengths back, a bit closer on turn but still 6 lengths behind, taken wide in straight and made good progress without threatening.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, 2 wide on turn, peaked on run 300M, ran on same pace to the line.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, angled out 700M, same margin back turning in, made no impression in straight.
Average to begin, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, ran on evenly thereafter.
Jumped awkwardly and bumped, raced 2 wide towards rear, commenced move 550M, very wide turning in, made no progress in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, no clear run in straight, not able to test properly.
Taken back from gate 8, raced 3 wide towards rear, 8 lengths or so back on turn, made no impression in straight
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths back, same margin back on turn, failed to close off in straight.

Jumped awkwardly and made contact with the left side of its barrier, raced in midfield on the outside, a bit closer after passing 900M, no cover for the majority of the race, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
