Taken back from gate 13, raced at rear on the inside, angled out after passing 550M, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to score.
Slightly slow out, raced 2 to 3 wide towards rear, commenced move 550M, finished off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Average to begin, positioned 2 wide slightly better than midfield, similar position on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared 200M, closed off well to take a place.
Moderately away, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, 3/4L back on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Shifted out at start and made contact, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 50M, weakened gradually thereafter. (Bled.)
Slightly slow out and crowded, raced behind midfield on the inside, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, unable to obtain clear run until final 50M, made good progress thereafter.

Moderately away, trapped wide in midfield early, moved a bit closer after passing 1200M, raced 3 wide better than midfield in the middle stages, showed some response early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, positioned 2 wide, 3 lengths back, there to turn, unable to obtain clear run until final 100M, made some progress thereafter.

Away well, sent forward to race prominently on the inside, allowed rival to cross near 950M, sat right behind the leader on turn, no clear run in straight, weakened gradually final 150M. (Rider dropped his whip near 50M.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the outside, 5 lengths or so back, moved closer on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, made no progress in straight.
Moderately away from a wide draw, trapped 3 wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, angled out 450M, peaked early in straight, eased final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began fairly from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, 3 lengths back, saved ground throughout, no clear run early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the outside, moved closer after passing 600M, very wide into straight, peaked on run 300M, weakened thereafter.
Pushed forward to race second away from the rail. Moved up to take narrow lead passing the 350m, fought well to hold off challenger in final stages to win narrowly. First two clear of third.

Raced in midfield along the rail throughout. Stayed nearer the inside on straightening, entered last section 3.5L from lead before closing well all the way to the line but just falling short. First two clear of third.
Had a nice run third on the rail for the majority. Moved off the rail just before straightening before finishing off only steadily to hold a non-threatening third on line.

Bumped heavily at start before steadying & getting back to third last away from rail. Was the widest runner on straightening, entered last section about 7L from lead before making some late ground running onto well held 4th.

Had a nice run 1,1 for the majority. Bumped just before straightening, entered last section just under 4L from the lead and more or less maintained that margin all the way to the line when finishing off only one paced.

Crowded & lost ground at the start & got back to race worse than midfield along the rail. Stayed nearer the inside on straightening when 6L from the lead before maintaining that margin all the way to the line.
Raced in midfield between runners throughout. Was ridden along passing the 600m before doing little in the straight.
Raced in midfield, three wide with cover throughout. Eased wider passing the 500m, was over 6L from the lead on straightening & could only hold deficit all the way to the line to be no factor.

Steadied from the outside gate & taken back to race near the tail. Continued rearward, shifted outwards entering final section when 8L from the lead before failing to make any headway in the straight. Well beaten.
Bumped on jumping before mustering quickly to lead. Peaked on run and headed at the 250m before weakening out very quickly in the last furlong to be well beaten.

Steadied when wide after start & got back to race last from the 900m. Shifted wider on the track approaching the corner, was a clear last entering final section when over 9L behind before weakening further.
Was trapped racing three wide without cover just forward of midfield in early & middle stages. Began yielding ground from the 600m & was then eased out of the race in the straight (blood in trachea).
Settled midfield 2 wide, responded well when asked inside 150M, finished off nicely.
Jumped awkwardly, sat better than midfield on the rail, made some progress in the early Straight.
Sat towards rear 2 wide, traveled smoothly, showed some response over the concluding 100M but just not quick enough.
Settled towards rear on the rail, responded okay inside 100M.
Sat worse than midfield on the rail, switched out in the Straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Settled in front of midfield, one pace.
Slow to begin, sat rear on the rail, made minor progress in the Straight, ran on fairly.
Settled behind midfield 3 wide, limited response when asked.
Sat better than midfield 3 wide, raced keenly in the early stages, weakened inside 200M (Lame right front leg, See Incident Report).
Ridden hard to lead, weakened approaching 300M and faded.
Jumped awkwardly, sat rear 3 wide, never in contention (Bled from both nostrils).
Sat handy, traveled okay in the early stages, weakened inside 300M (Substantial mucus in trachea).

Had a nice run in midfield away from the rail. Shifted wider on straightening, entered last section just under 3L from lead, dashed strongly to charge to lead nearing the furlong mark before drawing away to win easily again.

Raced in midfield along the rail early before drifting back to just worse than midfield around bend. Moved off the rail on straightening, made ground, shifted back down to rail near 300m before making steady headway to 2nd.
Raced in midfield along the rail. Moved away from the inside approaching the 500m mark, shifted outwards slightly passing the 350m before closing off pretty well to close to third in final 75m.
Pushed forward to lead. Joined & passed by the winner near the 200m mark before tiring a few lengths to hold a well beaten 4th on line.
Raced in midfield away from the rail. Was 4L from the lead entering final section before finishing off only one paced in the straight to be well held in midfield.

Slow to begin before making up lost ground & rejoining the field after 200m. Was third last on straightening, shifted outwards near 350m before passing a few tiring rivals when running onto well beaten midfield finish.
Pushed forward to race outside the leader. Was still close until peaking on effort at the 175m mark & weakened out late.

Hit the front of the gates before release & consequently lost considerable ground at the start. Eventually rejoined the field passing the 950m & raced near the tail thereafter. Was never in contention but had genuine excuse.
Drifted back from widest gate & positioned with only three runners behind in the early & middle stages. Was just under 6L from the lead on straightening but weakened a few lengths & was well beaten.

Was slow to begin, lost ground and consequently raced rearward throughout. Was last entering final section when about 9L from the lead before failing to make any ground & finishing a well beaten third last.
Had a nice run 1,1, throughout. Was only 2L from the lead entering final section, was still close at the 300m mark before being eased out of race thereafter (bled).
Had a nice run along the rail just behind the leading pair. Was ridden along from the 500m before weakening out badly in the final 350m to be a very long last (bled).
Slightly slow out, raced behind midfield on the inside, a bit closer in the middle stages, showed very good response in straight, hit the front 200M, ran on strongly to the line, easily scored.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 2 wide from 900M, angled out approaching 500M, finished off strongly to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide better than midfield, angle out after passing 500M, closed off well to take a place without threatening. (Lame left front leg next day morning.)
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, 3 wide from 900M, very wide into straight, finished off well to make frame without threatening.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the outside, very wide into straight, made good progress in the run home without threatening.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced in midfield on the outside, 3 lengths or so back, wider turning in, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Began fairly from gate 10, raced in 3rd, 3 wide with no cover throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Average to begin, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, there to turn, kept on well early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Quickly into stride, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/2L turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 200M, weakened final 150M.
Taken back to race at rear on the inside early, a bit closer after passing 1000M, saved ground throughout, showed limited response early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield early, 3 wide from 900M, 5 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Jumped awkwardly, raced 2 wide towards rear, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced in midfield on rail early, moved a bit closer after passing 1200M, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Broke well and ridden along to lead, travelled smoothly throughout, kicked clear at the top of the Straight and kept on well to score. (See Incident Report)
Settled midfield on the rail, under pressure at 400M, took some time to respond, closed off strongly inside final 200M to grab 2nd.
Sat outside the lead, kept on nicely for 3rd.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, ran on fairly to grab 4th. (Substantial Blood in Trachea)
Got hampered at the start, settled last, stayed on nicely.
Steadied after the start from the outside barrier and sat towards the rear, angled out in the Straight and made up some ground.
Settled midfield 2 wide, made some late progress after the 150M.
Settled worse than midfield on the rail, made no impression.
Sat behind the speed, limited response in the Straight.
Settled near the rear, never in contention.
Settled in a prominent position 2 wide, nothing in the Straight. (See Incident Report)
Caught 3 wide no cover throughout, weakened in the Straight.
Ridden along wide in first few after moderate start, gained 2nd 2-wide over 1100 metres out, came under pressure to challenge upon straightening and gained upper hand over 70 metres out.
Ridden positively from a poor draw, obtained rails run in front over 1250 metres out, led until narrowly headed over 70 metres out.

Ridden forward after moderate start, restrained just off the pace for cover 1400 metres out and mainly 2L back in 3rd rounding home bend, fought on under pressure to hold every chance inside final 200 metres.
Always thereabouts, some 3L back in 4th from 1100 metres, fought on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Settled better than midfield in joint 5th, failed to quicken to challenge in straight.
Settled in midfield on the rail, angled out for a run entering straight, not much room behind runners until the 200 metres, did best work late.
Settled 2-wide better than midfield in joint 5th, kept on same pace without quickening in straight.
Settled in last few, went widest into straight, finished off the race well inside final 200 metres.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground settling in last few on rail, inconvenienced and lost position 1050 metres out, saved ground turning in, kept on steadily without quickening.
Taken back to last from a poor draw, trailed the field into straight, fought on under pressure past well-beaten horses inside final 250 metres.
Travelled wide in midfield after beginning from a wide draw, wide into straight, unable to quicken under pressure.
Taken back to last few and wide without cover at times while racing keenly, wide into straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Settled towards rear, wide around home bend and wider into straight, soon faded.
Settled towards rear, faded under pressure in straight.
Soon led, took them along at a pace slower than standard, continued on well passing 400M, held off pursuing rivals comfortably over final stages.
From draw 1 moved up to track leaders, angled out 450M to challenge, closed off well to go 2nd near 100M but couldn't quite get to the winner.
Pressed forward to be racing outside the lead, tried hard on straightening but not going the pace to challenge leader, kept on steadily to hold 3rd.
Taken back from wide draw, waited with near the rear, brought wide to challenge early straight, closed off well under top weight, just missed 3rd.
Jumped only fairly, recovered to a midfield position along the inside, 5th at 400M, kept on steadily towards the line, always held by leaders.
Not hurried after the start, dropped back to race at the rear, finished off moderately final 400M, not reach leaders.
Held up 3-wide in midfield, gave limited response when driven out top of straight. No threat to leaders. (Jockey : his mount did not appreciate the "Good To Yielding" track conditions.)
Jumped fast, soon restrained to race in midfield 4Ls back, ran on one paced in the straight, never a winning threat.
Slow to begin, settled towards the rear racing along the fence, 6Ls to make up 400M but lacked a finishing response, ran past beaten horses only.
Pushed along after the start to go forward, steadied 1300M then continued to race keenly through the early and middle stages, left without a finishing effort in the straight, never dangerous.

Jumped only fairly, raced keenly behind midfield, was steadied away from the heels of a rival for some distance near 800M, 3-wide making the turn for home, unable to finish the race off as well as expected.
Raced keenly towards the rear in early stages, caught 4-wide no cover from 1000M, moved closer to midfield making home turn, came up empty passing 350M.
Chased leaders, came under pressure 550M, soon weakened on straightening.
Caught wide no cover from draw 14, crept closer to leaders passing 1000M, no extra from 300M, weakened to last.

Moderately away, positioned 5 lengths behind the leader on rail, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off very strongly to score.

Began awkwardly and made contact, positioned 3Ls behind the leader on rail, angled out and improved after passing 800M, shared the lead from 600M, 3 wide on turn, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner close home.
Bumped start, raced at tail, 8 to 9 lengths back, saved ground throughout, still 7 lengths or so back turning in, finished off well to take a place. (Dead-Heat 3rd.)
Jumped awkwardly and crowded, raced towards rear on the inside, 6 lengths or so back turning in, made good progress in straight to take a place. (Dead-Heat 3rd.)
From draw 1 moved forward to track leaders along the fence, 4th at 400M, kept on evenly under top weight, always held by leaders.
Clean jump, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, shared lead on turn, headed 300M, kept on evenly to 150M, weakened gradually thereafter. (Blood in trachea.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, raced behind midfield on the outside, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.

Away well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths or so back, hampered and carried wider near 800M, same margin back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, shared the lead with rivals from 600M, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened 250M, eased final 150M.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced towards rear on the outside, 7 lengths back, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, dropped to midfield after passing 600M, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight, eased final furlong. (Blood in trachea.)
Travelled strongly behind leader, hit lead 150M, drew clear to win comfortably.
Moved up to lead, pressed by eventual winner early straight, caught near 150M, faded late but held on for 2nd at the line.
Jumped fairly, settled in 4th a bit further back than anticipated, closed off steadily on straightening, just missed 2nd.
Jumped only fairly, settled 5th of 6, 4-5Ls to make up 400M, stayed on without serious threat to leaders.
Jumped on terms, restrained to race at the rear, struggled to keep up with rivals home turn, never involved.
Driven forward to chase leader, came under pressure 500M, out of contention early straight.
Jumped okay, ridden along to lead, made some progress inside 200M, kept on well to win.
Jumped awkwardly, settled midfield 2 wide, traveled comfortably, response well when asked to grab 2nd.
Chased the lead throughout, one pace to the finish.
Sat worse than midfield 2 wide, angled out making the Home Turn, improved nicely in the Straight, closed off okay.
Slow to begin, was crowded in the Straight, ran on evenly to the finish.
Sat handy, traveled okay, slightly weakened over the final 75M (See Incident Report).
Settled towards rear 2 wide, responded nicely when asked but just not quick enough.
Settled better than midfield 2 wide, no clear running in the Straight until 150M, weakened slightly thereafter.
Sat rear on the rail, in the middle stages raced keenly, ran on only fairly.
Jumped okay, sat towards rear 3 wide, limited response under pressure in the Straight (Roarer).
Settled in front of midfield, commenced to give ground at 600M, never a factor (Unacceptable performance, A series of consecutive barrier trials).

Placing: FE
Comment: Settled midfield on the rail, went amiss and dislodged its rider at 200M (See Incident Report).
Had a nice run 1,1 for the majority. Was only a length or so from the lead on straightening before dashing to the lead near the 200m mark before drawing away to win easily.

Steadied & taken rearward early. Commenced a mid-race move from the 900m, sweeping around the field to take narrow lead near 600m. Continued to hold narrow lead until joined by the winner at the 200m, held well beaten 2nd.

Raced in midfield along the rail in early & middle stages. Moved off the rail near the 700m, improved between runners near the 400m when about 5L from the lead before closing late to steal well beaten third in final stride.
Pushed forward to lead. Headed by the runner-up near the 600m, battled well to still be close to the lead at the 200m before over-run in concluding stages.

Raced second away from the rail in the early & middle stages. Relegated to third near the 600m, was a couple of lengths from the lead on straightening before being unable to finish as strongly as others, weakening to fifth.

Raced in midfield off the rail early before moving into the three wide line without cover from 1100m. Moved closer to the lead near the 800m when field bunched, unable to close off strongly in straight & was held in midfield.
Steadied & taken back towards the rear. Made some progress along the rail passing the 500m before just battling away in the straight to be well beaten in midfield.
Raced worse than midfield away from the rail. Was shuffled back to second last from the 600m, was well back on straightening and was unable to make any meaningful headway in the straight.

Drifted back to the tail after first section. Came under hard riding near the 550m when a clear last, was 8L from the lead entering final section & was unable to improve, beating only two tiring rivals home.

Raced in midfield along the rail early before coming off the rail & racing between runners from the 1200m. Hung outwards at the 550m bend & lost ground, relegated to last on straightening & weakened to be beaten a big margin.
Had a nice run in third along the rail for the majority. Began losing ground along the inside from about the 550m before weakening badly to be a long last.

Made contact at start, raced behind midfield on the outside, 6 lengths or so back, commenced move after passing 650M, took the lead 500M, led by 3/4L turning in, kept on very well in straight, won by 2-1/4L.

Slightly slow out and crowded, raced towards rear on the inside, 7 lengths or so back, angled out 600M, 4-1/2L back turning in, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, made very good progress in the run home to take a place without threatening.
Out with rest, raced in midfield on rail, 2 wide from 500M, wider turning in, made some progress in straight to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Bumped start, positioned 1 out 1 back, angled out 500M, showed limited response early in straight, ran on evenly to 50M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began smartly from gate 11, challenged by rival after entering the back straight, peaked and headed 500M, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened final 100M.

Made contact at start, raced behind midfield on the inside, angled out 550M, 4 lengths or so back turning in, showed limited response early in straight, blocked approaching 200M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Slightly slow out, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made minor progress early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened thereafter.

Bumped start, trapped 3 wide in midfield early, moved a bit closer after passing 1200M, found a 2 wide spot near 1000M, commenced move 600M, peaked on turn, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)

Began fairly and crowded, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out 600M, inconvenienced and dropped towards rear 550M, 5Ls back turning in, very wide into straight, failed to make any progress in the run home. (See Racing Incidents.)

Bumped start, raced better than midfield on the outside early, moved closer after passing 1250M, raced in 2nd in the middle stages, peaked on turn, inconvenienced early in straight, weakened and eased final furlong.
Broke very well and hard ridden to cross into a 2 wide position outside the leader, responded well in the Straight and battled gamely to the line and won.
Jumped nicely and settled in front of midfield on the rail, ran on strongly, had every chance.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, closed off nicely for 3rd.
Showed good early speed to assume the lead, kept on well until weakened slightly inside 50M.
Sat close to the pace, made the turn awkwardly, quickened okay, a bit one pace late.
Settled just behind the leaders, made a nice run along the rail at the top of the Straight but failed to run on.
Jumped with the field, settled worse than midfield on the rail, made decent progress inside 150M.
Settled midfield 2 wide, made no impression. (See Incident Report)
Settled towards the rear 2 wide, nothing in the Straight.
Settled midfield on the rail, under pressure at 450M and soon weakened.
At rear and never in contention.
Settled near the rear on the rail, never a threat.

Ridden forward to share early pace after moderate start, gained over half a length advantage on rail turning into back straight, kicked some 1L clear on straightening, just held off runner-up's strong late challenge.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground and taken back from 3-wide to share last spot, circled the field around home bend, worked home well down the centre of the track but the post came too soon.
Jumped fairly settling 3-wide in midfield, made steady headway inside 800 metres to reach 2L 4th 600 metres out and further closer into straight, only produced moderate progress without threatening.
Jumped well settling some 3L back in 5th on rail, dropped slightly further back briefly at the Rock, saved ground turning for home but unable to quicken under pressure.
Settled worse than midfield from a wide draw, tight behind runners upon straightening and switched out for a run 200 metres out, produced good late impression.
With leaders early 3-wide most of the way, came to dispute lead rounding home bend, unable to sustain effort inside final 150 metres after a tough journey.
Travelled wide without cover in midfield, commenced move inside 500 metres rounding home bend, one-paced in straight.

Ridden forward to share early pace, settled outside leader into back straight dropping to 1L 3rd home bend, not much room and unable to quicken under pressure early in straight, soon weakened. (Blood in trachea)
Travelled keenly and never better than midfield, held up dropping to last few into straight, produced good late impression inside final 150 metres.
Midfield briefly before settling towards rear on the rail, made no impression thereafter. (Blood in trachea)
Slow out and taken back, trailed the field most of way, never seen with a chance.
Jumped best before settling 2L back in 4th, gave ground steadily from 600 metres out.
Reserved in midfield 5Ls off the pace, swung wide into straight, dashed strongly final 200M under top weight, got up just in time.
From wide draw soon moved up to the lead, continued on well from 400M, caught by the odds-on favourite last stride.
Settled in 4th, always in touch, ran on well form 300M, nearest finish.
Jumped well, chased leader along the 2-path, battled on evenly to the line.
Chased leader, had every chance top of straight but couldn't get closer to leader, run ended 100M, lost several places late.
From wide draw slotted into a 2-wide spot ahead of mid-division, ran on moderately in the straight but never a winning chance.
Settled ahead of mid-division, kept on same pace final 300M, always held by leaders.
Fractious in the barriers, jumped awkwardly and lost ground, ended up in detached last over 10Ls off the pace, made some progress on straightening but not reached leaders.
Held up behind midfield 7Ls off the pace, pushed along near 400M but lacked a finishing response. Never able to challenge.
Slow to begin and then from a wide barrier was shifted across behind runners early stages, 3rd from last turning home, failed to make progress when driven out.
Slow to begin and then was crowded for room after the start, settled midfield, couldn't go on final 400M, never involved.
Dropped back to near the rear, 10Ls off the pace 400M, came up empty.

Shifted out at start and bumped, raced better than midfield on the inside, 2 lengths or so back, 2 wide from 600M, showed very good response in straight, hit the front 100M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Commenced well from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, 3-1/2L back, angled out 500M, finished off strongly to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Crowded on jumping, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the first two final 100M.
Crowded start, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, found rail 700M, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Began well, sent forward to race prominently on the outside, a length back on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 9, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground to turn, made minor progress in straight.
Moderately away from the widest draw, raced behind midfield on the outside, 7 lengths back turning in, made no impression in straight.
Average to begin, raced in midfield on the outside, very wide into straight, showed limited response early in straight, eased final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began only fairly, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made no progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 10 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped awkwardly, raced at rear on the outside, 8 lengths or so back on turn, failed to close off in straight.

Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length turning in, kept on very well in straight, easily scored.
Crowded start, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Bumped shortly after start, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, same position on turn, kept on same pace in straight.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced towards rear on the inside, 2 wide on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Bumped start, raced in midfield on the outside, 4 lengths or so back turning in, finished off evenly.
Crowded start, raced at tail, 7 lengths or so back, hampered near 450M, very wide into straight, made some headway in the run home.
Crowded start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Began well from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact at start, raced towards rear on the outside, 6 lengths back turning in, hampered near 450M, made no progress in straight.
Jumped with them, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made no impression in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, raced better than midfield on the outside, stumbled near 850M, no cover throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Made contact at start, raced 3 wide behind midfield early, 2 wide from 850M, angled out 450M, failed to close off in straight.
Settled in 3rd within striking distance, baulked on rail early in straight, obtained clear run 4-wide over 150 metres out, responded well to snatch victory near the line.
Chased outside race leader most of the way, amongst leaders upon straightening, fought on well only to be swamped close to home.
Settled in 5th over 4L off the pace, came to challenge early in straight holding every chance over 250 metres out, swamped close to home.
Settled in 4th some 3L back, pulled closer rounding home bend, quickened to hold every chance over 250 metres out, unable to sustain effort close to home.
Broke well to lead obtaining rails run shortly after, led until headed 300 metres out.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, ridden at the back and given reminder 700 metres out, never a danger.
Chased the leader and took the lead after 900M on the rail, traveled strongly, made good progress in the Straight, kept on well to win.
Sat rear 2 wide, no clear running in the early Straight, showed some dash over the final 75M to grab 2nd.
Jumped only fairly, settled behind midfield 2 wide, switched out making the Home Turn, made some progress over the final 50M, closed off okay.
Jumped only fairly, sat in front of midfield on the rail, ran on evenly to the finish.
Sat midfield 2 wide, traveled okay, one pace in the Straight.
Settled midfield 3 wide, angled out and improved making the Home Turn, made minor progress when asked but weakened after 100M.
Sat rear 3 wide, ran on fairly to the line.
Settled behind midfield 3 wide, weakened inside 300M, made no impression (Performance unacceptable, Barrier trial, See Incident Report).
Sat better than midfield 2 wide, no clear running until 250M, limited response when asked.
Settled in front of midfield 3 wide, weakened over the concluding stages (See Incident Report).
Settled towards rear, traveled only fairly, never a factor.
Sat handy, raced wide throughout, weakened approaching 300M, never a threat.
Ridden hard to lead until 950M, weakened and faded inside 400M (Performance unacceptable, Barrier trial).
Settled worse than midfield 3 wide, switched out to the center of the track, nothing when asked (Performance unacceptable, Barrier trial).

Ridden with the whip after start to improve but was caught racing three wide no cover in third throughout the early & middle stages. Moved up to take the lead passing the 300m & continued on to win at huge odds.
Raced in midfield along the rail. Moved off the inside on straightening, had difficulty getting clear 400m to 350m when racing tight before closing off well to move to second inside the final 50m.
Had a nice run on the leaders back in middle stages. Moved over the leaders heels near the 300m before closing steadily all the way to the line to only be beaten just over 1L into third.

Veered outwards at start before racing just off midfield. Was checked & lost ground between runners near the 900m & was slightly keen thereafter. Moved into clear running on straightening before making late ground, only be beaten 2L.
Had a nice position 1,1 for the majority. Raced tight near the 350m before finishing off only steadily to maintain deficit in the final section.
Raced three wide with cover in midfield throughout. Was ridden along from the 550m, was the widest runner on cornering before making up a length in the final section to not be beaten far in midfield.
Showed speed to lead. Joined & headed by the winner passing the 300m before weakening to midfield in the final furlong.

Steadied & taken back to race worse than midfield when three wide with cover. Shifted outwards just after straightening, entered last section 3.5L from the lead & finished off ok to be beaten 3L in midfield.
Slow to begin by about a length & raced worse than midfield along rail. Moved away from the inside on straightening, held up 300m to 200m before shifting outwards & finishing one paced late.
Was hampered after the start before getting back to race second last. Was second last and 4.5L from the lead on straightening & failed to make any headway in the straight.
Pushed forward to race outside the leader. Emptied early in the straight & weakened pretty poorly in the final 300m.
Drifted back after the start & raced a clear last throughout. Was 6.5L from the lead on straightening when continuing a clear last before weakening further in the straight to be beaten over 12L.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, enjoyed the easy lead in the middle stages, kept on very well in straight and scored.
Shifted out at start and bumped, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, found rail near 750M, sat right behind the leader on turn, finished off well to take 2nd.
Bumped start, positioned 2 wide slightly better than midfield, 4 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Jumped with them, taken back to race behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made good progress early in straight, peaked on run 150M, ran on same pace to the line.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, angled out 450M, made some headway in straight.
Crowded start, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths back, there to turn, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide towards rear, 8 lengths back turning in, made no impression in straight.
Crowded start, raced in midfield on the inside, 5 lengths back, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, kept on same pace to the line.
Made contact at start, trapped 3 wide with no cover, a length or so back, 2 wide from 750M, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from gate 11, raced at tail throughout, never a factor.
Jumped with the field, ridden along to sit just behind the pace, angled out into the clear at 750M, hit the front at 300M, headed at 150M, found more and holds on
Settled midfield 2 wide, closed off nicely in the Straight, always held.
Settled midfield on the rail, made decent progress, never threatened the top 2. (Substantial blood)
Broke nicely and ridden for speed, settled behind the leader, kept on okay.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, only one pace when asked.
Jumped well and assumed the lead, weakened inside 200M.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, limited response in the Straight.
Settled towards the rear, raced very ungenerously rounding the Home Turn, did made some late progress. (Racing Manners Unacceptable, must trial)
Settled worse than midfield on the rail, made no impression.
Sat behind midfield 2 wide, never in contention.
Sat near the rear, never a threat.
Sat last, got hampered at 600M and never travelled.

Broke well before taken over 2L back to 5th, steadied passing 1000 metres travelling keenly in 4L 7th rounding home bend, obtained clear passage 300 metres out, quickened well to prevail close to home despite hanging in.
Soon came to join race leader after moderate start, settled one back 2-wide rounding home bend, gained narrow advantage under pressure 300 metres out only to be caught close to home.
Bumped at start settling in last few, commenced move 3-wide rounding home bend, quickened well inside final 300 metres to grab 3rd late.

Jumped awkwardly losing ground, travelled wide in last few gaining to midfield 1150 metres out, sustained progress into straight holding every chance inside final 300 metres, unable to sustain effort inside final 100 metres.
Broke well from the one draw settling in midfield on rail, saved ground turning into straight but did not find much room until the 150 metres, produced good late impression late.
Travelled keenly 3-wide towards rear, in similar position rounding home bend, fought on steadily under pressure inside final 200 metres.
Gradually settled in midfield, dropped further back rounding home bend, produced good late impression inside final 200 metres.
Travelled prominently within 2L of pace on rail, in similar position in 3rd rounding home bend, one-paced under pressure in the run to the line.

Niggled along after moderate start gradually dropping to last few and racing keenly in middle stages, became one of last few approaching home turn but kept on well past well-beaten horses closing stages.
Ridden positively from the widest draw to lead on rail from 1200 metres out, steadied pace 1050 metres out approaching home bend, led until weakening under pressure inside final 300 metres.
Well back early gaining towards midfield along the rail inside 1000 metres, did not find much room early in straight until the 150 metres, made no further impression closing stages.
Shifted to last on rail from a wide draw, given reminders when tailing off over 900 metres out, hugged rail turning for home, made no impression.
Wide without cover in prominent position early stages, over 2L back in 4th rounding home bend, dropped out tamely in straight. (Tactic questioned)
Began well from draw 1, tracked leader on inside, maneuvered his way through a narrow passage to lead 150M out, drew clear to win comfortably.
From draw 11 taken across to a position behind midfield, caught 3-wide throughout, responded well on straightening to be challenging for lead 200M, not pace of winner late, got up for 2nd close home.
Tracked leader on outside, kept on well passing 400M, not finishing pace of winner over final 200M, lost 2nd late.
Dropped back to race at the rear, 6Ls to make up 400M, was held up from 300M-150M before closing off well final stages to get 4th. (Adjourned inquiry into jockey's riding. See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped only fairly, restrained to race near the rear, raced keenly middle stages, driven and ran on mildly passing 300M.
Emerged as leader 1100M, soon pressed by rivals early straight, fought on under top weight, led until 150M, no extra late.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners, held up towards the rear, had some difficulty obtaining clear running near 300M, stayed on without threat.
Caught racing wide no cover in midfield, moved closer to leaders passing 800M, not going the pace to challenge in straight, always held by leaders.
Chased leaders, battled on same pace in the straight, never a winning chance.
Held up in midfield along the fence, couldn't quicken when placed under pressure early straight, never able to challenge.
Held up in mid-division 2-wide, raced keenly middle stages, couldn't go on passing 300M, never threatened.
Settled towards the rear, 3-wide making the turn for home, came up empty. Made no impression on debut.
Out with rest, positioned 2 wide slightly better than midfield, there to turn, finished off strongly to score, quite comfortably.
Away well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide from 550M, closed off well to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide towards rear, there to turn, made good progress early in straight, no clear run 300M to 200M, finished off well to take a place without threatening.
Away with them, raced in midfield on the inside, 1-1/2L back on turn, hit the front 300M, peaked and headed 150M, kept on evenly to the line.
Made contact at start, taken back to race towards rear on the outside, very wide turning in, made some headway in straight.
Began well from the widest draw, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, carried wider 500M, showed some response early in straight, peaked on run 200M, ran on evenly to the line.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, similar position on turn, made good progress early in straight, peaked 200M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made minor progress early in straight, peaked on run 200M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Jumped awkwardly and made contact, raced behind midfield on rail, saved ground on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened thereafter.
Bumped start, raced prominently, 2 wide, shared lead on turn, peaked and headed 300M, weakened final 200M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced 2 wide at rear, 3 wide on turn, very wide into straight, made no progress in the run home.
Began well from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, shared the lead with rival on turn, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened final 300M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, sat right behind the leader on rail, angled out 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Crowded start, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, positioned 2 wide, 4 lengths back, same position on turn, finished off very strongly to score.
Commenced well, tracked leaders, 2 wide, there to turn, closed off well to take 2nd, no chance with winner final 100M.
Began smartly, raced prominently on the inside, shared lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Away well, sent forward to take the lead, 2 wide, shared the lead with rival on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, weakened gradually final 100M.
Taken back to race 2 wide behind midfield, found rail near 750M, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear run early in straight, cleared 300M, finished off well without threatening the first few.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced behind midfield on the outside, 5 lengths or so back, made some progress in straight.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at rear on the outside, 7 lengths back turning in, made good progress early in straight, no extra final 150M.
Began well from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, hard ridden from 300M but only showed limited response, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final 200M.
Slowly away, raced behind midfield on rail, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced in midfield on the outside, no cover on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Had a nice run on the leaders back. Shifted over heels at the 225m when only a length behind before closing well in concluding stages to take the lead in the final three strides to win.

Got back to race just off of midfield between runners. Was niggled along to travel better passing 700m, was about 5L from lead on straightening before making strong late ground in last furlong to charge to fast finishing 2nd.

Began well & showed speed, racing prominently before being crossed & racing 1,1 from 750m. Dashed well to take narrow lead at the 250m until swallowed up by winner in final three strides, only beaten half-length on line.
Showed customary early speed to lead. Joined & headed by the third near the 250m, battled on ok in final stages to only be 1.5L behind on the line when holding fourth.

Got back to race worse than midfield when three wide with cover. Shifted wider on cornering, entered last section 6L from the lead before finishing off well down the outside when running onto be beaten 2L.
Had a nice run 1,1 early before a pair further back about half-way. Was 3L from the lead on straightening before finishing off steadily to midfield to not be beaten far.

Drifted back after the start to share last place when galloping along the rail. Continued rearward and over 6L from the lead on straightening before making some steady late ground to halve deficit when running onto midfield.

Raced very wide down the back straight before improving position around the field to get up outside the leader from about the 750m. Was still close to lead until emptying near the 200m & weakening slightly after wide passage.

Shifted behind runners from a wide gate & raced between runners in a line of four at the rear. Continued rearward on straightening when 7L from lead before making up a few late lengths out wide when running onto midfield.

Was slow to begin before making up some ground along the rail to race worse than midfield. Stayed close to the rail on straightening when 6L from the lead before passing a few tiring rivals when making up a length or so late.
Raced wide without cover in midfield throughout. Was only 3L from the lead on straightening before peaking mid-straight & weakening a few lengths in final furlong.

Raced in midfield along the rail before becoming unbalanced near the 1100m & losing a length. Drifted further back in the field passing the 600m, moved away from the rail on straightening before weakening to finish 3rd last.
Taken back to race the widest in a line of four at the rear. Was very wide on straightening when continuing last 7.5L from the lead before weakening poorly to be long second last.
Raced three deep with cover in midfield throughout. Was ridden along from the 600m, was beaten on straightening before weakening badly in the straight to finish a long last (must trial).

Began smartly from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length on turn, kept on very well in straight, easily scored.
Jumped well from gate 1, sat right behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, kept on well in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Began well from a wide draw, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, same position on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped awkwardly, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, raced in midfield on rail, saved ground on turn, kept on same pace in straight.
Made contact at start, raced in midfield on the outside, 3 lengths or so back, very wide into straight, made no impression in the run home. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact at start, raced slightly better midfield on the outside, no cover on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Made contact at start, raced at tail, 7 lengths back turning in, one-paced in the run home.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at rear on the outside, 6 lengths back turning in, made no progress in straight.
Away with them, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 5 lengths back turning in, showed no response early in straight, weakened thereafter. (Irregular heart rhythm and Bled.)

Raced midfield early before improving position passing the 1000m mark & then getting to 1,1 from about the 850m. Dashed between rivals mid-straight before closing to the lead at the 125m & going on to win.

Raced in midfield away from the rail before moving three wide & commencing to improve around the field from the 1000m before improving to the lead near 900m. Continued in the lead until passed by winner at 125m, held second.

Raced in midfield along the rail. Shuffled further back after 1000m, moved wider at 950m, improved position to race forward of midfield from 700m. Shifted back towards rail on straightening before finishing steadily to 3rd.

Began awkwardly & lost ground before racing worse than midfield early. Was relegated to second last near 1000m, moved wider at the 750m & improved to midfield passing the 600m. Closed off steadily in the straight for 4th.

Raced third last early. Moved wider on the track & commenced to improve passing 1100m, improved to be only 2L from lead when racing four wide from 850m, continued close on cornering before finishing one paced in straight.

Raced worse than midfield away from the rail early. Moved wider & commenced mid-race move from 1100m & improved to race outside the lead from the 900m. Only half-length behind on straightening but weakened out in straight.

Shifted back to race at the tail early. Moved wider passing the 1000m, improved to midfield from the 850m when racing four wide with cover. Was 3.5L from the lead entering final section before weakening a length in straight.
Hampered after 150m and was steadied back to the rear. Was third last in front of only two stopping horses from the 500m, was over 7L from the lead at the 400m & only maintained deficit to the line.

Pushed forward to race on leaders back early. Lost position after the 900m when a number of runners improved position. Was hard ridden in midfield before being crowded near the 600m & then weakening poorly, beaten over 10L.

Raced fourth in the clear early. Lost position as others improved position after the 800m, was crowded & checked near the 550m when already under pressure before weakening badly thereafter to be beaten 11L (roarer again).

Pushed forward to race outside the leader early. Began losing position from the 1100m, dropped back through the field to be relegated to last from the 700m. Weakened out badly to be a distant second last (blood in trachea).

Showed speed after start to lead. Was headed in the lead near the 950m, began weakening through the field quickly from the 850m, was badly checked near the 550m when going backwards before tailing out to be a distant last.
Broke nicely, sat midfield 2 wide, began to improve from 550M, made some progress when asked over the final 75M.
Sat midfield on the rail, travelled smoothly, switched out making the Home Turn, showed some dash inside 100M to grab 2nd.
Fractious in the barriers, on jumping blundered, settled better than midfield, responded well under pressure in the Straight.
Ridden hard to chase the lead, travelled okay, but weakened passing the 100M (See Incident Report).
Sat worse than midfield 2 wide, made some progress inside 200M, closed off nicely.
Sat better than midfield 2 wide, slightly weakened entering the Straight, limited response over the concluding stages.
Sat towards rear 2 wide, made minor progress inside 100M but just not quick enough (See Incident Report).
Sat in front of midfield, weakened making the Home Turn, one pace thereafter (See Incident Report).
Settled towards rear, ran on fairly, no impression.
On jumping knuckled, settled midfield 3 wide, commenced to improve from 600M but weakened after 100M.
Ridden along to lead, weakened inside 250M.
Jumped awkwardly, sat rear, never in contention.

Showed speed after the start to dash through and lead. Dashed two lengths clear just before straightening, hung inwards mid-straight & brushed rail at 150m before drawing clear to win very impressively again.

Got back to race third last away from the rail. Was 6L from the lead entering final section, moved over heels at the 200m before closing well late to halve deficit when running onto well beaten second.
Had a nice run in midfield away from the rail. Was 3.5L from the lead entering final section, moved to second fleetingly in final furlong before holding deficit in the straight when finishing third.
Had a nice run in third along the rail. Was 2.5L from the lead entering last section before failing to make any ground, battling away to be beaten 4L.

Raced rearward after the start. Was over 6L from the lead at the 400m when galloping along the rail, stayed nearer the inside on straightening before passing a few tiring rivals when running onto well held fifth.

Showed customary early speed, led early before racing outside the leader/winner after 150m. Couldn't go with the leader approaching the corner, was about 2L behind on straightening before weakening to be beaten over 5L.
Raced in midfield along the rail. Was 4.5L from the lead entering final section, moved away from the rail & into clear running on straightening before weakening a length or two late to be well held.
Was slow to begin & raced at the tail. Was just under 8L from the lead entering final section & never really got involved.

Jumped only fairly & then improved position after the first furlong to race in midfield away from the rail. Was just under 5L from the lead entering last section, shifted wider on straightening but weakened to second last.
Raced worse than midfield early when wider on the track before drifting back around the first bend to be relegated to second last from the 500m. Was last on straightening & was never in contention.
Jumped well from gate 10, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably to turn, kept on very well in straight and scored.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, angled out 350M, finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Began well from gate 1, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, kept on well in straight to take a place without threatening.

Shifted out at start and made contact, trapped wide in midfield early, sent forward 1250M, raced in 2nd in the middle stages, 2 wide, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Slightly slow out, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, kept on same pace in straight.
Jumped very awkwardly and shifted out abruptly, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths or so back, same position on turn, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from gate 11, raced 2 wide towards rear, 6 lengths or so back, 3 wide after entering the back straight, commenced move 450M, very wide into straight, made minor progress in the run home.
Stood flat-footed on jumping and lost ground, raced at tail, 7 lengths back on turn, passed some tired runners in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths or so back, 3 wide approaching 800M, same margin back on turn, very wide into straight, made no progress in the run home.
Bumped start, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, peaked on turn, made no impression in straight.
Crowded on jumping, raced towards rear on the inside, 2 wide from 850M, 6 lengths or so back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.

Moderately away from the widest draw, raced behind midfield on the outside, moved a bit closer after entering the back straight, no cover for the majority of the race, peaked 400M, weakened early in straight when hard run took toll.
Broke nicely but was steadied to obtain cover, settled worse than midfield 2 wide, improve on the inside, angled out at 100M, ran on, always have the measure.
Jumped well and hard ridden early to assume the lead, kept on well for 2nd.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, stuck on nicely, but no threat to the top 2.
Settled midfield on the rail, angled out at 350M and only one pace when asked.
Sat midfield 2 wide, swung wide into the Straight, showed some dash early but unable to further quicken.
Tracked leader, limited response in the Straight.
Restrained to last from the outside barrier, made some progress.
Settled behind midfield on the rail, never impress.
Settled 3 wide towards the rear, never seriously tested. (See Incident Report)
Settled close to the pace, weakened in the Straight. (See Incident Report) (Lame right front the next morning)
Settled towards the rear, ridden along at 500M and failed to pick up.

Ridden from the one draw to be just off the pace on rail, drifted further back to 4th when tempo quickened over 900 metres out, regained 3rd on the bend 500 metres out, fought on dourly to hit the front 150 metres, just held on.
Slowly away settling well back on rail, saved ground turning for home, ran on stoutly under pressure to just fail to get up on line.
Settled in last few, saved ground turning for home, ran on under pressure to be nearest at finish.
Well there early, gradually settled some 2L back in 4th turning into back straight becoming 5th some 4L back in quick tempo, wide on home turn, made up good late ground inside final 150 metres.
Prominent early settling in midfield onto first bend, slightly worse from 900 metres out, wide on home turn, made up good late ground inside final 150 metres.
Never better than midfield on rail, snuck up inside final 400 metres reaching within 1L of pace 100 metres out, unable to sustain effort inside final 100 metres.

Began from a poor draw, travelled keenly and wide without cover behind midfield before swift progress from 1050 metres out, gained slender lead 950 metres out and held slight advantage until over 100 metres out.
Jumped awkwardly settling well behind, widest runner turning for home, ran on quite well down the centre of the track to be nearest at finish.
Soon took up running, led until narrowly headed 950 metres out, remained close-up in 2nd into straight, had no more to give inside final 100 metres.

Began well, gradually shuffled back to rear of midfield by first bend, dropped further back towards rear when without cover early in back straight, went wide on home turn, produced moderate late impression.
Jumped fairly settling in midfield on rail, remained similar into home straight, no further impression.
Pressed forward from a poor gate to briefly join the leaders 3-wide, restrained in 3rd over 950 metres out, became 4th rounding home bend and dropped out inside final 200 metres.
Jumped only fairly, went forward to press leader on outside, driven to the lead 150M, just held off the fast finishing 2nd at the line.
Restrained to a midfield position, ran on well under top weight form 300M, did best work late, just one stride short of catching the winner.
Sped forward, pressed by rivals middle stages, vied for lead from top of straight until headed 150M, lost 2nd late.
Crowded at the start, held up at the rear, did not obtain clear running until 150M, closed off well to take 4th close home.
Pressed forward from draw 12, caught 3-wide outside the lead, battled on to hold 3rd until 100M, held ground final stages.
Crowded at the start, restrained to race near the rear, made some progress passing 300M, not reach leaders.
From wide draw taken back to a rearward position, 3-wide making home turn, stayed on without threatening leaders.
Up with early pace before dropping back to midfield, hung out throughout the middle stages and lost ground rounding home turn, gave limited response in the straight.
Raced in midfield along the 2-path, couldn't go on passing 300M, never threatened.
Up with early pace, back in midfield making the home turn, raced 3-wide throughout, run ended 200M, no extra late.
Tracked leaders along inside, came up empty turning for home, weakened badly from 250M.
Soon outpaced after the start, raced in detached last, finished tailed out and never in the picture. Unacceptable Performance. (Jockey : his horse made respiratory noise during the race.)
Jumped well from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably to turn, kept on very well in straight and scored.
Taken back from gate 10, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide after passing 600M, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to take 2nd, nearest finish.
Away well, tracked leaders, 2 wide, similar position on turn, finished off well to take a place without threatening.
Bumped on jumping, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, kept on well in straight to make frame without threatening.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back, angled out 700M, no cover on turn, made little progress in straight.

Began well from a tricky gate, trapped 3 wide in midfield early, sent forward after entering the back straight, raced in 2nd from 800M, 2 wide, there to turn, peaked early in straight, kept on same pace to the line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide towards rear, 6 lengths or so back turning in, made some progress early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Bumped on jumping, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on same pace thereafter.
Bumped start, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made no progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back to race towards rear on the inside, 7 lengths or so back, still well back on turn, made no impression in straight.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 lengths back, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight. (Bled.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
