Taken back to race 2 wide towards rear, found rail after passing 800M, angled out 550M, finished off very strongly to score, won by a neck.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide better than midfield, angled out after passing 600M, showed good response in straight, hit the front 200M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner close home.
Slightly slow out, sat right behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, finished off well to take a place, just beaten by a neck. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from gate 10, raced at tail, 3 to 4 lengths back turning in, no clear run 400M to 200M, made very good progress thereafter to make frame, nearest on line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from gate 9, raced towards rear on the outside, very wide into straight, made good progress in the run home, no threat to the first few.
Shifted out at start and bumped, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 200M, weakened final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Crowded on jumping, raced 2 wide, 2-1/2L back, wider turning in, showed some response early in straight, peaked on run 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, raced prominently, 2 wide, peaked 500M, weakened gradually in straight.
Average to begin, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out approaching 450M, no clear run early in straight, cleared 200M, failed to make any progress thereafter.

Crowded start, raced better than midfield on the outside, moved a bit closer after passing 950M, shared lead on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M. (See Racing Incidents.) (Lost right hind plate.)

Pressed forward wide around first bend to take up running on rail turning into back straight, steadied up pace early on maintaining slender lead into home straight, just held off fast-finishing 2nd strong late challenge.
Settled in last few from a wide draw travelling keenly in slow tempo early in back straight, shifted wide for a run turning into straight, ran on well under pressure down the centre of the track.
Never far off, shuffled back to 2L 5th coming onto home bend, fought on steadily under pressure without threatening in straight.

Wide in forward of midfield rounding first bend, improved steadily to 2nd 3-wide early in back straight, 2-wide just outside race leader rounding home bend, faded steadily under pressure after straightening.
Lacked early pace, made rapid progress in back straight to reach 2L 4th briefly 900 metres out, remained wide around home bend when coming under pressure, one-paced from 3L 5th in straight.
Travelled wide in rear of midfield, keen in slow tempo early in back straight, towards rear out wide rounding home bend, fought on steadily without threatening.
Gradually picked up to midfield on rail, carried backward to 9th early in back straight, angled out for a run entering home straight, fought on steadily without threatening.

Broke well settling in front on rail, ceded lead for one back position 1400 metres out, drifted further back to 2L 4th 1050 metres out, renewed effort for 3rd coming onto home bend, soon faded in straight.
Wide in midfield to straight, ran home one-paced under pressure.
Never seen with a chance in last few, saved ground on home turn, made no show.
Soon recovered to 4th on rail after moderate start, carried backward to rear of midfield in 7th early in back straight, weakened under pressure in home straight.
Ridden along to lead on the rail, traveled nicely throughout, well response under pressure, kept on well to win.
Sat handy 2 wide, made good progress over the concluding stages, finished off nicely to hold 2nd.
Settled midfield 2 wide, switched out and raced tight making the Turn, made some progress in the early Straight.
Sat midfield on the rail, traveled keenly in the early stages, briefly held up in the Straight until 200M, could not be fully tested.
Jumped awkwardly, sat rear, showed some response in the early Straight but one pace thereafter.
Settled rear 2 wide, began to improve approaching 700M, limited response when asked in the Straight and faded (Unacceptable Performance, See Incident Report).

Steadied & got back to race near the rear when wide with cover. Was the widest runner on straightening when still 8.5L from lead before finishing very strongly down the outside to charge to lead inside last 100m & win easily.

Showed speed to get lead easily after the start. Raced 4L clear of his nearest rival passing the 600m, was still 4 or 5L clear at the 200m mark before being charged down by fast closing winner in final 100m, Held second.

Raced three wide just worse than midfield early before being left without cover after improving to midfield after the 1000m. Continued to be wide around bend, was over 7L behind at the 400m before closing well to third late.

Raced in midfield away from the rail before being a touch keen after 1200m mark. Was just under 6L from lead entering final section as leader raced clear before finishing off steadily all the way to the line to halve deficit.

Was slow away before racing just worse than midfield along the rail. Moved off the rail approaching the 400m when still a long way from lead, shifted out wider after the 300m mark before making some late ground to midfield.

Raced second in the clear around the first bend before being crossed & racing 1,1 from about the 1000m mark. Straightened in third place when just under 5L from lead but only finishing one paced to midfield.

Was steadied & taken rearward from the widest gate to share last place. Stayed close to the rail on straightening when over 10L from the lead before making up significant late ground from a hopeless position to be midfield.

Was trapped racing very wide around the first bend before improving position to get up outside the leader from about the 1000m. Was niggled along from the 600m as the leader raced away before weakening out in straight.

Drifted back to race near the rail throughout. Continued rearward, was just under 10L from the lead on corner, was hampered on straightening before doing nothing in the straight & being a well beaten third last. Poor.

Improved position around first bend to race in midfield away from the rail. Was ridden along from the 500m mark, began losing ground before straightening & weakened out poorly in the straight to be long second last.

Was slow to begin before shifting down to rail & getting position in midfield around first bend. Was hard ridden from the 500m, began losing ground before straightening before weakening very poorly to be distant last.
Began only fairly, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off very strongly to score, won by a narrow margin.
Moderately away from gate 1, sent forward to race prominently on the inside, took the lead near 800M, led by a length turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner late.
Bumped start, raced in 3rd, a length or so back, saved ground on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place, not quite able to challenge.
Began well, sent forward to take the early lead, headed near 800M, 2nd on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, similar position on turn, made some progress in straight.
Taken back from gate 9, raced towards rear on the outside, 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, no clear run early until 150M, made some progress thereafter.
Taken back to race at rear on the inside, 2 wide turning in, unable to obtain clear running until well inside final furlong, made some progress thereafter.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out 500M, one-paced in the run home.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced slightly behind midfield on the outside, very wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Bumped start, taken back to race at tail, 7 lengths or so back, 5 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced better than midfield on the outside, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Bumped start, raced in midfield on the inside, same position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Broke nicely, quickly moved towards the stands' rail and lead, kept on well and held on.
Jumped a bit slow, sat towards the rear center track, closed off strongly, peaked at final 50M, unable to challenge the winner.
Jumped well and sat close to the pace 4 from the stands' rail, responded okay when asked, held 3rd
Showed no early speed and settled at the rear on the stands' rail, switched in at 400M for clear running, ran on well.
Settled worse than midfield 3 from the stands rail, stuck in traffic until final 100M, closed off strongly.
Raced prominent 2 from the stands' rail, kept on fairly.
Sat towards the rear, made some progress. (See Incident Report)
Settled in front of midfield 3 from the stands' rail, held up for the final 400M, never involved.
Settled midfield near the center, limited response.
Jumped nicely and shared lead, weakened inside 150M. (See Incident Report)
Settled worse than midfield 2 from the stands' rail, never seriously tested
Settled in a prominent position 1 off the stands' rail, weakened inside 300M.
Settled in front of midfield 1 from the stands' rail despite ridden along early, never travelled. (See Incident Report)
Got hampered near 750M, never in contention.
Jumped moderately, pressed forward to take up running after first 100 metres shifting to the rail 1000 metres out, hung on well under pressure to prevail despite the quick tempo mid-race.
Broke well settling off the pace off the rail in 4th within striking distance, some 3L back in 5th entering home straight, ran on steadily under pressure to be nearest at finish.

Began well from a wide draw gradually taken back to rear and waited with, saved ground near rail rounding home bend, obtained clear run 300 metes out, fought on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Settled behind midfield from a wide-ish draw gaining rails run shortly after, travelled keenly coming onto home bend in joint 6th and saved ground turning in, kept on steadily without quickening.
Amongst first few and wide early stages, gained 2-wide position in joint 2nd coming onto home bend, unable to sustain effort upon straightening.
Jumped fairly settling not far off the pace in 5th on rail, gained closer turning for home, kept on in straight until finding no extra 150 metres out.
Jumped moderately recovered steadily to rear of midfield to 6th within 4L of pace, in similar position rounding home bend running wide into straight, made no further impression.
Crowded shortly after start losing ground, tailed-off to home straight, fought on inside final 250 metres past well-beaten horses.
Began well gradually settled 3-wide in midfield, taken back abruptly 900 metres out coming onto home bend, found nothing in straight.
Travelled very wide with race leaders, 3-wide without cover in 1L 3rd rounding home bend, folded up quickly after straightening.
Broke a step slow, raced in midfield, wide no cover from 900M, struck the lead past 350M, held on well when pressed by the persistent runner up over final 200M.
Close up behind leaders early stages, reined back to sit in 5th spot making home turn, lay in early straight when driven, emerged as the only challenger to leader passing 200M, just held.
Held up behind midfield, driven along 500M, stayed on moderately to claim 3rd, nearest finish.
Jumped only fairly from draw 1, moved up to chase leaders, briefly held up top of straight before closing off the race steadily. Just missed 3rd.
Settled down mid-division along the 2-path, made mild gains from 400M to claim 5th, not far off behind 3rd and 4th.
Up with early pace before taking a trailing spot behind leaders, kept on evenly turning home but never going the pace to challenge.
From wide draw dropped back to race in last, 8Ls off the pace middle stages, stayed on mildly passing 400M, not reach leaders.
Vied for lead on outside, tried to keep up with pursuers from 350M but to no avail, soon out of contention.
Sent forward, vied for the lead on inside, soon over taken 350M, weakened towards the finish.
Jumped only fairly from wide draw, soon shifted across to the fence, towards the rear entering home turn, made little impact from 400M.
From wide draw unable to slot in, travelled 3-wide towards the rear, wide into straight, couldn't make any headway.
Taken back from wide draw, settled towards the rear, couldn't go on passing 400M. Never involved.
Jumped awkwardly, recovered to a midfield position, under serious pressure 600M, faltered from top of straight. (Bled.)
Taken back from gate 10, raced 2 wide at rear, 3 wide from 900M, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to score by a neck.
Jumped with them, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed very good response in straight, hit the front 100M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner late.
Out with rest, raced better than midfield on the inside, angled out 600M, took the lead 200M, peaked and headed 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back turning in, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out 550M, kept on well in straight without threatening.
Away with them, raced better than midfield on the outside, a length or so back turning in, finished off evenly.
Made contact at start, raced in 2nd, there to turn, took the lead 350M, peaked and headed 200M, weakened final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with cover towards rear, moved a bit closer after passing 1000M, 4 lengths back turning in, one-paced in the run home.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some progress early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Average to begin, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M.
Made contact at start, trapped wide in midfield, similar position on turn, weakened early in straight, eased final furlong.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear throughout, never a factor. (See Racing Incidents.) (Lame right hind leg next day.)
Out with rest, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, same position on turn, took the lead 400M, kept on very well to hold off the challengers late, won by a head.
Taken back from gate 12, raced towards rear on the outside, moved a bit closer after passing 700M, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to take 2nd, just beaten by a head.
Away well, raced slightly behind midfield, 3 wide, moved a bit closer after passing 800M, 3rd turning in, kept on well to the line, always just held.
Began awkwardly and crowded, raced behind midfield on the inside, 2 wide turning in, unable to obtain clear run until final 100M, finished off well to make frame, nearest on line.
Taken back from a tricky draw, raced 2 wide towards rear, moved a bit closer after passing 650M, raced tight near 500M, made some headway in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced behind midfield on the outside, a bit closer on turn, showed some response early in straight, not enough room 100M, coasted home. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from a wide draw, raced 2 wide better than midfield, similar position on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually final 75M.
Shifted out at start, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, one-paced in the run home.
Began well from gate 1, sat right behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final 100M. (Irregular heart rhythm.)
Slowly away, raced at rear throughout.
Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked and headed 300M, weakened thereafter.

Stumbled start, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, 2 wide after entering the back straight, commenced move 400M, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to score, won by a narrow margin.
Made contact at start, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, kept on very well in straight, just beaten by a narrow margin.
Began well, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, angled out 350M, closed off well to take a place, just beaten by a neck.
Jumped with them, raced towards rear, 5 lengths back, very wide turning in, made good progress in straight to make frame, no threat to the first few.

Made contact at start, raced prominently on the outside, took the lead after entering the back straight, led by a length on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 100M, weakened final 50M.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, headed near 950M, 2nd on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Taken back from gate 7, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, same margin back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Settled 2-wide in mid-division, driven wide into straight, closed off well to lead 200M, drew clear late.
Sent forward, led passing 1300M, fought on steadily turning for home, not pace of winner final 200M.
Tracked leader on settling, kept one evenly final 300M, outfinished by winner final stages.
Chased leaders, in good spot turning into straight, tried hard to stay in contention under 135lb, always held by 2nd and 3rd . (Jockey could offer no excuse for the below expectation run.)
From wide draw shifted across behind runners, raced at the rear, gave limited response on straightening, ran past beaten horses only.
Settled behind midfield, couldn't find more turning home, never dangerous.
Held up in midfield along the fence, under pressure 500M, couldn't go on from top of straight. No factor.
Towards the rear, moved wide into straight then came up empty.
Sat handy, traveled strongly making the Home Turn, kept on well to the finish.
Broke smart, settled behind midfield, began to improve inside 500M, made some progress over the final 150M.
Settled midfield, traveled smoothly, held up making the Home Turn, one pace in the Straight.
Was slow to begin, sat rear, switched out and improved inside 800M, showed some response when asked in the Straight, closed off okay (See Incident Report).
Sat towards rear, minor progress approaching the 150M, ran on evenly.
Ridden along to lead, slightly weakened inside 600M, limited response after straightening.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, never in contention (Substantial amount of blood).

Began fast & got an easy lead after start. Was headed, crossed & raced on the leaders back from the 1200m. Stayed along the inside, had clear running up the rail, dashed to lead at 200m before pulling away to win easily.

Raced rearward early before improving position leaving the straight to get up outside the leader passing the 1100m. Continued second on straightening, battled on to hold off challengers for 2nd but was well behind winner.

Raced 1,1 early before being shuffled back to second last from the 1200m. Was relegated to last near the 600m, had clear running on straightening when only a couple of lengths behind before closing to third late.

Raced a clear last from about the 1300m. Moved wider on the track & commenced to improve around the field from the 600m, pushed four wide from the 500m, was very wide on straightening before closing off well in late stages.

Raced on leaders back early before being shuffled further back from 1200m. Raced tight on cornering when continuing along rail, was badly held up near the 200m before getting through late to be in a bunch behind easy winner.

Steadied & taken rearward early before improving position leaving straight, dashing around the field quickly to go to lead near 1200m. Came off the rail on cornering, passed by winner near 200m before battling last furlong.

Raced in midfield away from the rail early before improving position around first bend to get the 1,1 position from the 1000m. Raced keenly down the dip, eased wider at the 500m before weakening few lengths in last furlong.

Raced second after the start before being overtaken near the 1200m & then getting shuffled back to midfield from the 1100m. Was relegated to the final pair near 600m, was last at the 400m & failed to improve in the straight.
Taken back from gate 10, raced towards rear on the outside, commenced move 400M, very wide entering straight, showed very good response in straight, took the lead 150M, kept on very well to the line.
Away well, positioned 2 wide, 2-1/2L back, angled out 400M, closed off well to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Made contact at start, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, took the lead 250M, peaked and headed 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped with them, raced in midfield on the inside, 3 lengths back, same position on turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, 3 to 4 lengths back, similar position on turn, kept on same pace in straight.
Slowly away, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared 200M, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, there to turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked on run 150M, weakened gradually final 100M.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced slightly better than midfield on the outside, no cover throughout, very wide into straight, hampered early in straight, made no impression thereafter.
Made contact at start, raced in midfield on the outside, 3 to 4 lengths back, similar position on turn, inconvenienced 200M, made no impression thereafter.
Crowded start, raced towards rear, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, one-paced in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Away with them, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length turning in, peaked and headed 250M, weakened final 150M, eased thereafter.
Broke nicely, settled just behind the leaders, angled out at 300M, closed off strongly, battled hard and just got there.
Ridden along early to lead, kept on well, fought hard and just got beaten on the line.
Settled worse than midfield on the rail, made good progress but no threat to the top 2.
Caught 3 wide in midfield with cover, made decent progress but only one pace after 150M.
Settled midfield on the rail, only one paced when asked.
Settled midfield 2 wide, held up in the early part of the Straight, never seriously tested.
Settled towards the rear 2 wide, switched to 3 wide making the Home Turn, swung wide into the Straight, stayed on only fairly.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, nothing in the Straight.
Caught 3 wide no cover in a prominent position, weakened at 400M.
Showed good early speed to dispute the lead, weakened and faded quickly in the Straight. (Substantial Mucus)
Slow into stride and settled at the rear on the rail, never in contention. (Heart Irregularity) (Must Trial)
Settled at the rear 2 wide, never a threat.
Driven forward from a wide draw to share pace into back straight, settled just outside race leader most of the way and hit the front under pressure over 250 metres out, just held on to the line.
Driven forward to lead after first 100 metres, attempted to make all holding slender advantage to straight, fought on well to only to be denied narrowly.

Broke well before settling just over 2L off the pace, dropped slightly further back to 5th entering back straight, remained similar turning for home swinging wide, fought on well under pressure to be nearest finish.
Jumped best from the one draw settling just over 2L back in 4th, shared 3rd rounding home bend and saved ground into straight, unable to sustain effort inside final 150 metres.
Amongst leaders before hampered and dropped to one-out-one-back 4th, shared 3rd rounding home bend travelling 3-wide, kept on same pace under pressure without quickening.
Settled in midfield over 5L back in 6th, saved ground home turn, did not find much room closing stages.
Never better than midfield, wide into straight, produced good late impression down the centre of the track.
Travelled in last few from wide draw, wide into straight, fought on well under pressure down the centre of the track.
Settled at the back from the widest draw, saved ground turning for home, ran on well past well-beaten runners in straight. (Mucus in trachea) (Lame next day)
Jumped awkwardly and crowded, niggled along behind midfield, saved ground turning for home, folded up quickly inside final 200 metres.
Always in last few and never seen with a chance.
Jumped on terms, soon moved to the lead setting good pace, pulled away mid-straight and continued on with determination, won by good margin.
Moved up to 3rd entering back straight, within striking range passing 500M, kept on steadily to go 2nd near 150M, not reach winner.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners, settled near the rear 7Ls off the pace, finished off moderately through final 250M. Got up for 3rd late.
Held up behind midfield in a fast run race, travelled satisfactorily, stayed on final 300M without threatening winner. (Jockey : after changing lead early straight didn't finish off strongly.)
Eased back from draw 9, settled at the rear 8-9Ls off the pace, plenty to do 300M, closed off reasonably well making gradual gain late.
Pursued leader in a fast run race, battled on early straight but couldn't get close to winner, held 2nd to 150M, flattened out late.
Settled down midfield in a fast run race, lacked further response passing 250M, never a threat to leaders. (Jockey: his mount would derive benefit from tonight's run.)
From middle draw shifted across behind runners, reserved at the back, checked 150M to avoid a beaten rival, failed to quicken.
Away with them, settled towards the rear, pushed along 600M out, couldn't go on in the straight.

Raced in midfield along the fence, moved up to 3rd 400M, not quickened when placed under pressure, eased down by jockey 200M. (Jockey : concerned something had gone amiss near 200M. / No Vet findings.)
Moderately away, raced in midfield on the outside, 4 lengths back turning in, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to score.
Jumped only fairly, raced better than midfield on the inside, angled out 450M, hit the front 250M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner on line.

Jumped awkwardly and made contact, sent forward to take the early lead, headed near 900M, positioned 2 wide, a length behind the leader in the middle stages, 4 wide turning in, finished off well to take a place, always just held.
Taken back from gate 9, raced towards rear on the outside, 4 to 5 lengths back, very wide turning in, made good progress straight to be nearest on line, no threat to the first few.
Began fairly, raced in midfield, 2-1/2L back, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to be nearest on line.
Away well, raced better than midfield on the outside, similar position on turn, kept on same pace in straight.
Began smartly from gate 11, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead near 900M, led by 1/4L turning in, peaked and headed 250M, weakened final 150M. (Lame left front leg.)

Crowded shortly after start, raced towards rear on the inside, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away from gate 1, raced prominently on the inside, travelled well to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Jumped with them, raced behind midfield on rail, saved ground on turn, showed no response early in straight, weakened and eased thereafter.

Began well, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, same position on turn, hit the front 300M, kept on very well to the line, easily scored.
Jumped well from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, 2 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, finished off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Began only fairly, raced in midfield on rail, 3 lengths or so back, angled out 500M, closed off well to take a place without threatening.
Away well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, angled out approaching 450M, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, made some progress in straight.
Commenced well, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L turning in, peaked and headed 300M, weakened inside final furlong.
Average to begin, positioned 2 wide, 4 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made no impression in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slightly slow out, raced towards rear on the inside, 2 wide turning in, made no impression in straight. (Lame left front leg next day morning.)
Moderately away from a wide draw, taken back to race behind midfield on the outside, no cover for the majority of the race, 5 lengths back turning in, made no progress in straight.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide, 5 to 6 lengths back, angled out 500M, very wide into straight, failed to make any progress in the run home. (Mucus in trachea.) (Roarer.)
Showed customary early speed to come across to lead. Was half a length in from entering last section & held off all challengers to win.

Didn't begin fast & raced rearward throughout. Was second last but only 3.5L from the lead entering final section before shifting inwards at the 350m mark & closing well to move to second inside the last 150m.

Had limited early speed & raced second last along the stand side rail. Stayed along the stand side rail most of the way when closing strongly in the last furlong to steal fast finishing third in concluding stages.

Showed speed to race in second place for the majority. Was only half a length from the lead entering final section but couldn't go with the winner in concluding stages before being caught for a minor placing in final strides.

Was slightly slow to begin & raced last. Continued in last place entering final section before closing steadily between runners into tight room passing the 200m mark before being closest on the line when beaten under 2L.

Raced rearward after the start when galloping closer to the middle of the track. Was ridden along from half-way, entered last section 2.5L from the lead before passing a couple of rivals when running onto midfield late.
Raced in midfield along the stand side rail for the majority. Moved off the rail passing the 250m, finished off only steadily to midfield late & was never a threat.
Bumped at the start before racing in midfield between runners. Was only 1.5L from the lead entering final section but weakened tamely in the final 150m to be beaten just under 3L into midfield.
Raced in midfield when galloping closest to the center of the track. Was just over a length from the lead entering final section before weakening in final 150m to be beaten just over 3L.

Obtained position in midfield between runners. Was ridden along from the 400m when just over a length from the lead, raced tight near the 125m but was beaten at that stage before weakening to be beaten just under 4L.
Bumped at the start & was then steadied before getting position worse than midfield. Was held up passing the 400m mark & then failed to obtain clear running thereafter.

Was awkward on jumping before being steadied & racing rearward after the start. Was held up after the 350m mark before being fully tested from the 225m when close to stand side rail. Could have been slightly closer.

Showed some speed after the start to race in third position soon after the start. Drifted back to midfield after the first 400m before coming under pressure at the 400m and then weakening out to second last.
Raced in midfield after the start before improving to be just forward of midfield after the first 400m. Began losing ground from the 400m mark & weakened badly to long last.
Slow to jump, settled behind midfield on the rail, no clear running until 200M, showed some dash inside 100M, closed off strongly.
Sat in front of midfield 2 wide, traveled nicely throughout, made some progress in the Straight, just miss.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, angled out making the Home Turn, responded well when asked (Blood in its mouth).
Sat midfield on the rail, was held up in the early Straight until 200M, finished off nicely.
Sat midfield 2 wide, traveled smoothly, slightly weakened over the concluding 100M, ran on evenly.
Settled behind midfield 2 wide, minor progress approaching 200M, ran on okay.
Sat handy, travel okay until making the Home Turn, weakened inside 200M (See Incident Report).
Sat rear, limited response when placed under pressure, one pace (See Incident Report).
Jumped awkwardly, settled towards rear, no contention.
Ridden along to lead, weakened and faded quickly inside 300M (Substantial blood, must trial in Hong Kong).

Showed speed to lead. Was joined by the runner-up near the 250m mark before engaging in a two horse battle for the entire last furlong where he dug very deep to get his nose in front on the line. First two clear of third.

Raced forward of midfield after the start but was left three wide around the bend & was then without cover from the 800m. Dashed to join lead near the 250m, battled in a two horse war in last furlong, just missed out line.
Had a nice run 1,1 for the majority. Was just over a length from the lead on straightening when third, battled away to hold third placing but was a full 2L behind the first two.

Raced in midfield when three wide with cover throughout. Was just over 2L from the lead on straightening & finished off steadily all the way to the line to hold fourth but like the others was no match for the first two.

Steadied & taken back to race just worse than midfield when three wide with cover. Shifted outwards on cornering, was the widest runner on straightening when 3.5L from lead before finishing off steadily down the outside late.

Was third last soon after the start before improving along the rail to be worse than midfield around bend. Had head on the side passing 700m, stayed close to the rail in the straight before passing a few tiring rivals late.

Raced in midfield between runners early before drifting further back from the 700m. Had clear running on straightening when 4.5L from the lead before passing a few tiring rivals to run onto midfield without threatening.
Raced in midfield between runners throughout. Was ridden along before straightening, was only 3L behind at the 400m but weakened meekly in last furlong to be beaten 5.5L.
Had a soft run in the leaders back throughout. Was only 2L from the lead on straightening but gave up easily in the straight & weakened pretty poorly to be beaten 6L.
Didn't begin fast & was last after the start before sharing that position from the 750m when racing along the rail. Was 5.5L from the lead entering final section before doing nothing in the run home.

Ridden forward after the start, improved to second near after the first 150m when racing wide, shifted in to be two wide outside the leader from the 850m. Was beaten soon after straightening & weakened badly in straight.

Was slow to begin with rider losing his near side iron for the first 150m and races second last. Shared last place from the 800m when racing quite keenly. Did nothing in the straight & was a long last.
Jumped with them, raced in midfield on the outside, angled out after passing 500M, finished off very strongly to score.
Commenced well, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1-1/2L turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner late.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground in the middle stages, 3 lengths or so back turning in, finished off well to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Fast into stride, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, there to turn, hard ridden after passing 350M but only showed limited response, ran on evenly to the line. (Lost right hind plate.)
Began well, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, same position on turn, finished off evenly.
Away with them, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run 200M, weakened gradually close home.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, one-paced in the run home.
Bumped start, taken back to race at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made no impression in straight.
Began fairly, showed no early speed, raced behind midfield on the outside, 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start, taken back to race at rear, 6 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Broke nicely, sat just off the lead, travelled comfortably throughout, stuck on well, and won comfortably.
Steadied after the start from a wide barrier, settled at the rear, moved to 3 wide to improve at the 700M, closed off strongly for 2nd.
Ridden along early, settled midfield 3 wide with cover, began his run at 500M, kept on nicely for 3rd.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, switched out in the Straight, made decent progress and weakened final 100M
Settled worse than midfield 3 wide, made good progress.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, got held up for the majority of the Straight, and never seriously tested.
Settled behind midfield on the rail, made little impression.
Settled midfield 2 wide, made no ground.
Sat handy 3 wide no cover, gave ground in the Straight.
Jumped a bit awkward but was quick into stride and led, weakened inside 300M.
Sat just behind the leaders, raced keenly throughout, never a threat. (See Incident Report)
Jumped slowly, at the rear, never involved.
Broke slowly, at the rear, never in contention.
Settled towards the rear 2 wide, never impress.
Soon taken well back 3-wide with cover, remained similar rounding home bend, commenced move entering straight and quickened well to hit front over 200 metres out.

Settled wide without cover just worse than midfield between 5th and 6th, remained similar without cover around home bend, ran on steadily under pressure in straight to reach 2nd 150 metres only to find winner too good.
Gradually settled in rear and waited with, switched wide into straight and obtained clear run 300 metres out, finished off the race well.
Jumped fairly travelling just worse than midfield on the rail, did not find much room early in home straight, obtained run near the rail inside final 200 metres but unable to quicken to threaten.

Pressed forward from a wide draw to share early lead, taken half a length back coming onto home bend before renewed effort to hit the front early in straight, soon headed by eventual winner over 200 metres out.
Settled some 2L back in 3rd, travelled keenly from 1050 metres onto home bend, unable to quicken from prominent 3rd into straight.
Settled mainly in midfield, drifted backward 900 metres out onto home bend, in last few behind runners turning for home, fought on steadily under pressure to be nearest at finish.
Settled well back, saved ground on the rail around home bend sneaking closer into straight, baulked for a run until the 300 metres, finished off the race nicely.
Ridden forward to share early pace gaining over half a length advantage coming onto home bend, headed into straight and gradually faded.

Moderate start, gradually improved along the rail to just over 3L back in 4th, gained closer to 3rd 850 metres out, unable to sustain effort and weakened under pressure inside final 300 metres. (Blood in trachea)
Tracked leader, responded well when driven 350M, led near 100M fending off a late challenge final stages.
In touch, ran on willingly passing 400M, pushed winner to the wire but always held.
Soon led, fought hard to maintain the lead passing 300M, caught 150M out, faded late but held on for 3rd.
Tracked the pace, kept battling passing 300M but always held by leaders.
Settled near last, kept on mildly under top weight passing 400M, not reach leaders.
Held up at the rear, gave limited response when driven, never dangerous to leaders.
Held up near last, battled on at same pace to line. Never threatened.
Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 lengths or so back turning in, finished off very strongly to score, won by a length.

Moderately away from a wide draw, tracked leaders, 3 wide with no cover, found a 2 wide spot near 900M, angled out after passing 500M, hit the front 250M, peaked and headed 100M, ran on evenly to take 2nd.
Jumped well, raced slightly behind midfield, 3 wide with no cover, very wide into straight, finished off well to take a place without threatening the first two.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the outside, 6 lengths or so back turning in, made very good progress in straight to make frame, nearest finish.
Taken back from gate 13, raced behind midfield on the outside, 3 to 4 lengths back turning in, taken wide in straight and finished off well to be nearest on line, not quite able to challenge.
Slowly away, raced 2 wide towards rear, angled out 550M, very wide into straight, made some headway in the run home.
Away well, sat right behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, no clear run early in straight, cleared 300M, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, raced slightly better than midfield on the inside, angled out 550M, 4 wide turning in, showed some response early in straight, no extra final 150M.
Made contact at start, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, shared lead with rival turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Made contact at start, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, shared lead turning in, peaked on run 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped on jumping, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, one-paced in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover towards rear, 6 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, made no impression in the run home. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide in midfield, carried wider from 550M, peaked early in straight, weakened and eased final 150M.
Bumped start, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, failed to close off in straight.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide better than midfield, angled out and made contact 500M, hit the front 300M, kept on strongly to the line, won by 1-1/2L.
Clean jump, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well in the middle stages, headed 300M, kept on well to take 2nd.
Began only fairly, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight to take a place without threatening the first two.
Began well from gate 1, sat right behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, kept on evenly in straight.
Taken back from gate 11, raced at tail, 6 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening the first few.
Began fairly, raced in midfield on the inside, angled out 500M, finished off evenly.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 lengths or so back, angled out 450M, kept on same pace in straight.
Commenced well, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, wider turning in, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact at start, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced behind midfield on the outside, very wide into straight, made some progress early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Moderately away from the widest draw, raced at rear on the outside, 4-1/2L back turning in, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away from gate 9, raced better than midfield on the outside, no cover throughout, made contact and carried wider 500M, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect.

Away with them, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably to turn, kept on well in straight to hold off the challenger late.
Commenced well from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground to turn, finished off very strongly, just beaten by a narrow margin.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, angled out 350M, finished off well to take a place without threatening the first two.

Moderately away from a wide draw, trapped wide in midfield early, moved a bit closer after passing 1300M, a length or so back in the middle stages, no cover throughout, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, taken wide in straight and made minor progress.
Jumped with them, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, not enough room early in straight, cleared 100M, made some progress thereafter.
Bumped start, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Out in line, raced 2 wide at rear early, 3 wide after entering the back straight, very wide turning in, passed some tired runners in straight.
Away well, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, same position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 200M.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide in midfield, 3 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from gate 11, raced at tail, hard ridden after passing 800M but only showed limited response, positioned 4 wide behind midfield on turn, weakened early in straight, eased final 100M.

With leader early gradually settling just over 2L back in 4th on rail, gained closer to 3rd under pressure rounding home bend, obtained clear run upon straightening 300 metres out, hit the front under pressure 100 metres out.
Led first 200 metres before settling one back in 2nd from early in back straight, renewed effort turning in to hit the front only to be headed by winner 100 metres out.
Settled in midfield on the rail, commenced move but baulked approaching home turn, fought on steadily on the inside without threatening.
Settled in worse than midfield in 7th, looked a difficult rider early in straight, finished off the race well inside final 200 metres.
Crowded at start settling towards the rear in 9th, saved ground turning for home, kept on steadily in straight without threatening.
Unbalanced at start settling in rear of midfield in 8th on rail, saved ground turning for home, one-paced under pressure in straight
Travelled wide in rear from a wide draw and keen early, taken further back for cover in 11th early in back straight, in similar position turning for home, kept on steadily without quickening.
Crowded at start settling in last few on rail, saved ground turning for home, unable to sustain effort and faded 200 metres out.
Jumped awkwardly and checked losing ground, detached from the main body of the field despite niggling along most of the way, went past well-beaten horses in home straight.
Ridden forward after moderate start from a poor draw settling 2L back in 3rd passing the 1000 metres, given ground from approaching home turn.
Settled 2-wide in midfield in 5th or 6th, went widest into straight and soon weakened.
Hard ridden forward from the widest draw, took up running 2-wide 1000 metres out obtaining rails run 800 metres out, led until headed shortly after straightening and folded up quickly.
Settled midfield 2 wide, traveled smoothly, responded well over the concluding stages, closed off nicely.
Sat handy, traveled strongly, kept on okay early in the Straight, slightly weakened inside 200M, just held 2nd.
Sat towards rear 2 wide, commenced to improve inside 400M, angled out in the Straight, ran on evenly.
Sat towards rear, switched out making the Home Turn, made some progress over the concluding stages, closed off okay.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, traveled okay but limited response in the Straight (Substantial blood in the horse's trachea).
Slow to jump, sat rear, one pace throughout the event (See Incident Report).
Settled midfield on the rail, slightly weakened inside 500M, made no progress passing the Home Turn.
Ridden hard to lead, weakened inside 100M, no impression in the Straight.
Jumped awkwardly, weakened approaching 200M, no contention (Unacceptable performance, Must trial, See Incident Report).

Raced just worse than midfield away from the rail throughout. Was about 4L from lead entering last section, was the widest runner on straightening before closing strongly down the outside to take lead at 100m & win.
Raced in midfield away from the rail throughout. Peeled three wide approaching the 500m, entered last section 3L from lead, closed to second at the 100m & held that position on line.

Steadied from outside gate & taken back to share last place. Moved away from the inside passing the 500m, was second last on cornering before closing off well in the concluding stages to finishing a fast finishing third.
Raced in midfield along the rail throughout. Was held up behind a tiring runner when locked away on the rail from 450m until straightening before finishing off steadily in late stages.

Was steadied after start & taken back to share last place when racing away from rail. Forced three wide approaching the 450m, was last on straightening before making some late headway down the outside to finish midfield.

Was trapped racing three wide without cover in midfield before improving position in back straight to get outside the leader near 800m. Took narrow lead near 550m, continued in front until joined at the 100m & weakening late.

Improved quickly after 100m to race outside the leader before shifting down to rail near the 1200m & racing on the leaders back. Continued in third place on cornering before peaking mid-straight & weakening in last furlong.
Steadied on jumping & shifted across behind runners to race third last along the rail. Continued rearward along the rail on cornering before doing very little in the straight.
Pushed forward to lead. Joined by rival near the 800m, headed in the lead near the 550m, was beaten off early in the straight when continuing along the rail before weakening to be well beaten.

Raced prominently after the start before drifting slightly further back when racing along the rail to be in midfield for the majority. Was ridden along to hold place form the 500m before weakening poorly in the straight.

Raced fourth early, bumped heavily with rival after the 1400m before settling just forward of midfield away from the rail. Was ridden along to hold position passing 750m, began losing ground from the 500m & tailed out to bad last.

Slowly away, raced at rear, 6 lengths back, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared approaching 100M, finished off very strongly, joined leader close home. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, angled out 400M, showed very good response in straight, hit the front 100M, kept on well, joined close home.
Slowly away, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, a bit closer on turn, closed off well to take a place, not quite able to challenge.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed approaching 100M, weakened gradually close home.
Began smartly from gate 1, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Began fairly, positioned 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, kept on same pace in straight.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide towards rear, 5 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Average to begin, sent forward to race in 2nd, a length back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened 200M, eased final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with the field, ridden along early to assume the lead, kept on well and held off all challengers. (See Incident Report)
Broke particularly well, sat in the box-seated position, had every chance, always held. (See Incident Report)
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide, switched out to 3 wide to improve at the 600M, and closed off strongly, nearest finish.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, only one pace when asked.
Raced in a prominent position 3 wide, kept on fairly.
Steadied towards the rear after the start from wide barrier, swung wide entering the Home Straight, stayed on fairly.
Settled towards the rear 2 wide, made some progress.
Sat handy 2 wide, limited response in the Straight.
Settled midfield on the rail, never involved.
Settled behind midfield on the rail, made no impression. (Next day was lame in its left front leg and had sustained a bone injury to the left knee)
Settled midfield 2 wide, was checked rounding the Home Turn, never seriously tested.
Settled at the rear, never a factor.
Soon took up running before 1000-metre bend travelling keenly most of way in back straight, kicked over 1L clear into home straight and maintained advantage throughout.
Jumped awkwardly but amongst leaders early, shifted one back to 4th early in back straight, one-out-one-back turning for home, fought on steadily without threatening.
Settled just worse than midfield, very wide into straight, finished well down the centre of the track despite hanging.

Travelled wide without cover in midfield from the widest draw, obtained cover 3-wide in 6th about 850 metres out, gained closer to one back position rounding home bend, fought on steadily to the line.
Blundered and taken back from a wide draw, gained one closer to 11th 850 metres out, saved ground turning for home, ran on in straight to be nearest at finish.
Soon recovered from moderate start to join the leaders early in back straight, found nothing under pressure inside final 200 metres.
Jumped awkwardly settling in last few, 3-wide rounding home bend and widest into straight, kept on steadily without threatening down the centre of the track.
Settled mainly in 7th on rail in midfield or slightly worse, saved ground turning for home, baulked for a run over 200 metres out, one-paced under pressure.
Jumped awkwardly and taken back from a wide draw, trailed the field into straight saving ground on the turn, ran home one-paced
With leaders 3-wide to straight, unable to sustain effort over 200 metres out. (Tactic questioned)
Travelled within 2L of pace in 5th or 4th on the rail, faded under pressure from over 200 metres out.
Never better than midfield, wide into straight, one-paced when inconvenienced 200 metres out.
Settled well in midfield along the 2-path, brought wide to challenge 450M, closed off willingly to lead near 150M, well in control final stages.
Settled in 4th, well placed to strike turning for home, moved up to challenge for lead 250M but not pace of winner final stages.
Obtained a midfield spot on inside, 6Ls off the good pace in middle stages, came home well to claim 3rd near line.
Chased leader in a fast run race, led briefly early straight, outran by first 3 final 200M.
Held up in midfield 6Ls off the good pace, driven along 450M, made mild progress without posing serious threat to leaders.
Reserved near rear, held up 500M, 6Ls to make up turning home, stayed on without threat.
Began awkwardly, positioned behind midfield in a fast run race, raced keenly middle stages, kept on mildly final 300M, no threat to leaders.
Driven to lead setting fast pace for the first half of the race, caught by rivals 300M, couldn't find more and weakened.
Chased leaders, came under pressure 400M, soon couldn't keep up with rivals.
Stood flat-footed at start and lost ground, raced at the rear until 500M before making his move, failed to run on final 300M.
Settled behind midfield early stages, shuffled to near last home turn, came up empty in straight. (Jockey could offer no explanation for the disappointing run.)

Began smartly from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L on turn, kept on very well in straight to hold off the challengers late.
Commenced well, positioned 2 wide better than midfield, 3 lengths back turning in, finished off strongly to be nearest on line, just beaten by a neck.
Out with rest, raced slightly behind midfield on the outside, commenced move 400M, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to take a place, nearest finish.
Taken back to race at rear, 6 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, closed off well to make frame.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths or so back, very wide turning in, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Bumped on jumping, raced in midfield on the outside, 3 lengths or so back turning in, made some progress early in straight, peaked on run 100M, ran on evenly to the line. (Bled.)
Bumped on jumping, sent forward to race in 2nd, 3/4L back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 50M.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, ran on evenly thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, one-paced in the run home.
Bumped shortly after start, raced behind midfield on the inside, angled out 400M, 4 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)

Steadied after the start & shifted back to race at the tail. Moved three wide passing 600m, was the widest runner on cornering when still last before flying home down the outside to charge to lead at 50m & win very softly.

Raced in midfield away from the rail throughout. Moved three wide passing the 500m to avoid weakening rival, dashed well to share lead at 125m, passed quickly by winner in final 50m, narrowly held second. .

Got back to race third last away from the rail. Moved wider to improve passing the 450m, was very wide on cornering when still in second half, made some late ground down the outside late to just miss second.
Raced on the leaders back for the majority. Moved off the rail approaching the corner, dashed between runners to take lead soon after straightening, joined at the 125m, overrun for third late.

Raced just worse than midfield between runners. Improved to midfield down the back straight, shifted wider just before straightening, closed off steadily, despite hanging inwards to finish in midfield.
Raced in midfield along the rail. Was under 3L from the lead entering final section, stayed close to the rail on straightening, weakened a few lengths in late stages to be well held in midfield.

Had no early speed & drifted back to second last along the rail. Moved off the rail near the 600m, was held up on straightening when rearward before passing a couple of tiring rivals when finishing one paced to midfield.
Pushed forward to improve & raced outside the leader from the 1200m. Continued second approaching corner, hung outwards on straightening before peaking at the 250m & weakening quickly late.
Was trapped racing three wide without cover when just worse than midfield for the majority. Was ridden along from the 500m mark, before weakening a few lengths in the straight to be beaten over 7L.

Raced just worse than midfield along the rail. Was just over 4L from the lead entering final section, stayed close to the inside in the straight but did little in the run to the line & finished a well beaten third last.
Pushed forward to lead and set a strong pace for first two sections. Was headed soon after straightening before weakening quickly in last furlong to be a well beaten second last.
Obtained a nice position 1,1 from about the 1200m. Began losing ground before straightening & weakened badly to long last.
Settled behind midfield, switched out and improved inside 800M, made good progress in the Straight, closed off nicely.
Ridden along to lead on the rail, travel comfortably throughout, kept on well to hold 2nd.
Jumped only fairly, settled towards rear, showed some response when asked inside 200M, ran on evenly.
Settled in front of midfield, slightly improved rounding the Home Turn, one pace over the concluding stages.
Sat rear, angled out approaching the 400M, closed off okay.
Sat towards rear, angled out when entering the Straight, made minor progress thereafter (See Incident Report).
Sat midfield 2 wide, commenced to improve at 650M, slightly weakened at 200M.
Jumped awkwardly, sat in front of midfield on the rail, traveled okay, weakened and gave ground after 550M.
Sat midfield on the rail, limited response when asked, weakened and faded in the Straight (Dropped whip).
Ridden hard to chase the lead, traveled fairly in the early stages, no impression in the Straight (See Incident Report).

Showed speed after the start to lead. Joined by the runner-up near the 125m, looked destined for second but rallied hard in the final stages to kick back and despite drifting out in the late stages went on to win by a neck.

Raced prominently after start, improved after first bend to race second from the 1000m. Moved up to join lead near 125m, came together with leader who was shifting outwards, couldn't gain outright lead & was beaten a neck.
Had a nice run 1,1 for the majority. Peeled three wide on straightening, dashed ok but couldn't get to the first two in the straight & finished third, beaten just under 2L.

Raced on the leaders back for the majority. Was touch keen and threw head near the 900m, was just over a length form the lead approaching the corner battled on ok to be beaten 2.5L into forth in an improved effort.

Steadied from outside barrier & taken back to last. Stayed along the rail on cornering when still last and about 6L from the lead before making some late headway along rail in final furlong to finish a well held fifth.

Was bumped at the start & lost a length before racing near the rear. Continued in second half and about 5L from the lead on cornering before shifting outwards mid-straight & making some late closing ground to midfield.
Raced in midfield between runners throughout. Was just under 4L from the lead entering the last section & effectively held margin all the way to the line.

Was trapped racing three wide but with cover when worse than midfield throughout. Continued wide around the bend, was 4.5L from the lead entering final section before making no headway into deficit in straight.

Was trapped racing three wide without cover in midfield throughout. Was just over 3L from the lead entering final section, peaked on effort mid-straight before yielding some ground in last furlong after wide passage.

Steadied from second widest gate & taken back to race second last. Moved into three wide line down the back straight, continued back & wide entering last section when just under 6L from lead, made no headway in the straight.

Was slow to begin & bumped before mustering to improve to race just worse than midfield between runners. Was bumped & unbalanced near the 850m & lost a length. Began losing ground from the 550m mark & finished second last.

Was slow to begin before mustering to improve along the rail & race worse than midfield along the inside. Was bumped & unbalanced near 850m, was only 3L off lead at 400m before weakening poorly in straight to finish last.
Average to begin, raced at rear, 8 lengths back in the middle stages, made very good progress in straight, led close home.

Began well from gate 1, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, similar position on turn, kept to inside after straightening, hit the front 100M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner late.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back turning in, angled out early in straight, finished off well to take a place, nearest finish.
Made contact at start, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, there to turn, showed good response early in straight, peaked 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Crowded start, raced towards rear, 6 lengths or so back turning in, no clear run until final 50M, made good progress thereafter.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide in midfield, found rail near 600M, angled out 350M, made some progress in straight.
Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, 2 wide, shared lead turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 100M, weakened gradually final 50M.

Began awkwardly and made contact, sent forward to race prominently on the inside, shared lead turning in, kept on well early in straight, weakened final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.) (Blood in trachea.)
Bumped start, raced 3 wide better than midfield, 2 wide from 600M, angled out 350M, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Bumped start, trapped wide in midfield, no cover throughout, very wide into straight, one-paced in the run home.
Made contact at start, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from gate 11, raced at tail, detached 600M, finished tailed off, unacceptable performance.
Jumped with the field, showed no early speed, settled towards the rear, closed off strongly to score.
Sat just behind the leaders, hit the front at 100M, got ran down late, had every chance.
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide, made good progress in the Straight, had to checked at near 50M, still ran on.
Settled behind midfield on the rail, angled out at 250M, closed off fairly. (Lame right hind and sustained wound to the right hind pastern)
Settled midfield 2 wide between horses, lay in when under pressured, cannot be fully tested.
Settled behind the pace on the rail, limited response in the Straight. (See Incident Report)
Hard ridden early to assume the lead, weakened inside 150M.
Settled near the rear 2 wide, took some time to respond in the Straight, made some late headway
Sat midfield on the rail, made no impression. (See Incident Report)
Steadied after the start from a wide barrier, settled last, save ground along the rail, got badly hampered in the Straight and lost all chance.
Tracked leader 2 wide, weakened in the Straight. (See Incident Report) (Lame right front the next day)
Settled midfield 3 wide without cover, never a factor. (Heart Irregularity, Must Trial)
Settled in forward of midfield in 6th or 5th on the rail, gained closer to within 2L of pace into straight, fought on well to prevail inside final 100 metres.
Held up in rear after beginning from a wide draw, commenced move after bumped 600 metres out, switched wider into straight, stayed on well under pressure down the centre of the track.
Ridden to soon take up running setting a keen pace to back straight, kicked over 2L clear 700 metres out but came back to the main body of the field turning into straight, headed 100 metres out.
Settled in last few on the rail and waited with, commenced run over 500 metres out and given reminders into straight, ran on between runners to narrowly miss a place.
Obtained 2-wide position in 9th behind midfield, commenced move 3-wide 700 metres out running wide into straight, fought on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Keen in front early stages while taken back, settled 2-wide in 6th into back straight, renewed effort turning wide into home straight, kept on at the one pace without threatening.

Settled just worse than midfield on rail, came under pressure rounding home bend and saved ground into straight, snuck up to within 2L of pace over 200 metres out but unable to sustain effort inside final 70 metres.
Prominent and wide without cover, obtained cover in 4th early in back straight becoming 3rd inside the 500 metres, shifted ground upon straightening and gradually faded.
Settled within striking distance in 3rd on rail, gained 2nd 600 metres out, continued to make ground under pressure rounding home bend but dropped away quickly from 1L 2nd into straight.

Began well from a poor draw and gradually taken back, remained wide without cover in last few rounding first bend and trailed the field into back straight, renewed pressure on home bend but could find nothing.
Settled in midfield, yielded ground steadily from 700 metres out.
Ridden positively after moderate start from a wide-ish draw, chased race leader to 700 metres which hanging out, tired noticeably on home bend.
In touch with leaders, switched wide from 450M to challenge, responded well and ran on willing to lead near 50M.
In midfield early stages, wide no cover from 700M chasing leaders, hit lead 250M, caught by winner 50M. Clear from remainders.
Jumped fairly, held up in midfield, driven top of straight, stayed on to go 3rd 100M out, not reach first two.
Dropped back, settled towards the rear, swung wide into straight, ran on mildly to claim non-threatening 4th close home.
Tracked leader on inside, lacked a strong finishing effort on straightening, never a threat to leaders.
Reserved near the rear, saved ground on inside, stayed on without threatening.
Driven to lead, pressed by rival middle stages, headed 250M, faded towards the finish. (Jockey reminded to fully ride out to the finish)
Jumped well, eased back to a position behind midfield, came wide home turn, kept on final 300M without threat to leaders.
Jumped awkwardly and lost ground, settled at the rear further back than intended, shifted out top of straight to challenge, checked 150M before making limited progress to the line.
Jumped only fairly, chased leaders, struggled to keep up 450M, soon out of contention.
Positioned in midfield, came under pressure 600M out, already a spent force turning for home.
From widest gate caught wide no cover early stages, ridden forward to race outside the lead, badly unbalanced 300M when crowded for room, weakened.
