Average to begin, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, there to turn, showed good response in straight, hit the front 150M, kept on very well to the line and scored.
Began well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead 950M, headed 750M, 2nd turning in, hit the front approaching 200M, headed 150M, kept on well to take 2nd.
Began awkwardly and crowded, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear run until final 150M, closed off well to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Jumped well, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out 450M, not enough room early in straight, ran on evenly thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact at start, sent forward to race prominently on the inside, took the lead 750M, led by 3/4L turning in, peaked and headed near 200M, weakened gradually final 150M.
Made contact at start, raced in midfield on the inside, 3 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out 500M, no daylight early in straight, ran on evenly thereafter.
Crowded start, raced towards rear on the inside, angled out 550M, made minor progress early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Began well from a wide draw, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 wide from 700M, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced in midfield on the outside, 3-1/2L back, same margin back on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide towards rear, 6 lengths or so back on turn, made no impression in straight.
Bumped on jumping, raced behind midfield on the outside, 5 lengths or so back, very wide into straight, made no progress in the run home.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Out in line, raced prominently on the outside early, slightly taken back 750M, 3rd on turn, weakened early in straight.
Raced on outside of leader, established narrow lead 300M, kept on well final 200M when driven out.
Jumped awkwardly and lost ground, reserved in last, brought wide top of straight, closed off well to claim 2nd near line. (Jockey: instructed to ride his mount conservatively early stages.)

Soon lead, challenged by rival top of straight, outstayed by winner from 200M but refused to give in and fought hard to the finish. (Jockey suspended for 6 days for failing to ride out over the final stride.)
Chased leaders along the fence, attempted a run on the inside early straight but disappointed for a run near 250M, shifted lane and stayed on well to the line, just missed 3rd.
In 4th place always in touch, had every chance from top of straight, held by leaders final stages.
Settled midfield, kept on steadily from top of straight but lacked the needed response to challenge leaders.
Jumped awkwardly, held up near rear, ran on mildly over final 400M but not going the pace to challenge.
Held up in mid-division, kept on one paced behind leaders on straightening, raced in restricted room after 150M.
Settled in a position behind midfield, shifted out from fence 600M out and soon ridden along, held up from 250M and unable to secure clear running from that point. (Jockey questioned re his riding.)
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, traveled comfortably, made good progress over the final 150M, closed off nicely.
Sat in front of midfield on the rail, traveled strongly, showed some dash over the concluding stages, kept on well for 2nd.
Ridden along to share lead until the Turn, raced keenly in the early and middle stages, responded fairly well when asked (See Incident Report).
Sat handy, slightly lay out in the Straight, ran on evenly.
Sat midfield 2 wide, commenced to improve rounding the Turn, lay out over the final 100M, ran on fairly.
Settled towards rear, switched out entering the Home Straight, show some response under pressure, closed off okay.
Slow to jump, settled worse than midfield 2 wide, no clear run and steadied until 150M.
Jumped okay, ridden hard to share lead, slightly weakened in the Straight, further dropped back inside 250M (Bled, Must trial).
Settled in front of midfield, traveled fairly, held up until 250M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped only fairly, sat behind midfield, limited response when asked, one pace.
Settled worse than midfield 3 wide, raced keenly from 950M, weakened passing 250M, never a danger.
Sat midfield on the rail, weakened and faded passing 200M.
Settled midfield, raced wide and without cover throughout, never a threat.
Sat rear, never improve, no contention.
Raced in midfield along the rail. Came off the rail on straightening, shifted over heels to get clear mid-straight before making continual ground to steal the lead in final few strides to win.
Pushed forward to lead. Dashed clear of immediate challengers mid-straight, continued in front until being caught in the shadows of the post.

Drifted back to race last. Shifted out to be the widest runner on straightening, asked for full effort mid-straight & closed off strongly down the outside to charge to fast finishing third late in fast run final section.
Bumped at the start before racing in midfield away from the rail. Moved wider on cornering, closed off steadily down the outside to be beaten under 2L into fourth.
Showed speed to share lead early & raced outside the leader for the majority. Contused in second but leader had raced over a length clear mid-straight, battled on but weakened a few lengths late.

Got back to race second last along the rail. Moved off the rail just before straightening, was just over 3L from the lead entering last section & effectively maintained that deficit all the way to the line.
Bumped at the start before drifting back to race third last. Came wider on cornering when 3.5L from the lead before finishing off only fairly in the fast run final section to be beaten just under 5L.
Raced fourth along the rail after start & improved to race on the leaders back from about the 700m. Travelled strongly approaching final corner before giving a few lengths to be beaten 5L on line.

Got a nice position 1,1 throughout. Was niggled along just before straightening, entered last section just over 1L from the lead, peaked on run mid-straight & weakened plainly in last furlong to be beaten over 7L in last.
Out with rest, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out 600M, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to score.
Jumped with them, sat a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out 500M, took the lead 300M, kept on well but not able to hold off the winner 200M, finished 2nd.
Slow to begin, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, bumped heavily 350M, finished off strongly to take a place, nearest on line.
Away well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, a bit closer on turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide towards rear, wider turning in, bumped heavily and unbalanced 350M, closed off well without threatening.
Began well from gate 14, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, ran on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.) (Lost left front plate.)
Began fairly from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, showed limited response early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened thereafter.
Bumped start, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, ran on evenly thereafter.
Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead 1150M, led by 1/2L in the middle stages, headed 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Began smartly, took the early lead, headed 1150M, 1/2L back in the middle stages, retook the lead 500M, peaked and headed 300M, weakened final furlong.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Slowly away, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Away well, raced 3 wide with cover slightly behind midfield, wider turning in, checked near 350M, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with no cover, a length or so back, there to turn, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect. (See Racing Incidents.)
Broke nicely, settled in front of midfield 2 wide, travelled comfortably throughout, switched out to 3 wide at 600M, and ran on very nicely, always doing enough.
Jumped alertly, settled near midfield on the rail, closed off nicely, can't hold off the winner.
Sat handy just behind the pace, kept on nicely for 3rd.
Tracked leader 2 wide, kept on well until weakened slightly at 100M. (See Incident Report)
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, saved every ground, closed off fairly. (See Incident Report)
Restrained early and moved across towards the rail at the start, settled towards the rear, stayed on okay.
Settled midfield 2 wide, only one pace when asked.
Settled near the rear 2 wide, had some trouble obtaining clear running in the Straight, and never seriously tested.
Broke nicely and led, weakened inside 250M. (See Incident Report)
Settled midfield on the rail, made little impression.
Sat last on the rail early, moved out to 2 wide down the back Straight, shifted out to 3 wide to improve at 800M, limited response in the Straight.
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide, never a factor.
Raced behind midfield on the rail, never in contention.
Ridden along before settling in 2L 4th 2-wide, came to challenge soon after straightening and gained upper hand close to home.
Soon took up running attempting to make all but only to be over-shadowed final few strides.
Settled one back in 3rd on rail, did not find much room early in straight, came to challenge inside final 200 metres but never able to threaten.
Jumped awkwardly, settled just outside race leader, unable to sustain effort inside final 250 metres.
Settled mainly in 5th towards rear of the small field, crowded and lost position 900 metres out, ran home one-paced.
Soon recovered from moderate start to 5th in rear of midfield, travelling keenly throughout early stages and steadied and lost position about 1000 metres out, ran home one-paced under pressure.
Began moderately, always well behind and never seen with a chance.
Settled 4th in a 5 runner race, cruised to the fore 350M, led mid-straight, strongly challenged by rival final stages, just held on at the line.
Reserved in last in a 5 runner race, ran on strongly passing 250M, just denied at the post. (Jockey lost whip 300M.)
Pressed leader on outside, vied for lead from 500M, outsprinted by first 2 mid-straight, held on for non-threatening 3rd.
Obliged to make early use when obtaining the lead, set fast pace up front and was taken on by rival from 500M, could find no extra 200M.
Jumped fairly, tracked the pace, came under pressure 500M, failed to respond on straightening.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide towards rear, moved a bit closer after passing 1250M, 3 lengths or so back in the middle stages, commenced move 550M, finished off very strongly to score.
Away well, raced in 2nd, travelled well to turn, hit the front 400M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 100M.
Began well, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1-1/2L, challenged by rival from 500M, peaked and headed 400M, kept on evenly to the line.
Average to begin, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, made some progress in straight, crowded close home.
Began only fairly, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on same pace in straight.
Began fairly, taken back to race at tail, 4 lengths or so back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Commenced well, positioned 2 wide, 2-1/2L back, similar position on turn, ran on evenly in straight.
Taken back from gate 9, raced towards rear on the outside, 4 lengths or so back, one-paced in the run home.

Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide behind midfield early, sent forward after entering the back straight, raced in 3rd in the middle stages, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter. (Lame right front leg next day.)
Began fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, slightly improved on turn, finished off very strongly, easily scored.
Out in line, raced behind midfield on the inside, 2 wide after passing 700M, 5 to 6 lengths back turning in, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, similar position on turn, showed good response early in straight, peaked on run 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, found rail near 750M, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, closed off well to make frame without threatening.
Moderately away, sent forward to race in 2nd, challenged the leader turning in, took the lead 400M, peaked and headed 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Shifted out at start and made contact, raced slightly better than midfield on the inside, angled out 600M, 2 to 3 wide turning in, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Began smartly, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, 2 wide from 550M, no clear run early in straight, cleared 200M, failed to make any progress thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from gate 13, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths or so back turning in, passed some tired runners in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped awkwardly, raced 2 wide towards rear, 3 wide from 700M, 5 lengths or so back turning in, one-paced in the run home.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 9 lengths back turning in, passed some tired runners in straight.
Jumped awkwardly, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Made contact at start, raced slightly better than midfield on the outside, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, weakened early in straight.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, challenged by rival turning in, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened and eased thereafter. (Bled.)

Jumped only fairly before improving position and then racing on the leaders back. Moved over the leaders heals approaching the 300m mark, dashed well to move to lead at passing 100m & went on to win well.

Jumped awkwardly before shifting across behind runners to the rail & then racing midfield. Stayed along the rail on straightening when about 3.5L from lead, closed off well & improved to take second place in final 25m.

Jumped fairly, was crowded & consequently raced worse than midfield along the rail. Stayed along rail on straightening, was 5L behind entering last section before making good late ground, moving to 3rd in final strides.
Showed customary early speed to lead. Dropped off immediate challenger on straightening, was still 1L clear of nearest rival at 200m mark before being caught for third in final few strides.
Raced in midfield away from the rail. Was just under 4L from the lead on straightening, held up for clear running passing the 300m before getting clear at the 250m & closing off steadily late.

Raced just worse than midfield away from the rail. Shifted outwards on straightening and bumped, entered last section 5L from the lead before making some late ground down the outside to be beaten just over 2L into midfield.
Raced three wide without cover in midfield throughout. Was just under 4L from the lead on straightening, was bumped at the 200m when finishing off steadily & was only fair in the concluding stages.

Was shifted across behind runners from the outside gate & raced at the tail. Stayed along the rail on straightening when 6L from lead before making strong late ground in the final stages when finishing off close to the rail.

Jumped only fairly before making up ground and racing in midfield along rail. Moved off the rail just prior to straightening, was only 2.5L from the lead entering last section, finished off only moderately in last furlong.
Had a nice run 1,1 throughout. Was ridden along passing the 500m mark, was 3L from the lead entering last section, was bumped passing the 250m mark before weakening a length or so in final stages.

Raced just worse than midfield when three wide with cover. Came wider on straightening, was bumped at the 400m mark when 5L from the lead before finishing off steadily down the outside without ever looking a real threat.

Drifted back from a wide gate after the start & raced rearward when wide with cover. Continued back and wide around bend, shifted outwards to be the widest runner at the 400m when 6.5L from the lead, never really ran on.

Shifted across behind runners from a wide draw & raced rearward. Shared last place from the 800m, came under hard ridding before straightening, was just under 8L from the lead in straightening, never improved.
Pushed forward to race outside the leader. Was beaten early in the straight & weakened poorly in final furlong to be beaten a long last. (Failed to run out 1400m  rider).

Average to begin, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on the inside, same margin back on turn, finished off very strongly to score.
Began well, sent forward to race in 2nd, a length back, same position on turn, hit the front 200M, peaked and headed 100M, stayed on evenly to take 2nd.
Made contact at start, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off well to take a place.
Taken back from gate 12, raced at rear, 6 lengths or so back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to make frame without threatening the first few.
Commenced well, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, kept on well early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at rear on the inside, 7 lengths or so back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced in midfield on the outside, similar position on turn, one-paced in straight.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide in midfield, hampered and dropped towards rear 550M, 5 lengths back turning in, one-paced in the run home. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact at start, raced towards rear on the outside, moved a bit closer after passing 600M, 5 lengths back turning in, made no progress in straight.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced better than midfield on the outside, 2 lengths back, same margin back on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Began well from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length turning in, peaked and headed 200M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away well, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, hampered and dropped to rear 550M, last turning in, failed to make any progress in straight.

Raced just worse than midfield early. Drifted further back near half-way, moved into three wide line near 750m. Swung very wide on straightening before flying home down the outside to charge to lead at 75m & win going away.

Began awkwardly & bumped with rival before being taken back to last. Continued last approaching the final corner before shifting outwards & making late ground in the concluding stages to charge to second inside last 50m.

Steadied & taken back to third last after start before commencing a mid-race move from 900m circling field to take the lead passing the 700m. Was over a length clear on straightening, held lead until the 75m mark, held third.
Began awkwardly & bumped rival before racing third last along rail. Continued rearward along the rail around bend, was 6L behind on straightening before making some late ground to be beaten under 3L.

Pushed forward after start, improved to take lead approaching 1200m before being headed in the lead near the 700m. Over a length from the lead on straightening before drifting left when finishing off steadily to midfield.

Shifted across behind runners to race in midfield along the rail throughout. Stayed close to the rail entering last section when 4.5L from lead before finishing off only steadily to be beaten a similar margin on line.

Ridden forward to lead early before being crossed & racing on the leaders back from 1150m. Continued to race in fourth place entering last section, shifted back inwards after straightening before weakening in last furlong.

Bumped after the start before racing just worse than midfield when three deep with cover. Improved to midfield at about half-way when continuing wide. Was very wide on cornering before finishing off one paced to midfield.

Raced in midfield along the rail before coming off the rail after 1100m mark when racing keenly. Was shuffled further back after half-way when continuing between horses. Was 5L behind on straightening but failed to improve.

Ridden at start, raced on the leaders back early before coming off the rail near 1000m. Just under 4L from lead entering last section when between runners, was held up near the 300m, shifted out but only weakened thereafter.

Ridden with the whip after jumping, raced 1,1 momentarily before racing second, away from the rail & without cover from the 1000m. Raced third from the 700m, was hard ridden passing the 500m before weakening out poorly.

Was trapped racing three wide without cover after first bend. Improved to third place momentarily near half-way when continuing wide without cover. Was beaten on straightening before weakening badly in the straight, last.
Settled towards rear 2 wide, traveled smoothly, commence to improve and switch out rounding the Turn, made good progress in Straight, finished off nicely.
Sat midfield, traveled okay, lay in over the final 100M, stayed on well to grab 2nd.
Settled midfield, angled out, traveled wide and challenged the leader from 950M, slightly weakened inside 200M, closed off okay (See Incident Report).
Sat behind midfield on the rail, traveled keenly in the middle stages, one pace after 300M.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, switched out rounding the Turn, made some progress passing 100M, ran on evenly.
Settled towards rear on the rail, traveled fairly, no clear run in the early Straight until 150M, closed off okay.
Ridden hard to share lead 2 wide, weakened in the Straight, limited response when asked.
Sat handy 2 wide, made minor progress, weakened inside 200M.
Sat rear 2 wide, raced at rear throughout, no impression.
Jumped nicely, settled handy, was crowded and checked inside 250M, finished off only fairly.
Sat rear on the rail, raced at rear throughout, no contention.
Ridden along to lead, slightly weakened making the Turn, steadied when being crowded inside 250M, could not quicken thereafter.

Allowed to drift back from wide gate & raced just worse than midfield when three wide. Pushed very wide from 500m, extremely wide on straightening before flying home down the outside to charge to lead at 50m & go on to win.

Raced in midfield away from the rail. Eased wider near the 500m, entered last section just under 3L from lead, was the second widest on straightening before making good late ground to move to second late.

Was steadied from the widest gate after 100m & taken back to third last. Was over 4L from the lead on straightening before dashing well between runners passing the 200m, closed well late but couldn't hold out wide closers.
Mustered speed after the start to improve to race in midfield along the rail. Was only 2.25L from the lead at the 400m, moved off the rail on straightening before closing well to be beaten under 2L.
Had a nice run in midfield just behind the speed. Shifted wider to get clear running just before straightening, closed off steadily all the way to the line to be beaten under 2L.

Had customary early speed to hold the rail in a line of four contesting the lead early. Was shaded by outside two rivals taking first bend, improved to again share lead from 400m, held narrow lead until 125m, swamped late.

Drifted back to race third last along the rail. Was just under 4L form the lead entering last sections, stayed along the rail in straight and made up a length or so to be beaten just under 3L into midfield.

Slow to begin & raced second last in the middle stages. Was awkward & brushed rail near the 550m bend, was still second last on straightening before passing a few tiring rivals when making up a few lengths, no threat.

Ridden forward after start, was three wide in a line of four contesting the early lead before coming back just before the first bend to race behind leading trio. Had clear running on straightening but weakened late.

Began awkwardly before mustering speed, raced the widest in a line of four contesting early lead. Gained narrow lead near the 650m when three wide, shared lead again on straightening before weakening in final furlong.

Crowded after the start & got back to race at the tail. Was a clear last approaching corner when just under 8L from the lead, stayed close to rail in straight but couldn't make challenging ground despite limited riding late.

Showed speed after the start, was two wide in a line of four at the front all challenging for the early lead before continuing to gallop between runners around the bend. Peaked on effort early in straight & weakened to last.
Away well, sent forward to take the early lead, headed near 850M, sat right behind the leader in the middle stages, hit the front 150M, kept on well to the line and scored. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well, raced 2 wide in midfield early, commenced move 1000M, took the lead 850M, led by 1/2L turning in, peaked and headed 150M, kept on evenly to the line.
Out in line, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, 1/2L back on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 8 lengths back turning in, made very good progress in straight to make frame, nearest on line.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced at rear on the outside early, sent forward 1100M, raced 3 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back in the middle stages, finished off evenly.
Began fairly, raced in midfield on the inside, 3 lengths or so back, 2 wide from 600M, wider after passing 400M, made some progress in straight.
Taken back from gate 9, positioned 5 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, made some progress in straight.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped with them, raced behind midfield on the inside, 2 wide after entering the back straight, very wide turning in, peaked early in straight, one-paced thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, dropped to midfield on turn, made no progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide towards rear, 6 lengths or so back on turn, very wide into straight, made no progress in straight.
Out with rest, raced 2 wide behind midfield, inconvenience near 1000M, 3 wide in the middle stages, failed to close off in straight.
Broke nicely and ridden along early to led, travelled comfortably throughout, kicked clear at the top of the Straight, kept on well to score. (See Incident Report)
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, closed off nicely, best stride late.
Caught 3 wide early on, pressed on to track leader, kept on fairly, just held 3rd.
Settled in a prominent position 2 wide, only one pace when asked.
Settled midfield on the rail, ran on fairly.
Settled towards the rear 2 wide, stayed on nicely.
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide, made some progress despite shifting ground. (See Incident Report)
Settled at the rear on the rail, only able to pass weakened rivals.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, limited response in the Straight. (See Incident Report)
Raced at the rear 2 wide, made no impression.
Settled last 3 wide, never in contention.
Settled worse than midfield on the rail, never a factor.

Settled towards rear early stages, travelled keenly in back straight pulling forward to midfield 7th over 3L back 3-wide onto home bend, went widest into straight, quickened well under pressure to assert authority 100 metres out.
Broke well before settling one back in 3rd on rail, hit the front briefly over 200 metres out, no answer to winner's late surge close stages.
Broke well before gradually taken back towards the rear on rail, remained similar into straight hugging the rail, fought on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Settled in 4th over 2L back, baulked for a run over 200 metres out, sustained good progress in closing stages.
Broke well before settling in midfield on rail, niggled along in similar position into straight, baulked for a run until obtaining a clear run 200 metres out, ran home one-paced.
Pressed forward from a wide draw settling one back in 2nd 2-wide, came under pressure to challenge 450 metres out but unable to quicken to threaten.
Settled well behind, commenced move 3-wide rounding home bend, opted for inner route on straightening but forced to change course 100 metres out, made no further impression.
Began well settling in rear of midfield, lost position under pressure rounding home bend, found nothing in straight.
Began awkwardly losing ground and soon shifted across for rails run at the back, niggled along from over 800 metres out but couldn't find much.
Crowded at start, travelled wide without cover in midfield in 5th some 3L back, commenced move over 600 metres out but dropped out from wide into straight.

Began awkwardly from the widest draw travelling wide without cover in last few, gained slightly closer around the 900 metres, one of the widest rounding home bend and into straight, soon weakened under pressure.
Ridden forward from moderate start obtaining rails run in front onto first bend, dropped away quickly inside final 250 metres.
Crowded shortly after the start, from wide draw taken across behind runners, 5Ls off the pace 400M, ran on well between horses, got up close home.
Held up towards the rear, swung wide into straight, closed off well down outside, got up for 2nd near line.
From draw 10 caught wide no cover chasing leaders, switched wider on straightening, battled well to the line and getting up for 3rd in a close finish.
Allowed an uncontested lead, drifted to center of track on straightening, fought on to hold lead until headed closing stages.
Caught racing 3-wide towards the rear, swung widest for home, closed off well to take joint 5th, beaten just under 1L.
Unhurried, dropped back to race in last, 7Ls to make up approaching straight, finished off final 400M fastest. Nearest finish.
Jumped awkwardly, in touch behind leaders, held every chance from top of straight before fading over closing stages.
Crowded on jumping, settled in midfield along the 2-path, put in a mild bid from 300M, always held by leaders in a blanket finish.
Chased leader, fought on one paced from 300M, no serious threat from mid-straight. (Jockey said his mount dipped near 900M and didn't travel well thereafter.)
From draw 5 ended up racing 3-wide in midfield, kept on fairly over final 300M, not beaten far but always held by leaders.
From wide draw taken soon across behind runners, raced in midfield along the inside, couldn't go on passing 250M.
In touch behind leaders, came under serious pressure 500M, weakened rapidly turning into straight. (No Vet findings.)

Jumped well from gate 1, raced in 2nd, easy run to turn, showed good response in straight, hit the front 100M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Average to begin, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off strongly to take 2nd, always held.
Quickly into stride, sent forward to take the lead, led by 2 lengths turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked 200M, headed 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, angled out 450M, finished off well to make frame without threatening.
Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 6 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Taken back from gate 13, raced 2 wide at rear, 8 to 9 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight, nearest finish.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide behind midfield, no cover from 900M, 6 lengths or so back turning in, finished off evenly.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out 500M, finished off evenly.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the inside, 10 lengths back turning in, made some progress early in straight, slightly inconvenienced near 200M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Bumped on jumping, race 3 wide with cover towards rear, 9 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the outside, 9 to 10 lengths back on turn, showed some response early in straight, no clear run from 200M, eased final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well, tracked leaders, 2 wide, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Moderately away, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Taken back from gate 9, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened and eased final furlong.
Began moderately before travelling amongst the leaders, held narrow advantage coming onto course proper, driven clear inside final 150 metres.
Broke well settling behind midfield near the centre of the track, came to challenge under pressure coming onto course proper, ran on well under pressure without threatening.
Settled in clear last on stands rails, shifted towards the centre of the track passing the 400 metres, charged home strongly inside final 180 metres despite racing greenly.
Inconvenienced at start settling amongst leaders near the centre of the track, came under pressure inside final 200 metres but unable to sustain effort shortly after.
Jumped awkwardly settled some 3L back in rear on stands rails, given reminders from 350 metres out, produced good late impression under pressure.
Well there on stands rails, came under pressure to hold place inside final 350 metres but had nothing to give.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, travelled within 2L of pace to course proper, badly bumped and unbalanced over 350 metres out, never recovered.
Settled just over 2L off the pace in 8th, slightly further back some 3L back coming onto course proper, steadied for a run 200 metres out, made no further impression.
Shared early pace, weakened noticeably inside final 400 metres.
Began well settling amongst leaders, weakened under pressure past the 400 metres.
Never better than midfield, given reminders just before hampered 350 metres out, never recovered.
Well there early, gradually drifted 2L back coming onto course proper, looked beaten before badly hampered over 350 metres out, never recovered.
Settled in midfield some 3L off the pace, came under pressure coming onto course proper before badly hampered over 350 metres out, never recovered.
Settled rear 2 wide, traveled strongly, angled out rounding the Turn, made great progress over the final 200M, stayed on well to win.
Sat behind midfield, angled out making the Turn, responded well when asked inside 250M, closed off strongly.
Ridden hard to lead on the rail, traveled smoothly, slightly weakened over the concluding 75M, kept on nice to the line (See Incident Report).
Settled towards rear 2 wide, lay out inside the 250M, continued to lay out to the finish.
Jumped only fairly, blundered shortly after the start, sat rear on the rail, traveled okay, one pace.
Sat midfield, traveled fairly, ran on evenly (See Incident Report).
Jumped only fairly, settled towards rear, commenced to improve inside 600M, but limited when asked, weakened inside 200M.
Chased the lead 3 wide, traveled keenly in the early stages, weakened and faded passing the 150M (Substantial blood in trachea).
Sat handy, could not be quickened in the Straight, one pace to the finish.
Settled in front of midfield, traveled fairly, weakened over the final 100M (See Incident Report).
Sat in front of midfield, raced wide and without cover from 750M, limited when asked, no impression.
Settled worse than midfield, raced wide and without cover throughout, dropped back quickly after making the Turn, never a threat.
Had a nice run third on the rail for the majority. Shifted over the heels of the leading pair on straightening, dashed up to take lead at the 150m & drew away late to win by 2L.

Showed customary early speed to lead narrowly before sharing lead after first furlong when racing away from rail. Improved to take half-length advantage from 700m, joined & headed by winner at 150m, held second narrowly.

Raced in midfield but was trapped racing three wide without cover. Hung outwards around bend, was only 2.5L from lead on straightening before finishing off steadily down the outside to just miss second on line.

Bumped heavily soon after the start, was rearward early before improving to race in midfield along the rail. Was 3L from lead on straightening before finishing off well nearer the inside to be just behind the placed horses.

Ridden forward after start before getting nice run 1,1 from the 1000m. Eased three wide passing the 500m, was only 1.5L from the lead on straightening was still in third place at furlong pole, finished fairly late stages.
Raced in midfield between runners for the majority. Was steadied from heels near the 600m when racing keenly. Was under 3L from the lead entering last section before finishing off fairly to midfield.
Drifted back from widest draw & raced three wide with cover when just worse than midfield throughout. Was just under 4L from the lead entering last section, finished off fairly to line.

Had some speed after start, allowed to drift back from wide gate but raced four wide without cover when worse than midfield. Continued very wide around bend, was 3.5L from lead at 400m, could only finish moderately late.
Was slow to begin, crossed down to the rail and raced second last. Improved to third last from the 700m, was 4.5L from the lead entering last section and filed to make any headway in the straight.

Showed speed after the start to hold the rail & share the lead after the first furlong. Was shaded in the lead by the outside horse form the 700m, was beaten early in the straight & weakened to be beaten 7.5L.

Was slow to begin & got back to race third last after start. Was relegated to second last passing the 700m, was just over 6L from the lead entering last section when continuing second last before doing nothing in straight.

Was bumped heavily soon after the start & then had no speed & was last after the first furlong. Continued a clear last in the middle stages, was 7.5L from the lead entering last section & did nothing in the straight.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, a bit closer on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared after passing 200M, finished off very strongly, won by 3/4L.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, shared lead with rival on turn, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner final 50M.
Jumped with them, raced behind midfield on the inside, angled out 500M, made good progress in straight to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Slightly slow out, raced towards rear on the inside, 8 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear run until 150M, closed off well to make frame without threatening.
Out with rest, raced 2 wide, 7 lengths back, 3 wide from 750M, moved closer on turn, made good progress early in straight, no extra final 150M.
Jumped with them, raced prominently on the outside, shared lead on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away with them, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, bumped 400M, finished off evenly.
Jumped well, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear run in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)

Began well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, allowed rival to cross near 800M, a length or so back on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared 150M, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)

Moderately away from the widest draw, raced behind midfield on the outside early, moved closer after passing 1300M, 2 to 3 lengths back in the middle stages, showed limited response early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Out in line, raced 3 wide, a length or so back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Began awkwardly, raced towards rear on the outside, 7 to 8 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Slightly slow out, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Broke well and assumed the lead, kept on well to the line.
Jumped nicely and ridden to be prominent, moved to 3 wide rounding the Home Turn, made decent progress in the Straight to get 2nd.
Settled midfield on the rail, held up early in the Straight, ran on nicely when in the clear. (See Incident Report)
Showed good early speed and sat just behind the leader, kept on but unable to further quicken.
Restrained towards the rear from the outside barrier, made its run along the rail, stayed on fairly.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, pushed out to 4 wide entering the Home Straight, only one pace when asked.
Broke a step slow, settled at the rear on the rail, improved along the rail at the 600M, limited response in the Straight.
Caught 3 wide no cover midfield, 5 wide when entering the Straight, got hampered near the 200M, never seriously tested. (See Incident Report)
Settled midfield between horses, made no impression.
Raced 4 wide without cover worse than midfield, showed some dash at the top of the Straight, run peaked soon after.
Raced at the rear 2 wide, made little progress.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, weakened in the Straight.
Raced near the rear 3 wide, got crowded and steadied near the 200M, never tested.
Raced near the rear, never a factor.

Settled not far off the pace in joint 4th, gained closer to leaders when pace slackened rounding home bend, quickened well to gain upper hand over 100 metres out and just held off runner-up's strong late challenge.

Crowded at start before travelling keenly in rear of midfield in 7th on the rail, switched out to challenge approaching the final corner, ran on well inside final 250 metres to just fail to get up on line.
Broke well settling not far off the pace in 4th 2-wide, commenced move 4-wide in 2nd into straight holding every chance early on, unable to sustain effort inside final 50 metres.
Settled in last few from moderate start, went one of the widest turning for home, ran on dourly inside final 300 metres down the centre of the track and did best work late.
Slowly away and soon taken across to the rail in rear, travelled one from last to straight hugging inside rail, produced good late impression closing stages.

Soon recovered to joint 5th just over 2L back from moderate start, drifted 3L back 1000 metres out and further away around the bend, shifted 5-wide into straight, unable to quicken under pressure to challenge.
Soon took up on the rail after the first 250 metres, held slender advantage until joined early in home straight, found no extra and swamped inside final 150 metres.

With leaders early stages, drifted 1L back to 3rd coming onto home bend, inconvenienced 700 metres out but recovered well to hold every chance early in straight, dropped out tamely inside final 150 metres.
Began well from a wide draw, travelled wide with leaders in back straight and 2-wide in 2nd rounding home bend, weakened out of contention upon straightening.
Jumped awkwardly from a wide draw before settling just worse than midfield in 8th 2-wide, commenced move rounding home bend and one of the widest turning into straight, found nothing in straight.
Never a factor.
From draw 10 moved up to take the lead passing 1000M, steadied the pace middle stages, found plenty under pressure final 300M and held off pursuing rivals comfortably.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners, settled at the rear along inside, brought outwards from 400M, closed off well to go 2nd near line, not reach winner.
Reserved in midfield 3-wide, ran on steadily from 400M but not going the pace to challenge leader.
Crowded after the start, settled down midfield, put in a mild bid from 400M, ran on steadily to the line but never a threat to the runaway winner.
Held up behind midfield, stayed on moderately from 400M, always held by leaders.
Restrained behind midfield, switched wide on straightening, ran on only fairly and was never a threat. (Jockey: disadvantaged by the pace steadying in middle stages.)
Crowded after the start, ended up at the rear, gave limited response on straightening and ran past beaten horses only.
Chased leader, kept on same pace early straight, no extra passing 200M.
Never far off from leaders in a steadily run race, moved up to challenge for lead 500M, run ended mid-straight and weakened away. (Jockey : raced keenly early and middle stages.)
Travelled 3-wide towards the rear, went wider from 500M, found disappointingly little on straightening.
Driven forward, relinquished lead 1000M to race in a trailing spot , weakened from 300M. (Jockey was told he made an error of judgement 1200M when he didn't continue to ride his mount forward.)
Clean jump, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably in the middle stages, kept on very well in straight and scored.
Out with rest, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, closed off well to take 2nd, always held.

Jumped with them, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared 150M, finished off well to take a place without threatening the first two.
Out in line, positioned 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, similar position on turn, showed good response early in straight, peaked on run 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out 500M, unable to obtain clear run until 200M, made some progress thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out 550M, made contact 450M, finished off evenly.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Began well from gate 1, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 550M, 4 lengths back turning in, kept on same pace in straight.

Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide towards rear, 3 wide from 850M, carried wider 550M, made contact early in straight, hard ridden 400M but only showed limited response, bumped and unbalanced near 250M, ran on evenly to the line.
Bumped on jumping, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off evenly.
Away well, raced prominently on the outside, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M.
Taken back from gate 14, raced at rear on the outside, very wide into straight, one-paced in the run home.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, one-paced in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, led by 2 lengths turning in, kept on well in straight to hold off the challengers, won by a head.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, finished off strongly, just beaten by a head.
Bumped shortly after start, taken back to race at tail, still 9 lengths back turning in, finished off very strongly to take a place, nearest on line.
Bumped start, raced in midfield on the inside, 4 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, closed off well to make frame without threatening.
Began only fairly, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, a bit closer on turn, no clear run early in straight, ran on evenly thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact at start, raced in midfield on the outside, 4-1/2L back, similar position on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide behind midfield early, found rail approaching 800M, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, ran on evenly thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide better than midfield, similar position on turn, kept on same pace in straight.
Made contact at start, taken back to race 2 wide behind midfield, 7 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made no impression in straight.
Fast into stride, raced in 2nd, 2 lengths or so back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.

Made contact at start, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length turning in, kept on well in straight to hold off the challengers.
Made contact shortly after start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide turning in, closed off well to take 2nd, always held.
Slightly slow out, raced at tail, 4 lengths or so back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Average to begin, raced in 2nd, a length or so back on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Shifted in at start and made contact, raced 3 wide with cover slightly behind midfield, 3 lengths or so back turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Made contact at start, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on well early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Made contact at start, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, one-paced in straight.
Away well, taken back to race 2 wide towards rear, 4 lengths back turning in, made some progress early in straight, peaked 150M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Moderately away, tracked leaders on the outside, 2 lengths or so back turning it, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Never far off the pace, within striking distance from leaders 400M, ran on willingly to lead near 100M, drew away.
Pursued from mid-division, bustled along home turn, stayed on well to go 2nd near line.
Moved up to press leader along the 2-path, kept on steadily over final 300M, not finishing pace of first 2 late.
Jumped well, raced keenly in a 3-wide spot outside leaders, kept on one paced in the straight and was well held by leaders in the finish. (Jockey questioned riding tactics.)
Soon led, pressed by rivals mid-stages, kept on well early straight, headed near 100M then faded to finish 5th.
Taken back to race near the rear, 4Ls to make up 400M, made some progress in the straight without threatening first few.
Fractious as the start was effected and slowly away, raced towards the rear, not quickened passing 300M and failed to threaten.
Slow to begin, lacked pace ended up racing at the rear, never involved.
Slow to jump, settled rear, traveled comfortably, switched out to the center of the track entering the Straight, showed some dash over the final 200M, stayed on well to win.
Sat in front of midfield on the rail, traveled smoothly, angled out rounding the Turn, made good progress in the Straight, closed off nicely (Must BT).
Jumped awkwardly, settled in front of midfield, switched out making the Turn, responded nicely when asked.
Settled midfield, took off to lead inside 900M, made some progress in the early Straight, ran on evenly to the line (See Incident Report).
Sat handy, commenced to improve approaching 650M, one pace entering the Straight.
Settled behind midfield, limited response when asked, ran on fairly.
Settled towards rear, made little progress over the concluding stages, no impression.
Chased the lead on the rail, traveled okay, slightly weakened approaching 550M, bumped near 100M.
Jumped only fairly, sat towards rear, was steadied near 1200M, again was crowded near 100M, could not be ridden out thereafter.
Chased the lead 2 wide, weakened in the Straight, was crowded and checked passing 100M.
Ridden along to lead, traveled okay, weakened passing 400M and faded (Substantial blood in the trachea, Must BT, See Incident Report).
Had a nice run third on the rail in the early & middle stages. Improved to second just before straightening, dashed to lead early in the straight before going on to win easily.
Raced in midfield along the rail throughout. Had clear running on straightening before closing well to move to second near the 125m, no match for winner but ran ok.

Got back to race third last along the rail. Shared last place from the 550m, was just under 7L from the lead entering last section before making late headway to steal well beaten third place in final stride.

Raced in midfield away from the rail throughout. Eased wider near the 500m and wider again passing the 400m when 4.5L from the lead, finished off steadily down the outside & just missed a placing on line.

Was slow to begin by about 4L before making up ground after the start to race in midfield along the rail. Came away from the rail just before cornering when about 3L from lead before finishing off one paced in the straight.
Pushed forward to lead. Was headed in the lead by the winner early in the straight before weakening to be beaten 5L into midfield.

Steadied after start & taken back towards the rear. Relegated to least near 650m, shifted wider near 400m when still last & 7L behind, was the widest in the straight & passing a few tiring rivals without threatening.

Lifted feet at the start before shifting to inside & settling at the tail. Moved into three wide line down back straight, had a few runners behind after 600m bend, was the widest on straightening but failed to improve.

Had a nice run 1,1 in the early & middle stages. Was momentarily steadied near 450m before coming under hard riding soon after, bumped at the 200m when giving ground before ultimately being beaten over 6L.

Pushed forward and race second away from the rail. Continued second when 2L behind at half-way, moved up to be within a length at the 650m, began losing ground from the 500m mark & weakened poorly in straight.

Was trapped racing three wide without cover in midfield after the start. Continued wide when improving to be third from about the 650m, came under hard riding near the 550m, began losing ground before weakening in straight.

Got back after the start to race just worse than midfield away from the rail. Was relegated to third last when galloping between runners near 550m, about 6L from lead on straightening but weakened poorly to finish long last.
Fast into stride, sat right behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, hit the front 150M, kept on very well to hold off the challengers.
Out with rest, raced 3 wide better than midfield, no cover in the middle stages, finished off well to take 2nd, always held.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to take a place, nearest on line.
Began well from the widest draw, raced prominently on the outside, there to turn, took the lead 200M, peaked and headed 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Began only fairly from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, there to turn, no clear run until final 100M, finished off evenly.
Bumped shortly after start, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/4L turning in, peaked and headed 200M, ran on evenly to the line.
Made contact shortly after start, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, no clear run until final 150M, finished off well to be nearest on line.
Made contact shortly after start, positioned 2 wide better than midfield, angled out 350M, no clear run early in straight, kept on evenly thereafter.
Bumped start, taken back to race at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made good progress early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Bumped on jumping, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, made some progress early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced behind midfield on the outside, 3-1/2L back turning in, made no progress in straight.
Crowded start and unbalanced, raced at rear on the outside, very wide into straight, one-paced in the run home.
Broke well, settled in front of midfield on the rail, angled out in the Straight, ran on nicely to score.
Settled midfield 2 wide early, got shuffled back at the 700M, began to improve at 500M, closed off nicely for 2nd.
Caught 3 wide no cover midfield, 4 wide rounding the Home Turn, kept on nicely despite a tough run.
Jumped well from the outside barrier and showed good early speed to work across the rail and to lead, weakened inside final 75M.
Ridden along early but showed no early speed and settled at the rear, stayed on fairly.
Settled towards the rear 2 wide, some progress late.
Raced near the rear on the rail, only able to pass weakened rivals.
Settled midfield 2 wide, limited response when asked.
Sat just behind the leader, switched out to 2 wide to challenge near the 500M, weakened quickly inside final 100M.
Caught 3 wide no cover early until slotted into 2 wide in front of midfield at near 700M, travelled ungenerously in the middle stages, got checked in the Straight and weakened. (See Incident Report)
Settled in a prominent position 2 wide, weakened and faded in the Straight. (See Incident Report)
Broke a step slow, raced greenly throughout, never a factor. (See Incident Report)
Settled one from last and waited with, commenced move wide rounding home bend and widest in last into straight, cantered to lead down the centre of the track to win convincingly.

Settled in 5th on rail some 4L off the pace, came 6th coming onto home bend, saved ground turning for home hitting the front under pressure 200 metres out only to be overshadowed by fast-finishing winner shortly after.

Began well from a middle draw gradually crossing to rails in front racing keenly most of the way to the 750 metres, maintained 1L advantage rounding final bend and into straight, headed under pressure 200 metres out.

Settled at the back from the widest draw and waited with, trailed the field coming under pressure 500 metres out, saved ground making home turn holding some chance 200 briefly metres out, made no further impression.
Began well from a poor draw settling some 3L back in 4th, gained closer to pace half-way out before coming under pressure home bend, ran home one-paced from 4-wide into straight.

Settled just behind midfield mainly in 7th on the rail, lost position before coming under pressure onto home bend, inconvenienced behind runners 350 metres out, kept on at the one pace under pressure.
Settled just worse than midfield 2-wide, went wider rounding home bend and into straight, fought on steadily under pressure after inconvenienced 150 metres out.

Vied for lead from a poor draw holding narrow advantage briefly first time past the post, shifted back to 1L 2nd 2-wide onto first bend, came under pressure rounding final bend but soon faded after straightening.
Broke well before taking back to midfield over 4L back, went one of the widest turning for home, dropped out tamely. (Jockey reported racing too keenly.)
Jumped awkwardly settling just off the pace in 2L 3rd, weakened sharply out of contention 500 metres out.
Given a waiting ride towards the rear in a fast run race, plenty to do top of straight but lengthened stride impressively to take lead close home.
Sped to the lead, set fast pace to straight and opened up 2L lead 350M, run ended 50M and caught by fast finishing winner close home.
Reserved behind midfield, ran on well from top of straight although not finishing pace of winner passing 200M, checked over concluding stages.
Settled ahead of mid-division in a fast run race, 4Ls behind leader home turn, kept on steadily to the line for a moderate 4th.
Tracked leader in a fast run race, battled on to hold 2nd until 100M, checked late stages and faded to 5th.
Held up towards the rear early stages, improved position from 600M, stayed on moderately over final 300M but never a serious threat.
Settled midfield, driven along 500M, kept on final 300M without seriously threatening.
Began well, restrained to a position ahead of midfield, soon outpaced on straightening and out of contention.
Dropped back to the rear in a fast run race, bustled along home turn, gave limited response turning home, never dangerous.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners early stages, settled near last in a fast run race, lacked finishing effort passing 400M.
Driven forward from draw 11, tracked leader to straight but came up empty. (Jockey : Unable to finish off carrying top weight and from outside draw stepping up to 1200M first time.)
