Moderately away from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, hit the front 250M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Began only fairly, raced at rear on the inside, 6 lengths back, slightly improved along the rail on turn, finished off well to take 2nd, always held.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Began only fairly, raced behind midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 500M, no clear run early in straight, kept on well thereafter to make frame.
Bumped shortly after start, sent forward to race in 2nd, a length or so back, there to turn, kept on evenly to 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped only fairly, raced 2 wide towards rear, 3 wide from 500M, passed some tired runners in straight.
Moderately away, raced behind midfield on the outside, 4 lengths back, same margin back on turn, one-paced in straight.
Shifted out at start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide from 600M, made some progress early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)

Shifted in at start and made contact, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 250M, weakened inside final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began awkwardly, raced at rear on the outside, very wide into straight, failed to make any progress in the run home.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced in midfield on the outside, moved a bit closer after passing 900M, no cover throughout, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect.
Amongst leaders before settling in 3rd on rails, ran on steadily to hit the front 100 metres out.
Wide in prominent 4th some 2L off the pace, 3-wide rounding home bend and wider into straight, ran on without threatening.
Ridden along amongst leaders, gained advantage 1050 metres out and rails run shortly after, held clear advantage into straight but flattered and swamped inside final 150 metres.
Gradually dropped to last few despite ridden along, tightened 700 metres out, saved ground turning in, ran on between runners to do best work late.
Bumped at start, travelled in 6th or 5th near midfield, kept on steadily without threatening in straight.
Travelled keenly in midfield on rails, carried backward from 850 metres out to last few onto home bend, made up good ground inside final 200 metres.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, travelled wide without cover in last few, made up good ground inside final 300 metres down the centre of the track.
Crowded and blundered at start losing ground, failed to muster in back straight, wide in last few rounding home bend, ran on under pressure.
Settled wide in rear of midfield from the widest draw, in similar position into straight, ran home one-paced. (Blood in trachea)
Soon came from a wide draw to join the leaders, settled 2-wide in 2nd coming onto home bend, came under pressure to hold place until folded up quickly inside final 200 metres.
Ridden along just over 2L off the pace on rails, drifted backward from 800 metres out, found nothing after straightening.
Soon dropped to last few and never seen with a chance.
Jumped okay, settled in front of midfield on the stand's rail, responded well when place under pressure inside 200M, closed off strongly.
Settled midfield, switched in passing 350M, made some progress when asked, finished off nicely.
Jumped awkwardly, settled behind midfield 4 wide from the stand's rail, commenced to improve inside 250M, one pace to the line.
Jumped awkwardly, sat worse than midfield, was steadied and no clear run until 150M, closed off okay.
Sat towards rear on the stand's rail, traveled okay, shifted in to obtain clear run inside 150M, ran on evenly.
Settled midfield 3 wide from the stand's rail, traveled smoothly, minor progress made when asked, one pace to the line.
Jumped awkwardly, ridden along to lead, slightly weakened inside 300M, ran on fairly.
Sat in front of midfield, limited response when asked, made no impression.
Slow to jump, sat towards rear, was steadied and got its head up approaching 450M, made minor progress over the concluding stages.
As the start was effected lowered its head, lost ground, sat towards rear, failed to respond when asked (See Incident Report).
Sat behind midfield, traveled fairly, slightly held up inside 250M, never a threat.
Ridden along to chase the lead, weakened and faded notably inside 300M (Roarer previously reported).
Slow to begin, sat towards rear, no clear run in the early stages, eased down over the concluding stages (Unacceptable performance, Roarer, Must trial, See Incident Report).
Settled rear, raced rear throughout, no contention (Unacceptable performance, Must trial).
Had a nice run 1,1 for the majority. Came wider just before straightening, moved up to share lead at 250m & was too strong for immediate challenger late. First two well clear of the rest.

Raced worse than midfield when three deep with cover. Shifted wider passing the 700m, was wide on straightening when laying outwards, moved up to share lead at 250m, tried hard but couldn't get passed winner, clear of third.

Drifted back from outside draw & shared last place after the start. Had only a few runners behind on straightening before making steady late ground between runners in final furlong to move to well beaten third in final 100m.
Pushed forward & had a nice run on the leaders back. Had clear running entering the final section when only a length from the lead, battled fairly to hold well beaten fourth on the line.

Slightly slow to begin before racing worse than midfield between runners. Shifted outwards near 550m, was the second widest on straightening when over 4L behind before passing a few tiring rivals when running onto midfield.
Raced in midfield when galloping three wide with cover. Was 3L from the lead on straightening but finished only one paced to the line.
Pushed forward to lead. Continued in the lead until near the 250m before weakening to be well beaten in midfield.

Trapped racing three deep without cover when galloping just forward of midfield. Was only about a length from the lead on straightening, emptied out near the 200m & weakened out quickly in late stages after wide passage.
Was shifted across behind runners after the start & shared last place. Continued rearward and near the rail on straightening before failing to challenge in straight.

Steadied after the start & raced worse than midfield between runners. Came wider passing the 550m when in the final three, was forced very wide on straightening before failing to make any ground & being well beaten on line.
Didn't begin fast & raced worse than midfield along the rail. Stayed along the rail on straightening when still in the second half but did nothing in the run to the line & was beaten over 8L.
Raced in midfield along the rail throughout. Was only 2.5L from the lead entering final section but weakened badly in the straight to be a long second last.
Began well & showed early speed to race second away from the rail for the majority. Was only 1L from the lead entering last section before weakening badly in the straight to be a distant last.
Taken back from gate 12, raced at tail, 6 lengths or so back, slightly improved after passing 700M, 4 lengths back in the middle stages, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to score.
Bumped start, raced in 3rd, a length back on turn, showed good response in straight, hit the front 200M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner late.
Average to begin, positioned 3 wide with cover, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off well to take a place without threatening.
Made contact at start, raced behind midfield on the inside, 3 to 4 lengths back, saved ground on turn, finished off well to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Began awkwardly, raced prominently on the outside, 1/2L back turning in, took the lead 300M, peaked and headed 200M, weakened gradually final 100M.
Jumped only fairly, taken back to race at rear on the inside, 5 lengths or so back, angled out 450M, made some headway in straight.
Jumped with them, raced in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, kept on same pace to the line. (See Racing Incidents.) (Blood in trachea.)

Began only fairly and made contact, raced better than midfield on the inside, 2 lengths or so back, saved ground throughout, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Jumped well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, trapped very wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, peaked and dropped towards rear 450M, 3-1/2L back turning in, made no impression in straight.
Out with rest, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/2L turning in, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened and eased final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths or so back on turn, showed no response early in straight, eased final furlong.
Jumped awkwardly and made contact, raced 2 wide better than midfield, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.
Jumped with the field, settled in front of midfield on the rail, switched to 2 wide at 550M and improved nicely, kicked clear at 150M and kept on.
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide after being caught 3 wide earlier, closed off nicely for 2nd.
Settled towards the rear, made good progress near the rail early in the Straight, held up slightly at 200M, closed off nicely once in the clear
Tracked leader, kept on okay, weakened slightly final 50M.
Sat just behind the leaders, only one pace when asked.
Settled midfield 2 wide, angled out rounding the Home Turn, stayed on only fairly.
Broke well and showed good early speed to lead, weakened inside 150M. (See Incident Report)
Sat at the rear, swung wide in the Straight, only able to pass weakened rivals.
Ridden along early, sat midfield 3 wide, limited in the Straight.
Broke slowly, settled worse than midfield on the rail, made no impression.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, unable to quickened in the Straight.
Caught 3 wide with cover behind midfield, made no progress.
Settled in a prominent position 2 wide, weakened and faded in the Straight. (See Incident Report)
Caught wide up with the pace early, then settled in front of midfield 3 wide, gave ground at 500M, finished tailed out. (Performance unacceptable, must trial)
Settled some 2L off the pace between runners, obtained clear passage 300 metres out, quickened well to assert authority over 150 metres out.
Settled within 2L of the pace on stands rails, came under pressure inside final 400 metres, fought on steadily without threatening.
Settled in rear, improved slightly to about 2L off the pace onto course proper, ran on under pressure to hold every chance until finding no extra 100 metres out.
Well there from a high draw, gained slender lead briefly coming onto course proper, unable to sustain effort closing stages.
Settled at the back of small field and waited with, switched onto stands rail over 300 metres out but baulked for a run most of the way to finish.
Well there nearest to the centre of the track, came under pressure to challenge coming onto course proper holding place chance until swamped over 50 metres out.
Jumped moderately, settled within 1.5L of the pace, briefly baulked about 350 metres out, made no impression inside final 300 metres.
Soon took up running, led until narrowly headed over 500 metres out, weakened under pressure.
Well there, came under pressure to hold place coming onto proper, unable to sustain effort inside final 200 metres.
Reserved behind midfield 3-wide, wide into straight then came with a strong finish, led nearing 50M for two consecutive wins.
Began only fairly, moved up to race in midfield early and middle stages, ran on well final 300M but not pace of winner late. (Jockey questioned regarding riding position.)
Settled ahead of midfield, quickened up strongly early straight to lead near 200M, caught by first 2 late stages.
In mid-division, raced keenly in the middle stages, gave good response early straight before turning one pace late on.
Jumped only fairly, reserved near last, 7Ls to make up 400M, ran on moderately to claim 5th.
Dropped back to the rear, 8Ls behind making the home turn, stayed on without reaching first few.
Held up in midfield, caught 3-wide without cover from 1200M, ran on fairly passing 400M, never going the pace to challenge.
Emerged as leader passing 1300M, led at good pace first half of the race, headed mid-straight then faded towards the line.
Chased leaders, struggled to keep up from 550M, kept on fairly under top weight final 400M. (Jockey: stepping up to 1600M, raced greenly, particularly under pressure in the Home Straight.)
Up with early pace, 3rd on settling, had every chance turning home, run ended mid-straight and faded.
From draw 14 moved up to sit outside leader, couldn't keep up 300M, weakened away. (Jockey: asked to take up a forward position from wide draw.)
Positioned ahead of midfield, commenced to race keenly from 900M with blinkers applied first time, left with no finishing effort in the straight.
Settled towards the rear 6-7Ls off the pace, not quickened under pressure passing 450M ,eased late stages when no chance.
Slow to begin, ended up racing towards the rear, came under pressure home turn, failed to respond and soon left behind.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out 500M, finished off very strongly, led close home.

Jumped well, raced prominently, 2 wide, found rail and sat right behind the leader 1250M, saved ground on turn, angled out after passing 500M, took the lead approaching 200M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner close home.
Slowly away, raced 2 wide towards rear, 3 wide after passing 1000M, angled out 500M, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to take a place, nearest finish.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, angled out 500M, kept on well until hampered 50M, finished 4th.
Jumped awkwardly, raced behind midfield on the outside, very wide turning in, closed off well without threatening.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, a bit closer on turn, kept on well early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Began well, raced slightly better than midfield on the outside, no cover for the majority of the race, very wide into straight, kept on evenly in the run home.
Moderately away from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently on the outside, challenged the leader 550M, kept on well early in straight, peaked 200M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, challenged by rival from 550M, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 200M, weakened gradually close home.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Missed break and lost significant ground, detached early, latched on to main group at halfway, 5 lengths or so back turning in, ran on evenly in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, 2 wide turning in, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced towards rear on the inside, 7 lengths back, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Began awkwardly, raced at rear throughout, never a factor. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from gate 11, raced 3 wide behind midfield, 2 wide from 850M, closer on turn, not enough room early in straight, cleared 300M, finished off very strongly, easily scored.
Began well, raced prominently on the outside, shared lead on turn, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner final 100M.
Began well from a wide draw, raced in midfield on the outside, there to turn, finished off well to take a place without threatening the first two.
Commenced well, took the early lead, slightly taken back 1000M, positioned 1 out 1 back in the middle stages, kept on same pace in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the outside, there to turn, taken wide in straight and made good progress to be nearest on line.
Bumped heavily shortly after start, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, no clear run early in straight, ran on evenly thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 6 lengths or so back turning in, made some headway in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, wider turning in, showed limited response early in straight, ran on evenly thereafter.
Jumped awkwardly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide from 600M, 4 lengths back turning in, made no impression in straight.
Began only fairly, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, kept on well early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Jumped with them, showed no early speed, raced at rear on the inside, 5 lengths back turning in, failed to make any progress in straight.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Average to begin, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked 300M, weakened final furlong.
Shifted in at start and bumped, sent forward to take the lead, shared the lead with rival on turn, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened thereafter.

Jockey: Comments on Running is not available for this race.
Gear: Comments on Running is not available for this race.

Taken back to race at rear on the inside, 2-1/2L back on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared 200M, hit the front 100M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Taken back to race towards rear on the outside, a bit closer after passing 700M, very wide into straight, finished off well to take 2nd.

Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, commenced move after passing 900M, shared lead from 700M, 3 wide on turn, peaked early in straight, headed 100M, ran on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)

Shifted out at start and bumped, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, 2 wide and moved a bit closer after passing 800M, 3 wide turning in, made good progress early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Began well from gate 1, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on throughout, kept on well early in straight, no extra final 100M.

Jumped well, raced behind midfield on the outside, sent forward after passing 1200M, took the lead 1100M, shared lead with rivals from 700M, peaked early in straight, headed 200M, weakened final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, took the early lead, led by 3/4L, headed near 1100M, challenged the leader from 700M, steadied off heels 300M, no clear run early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Began smartly, raced 2 wide in 2nd, 3 wide from 800M, dropped to midfield in the middle stages, peaked on run 400M, weakened gradually in straight.
Restrained in midfield, raced keenly middle stages, quickened up well passing 300M, led nearing 50M and won going away.
Bumped at the start, strolled forward to be tracking leader, took lead near 200M, kept on well but not pace of fast finishing winner late stages.
Tracked leaders, well placed to strike top of straight and had every chance, not pace of winner final 150M.
Driven early, settled in 5th spot never far off from leaders, ran on mildly passing 300M for 4th.
Crowded after the start, took up a position in midfield, over-raced middle stages, kept on without threat in the straight, well held by leaders final 200M.
Up with early pace before taken back to 4th spot, close enough turning home but fought on one paced to the line.
Jumped awkwardly and lost ground, settled behind midfield 6Ls off the pace, badly held up 150M behind a weakening rival losing momentum. Inconclusive run.
Waited with in a rearward spot, 7Ls to make up 400M, gave limited response under top weight.
Jumped fairly, settled behind midfield and slightly further behind than anticipated, kept on same pace final 300M. Never dangerous.
Dropped back to the rear, held up near last, not going the pace to challenge on straightening.
Soon led, headed near 200M then faded away. (Jockey was asked to take up a forward position but didn't expect his horse would show the pace to lead.)
From wide draw taken back to last, responded fairly on straightening, was not going to threaten when checked 100M.
Sat in front of midfield, traveled smoothly, commenced to improve rounding the Turn, made good progress inside 150M, closed off nicely.
Settled towards rear 2 wide, made the forward move inside 550M, responded well over the concluding stages.
Sat handy 3 wide, raced wide throughout, closed off okay.
Sat worse than midfield, traveled okay, held up in the early Straight, responded fairly when asked.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, commenced to improve inside 600M, ran on evenly.
Sat rear 2 wide, raced keenly in the early stages, made the Turn wide, made some progress over the concluding stages.
Settled midfield on the rail, slightly weakened entering the Straight, closed off okay.
Settled midfield 3 wide, no clear running until 200M, closed off only fairly.
Settled towards rear, traveled fairly, limited response when asked.
Ridden hard to sit on-pace, raced keenly in the early stages, weakened and faded passing 150M (See Incident Report).
Jumped awkwardly, sat rear on the rail, switched out rounding the Turn, made no impression in the Straight.
Ridden along to lead, weakened notably inside 200M (See Incident Report).
Raced in midfield away from the rail. Shifted wider on straightening & bumped, dashed quickly passing the 200m, hung inwards but charged to lead at 75m & went on to win strongly.

Outpaced after the start & got back to race second last. Continued rearward, came under hard ridding passing the 500m, came out to be the widest runner before charging home from the back to steal fast finishing second late.

Drifted back from wide draw & raced worse than midfield when three deep with cover. Came back inside the winners heals on straightening, began making ground before shifting wider at 150m & closing well late to steal third.

Began awkwardly & bumped before mustering usual early speed to charge forward, racing second before continuing to lead near 750m. Continued in lead until passed quickly by winner at 75m, caught for a minor placing late.

Had a soft run in midfield along the rail in early & middle stages. Came away from the rail near the 450m, raced tight & bumped between runners passing the 150m when close to lead before battling ok late.

Was slightly slow to begin & raced rearward along the rail in middle stages. Came away from the rail before first bend, closed off steadily between runners when nearer to the inside in final stages & was closest on line.

Drifted back after the start & raced at the tail. Continued last entering last section, came out wider on the track on straightening before making late ground down the outside from a long way back to be closest on the line.
Was trapped racing three wide without cover in midfield throughout. Hung outwards & was then forced wider on cornering before failing to run on in the straight.
Had a nice run in midfield away from rail. Hung outwards on cornering, raced tight between runners on straightening before giving a couple of lengths in the straight.

Showed customary early speed to lead before being headed near 750m & racing second thereafter. Was second, only 1L from the lead on straightening, raced tight inside of rivals near the 150m before giving a few lengths late.

Raced second after the start before racing third along the inside after first furlong. Improved onto the leaders back before straightening, had clear running along the inside but emptied at 150m & weakened in final stages.

Slightly slow to begin before racing worse than midfield along rail. Ridden along around bend, stayed near the inside, began making ground before being unable to be ridden out in final 150m. Last but should have been closer.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide in midfield, 2 lengths or so back, commenced move 450M, finished off very strongly to score.
Taken back to race 2 wide at rear, sent forward after entering the back straight, took the lead 750M, led by 3/4L turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner final 50M.

Commenced well, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, 3 wide on turn, short of room early in straight, cleared 150M, finished off well to take a place without threatening the first two. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away, raced 2 wide towards rear, commenced move 500M, very wide into straight, made some progress in straight to make frame.
Away well, sent forward to take the lead, headed near 750M, 2nd on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back to race at rear on the inside, angled out 350M, unable to obtain clear run until final 100M, made some progress thereafter.
Average to begin, raced behind midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 400M, one-paced in straight.
Began well from gate 1, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Settled worse than midfield, began to improve 800M, had a nice run through, switched out in the Straight, closed off strongly to score.
Broke nicely, tracked leader, quickened up at 800M, kept on nicely, just can't hold off the winner.
Jumped with the field, caught 3 wides, got hampered badly at 1300M, lost ground significantly, sat worse than midfield 3 wide, made decent progress in the Straight, run well despite the troubles.
Ridden along early to maintain a prominent position on the rail, made some ground early in the Straight, run peaked the 150M, a bit one pace afterwards.
Broke nicely, settled behind the leaders, only one pace when asked.
Steadied after the start from a wide barrier, sat last, held up slightly at 400M, made some ground.
Settled towards the rear 2 wide, only able to pass weakened rivals.
Settled at the rear, made little impression.
Showed good early speed to lead, under pressure at 600M, no response.
Caught 3 wide early, made a forward move to sit outside the lead at 850M, weakened and faded in the Straight.
Raced ungenerously throughout, never really involved. (Racing Manners unacceptable, must trial)
Settled midfield on the rail, travelled keenly down the back Straight, never a factor.
Broke well before gradually settling near midfield on rail, commenced move home bend saved ground into straight, fought on steadily to assert authority 100 metres out.
Ridden along behind midfield after moderate start, made steady headway home bend to be 5L 6th into straight, switched for a clear run 150 metres out and did best work late.
Travelled wide in last few early, gained closer to 5L 7th 800 metres out, one of the widest into straight, finished off the race strongly to snatch 3rd late.
Pressed forward from the widest draw to be 2-wide one back in 2nd turning into back straight, in similar position making home turn, fought on steadily without threatening.
Pressed forward from a poor draw to take up running 1050 metres out and rails run shortly after, led until headed by eventual winner 100 metres out, lost placing final strides.
Began well in front briefly before settling two back in 3rd, switched 3-wide entering home straight, one-paced.
Broke well before drifting back wide in midfield, made headway early in back straight to reach 3L 4th, wide in 5th into straight and made no further impression. (Blood in trachea)
Settled wide in last few from a wide draw, came under pressure rounding home bend and widest into straight, produced good late impression closing stages.
Settled in midfield, shuffled further back travelling keenly early in back straight, fought on under pressure closing stages.
Settled in last few, went wide into straight, ran home one-paced under pressure.
Slightly slow out and inconvenienced, travelled well behind on the rail and never seen with a chance.
Broke well before gradually drifted back to midfield, travelled keenly and lost position 700 metres out, folded up quickly after straightening.
Crowded shortly after the start, travelled well in mid-division, quickened up smartly passing 300M, led mid-straight and drew away late.
Set the pace under pressure from outer rival, drifted to center of track on straightening, continued on well but was outkicked by winner in the late stages.
Not hurried early stages, reserved behind midfield, kept on steadily final 300M to claim 3rd without troubling the winner.
Settled behind midfield, ran on moderately from 300M but failed to find the needed kick.
Jumped only fairly from wide draw, settled in a rearward position further back than intended, closed off mildly on straightening. Not reach leaders.
Away fast, settled just off the pace, tried hard to stay in contention early straight, run ended and faded final 150M.
Slow to begin, dropped back to race at the rear 7-8Ls off the pace, brought wide early straight, made some progress towards the line.
Settled down in midfield along the fence, driven out 300M but responded only fairly under top weight, no threat from mid-straight.
Jumped awkwardly, settled at the back of the field, failed to run on after straightening. Never involved. (Jockey : raced in a disappointing manner.)
Jumped only fairly, tracked leaders but raced ungenerously throughout the early and middle stages, found disappointingly little in the finish.
Bumped after the start, moved up to track leaders, failed to run on passing 300M, soon out of contention.
From draw 12 caught wide no cover chasing leaders, gave ground early straight, soon weakened to last.

Jumped well from a wide draw, raced prominently on the outside, found rail near 1000M, took the lead near 450M, kept on very well in straight, won by 1-1/2L.
Slowly away, raced at tail in the early stages, sent forward after passing 1300M, took the lead 1050M, led by 3/4L on turn, headed near 450M, kept on evenly in straight to take 2nd.
Away well, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, finished off well to take a place without threatening.
Slow to begin, raced at rear, 5 lengths back, a bit closer turning in, made good progress in straight to make frame without threatening.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced in midfield on the outside, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, tracked leaders, 2 wide, there to turn, angled out 500M, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well, tracked leaders on the outside, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, one-paced thereafter.
Began fairly, raced towards rear, 4 lengths or so back turning in, made some progress early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Clean jump, sent forward to take the lead, headed near 1050M, positioned a length behind the leader on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 250M. (See Racing Incidents.) (Blood in trachea.)
Began only fairly, always towards rear, never a factor. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Raced in midfield away from the rail before moving closer to the lead nearing the 700m mark & racing 1,1 thereafter. Moved up to take the lead at the 250m & went on to win by a length.

Crowded after start, recovered to race second before being crossed near 900m & racing behind the leading pair. Had difficulty getting clear on straightening before shifting outwards at 250m & closing well, beaten only 1L.

Raced in midfield along the rail for the majority. Came away from the inside just before straightening, was crowded & taken outwards near 250m when building momentum before finishing off well in final 100m to finish third.

Jumped awkwardly before racing worse than midfield. Crowded near the 600m when racing tight between runners, was beginning to finish steadily before being checked near 250m before closing well late to steal fourth.

Jumped awkwardly & lost ground before racing a clear last after the start. Continued rearward on straightening, stayed along the rail before passing halving deficit in the final section when finishing off to midfield late.

Raced in third position away from the rail soon after the start before improving to race at the leaders' quarters from the 650m. Moved to lead momentarily passing the 400m, passed by winner at 250m, gave a few lengths late.

Bumped at the start before racing with only the final pair behind. Was forced wider around the bend when three deep with cover, was the widest runner on straightening when 4.5L from the lead, finished off only fairly late.

Jumped on fairly & bumped before hanging outwards around the first bend when racing wide & just worse than midfield. Continued wide, was under 3L from lead at 400m, continued to shift ground in straight when holding margin.
Pushed forward from wide draw to lead before crossing to the rail when leading near the 900m. Was joined on straightening & headed soon after before weakening in last furlong to be beaten over 4L.
Began fairly before racing in midfield along the rail. Raced tight with rival approaching the 600m, was 4L from the lead on straightening but couldn't improve & beat only two rivals home.

Jumped only fairly before racing three wide without cover in midfield. Was only 3L from the lead entering last section, was finishing steadily before being crowded & checked near the 250m & never proving a factor thereafter.

Jumped awkwardly, shifted out & bumped before racing second last away from the rail. Was relegated to last near the 850m, came wider on the track on straightening when 6L behind but make no headway into that deficit.
Ridden along to chase the lead, traveled nicely, commenced to improve in the early Straight, well responded over the concluding stages, closed off strongly.
Ridden hard to lead, traveled smoothly, kept on well to hold 2nd.
Sat handy, traveled okay throughout, slightly weakened inside 250M, made some progress over the concluding stages.
Jumped awkwardly, settled in front of midfield, switched out in the Straight, ran on evenly.
Settled behind midfield 3 wide, was taken out rounding the Turn then raced wide, closed off okay.
Sat rear, slightly improve rounding the Turn switched out, made some ground in the Straight.
Sat midfield, traveled okay, minor progress when asked in the early Straight.
Jumped only fairly, raced greenly, over-raced in the middle stages, finished off fairly.
Sat towards rear 2 wide, traveled fairly, one pace throughout.
Sat midfield on the rail, slightly weakened inside 250M, limited response when asked.
Sat rear, slightly improved passing 300M, no impression made thereafter.
Settled worse than midfield, weakened inside 250M, never a danger.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, weakened notably approaching 200M, never a threat.
Settled towards rear on the rail, raced rear, weakened and faded entering the Straight (Bled, Must BT).

Raced in midfield along the rail for the majority. Was just over 2L from the lead entering last section, stayed along the rail, burst through to take lead at the 175m before going on to win by 1.75L but being eased near line.

Jumped only fairly & raced worse than midfield along the rail. Came off the rail near the 500m, made ground between runner's near the 250m, improved to second near the 100m mark & held that place to line.

Pushed forward, raced in third place after start before continuing between runners in midfield in the middle stages. Shifted out into clear running on straightening when just under 3L from lead, closed well to just miss 2nd.

Raced in midfield between runners throughout. Had clear running on straightening, entered last section just under 4L from lead, closed off well down the outside in final stages to be just behind second.
Jumped awkwardly & lost ground, consequently racing rearward. Stayed nearer the rail on straightening when 4.5L from the lead before making some late ground to finish a non-threatening fifth.
Pushed forward to lead before crossing to the rail near the 1000m when leading. Continued in the lead before being joined & headed by the winner near the 175m & then weakening a few lengths late.

Jumped fairly, bumped & unbalanced soon after & consequently raced rearward. Continued to gallop between runners around bend. Shifted inwards at 400m to get clear, was again held up near 300m, got clear late but some excuse.

Raced prominently, crossed by the leading pair near the 1000m & raced on the leaders back thereafter. Had no clear run from the 400m until the 300m when only a length from the lead before finishing pretty weakly in the last furlong.
Pushed forward to race outside the leader. Continued close to the lead until emptying at the 200m & weakening out in last furlong.

Raced four wide without cover in midfield after start before improving position approaching the 1000m & getting up to be three wide outside the leaders from the 750m. Was beaten early in straight & weakened in last 250m.

Raced wide with cover in midfield after the start before becoming keen & throwing head from the 1000m mark before eventually becoming more relaxed passing 600m. Was wide on straightening before failing to run on in straight.

Bumped after the start before drifting back to race worse than midfield when three wide with cover. Shifted outwards at 500m, was the second widest runner on straightening when 6L behind before doing nothing in straight.

Drifted back after start & raced rearward. Continued last when galloping wide with cover. Shifted wider passing 600m, forced very wide from 550m, was widest on straightening when 6L behind but failed to improve in straight.

Raced four wide early before being hard ridden to improve. Got 1,1 momentarily passing 900m, was forced wide again around the bend, began losing ground from the 550m, hung out on straightening before weakening to long last.
Jumped awkwardly, raced better than midfield on the inside, 2 lengths or so back, angled out after passing 450M, finished off very strongly, led last stride.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably to turn, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner on line.
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced better than midfield but trapped 3 wide, 2 lengths or so back turning in, closed off well to take a place.
Average to begin, raced behind midfield on the outside, commenced move 550M, very wide into straight, made very good progress early in straight, peaked on run 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Began awkwardly and bumped shortly after start, raced behind midfield on the inside, 5 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, 2 wide turning in, finished off well without threatening.
Jumped well, raced in midfield on outer, very wide turning in, finished off evenly.
Out in line, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out 450M, no clear run early in straight, made minor progress thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Moderately away, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened inside final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped shortly after start, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Commenced well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 wide from 450M, short of room near 400M, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from gate 11, raced at rear on the inside, 6 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Jumped with the field, settled worse than midfield 2 wide, closed off strongly, score comfortably.
Settled at the rear 2 wide, swung wide into the Straight, stayed on well for 2nd
Raced in front of midfield on the rail, had trouble finding daylight until the 200M, made decent progress afterwards.
Settled midfield on the rail, angled out rounding the Home Turn, struck the front at 150M, run peaked soon after, hung on for 4th.
Sat in front of midfield 2 wide, hit the front at 300M and kept on fairly.
Settled behind midfield on the rail, held up until the 200M, made some ground inside final 150M, best stride late.
Caught 3 wide no cover near midfield, one pace in the Straight.
Settled near the rear 2 wide, no luck in running early in the Straight, showed some dash final 200M. (See Incident Report)
Showed good early speed to be prominent, weakened inside 300M.
No early speed early, sat at the rear, made no impression.
Tracked leaders 2 wide, weakened in the Straight. (See Incident Report)
Raced 3 wide midfield, under pressure at 550M, never involved.
Ridden along early to lead, weakened and faded inside 200M.
Settled midfield 2 wide between horses, taken wider rounding the turn, never a factor. (Blood in trachea)

Well there from a wide draw before settling some 3L back in 5th, improved to 2L 4th 1300 metres out and further closer around home bend, came to challenge upon straightening and asserted authority about 350 metres out.
Settled at the back and waited with, saved ground turning for home, quickened well between runners to have every chance when forced to check over 50 metres out. (Finished 3rd, placed 2nd)

Pressed forward from a wide draw before settling one back on rail in 3rd, baulked for a run early in straight until the 300 metres out, shifted ground causing interference over 50 metres out. (Finished 2nd, placed 3rd)
Jumped fairly, gradually settled in 7th just worse than midfield, commenced move 4-wide into home straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Settled in 6th mostly some 4L back in rear of midfield, came to challenge under pressure upon straightening, fought on steadily without threatening.
Soon took up running and attempted to make all, headed by eventual winner about 350 metres out and gradually faded.
Settled well behind, widest into home straight, kept on steadily without quickening.
Not far off in early stages, gradually drifted back to 5th over 4L back near midfield 1300 metres out, came under pressure entering home straight, faded steadily.
Pressed forward out wide from the widest draw, shared pace briefly early in back straight, remained in 2nd to 400 metres and soon weakened. (Tactic questioned)
Settled in last few and never seen with a chance. (Bled)
Caught wide from outside gate, dropped back and settled at the rear further back than intended, plenty to do 400M, finished determinedly from last place to lead the field near 50M. Nice win.
From wide draw taken back to a rearward spot, brought wide 500M, came with a good rally to take 2nd. Encouraging debut.
Settled down midfield along the fence, switched out 450M to challenge, ran on well to go 3rd near line.
Held up in mid-division, kept on steadily over final 300M, got up for 4th late.
Soon led, kept on well turning for home, caught by first few final 50M.
In 5th place on settling, always in touch, responded well early straight to go 2nd, couldn't sustain the challenge past 150M.
Given a waiting ride towards the rear, 8Ls off the pace 400M, was making good progress when checked 150M and lost all chance.
From wide draw went forward to race outside leader, held on to 2nd until nearing 200M, had little left late.
Chased leaders on inside, couldn't keep up passing 200M, faded towards the finish.
Tracked leaders along 2-path, fought hard to stay in contention early straight, no extra final 150M.
Jumped only fairly, settled near last, driven along 550M but failed to respond to riding. Made no impression on debut.
Began fairly, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 700M, angled out 450M, finished off very strongly to score.
Jumped with them, raced better than midfield on the outside, moved closer after passing 500M, took the lead 200M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner late.
Bumped shortly after start, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Began awkwardly and bumped, took the lead, 2 wide, found rail near 700M, led by 3/4L turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, made some progress thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide towards rear, 6 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, made some progress early in straight, blocked near 200M, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Average to begin, raced in midfield on the outside, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Taken back from gate 10, raced at rear on the outside, 6 lengths back on turn, passed some tired runners in straight.
Bumped start, tracked leaders, 2 wide, 3 wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced prominently but 3 wide, 3/4L back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened 300M, eased final 150M.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 3 wide on turn, peaked and lost position near 450M, soon struggling.
Bumped shortly after start, raced prominently on the inside, allowed rival to cross near 700M, 2 wide turning in, weakened early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well, raced in midfield on outer, no cover on turn, weakened 450M when hard run took effect. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared 150M, finished off very strongly to score.
Bumped on jumping, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, 4 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, no daylight early in straight, cleared approaching 100M, closed off well to take 2nd.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide towards rear, angled out after passing 500M, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Jumped with them, raced in midfield on outer, similar position on turn, closed off well to make frame without threatening.
Began awkwardly, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length turning in, kept on well until approaching 100M, headed 50M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, allowed rival to cross 950M, 2 lengths back turning in, made some progress early in straight, peaked on run 100M, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the outside, 6 lengths back turning in, made some headway in straight.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield early, found rail near 1100M, 3 lengths back on turn, made good progress early in straight, no clear run final 200M.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back, 3 wide from 750M, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, eased final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began only fairly and crowded shortly after start, raced at rear on the inside, 8 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, dropped to midfield on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced prominently, trapped 3 wide early, 2 wide from 950M, a length back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened 200M, eased final 100M.

Slow to begin, raced 3 wide behind midfield, 2 wide on turn, finished off very strongly, won by 3-1/2L.
Slowly away, raced towards rear on the inside, 5 lengths or so back, angled out 500M, same margin back turning in, made good progress in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 6 lengths or so back turning in, finished off well to take a place without threatening.
Shifted out at start, sent forward to take the lead, shared lead with rival on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 100M, weakened thereafter.
Slowly away and checked, raced at rear, 6 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, made some headway in straight.
Fast into stride, tracked leaders, 2 wide, similar position on turn, showed some response early in straight, no extra inside final furlong.
Jumped well from gate 10, raced in midfield on the outside, there to turn, very wide into straight, showed some response early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened final 100M.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide towards rear, 8 lengths back turning in, made no impression in straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced prominently on the outside, shared lead on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide better than midfield, wider turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M.
Jumped well from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter, eased final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run and inconvenienced early in straight, soon weakened. (Lame left front leg next day morning.)

Jumped awkwardly losing ground, travelled keenly in rear on rail before gaining steadily to joint 9th onto home bend, obtained clear run over 250 metres out and quickened well to assert authority inside the 150 metres.

Broke well with a few others, gradually settled in 4th over 1150 metres out, 3-wide rounding home bend and into straight, quickened under pressure to lead 250 metres out only to be headed by the winner 150 metres out.
Ridden in prominent position early before settling in midfield in 6th, soon came under pressure from a similar position into straight, fought on steadily under pressure to be nearest at finish.
Crowded at start, travelled in worse than midfield after moderate start, in similar position into straight, did not find much room before making good late headway inside final 200 metres.
Settled well behind, saved ground turning for home, did not find much room early in straight, produced good late impression closing stages.
Settled just worse than midfield in 7th, snuck up on rail entering straight holding place chance 200 metres out, unable to sustain effort closing stages.
Soon recovered from moderate start to 5th along the rail just about 3L back, switched off rails for a run entering straight, baulked behind runners until the 200 metres, made no further impression.
Gradually drifted backward to last few wide without cover, widest runner into straight, fought on steadily near the centre of the track without threatening.
Ridden forward with leaders early, gradually shifted back to 3rd approaching home bend, switched 3-wide to challenge entering straight holding every chance until inside the final 200 metres.
Pressed forward to join the leaders from a poor draw, obtained 2nd 2-wide coming onto home bend and drew level into straight but soon weakened.
Amongst leaders after beginning from a poor gate, obtained rails run in front over 1000 metres out, led until headed under pressure inside final 400 metres.
Soon took back to rear from the widest draw, went wide entering straight, never seen with a chance.
Ridden hard to lead 2 wide, traveled strongly, slightly weakened entering the Straight, kept on well to win.
Sat in front of midfield, raced keenly in the early stages, responded well in the concluding stages under pressure, just missed.
Settled towards rear on the rail, made good ground inside 150M, closed off nicely.
Sat towards rear, traveled okay, switched out rounding the Turn, ran on evenly.
Sat midfield, made some progress in the Straight, finished off okay (Substantial mucus in horse's trachea).
Ridden along to sit handy 3 wide, traveled smoothly, slightly weakened entering the Straight, limited response when asked thereafter.
Sat rear, traveled fairly, no contention (See Incident Report).
Chased the lead on the rail, weakened and faded quickly inside 150M (See Incident Report).

Showed some speed after the start & improved position after the first 300m to be less than a length from the lead at half-way. Sprinted well to take lead passing the 150m mark & pulled clear for impressive debut win.
Showed early speed to lead when racing along stand side rail. Continued in the lead until being joined by winner at 150m, finished ok to hold second when 1.5L clear of third.

Had a nice trail in midfield when racing just behind a line of horses near the lead. Shifted inwards at 400m when just over 2L from lead, closed off well to move to third near the 150m & held that placing in acceptable debut.

Showed speed after the start to race prominently. Was still close at half-way when racing in a line of 4 near the lead. Couldn't go with the first two passing the 300m mark, boxed on fairly to hold well beaten 4th.

Raced in midfield when galloping between rivals nearer to center of the track. Steadied & shifted inwards near the 400m when about 4L from lead, finished steadily near the middle of the track to be beaten a similar margin.

Close to lead in first 100m before coming a back a length to race in midfield when one horse from the stand rail. Was just under 4L from lead entering last section, made no inroads into that margin when finishing midfield.

Slow to begin and then shifted outwards to the stand side rail & raced worse than midfield in middle stages. Was 3.5L from the lead entering last section, finished off steadily to midfield without making any relative ground.
Raced worse than midfield throughout. Was just under 5L from the lead entering last section, finished off only one paced to the line when finishing midfield.

Slow to begin & was then tightened & consequently raced rearward. Was ridden along from half-way, had only two runners behind entering last section when 5L from the lead, finished off only one paced to midfield.
Showed early speed to race close to the lead in a line of 4 at the front at half-way. Peaked on effort passing the 300m mark & weakened tamely to be beaten 6L into midfield.

Raced in midfield through the early & middle stages when galloping the closes to the center of the track. Continued in midfield and was only 2.25L from the lead entering last section but gave ground in the run to the line.

Slow to begin, had no early speed & raced a clear last. Continued last & 9.5L from lead entering final section before running home in the fastest last 400m despite being beaten 7.75L on line. Better with the experience.

Showed speed to race second, only a neck from the lead in early stages. Peaked on effort near 300m, began losing ground quickly soon after & was beaten nearly 10L when second last (over-raced in early stages  rider).

Slow to begin & was hard ridden but had no early speed & raced a clear second last when nearer to center of track. Continued to be ridden along throughout the middle stages before weakening a further few lengths to 10.75L last.
Moderately away, raced in 3rd, 2 to 3 lengths back, there to turn, hard ridden from 350M, showed very good response, hit the front approaching 100M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide in midfield, 5 lengths back turning in, finished off strongly to take 2nd, good debut.
Away with them, raced in midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 550M, kept on well in straight to take a place without threatening.

Bumped on jumping, raced towards rear on the inside, slightly improved along the rail on turn, unable to obtain clear run until near 150M, made some progress thereafter to make frame. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1 to 2 lengths on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed approaching 100M, weakened gradually close home.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 3 wide with cover towards rear, 2 wide from 500M, 7 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Commenced well, raced in 2nd, 1 to 2 lengths back turning in, one-paced in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide in midfield, dropped towards rear in the middle stages, inconvenienced near 500M, 8 lengths back turning in, made some headway in straight.
Jumped well, unable to slot in, trapped wide behind midfield, 8 lengths back turning in, made some headway in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from gate 12, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some progress in straight.
Jumped awkwardly, raced 2 wide towards rear, angled out 500M, showed some response in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, dropped to midfield 800M, carried wider 550M, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M.
Broke nicely, quickly assumed the lead, travelled comfortably throughout, kicked clear at the top of the Straight and was not for catching, won smartly.
Sat behind the leaders, made good progress in the Straight, never threatened winner.
Jumped a bit slow, settled behind midfield on the rail, stayed on fairly.
Tracked leader, kept on only fairly.
Jumped well, ridden along early and settled in front of midfield, got inconvenienced rounding the turn, closed off okay.
Slow to begin, settled worse than midfield between horses, showed some dash at the 250M, only one pace afterwards. (See Incident Report)
Settled midfield, made no impression. (See Incident Report)
Settled behind midfield 3 wide, made no ground.
Settled towards the rear, had some trouble finding daylight early in the Straight, limited response when in the clear.
Settled near the rear 2 wide, unable to improve in the Straight.
Jumped with the field, ridden along but showed no speed at all, detached at the 900M, continue to be hard ridden, never involved. (Heart Irregularity, must trial)
Hard ridden along early but showed insufficient early speed, caught very wide, weakened and faded at 500M.

Veered left from the widest draw, taken to rear of field on the rail, tight between runners on straightening, responded well inside final 300 metres down the centre of the track to just get up on line.
Held up in 5th over 3L off the pace, commenced move approaching home turn and fought on steadily under pressure only to be denied by fast-finishing winner final strides.
Jumped fairly before settling not far off the pace in 4th on the rail, switched out for a run 600 metres out, ran on steadily under pressure to be nearest at finish.

Ridden from moderate start to forward of midfield in 6th on the rail, in similar position rounding home bend, baulked for a run early in straight until the 200 metres, fought on dourly closing stages.
Pressed forward from a wide draw to soon take up running on the rail setting a sound pace, held more than 1L advantage turning in, unable to sustain effort and overhauled close to home.
Broke well settling just off the pace one-out-one-back, 1L back in 2nd turning into straight, unable to quicken to challenge under pressure.
Settled 3-wide in midfield, obtained clear passage upon straightening, fought on steadily without quickening in the run to the line.
Taken back from a poor draw for midfield run near the rail, lost position between runners rounding home bend, made steady headway under pressure in straight.
Settled in last few after moderate start, switched off the rail into straight, kept on before making good late impression closing stages.
Began well from a wide draw before taken back to rear of field, remained well behind when widest into straight, fought on steadily under pressure past well-beaten runners without threatening.
Slowly away, one of the last before gaining 11th about 1350 metres out, went wide in similar position rounding home turn, kept on steadily without quickening.

Began well from a poor draw before quickly taken backward, obtained rails run just behind midfield in 9th, made moderate progress under pressure early in straight but had no more to give inside final 200 metres.
Broke well from a wide draw, gradually shifted back to worse than midfield remaining 3-wide without cover, unbalanced and lost position 500 metres out, made no further impression. (Blood in trachea)

Began moderately, worked his way forward steadily to join the leaders 3-wide passing the 1100 metres, shifted one back to 1.5L 2nd rounding home bend, folded up quickly inside final 500 metres. (Irregular heart rhythm)
Tracked leader, responded well on straightening, gained lead 350M, fought off the persistent runner-up over final 200M. Game win.
Settled just off the pace, came with a strong challenge passing 250M, fought hard to the finish and was just held at the line.
Never far off the pace, 4th making home turn, closed well for a creditable 3rd behind two progressive looking horses. Clear from rest.
Driven to find the lead, headed 350M, faded over final 200M to finish a distant 4th.
Settled behind midfield, ran on moderately from 300M to finish remote 5th.
Up with early pace before sitting back in a position behind midfield, kept on one paced final 400M, not reach leaders.
Held up in mid-division along the inside, not going the pace to challenge passing 400M. Never involved.
Settled 2-wide in midfield, gave limited response turning into straight, no extra late stages.
Dropped back to the rear 8-9Ls off leader, lacked a response turning into straight , never in the picture.
Began only fairly, held up towards the rear, couldn't pick up passing 400M. Never a factor.
Dropped back to near the rear, came under pressure 600M, failed to finish off. (Jockey : respiratory noise noted.)
Began well, raced better than midfield, 2 away from the stands' rail, hard ridden 350M, finished off strongly to score.
Made contact at start, tracked leaders, nearer to the middle track, hard ridden approaching 300M, took the lead 200M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner close home.
Made contact at start, raced in midfield, nearer to the middle track, hard ridden 350M, finished off well to take a place without threatening.
Began smartly, raced prominently on the stands' side, hard ridden from 300M, finished off evenly.
Clean jump, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well in the middle stages, peaked and headed 200M, ran on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back to race towards rear in the middle of the track, 4 to 5 lengths back at 400M, finished off well without threatening the first few.
Slowly away, raced behind midfield on the stands' side, not enough room after passing 400M, cleared 75M, made minor progress thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced behind midfield on the middle track, kept on same pace final 400M.
Slightly slow out and crowded, raced at tail, still 8 lengths back at 400M, passed some tired runners final 300M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact at start, raced in midfield on the stands' side, showed limited response after passing 400M, weakened gradually final 100M.
Moderately away from gate 14, positioned a length behind the leader on the stands' rail, hard ridden from 350M but only showed limited response, weakened gradually final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from gate 1, raced at rear, 6 lengths or so back, made some progress after passing 400M, blocked 100M, eased thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped awkwardly and made contact, raced towards rear, 5 lengths or so back, failed to make any progress final 400M.
Made contact at start, sent forward to race prominently, 2 away from the stands' rail, peaked on run 300M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Commenced well, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, angled out 500M, showed very good response in straight, hit the front 150M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Away with them, sat right behind the leader on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out 450M, took the lead 350M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner 150M, finished 2nd.
Crowded shortly after start, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, very wide turning in, made very good progress in straight to take a place, nearest on line.
Bumped start, taken back to race at rear, 7 lengths or so back, closer turning in, closed off well to make frame without threatening.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, wider turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Made contact shortly after start, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run and raced tight early in straight, found daylight 200M, finished off evenly.
Began well from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 500M, showed some response early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened gradually final furlong.
Began fairly, raced towards rear on the outside, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back turning in, passed some tired runners in straight.

Bumped on jumping, raced towards rear on the inside, a bit closer in the middle stages, 2 wide turning in, raced tight and made some progress early in straight, no clear run 300M to 200M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Made contact at start, raced better than midfield on the outside, similar position on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked 250M, weakened final furlong.
Jumped well from the widest draw, took the early lead, headed 1100M, shared lead from 600M, peaked and headed 350M, weakened final furlong.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear throughout, never a factor. (Irregular heart rhythm.)
Out with rest, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead 1100M, shared lead with rival from 600M, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened final 250M.
Jumped with them, trapped wide in midfield, no cover for the majority of the race, weakened from 500M, eased early in straight.

Taken back from gate 9, raced at tail, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to score.
Jumped with them, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with no cover slightly behind midfield, moved closer after passing 1000M, raced better than midfield on turn, kept on well in straight to take 2nd.
Moderately away, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, took the lead 750M, led by 1/2L turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the first two close home.
Began well, sent forward to take the lead, headed near 750M, 2nd on turn, kept on well in straight to make frame.
Moderately away, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, kept on same pace in straight.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide in midfield, a bit closer on turn, kept on evenly in straight.

Crowded shortly after start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, made contact near 500M, made minor progress early in straight, no extra final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.) (Lame left hind leg next day morning.)
Away with them, raced towards rear on the outside, moved a bit closer after entering the back straight, made contact near 500M, 4 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, eased final 100M.
Began awkwardly, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, hampered 500M, failed to make any progress in straight.
Away fast then restrained to sit ahead of midfield, well placed to strike turning for home, quickened to led nearing 100M, kept on well to the line.
Reserved near last, very wide into straight, finished off nicely down outside getting up for 2nd near line.
Jumped well, restrained to race behind midfield, closed off well over final 300M for 3rd.
Sent forward to lead, soon pressed by rival from 1000M, drifted out to center of track on straightening, couldn't hold off first few over final 150M.
Settled down 3-wide behind midfield, lay in under pressure and difficult to obtain clear running early straight, ran home steadily but was awkwardly placed late and couldn't be fully ridden out.
Soon taken across from wide draw, raced near last, kept on moderately along the fence over final 300M, not able to challenge leaders.
Settled behind midfield, raced keenly in early stages, failed to close off the race passing 300M, Never dangerous.
Blundered after the start, settled at the back, ran into interference 200M, not going the pace to challenge after. (Blood in trachea.)
Caught racing wide no cover in midfield on jumping from draw 12, wide into straight, checked near 200M and lost all chance.
From draw 1 raced close to the leaders along the inside, shifted out to center of track for his challenge, checked 200M losing momentum, not recovered from the interference.
Jumped on terms, moved up to track leaders in 3rd, taken wide into straight, badly checked near 150M and lost all chance.
Ridden forward to race outside leader, under heavy pressure 500M, soon gave ground rapidly to finish last.
Jumped okay, ridden along to lead on the rail, commenced to improve inside 900M, responded well when asked near 150M, kept on well to win.
Sat handy on the rail, traveled smoothly, made some progress in the Straight, closed off nicely.
Ridden along to chase the lead 2 wide, traveled strongly, slightly hung out in the Straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Settled in front of midfield, traveled okay, made minor progress over the concluding stages.
Sat midfield 3 wide, commenced to improve rounding the Turn, closed off fairly.
Sat rear on the rail, switched out rounding the Turn, one pace.
Sat towards rear 2 wide, commenced to improve inside 700M, finished off fairly.
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide, limited response when asked in the Straight, slightly weakened over the final 50M.
Jumped awkwardly, sat worse than midfield, slightly weakened near 800M, no impression in the Straight.
Settled towards rear 2 wide, weakened passing 150M, never a threat.
Jumped awkwardly, sat midfield, limited response when asked, never a danger.
Sat in front of midfield, raced wide, weakened and faded notably inside 150M (Bled, Must trial, See incident Report).

Raced just worse than midfield away from the rail. Moved wider near the 600m to improve, made continual ground in the straight, lay inwards near 150m but charged to lead 75m & went on to win strongly (trainer questioned).

Began improving position after first 100m, raced outside the leader momentarily then getting leaders back near 1200m. Came over leaders heals near 450m, moved up to share lead fleetingly near 125m, couldn't hold out winner.
Pushed forward to lead. Was a length clear on straightening, Shifted outwards under pressure near the 150m mark when still leading, joined by the winner at the 100m, held third on line.
Raced in midfield away from the rail. Shifted outwards near the 500m to avoid stopping rival, finished steadily all the way to the line to be beaten just over 2L.
Jumped only fairly & raced at the tail. Stayed close the rail around the home bend, was over 5L from the lead at the 400m before making up a few lengths in straight to be beaten 3L into midfield.

Raced in midfield along the rail throughout. Improved to third place at 400m when only 2L from lead, had clear running on straightening, finished off only moderately in last furlong when weakening a length or so to midfield.

Was trapped racing wide in midfield for the first 600m before getting two wide near the 1000m. Was steadied when held up between runners near 475m, shifted wider on straightening before making up a length to midfield late.

Raced worse than midfield after start before drifting further back, relegated to last near 500m. Was 7L behind entering last section, stayed near inside on straightening before halving beaten margin but never threatening.

Raced in midfield along the rail throughout. Fleetingly held up behind a tiring rival near the 400m mark before moving off rail to improve when 4.5L from the lead, finished only one paced to the line & was never a threat.

Began only fairly, had no customary early speed & raced worse than midfield along rail. Came off the rail near 500m, was forced very wide passing 400m when 5.5L from lead, made no headway in the straight & finished 3rd last.

Jumped fairly, was shifted behind runners to race rearward. Commenced to improve position from 700m when coursing wide, forced even wider passing 600m, extremely wide on straightening, made no headway & was beaten over 6L.

Pushed forward from widest gate, worked hard around first bend before getting to second place near the 1200m when racing away from rail. Began losing ground quickly from the 500m & weakened badly to be a distant last.

Began smartly from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out after passing 350M, showed very good response in straight, hit the front 200M, kept on strongly to the line.
Jumped with them, raced better than midfield on the outside, 2 lengths or so back on turn, closed off well to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Taken back from gate 11, raced towards rear on the inside, 5 lengths or so back turning in, made good progress in straight to take a place without threatening.
Jumped well, took the early lead, headed 950M, retook the lead 750M, led by 1/4L turning in, peaked and headed 200M, weakened gradually final 100M.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at rear, 6 lengths or so back on turn, made good progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, angled out 350M, finished off evenly.
Away with them, raced in 3rd, a length or so back, same position on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Crowded shortly after start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, commenced move 400M, very wide turning in, one-paced in the run home.
Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead 950M, headed 750M, 2nd on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.

Began awkwardly and made contact, raced slightly behind midfield on the outside, no cover for the majority of the race, carried wider 400M, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Moderately away, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened and eased thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well and assumed the lead comfortably, kicked clear in the Straight, always doing enough.
Sat 3 wide outside the leaders, kept on nicely for 2nd.
Settled behind the leaders, made good progress on the inside, closest at finish.
Jumped with the field, settled midfield on the rail, closed off nicely along the rail.
Settled worse than midfield 3 wide, swung wide entering the Straight, stayed on well.
Broke alertly and ridden along early, sat in a prominent position 2 wide, made some ground.
Sat towards the rear on the rail, only able to pass weakened rivals.
Settled midfield 2 wide, only one pace when asked.
Travelled keenly in the early and middle stages, raced 3 wide in front of midfield, weakened inside 200M.
Settled last 2 wide, made no impression.
Showed good early speed to sit outside the leader, weakened in the Straight.
Jumped awkwardly, caught 4 wide no cover throughout, weakened and faded in the Straight. (See Incident Report)
Prominent early stages before gradually drifted backward to just worse than midfield, commenced move entering straight responding well inside final 200 metres to assert authority close to home.
Settled well back from a poor draw, checked and lost ground 1000 metres out trailing the field to the 150 metres, finished off the race strongly to snatch 2nd final strides.
Broke well from the one draw before settling in midfield in 5th some 3L off the pace, saved ground turning in, fought on to hold every chance in straight only to be pipped for 2nd late.
Travelled wide without cover in midfield, one of the widest turning into straight, ran on under pressure to narrowly miss a placing.
Travelled in last few 3-wide with cover, commenced move approaching home turn and widest into straight, ran on well under pressure down the centre of track to be nearest at finish.
Ridden forward at start before settling some 2L back in 3rd on rail, gained slightly closer to 2nd rounding home bend and switched out for a run into straight but unable to quicken to threaten.
Soon dropped backward travelling well back to straight, ran on well between runners down the inside until finding no extra inside final 100 metres.

Well there early stages, settling just over 2L back in 4th, slightly further off the pace passing the 800 metres, held good chance from wide into straight but unable to sustain effort inside final 100 metres.
Settled towards rear on the rail, saved ground turning for home, making ground when tightened over 150 metres out, made no further impression.

Pressed forward from a poor draw to reach 2nd 3-wide into back straight, gained closer to rail passing the 800 metres remaining one-out-one-back to home turn, kept on in straight before jostled and faded inside final 200 metres.
Driven forward from the widest draw to take up running 3-wide into back straight, obtained rails run 800 metres out and led the field until finding no extra inside final 200 metres.
Chased leader, gave good response passing 400M, led 250M out, continued on well and was in total command final stages.
Sped to early lead, steadied the pace from 1100M but still enjoyed uncontested lead, caught by winner 250M, kept on well enough to hold 2nd.
Up with early pace before settling down in 4th, battled on steadily over final 300M, always held by leaders.
Restrained to a position behind midfield, gave a mild response final 300M, just missed 3rd.
Given a waiting ride towards the rear, raced a shade keenly middle stages with the sectional time being outside of standard, kept on moderately without threat in the straight.
Switched off to race at the rear 8Ls off the pace, made limited progress final 300M, not reach leaders.
Caught wide in midfield early stages, moved up to 3rd 1100M, not going the pace to challenge turning for home, never a serious threat to leaders.
Settled behind mid-division, raced wide without cover from 1300M, swung wide for home but found disappointing little in the finish. (No vet findings.)

Held up in midfield, failed to finish off final 400M, ran home same pace. Performance considered to be disappointing. (Jockey : not suited by the race being run at a more genuine pace compared to last start.)
Jumped on terms, restrained to race towards the rear, pushed along 500M but not quickened. Never a threat.
Settled down behind midfield, struggled to keep up 500M, soon left behind by rivals top of straight.
Dropped back to race at the rear 8Ls off the pace, failed to respond when urged along 400M, never in the picture.
